NK033(gi)001:1: // gnyis pa byin rlabs dbang gi skor la /
NK033(gi)001:3: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:4: bdud rtsi 'khyil bar brten pa'i rgya mtsho khrus kyii lung la /
NK033(gi)001:8: de la dang po sbyor ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:9: rin po che la sogs pa ji snyed pa'i bum
NK033(gi)001:10: pa bre gang nas phul gang shong ba yan chad
NK033(gi)001:12: de'i nang du spos ltom pa la /
NK033(gi)001:13: mi ltom pa gla rtsi mi btang /
NK033(gi)001:16: mi ltom pa a mri ta mi btang /
NK033(gi)001:17: gzhan bzang drug la sogs pa grub tshad btang /
NK033(gi)001:19: mi ltom pa thod pa la mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:22: shing 'bras bu can gyis kha brgyan /
NK033(gi)001:23: mgul chings dang gzungs thag btags la /
NK033(gi)001:24: me tog tshom bu lnga'i steng du bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:25: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags brjod pas bum chu mi dmigs par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:27: bdag gi thugs ka nas +aahgaciga dkar rgyangs kyis byung bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:28: +aahde las 'od 'phros pas bum pa'i nang du lam ser po /
NK033(gi)001:31: de las bum pa gad na rim pa gsum dang
NK033(gi)001:32: ldan pa sked pa nor bu gsum dang ldan pa
NK033(gi)001:33: / mu tig gi nor bu yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:35: mchu 'phyangs pa gcig tu lam gyis bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:36: de nas yang +aahde las 'od zer gcig 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)001:37: pad+ma'i ze'u la h'u t+r+aam ljang khu bsgril ba gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:38: h'u t+r+aam de las bcom ldan 'das bdud rtsi 'khyil
NK033(gi)001:39: ba sku mdog ljang gu phyag gnyis pa g.yas gser
NK033(gi)001:40: gyi rdo rje g.yon pa shel gyi gri gug /
NK033(gi)001:42: mdun gyi nam mkha' la h'u bsgril ma gcig tu gyur /
NK033(gi)001:44: ba ti smug po sku la gsol ba gcig krong gis bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:45: de gnas 'gyur ba las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba snga ma lta bu gcig tu gyur /
NK033(gi)001:46: yang rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas
NK033(gi)001:47: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phog
NK033(gi)001:48: / phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i 'od zer dbu'i gtsug tor nas byung /
NK033(gi)001:49: gsung gi 'od zer ljags kyi dbang po las byung /
NK033(gi)001:50: thugs kyi 'od zer shangs bug g.yon nas byung bas /
NK033(gi)001:51: mdun gyi bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la phog ste 'od du zhu /
NK033(gi)001:52: bum pa'i bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la phog pas /
NK033(gi)001:53: lha yang dam tshig gi bdud rtsir zhu bas /
NK033(gi)001:54: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi dam tshig gi bdud rtsi la phog pas /
NK033(gi)001:55: 'o ma dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin du gnyis
NK033(gi)001:56: su med par dkrug gis 'dres nas dkar mer gyis
NK033(gi)001:58: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rgyun par breng nge
NK033(gi)001:59: 'ong bar bsam zhing lag pas blangs la gzungs 'di
NK033(gi)001:61: e ho shud+d+he shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:62: bam ho shud+d+he shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:63: ram ho shud+d+he shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:64: e bam ram bi ho shud+d+he shud+d+he a a s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:66: de nas lag pa g.yon pa'i mthe bos mathe'u mnan
NK033(gi)001:67: la bum pa la sor mo gsum reg la gung
NK033(gi)001:68: mo la / srin lag la +aah mdzub mo la h+aum bsam /
NK033(gi)001:69: des bum pa rgyas gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:70: +aahh+aum a +aah zhes pas rgyas gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:71: de nas gzungs thog gzed kha yang bcad /
NK033(gi)001:73: de nas nangs par gong lang la sems bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:74: mo dang srin lag gnyis kyi bar du /
NK033(gi)001:75: bum pa'i mgrin par bzung la /
NK033(gi)001:77: chu phud nam mkha' la gtor /
NK033(gi)001:80: bde gshegs la bdud rtsi'i phud 'bul /
NK033(gi)001:81: dgyes nas thugs dag nyams chag skong bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:82: brjod cing chu blugs rang ngam gzhan /
NK033(gi)001:83: pas phyogs bzhi nas lha mo bzhis bum pa thogs nas bkrus par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:84: de yang lha mo bzhi ni shar phyogs nas na
NK033(gi)001:85: bza' dkar mo ke ke ru dkar po'i bum pa
NK033(gi)001:86: thogs pa / lho nas sangs rgyas spyan ma sngon mo bee d+aur+ya sngon po'i bum pa thogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:87: nub nas m+aa ma k+ai dmar mo pad+ma r+aa ga'i bum pa thogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:88: byang nas sgrol ma ljang khu in+d+ra n+ai la'i bum pa thogs pa byon nas /
NK033(gi)001:89: bdag gi spyi bo nas mar la bdud rtsi'i chu blugs nas 'khru bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:90: de nas gdong pa bkrus pas dbang po lnga'i dri ma dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:93: 'thung bas yid kyi dri ma dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:94: de nas kha bshal lhag mas bakru'o //
NK033(gi)001:95: de nas de'i rjes la chu gcig khyor khyor ba gsum tsam /
NK033(gi)001:98: 'dod khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig byas la gtor /
NK033(gi)001:100: gzugs khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig byas la gtor ro //
NK033(gi)001:102: gzugs med khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig byas la gtor ro //
NK033(gi)001:103: de ni rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:104: de'i rjes la sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:105: khrus chog la bum pa gsum bca' /
NK033(gi)001:106: bum pa gcig tu rnam 'joms sgrub /
NK033(gi)001:107: bum pa gcig tu e ho sgrub /
NK033(gi)001:108: bum pa gcig tu dug byab /
NK033(gi)001:109: e ho sgrub pa des dang po shug pa sreg /
NK033(gi)001:114: de nas dug gi bum par dug byab bo //
NK033(gi)001:115: de nas me mdag gi gseb tu sgron ma bcug la e ho'i khrus bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:116: de nas rnam 'joms kyi bum pas dbang bskur la bakru'o //
NK033(gi)001:118: sngon 'gro las ma dag pa dag par byed pa sngon 'gro rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:119: nang dag pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung la /
NK033(gi)001:120: nangs par tho rangs khar lang la dang po stong par bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:121: de nas rang gi lus 'di kham ser po gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:123: rang lus gser gyi bum par gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:124: de nas bum pa'i nang du pam dmar po las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa bsam /
NK033(gi)001:125: de'i lte ba la h'u ljang khu gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:126: de 'od du zhu ba las khro bo bdud rtsi
NK033(gi)001:127: 'khyil ba zhal gcig phyag gnyis dku la brten pa
NK033(gi)001:128: / ba ti sngon po sku la gsol ba zhig bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:129: rang lus bum par yod pa'i spyi bor yang h+aum ljang gu gcig la bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:130: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba de'i thugs ka nas 'od zer
NK033(gi)001:131: 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK033(gi)001:132: la phog pas mnyes nas phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs
NK033(gi)001:133: pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer
NK033(gi)001:134: tshur 'dus pas bum pa'i steng gi bdud rtsi 'khyil
NK033(gi)001:136: de yang 'od du zhu nas bdud rtsi dkar po
NK033(gi)001:137: mer la gyur par bsam zhing e ho'i sngags bzlas
NK033(gi)001:138: shing / de'i rjes la a yang mang du brjod /
NK033(gi)001:139: de nas bum pa'i nang du +aahmh'u gsum bsam la bum pa la rgyas gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:140: de nas rang gi chu de snod gtsang mar blugs la mdog brtag /
NK033(gi)001:144: ser sangs la chos bskor du 'khor na bzang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:145: kha dog ngan na chu de sa gtsang mar bo la /
NK033(gi)001:146: chu gtsang ma byas la khrus bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:147: 'pho mi dgos na chu de la srin lag btsugs la /
NK033(gi)001:148: bla ma yi dam d+aa ki mchod /
NK033(gi)001:149: de nas rang gi kha gdong la sogs bakru'o //
NK033(gi)001:150: de nas lhag ma de khyor bar blugs la /
NK033(gi)001:151: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams kyi sgrib pa dag par gyur cig byas la gtor ro //
NK033(gi)001:153: de nas sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa byas la brda' bzhi la sbyar ro //
NK033(gi)001:155: nyin mo snang ba sna tshogs lam du khyer /
NK033(gi)001:156: mtshan mo shes bya bum par gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:157: dri chu dron mo la skyon bdun /
NK033(gi)001:165: grang mo la yon tan bdun no //
NK033(gi)001:173: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:174: ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung la /
NK033(gi)001:176: dag pa rgya mtsho'i lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:178: ma dag pa ni kun tu bzang po 'khor ba'i sems can no //
NK033(gi)001:179: gnas pa rgya mtsho'i lung dang //
NK033(gi)001:180: brten pa rgya mtsho'i lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:181: gnas pa rgya mtsho'i lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:182: lus gang na gnas pa na rtsa gnas /
NK033(gi)001:183: rtsa gang na gnas pa na rlung gnas /
NK033(gi)001:184: rlung gang na gnas pa na khrag gnas so //
NK033(gi)001:185: de ni gnas pa rgya mtsho'i lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:186: brten pa rgya mtsho'i lung ni rang gi dri chu'o //
NK033(gi)001:187: de la sbyor ba dngos gzhi gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:191: kham phor du blugs pas chu g.yon nas g.yas su 'khor ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:192: rlung g.yon nas rgyu ba 'dzom na bzang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:194: de nas chu kha gting 'khrugs na ngan /
NK033(gi)001:201: dwangs sang nge ba gcig byung na lbu ba chag la brten no //
NK033(gi)001:202: dngos gzhi snod kyi nang du yi ge mam lam ser po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:204: gser gyi snod ser ba che ba zhig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:205: de'i nang du yi ge pam dmar po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:206: de 'od du zhu ba las sna tshogs pad+ma'i sdong po gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:207: de'i ge sar la h'u ljang khu gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:208: de la h'u zhes lce rtsa 'gul tsam gcig bzlas
NK033(gi)001:209: pas h'u de las bcom ldan 'das bdud rtsi 'khyil
NK033(gi)001:210: ba sku mdog ljang khu phyag gnyis dku la brten
NK033(gi)001:212: de nas de las 'od zer 'phros pas sems can gyi don byas tshur 'dus pa las /
NK033(gi)001:213: ye shes kyi 'od de dam tshig gi bdud rtsi
NK033(gi)001:214: 'khyil ba la phog pas 'od du dkar mer gyis
NK033(gi)001:215: byung bar bsam / de nas sngags 'di bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:220: bi ram shud+d+he shud+d+he a +aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:221: zhes lan bdun bdun srin lag gi rtse mos gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:222: de nas a a a a zhes brjod pas lha
NK033(gi)001:223: mo bzhis bdud rtsi'i bum pa sku mdog dang mthun
NK033(gi)001:224: pa bsnams nas bdag gi spyi bo nas mar la
NK033(gi)001:226: lus shel gong phyis pa ltar dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:227: de nas hub gcig btung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:229: de nas chu'i lhag ma gtor la khams gsum gyi sems can lus ngag yid gsum gyi /
NK033(gi)001:230: gyi sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:231: de yang rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung las /
NK033(gi)001:232: phung po lnga nyon mongs pa'i phung po /
NK033(gi)001:236: de dang de las byung ba'i phung po'o //
NK033(gi)001:238: nyon mongs lnga ni sbyong byed pa //
NK033(gi)001:239: ye shees lnga chu so sor rtog pa /
NK033(gi)001:243: nam mkha' bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK033(gi)001:245: rang bzhin gyi ni 'od gsal lo //
NK033(gi)001:246: de ni lus 'od gsal la thim pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:248: ma smin smin par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:250: da ni sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa la /
NK033(gi)001:251: lus dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal /
NK033(gi)001:252: ngag dang ba'i sgo nas snying po bzla /
NK033(gi)001:253: sems dang ba'i sgo nas bsam gtan bsgom pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:254: de la dang po rang gi snying nang na +amo
NK033(gi)001:255: kha dog lnga dang ldan pa de las 'od zer
NK033(gi)001:256: 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK033(gi)001:257: dpa' thams cad mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon par
NK033(gi)001:258: bsam la / lag pa thal mo'i phyag rgya bya zhing /
NK033(gi)001:260: zhes brjod pa se gol bsnol mar lan gsum gtogs
NK033(gi)001:261: pas mdun gyi nam mkha' la bla ma yi dam
NK033(gi)001:262: mkha' 'gro sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK033(gi)001:264: de nas yang +amo las 'od zer byung nas thal
NK033(gi)001:265: mo'i nang du rin po che la sogs pa mchod
NK033(gi)001:266: pa'i rdzas bsam la phyag lan re la rdzas lan
NK033(gi)001:268: mgo bos bla ma la sogs pa'i zhabs la thug
NK033(gi)001:269: pas lus ngag yid gsum gyi dri ma sangs kyis
NK033(gi)001:270: dag par bsam zhing phyag bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:271: de la dang po dkon mchog gsum la btsal ba /
NK033(gi)001:272: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:273: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid dbyings dang
NK033(gi)001:274: ye shes gnyis su med pa la phyag 'tshal zhing
NK033(gi)001:275: skyabs su mchi'o // zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:277: yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:278: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun sa chen po la rab tu
NK033(gi)001:279: bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po phyir mi
NK033(gi)001:280: ldog pa chen po la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su
NK033(gi)001:281: mchi'o // de nas bla ma la /
NK033(gi)001:282: ma rig las kyi 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK033(gi)001:283: nyon mongs nad kyis gdung ba la //
NK033(gi)001:284: chos kyi bdud rtsis gso mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:285: dus gsum bla ma rnams la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:287: rgyal ba thams cad dbyer med dbyings mnyam yang //
NK033(gi)001:288: bsnyen bkur dag gis mchod cing dbu la bkod //
NK033(gi)001:289: dngos grub rnam gnyis myur du ster mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:290: rigs lnga he ru ka la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:292: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK033(gi)001:293: 'dod par rgyug pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK033(gi)001:294: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:295: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:297: dug gsum las kyi klong nas 'khor ba'i ru bzlog pa //
NK033(gi)001:298: nyon mongs tha ba'i gnas nas byang chub myu gu bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:299: srid dang 'das phyir 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:300: bcom ldan lha yi lha la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:302: de nas ngag dang ba'i sgo nas snying po bzla ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:303: thugs rje'i bdag po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs nor
NK033(gi)001:304: bu mchog ldan gyi phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK033(gi)001:305: thams cad kyi snying po ni /
NK033(gi)001:308: yid dang ba'i sgo nas bsam gtan bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:309: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bsdu /
NK033(gi)001:310: mkha' 'gro thams cad bla ma la bsdu /
NK033(gi)001:311: bla ma yi dam gyi lha la bsdu /
NK033(gi)001:317: zla tshes thig le la bsdu /
NK033(gi)001:318: thig le de smin mtshams kyi thad ka'i nam mkha' la bsam /
NK033(gi)001:319: de nas +aahh+aum byas pas rang gi spyi bo'i gtsug
NK033(gi)001:320: tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar la thim par bsam
NK033(gi)001:321: / de nas brda'i gnad byas la bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:322: de ni sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:323: da ni smin pa grol bar byed pa'i sgom tshul bla ma'i lung yin te /
NK033(gi)001:324: byin rlabs kyi dus tshul shing gtod tsa na bla
NK033(gi)001:325: ma la dmigs pa gtad nas sgom du 'jug pa
NK033(gi)001:326: de yin no // rdo rje'i tshig ni /
NK033(gi)001:327: dus kyi brda' la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:328: gnad kyi brda yis gnas 'gyur ba //
NK033(gi)001:333: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang rnam par byang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:334: kun nas nyon mongs pa'ang bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:335: nyon mongs pa can gyi gzhi dang /
NK033(gi)001:336: bag chags sog byed kyi snod dang /
NK033(gi)001:337: sa bon cha'i kun gzhi dang /
NK033(gi)001:338: rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma rig pa 'khrul pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:339: rnam par byang ba la'ang bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:340: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:341: mi rtog pa chos nyid dang /
NK033(gi)001:342: zag pa med pa'i bde ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:344: de nas 'gyur ba ni gang nas 'gyur na nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi gzhi 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:345: gang gis 'gyur na dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pas 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:346: gang du 'gyur na rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal du 'gyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:347: gang nas 'gyur ba bag chags sog byed kyi snod du 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:348: gang gis 'gyur na dbang po sgo ma g.yos pas 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:349: gang du 'gyur na mi rtog pa chos nyid du 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:350: gang nas gnas 'gyur na sa bon cha'i kun gzhi gnas 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:351: gang gis 'gyur na 'og rlung yid tsam cung zhig 'then pas 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:352: gang du 'gyur na zag pa med pa'i bde bar 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:353: gang nas gnas 'gyur na rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma rig pa 'khrul par 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:354: gang gis 'gyur na lce'i rtse mo gang la'ang ma reg pas 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:355: gang du 'gyur na chos nyid dbyer med par 'gyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:356: de ni smin pa grol bar byed pa rdo rje'i tshig go //
NK033(gi)001:357: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi lag len no //
NK033(gi)001:359: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi lung bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:361: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi lung phog pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:362: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:363: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK033(gi)001:364: sems dpa' rnams dang 'phags pa thams cad kyis bdag
NK033(gi)001:365: la byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)001:366: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung
NK033(gi)001:367: ste snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du
NK033(gi)001:368: lo byung ngo cog gi zla ba ra ba bzhi'i
NK033(gi)001:369: nya gsum la / ma dag pa dag par byed
NK033(gi)001:370: pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung la mngon par phyogs
NK033(gi)001:372: ma smin pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum las
NK033(gi)001:373: kyi spyod pa la mngon par spyod pa bgyid lags
NK033(gi)001:374: so // ma grol ba grol bar byed pa sgom
NK033(gi)001:375: tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la mngon par spyod pa
NK033(gi)001:376: so // bgyid lags so // grol ba mthar phyin
NK033(gi)001:377: par byed pa snying po ye shes kyi rlung rdo
NK033(gi)001:378: rje la dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi rjes su 'jug
NK033(gi)001:379: so // bgyid lags so // / rjes su bgyid /
NK033(gi)001:382: mngon par phyogs par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:384: mchog tu gyur pa legs so //
NK033(gi)001:387: bla ma rje btsun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:388: 'dzeng rdo rje sba bas mdzad pa'i he ru ka
NK033(gi)001:389: mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po gzhal yas khang dang bcas
NK033(gi)001:390: pa bsgom pa man+dala byin rlabs ni /
NK033(gi)001:391: dbus phyogs mngon par dga' ba gu lang gser gyi gzhal yas khang na /
NK033(gi)001:393: de nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste /
NK033(gi)001:394: e bsnol ze'u 'bru brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:395: bud+d+he he ru ka ni mngon rdzogs te //
NK033(gi)001:396: mngon rdzogs he ru ka yis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:397: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:398: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:399: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:400: shar phyogs ke ke ru yi zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:401: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:402: de nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:403: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:404: badz+ra mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:405: he ru ka yis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:406: rdo rje mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:407: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:408: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:409: lho phyogs bee d+aur+ya yi zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:410: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:411: de nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:412: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:413: rat+na mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:414: he ru ka yis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:415: rin chen mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:416: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:417: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:418: nub phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:419: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:420: de nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:421: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:422: pad+ma mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:423: he ru ka yis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:425: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:426: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:427: byang phyogs in+d+ra n+ai la'i mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:428: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:429: de nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:430: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:431: karma mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:432: he ru ka yis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:433: las kyi mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:434: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:435: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:436: k+shi sh+r+ai badz+ra thugs kyi snying po /
NK033(gi)001:437: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:440: ru lu bsnyen pa la gdags /
NK033(gi)001:441: ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:443: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:446: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:448: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:451: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:453: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:456: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:458: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:461: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:463: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:466: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:467: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru gsung gi snying po /
NK033(gi)001:471: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:473: badz+ra bee ro tsa na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:476: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:479: ma h+aa pany+tsa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:481: man+da la k+aa ya byin rlabs kyi dus su gdags /
NK033(gi)001:488: ma h+aa sa ma ya phata /
NK033(gi)001:489: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:504: ma h+aa sa d+ha la h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:505: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:506: +aahh+aumh ma h+aa yo ga ad d+ha ma h+aa sa ma ya /
NK033(gi)001:507: a su ra hoh ka ma la sh+r+ai he ru /
NK033(gi)001:512: ma h+aa sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:513: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:514: ga na 'di btags pas mchod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:517: a smin pa la ya ba do to /
NK033(gi)001:518: a pa la hoh tshogs byin gyis brlab pa dang mchod pa 'bul ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:519: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs pa'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:520: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:522: h+aum h+r+aih thig le byin gyis brlab pa'o ////
NK033(gi)001:523: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs rgyas pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:524: na mo gu ru bud+d+ha bo d+hi sat+wa /
NK033(gi)001:525: sgom tshul ma smin pa smin par byed pa'i /
NK033(gi)001:526: bla ma'i byin rlabs 'di la don gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:528: sbyor ba dang dngos gzhi rnam gnyis rjes kyi cho ga dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:529: de la dang po sbyor ba bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:530: sngon du sgrib pa sbyang ba'i zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:531: man+dala shin de nas gnas khang legs par /
NK033(gi)001:534: de la bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pas chag chag btab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:535: de nas man+dala sa tshon sna lngas /
NK033(gi)001:542: pad+ma kha dog sna tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:545: de yi nang du rdo rje'i gdan zur drug pa /
NK033(gi)001:547: bud+d+ha he ru ka mngon rdzogs yab yum bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:548: man+dala de'i shar phyogs kyi zhing khams dkar po ke ke ru //
NK033(gi)001:549: lho phyogs kyi zhing khams bee d+aur+ya mthing kha'o //
NK033(gi)001:550: nub tu phyogs kyi zhing khams pad+ma r+aa ga dmar po la //
NK033(gi)001:551: byang du phyogs kyi zhing khams /
NK033(gi)001:556: phyogs las shar dmar lho ljang nub dkar byang mthing kha'o //
NK033(gi)001:558: de nas bum pa man+dala gyi dbus su /
NK033(gi)001:560: rin po che zangs gser med na rdza la bya /
NK033(gi)001:562: nag po ra ri med par bya /
NK033(gi)001:563: gu gul shin tu dag par bkrus la /
NK033(gi)001:566: sum b+ha ni sogs bgegs kyang bskrad //
NK033(gi)001:567: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags ring gis /
NK033(gi)001:568: srog chags med pa'i chu yis gtsang ma /
NK033(gi)001:570: rin chen lnga dang 'bru 'bras so ba sran ma nas gro sna lnga //
NK033(gi)001:571: bzang mar bu dam sbrang rtsi po drug dang snying po lnga //
NK033(gi)001:572: tsan+dana la sogs pa'i yang dri bzang bstsal //
NK033(gi)001:573: kha tshar ma nyams pa'i ras kyis mgul ba /
NK033(gi)001:575: gdan nas kyi bcas pho brang gi steng lte ba du gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:577: de nas bum pa'i steng du ka p+aa dum bu gcig pa /
NK033(gi)001:579: sin chos 'byung bsnol ma'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)001:580: rtsibs drug la a am h+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum ham zhes bri /
NK033(gi)001:581: d+hu ra sogs man+da la bzhengs //
NK033(gi)001:582: chang blug ka p+aa la'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:584: shar ka p+aa la'i mdun phyogs ngos su bstan la bum steng gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:586: de nas k+aa p+aa la'i steng du me long man+dala la bzhengs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:587: sin d+hu ra yi man+dala chos 'byung bsnol mar bri /
NK033(gi)001:589: yi ge dbus su a am ham h+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum bris /
NK033(gi)001:593: da byid dkar po gcig thub /
NK033(gi)001:597: mar la rta byas la sbyar /
NK033(gi)001:605: thig le dkar dmar gyi skyobs dang bcas //
NK033(gi)001:606: bdud rtsi ril bu zung du byas la me long gi steng du bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:607: dkar bdud rtsi ril bu de dmar dar gyis kha bcad de //
NK033(gi)001:608: ka p+aa la yi steng du gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:610: gzhan yang mkho dang por ba'i yo byad bsags pa /
NK033(gi)001:612: tshogs sha la sogs pa'i dang khyad par gtor mkha' 'gro ma gsum la ma gsum //
NK033(gi)001:614: sha chen gtor ma khrag dang zhag chen gyi gtor ma /
NK033(gi)001:616: dkar gsum gyi mngar gsum gyi gtor ma'o //
NK033(gi)001:617: khyad par mkha' 'gro gsum la me mar mtshan thub gsum //
NK033(gi)001:619: 'bru dang mar nag gi zhun chen gyi rtsi mar mar dkar gyi ro //
NK033(gi)001:620: mchod me tog spos mar me dri chab zhal zas /
NK033(gi)001:621: pa lnga dang ldan pa ste //
NK033(gi)001:622: dar gyi cod phan dang bsrung skud dang mda' chung gzhu rnams sogs //
NK033(gi)001:623: so tshul shing dang sgom thag dang sgom rten dang kun //
NK033(gi)001:624: mkho ba'i yo byad tshang bar bshams //
NK033(gi)001:625: skabs 'dir rang gzhan gyi don du phyi nang gi
NK033(gi)001:626: rgya mtsho khrus lung sngon du 'gro ba 'thad par
NK033(gi)001:627: sems pas zur du bkol ba ltar ro //
NK033(gi)001:629: de nas cho ga'i dngos gzhi la don gnyis te //
NK033(gi)001:630: byin gyis brlab dang gcig cho ga'o //
NK033(gi)001:632: dang po byin rlabs la rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK033(gi)001:633: man+dala byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:636: de la dang po man+dala byin gyis rlabs par bya ba /
NK033(gi)001:638: dbus man+dala kyi gu lang ser po'i steng du //
NK033(gi)001:639: gu ni ser po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:640: gu lang man+dala h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:641: gser gyi sa gzhir gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:642: phyi man+dala de yi yi sna tshogs pad ge sar dmar ljang la /
NK033(gi)001:644: pam dkar ser dmar la sogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:645: ni dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:646: pam pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:647: sna kha dog tshogs pa'i pad+mara gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:648: de 'i nang du mu khyud dkar po la //
NK033(gi)001:649: a ni dkar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:650: a tsan+d+ra man+dala la zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:651: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dkar po gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:652: de 'i nang du mu khyud dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:653: du ma ni dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:654: ma s+aur+ya man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:655: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dmar po gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:656: de dbus chos 'byung nag po'i gru gsum pa steng //
NK033(gi)001:657: du ba ni mthing kha gcig tu gyur bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:658: ba ti tish+tha zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:659: ba ti sngon po'i gdan gcig tu gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:660: de 'i steng du ba ti dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:661: du ba ni dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:662: ba ti tish+tha zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:663: ba ti dmar po'i gdan gcig gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:664: de'i dbus kyi pad+ma ge sar gyi steng //
NK033(gi)001:665: du yi ge b+h+r+aum gcig bsam par bya //
NK033(gi)001:667: sna tshogs pad+ma'i ge sar du bsam //
NK033(gi)001:669: shar phyogs gyi man+dala dkar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:670: ke ni dkar po gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)001:671: kee ru man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:672: kee ru dkar po'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)001:673: lho yi zhing khams man+dala sngon po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:674: bee ni mthing ga gcig bsam ste /
NK033(gi)001:675: bee d+aur+ya man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:676: bee d+aur+ya yi zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)001:677: nub phyogs zhing khams man+dala dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:678: pam ni dmar po gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)001:679: pam pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:680: pad+ma r+aa ga'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)001:681: byang phyogs zhing khams man+dala ljang khu'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:682: i ni ljang khu gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)001:683: in+d+ra n+ai la man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:684: in+d+ra n+ai la'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)001:685: de nas rdzas bum pa thod pa me long gsum byin gyis brlab par bya ste //
NK033(gi)001:686: dbus kyi sna tshogs pad+ma'i ge sar gyi steng //
NK033(gi)001:687: du bum pa bzhugs pa'i nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:688: kha dog lnga yi +amo thig le mthing ga /
NK033(gi)001:697: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK033(gi)001:699: thugs dam rgyud ni bskul nas su //
NK033(gi)001:700: sku yi 'od zer rnam pa lnga //
NK033(gi)001:701: dbu yi gtsug tor las thon nas //
NK033(gi)001:702: bum pa'i nang du byon par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:703: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)001:705: snying sku'i po 'di ni brjod par bya //
NK033(gi)001:706: +amo sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra
NK033(gi)001:707: kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK033(gi)001:708: b+h+yo h+aum / de la sngags grangs stong tsam re them pa bzlas par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:710: de steng ka p+aa la yi nang //
NK033(gi)001:711: a ni dmar ser gcig bsgom ste //
NK033(gi)001:712: de las 'od zer lnga kha dog 'phros pas //
NK033(gi)001:713: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:715: thugs dam gyi rgyud ni bskul nas su //
NK033(gi)001:716: ljags kyi dbang po las thon gsung gi 'od zer /
NK033(gi)001:718: ka p+aa thod pa'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:720: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)001:722: gsung gi snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:723: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa gsung gi 'od zer a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK033(gi)001:725: tsam re them pa bzlas par bya /
NK033(gi)001:727: de steng me long nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:728: ham ni dkar po gcig bsgoms 'od zer dkar dmar chil gyi /
NK033(gi)001:730: de las 'od zer lnga kha dog 'phros pas //
NK033(gi)001:731: bde phyogs bcu'i gshegs pa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul nas //
NK033(gi)001:732: 'od thugs kyi zer thugs ka las thon nas //
NK033(gi)001:733: me long thog tu babs par bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:734: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)001:736: thugs kyi snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:738: sku gsung thugs kyi sngags grangs stong tsam bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:740: bar chad med par bzlas pa na //
NK033(gi)001:741: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi spyan drangs dam tshig gi bdud rtsi /
NK033(gi)001:743: gnyis su med par gyur par bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:744: gnyis pa cho ga'i rim pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:745: sbyor ba dngos gzhi rnam gnyis te //
NK033(gi)001:746: dang po sbyor ba bstan pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:747: dang po bgegs la bka' bsgo de nas bden pa brdar bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:748: de nas khro bo bgegs ni mthar byed dang //
NK033(gi)001:749: khro bo las ni thams cad pas //
NK033(gi)001:750: bgegs dang bar chad bsal bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:751: badz+ra yak+sha bgegs mthar byed kyi /
NK033(gi)001:752: kro d+ha ha la ha la h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:753: sum khro bo las thams cad pa'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:754: b+ha ni be ga ba ti rak+sha rak+sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:755: sngags de lan lnga'am bdun gyis bgegs bskrad do //
NK033(gi)001:756: de nas mtshams yang dag gsang ba /
NK033(gi)001:758: yi dam gzhung yang bsrang bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:759: tshogs kyi mchod pa bzang po bya //
NK033(gi)001:760: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed cho ga bar 'dir bya //
NK033(gi)001:761: rjes la 'byung po'i gtor kha 'bar ma /
NK033(gi)001:763: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i cho ga la //
NK033(gi)001:764: spyi yi don ni bco lnga las //
NK033(gi)001:765: dang po skabs 'dir bum pa khrus lung ltar sgrub pas /
NK033(gi)001:768: gnyis pa gdan la bzhugs pa slob ma rnams phyi
NK033(gi)001:769: rol tu khrus byas nas rdo rje la 'jus nas
NK033(gi)001:770: nang du 'dren tsa na bgegs bskrad /
NK033(gi)001:771: rdo rje la 'jus nas gdan la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:773: snam bu dkar po'i steng du ni //
NK033(gi)001:774: tshom bu lnga pa'i me tog bkod //
NK033(gi)001:775: slob mas rdo rje la bzung ste //
NK033(gi)001:776: tshig ni 'di dag brjod la nang du drang /
NK033(gi)001:778: 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste //
NK033(gi)001:779: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol //
NK033(gi)001:780: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:781: chos dang chos nyid bsgom par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:782: zhes pas slob ma de rnams gdan la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:783: gsum pa mna' chu blud pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:785: 'di ni rdo rje dmyal ba'i chu //
NK033(gi)001:786: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK033(gi)001:787: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ster //
NK033(gi)001:789: las byang ltar skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed 'bogs /
NK033(gi)001:791: badz+ra a mri ta ha na ha na h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:792: zhes pas dam tshig gi mna' chu blud do //
NK033(gi)001:793: bzhi pa ye shes bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:794: ye shes 'di ni ye shes che //
NK033(gi)001:795: ye shes dam pa yod med shes //
NK033(gi)001:796: ye shes ye shes khyad par shes //
NK033(gi)001:797: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:799: lnga pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:800: slob dpon dag ni dpa' chen po //
NK033(gi)001:801: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK033(gi)001:802: mgon pos bdag ni 'jug pa ra 'tshal //
NK033(gi)001:803: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:804: bdag ni tshul chen snod yin te //
NK033(gi)001:805: zhes gsol ba lan gsum du gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:806: drug pa gnang ba 'bog pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:807: rigs kyi bu khyod gang la dga' //
NK033(gi)001:809: bdag ni bde ba chen po skal bzang la dga' //
NK033(gi)001:811: bdun pa dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:812: slob mas rdo rje la bzung ste /
NK033(gi)001:813: bu 'dir shog cig theg chen don //
NK033(gi)001:814: khyod la yang dag bstan par bya //
NK033(gi)001:815: dkyil 'khor chen po la gnas pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:816: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK033(gi)001:817: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)001:818: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:820: brgyad pa dam tshig 'bog pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:821: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK033(gi)001:822: bsgom bya lha dang sgom byed mi //
NK033(gi)001:823: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NK033(gi)001:824: dang po rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK033(gi)001:825: lus kyi lha dang ngag gi sngags //
NK033(gi)001:826: yid kyi brda la lta ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:827: gnyis pa la ni rnam pa gsum //
NK033(gi)001:828: seng ge dkar mo'i sha mi za //
NK033(gi)001:829: za ma tog tu dug mi btso //
NK033(gi)001:830: gnam lcags ngur mo'i kha mi brdab //
NK033(gi)001:831: dgu pa sngags kyis byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:832: lus ni bag pheb ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)001:833: spyi bo'i steng du 'khor lo ni //
NK033(gi)001:834: gser las grub pa'i rtsibs brgyad pa //
NK033(gi)001:835: yi ge +amo gyis mtshan par bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:836: lce yi steng du pad+ma ni //
NK033(gi)001:837: pad ma 'dab ma brgyad pa la //
NK033(gi)001:838: ze'u 'bru a yis mtshan pa bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:839: snying khar rdo rje rgya gram la //
NK033(gi)001:840: mthing ga'i lte ba h'u gis brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:841: de la sems ni zin pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:845: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:846: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags bstan pa //
NK033(gi)001:847: spyi gtsug d+hu ti'i nang na mar //
NK033(gi)001:848: yi ge ham ni mgo mthur 'phyang //
NK033(gi)001:849: dkar la 'tsher ba bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)001:851: dus mtha'i me bzhin dmar ba la //
NK033(gi)001:852: me mar bzhin du 'bar ba las //
NK033(gi)001:853: spyi bo'i ham las bdud rtsi bab //
NK033(gi)001:854: rang lus bde bas khengs par bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:855: de la shes pa zin pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:857: brjod cing mang du sgra yang rol mo /
NK033(gi)001:859: bzlas brjod las kyi sngags bstan pa //
NK033(gi)001:862: d+aa ki ma ni gsum du gyur //
NK033(gi)001:863: bud med dmar mo gzhon sha can //
NK033(gi)001:864: gcer bu rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:865: skra grol ba ti'i sham thabs can //
NK033(gi)001:866: da ma ru dang kha t+w+aam ka /
NK033(gi)001:868: lo brgyad pa yi na tshod la //
NK033(gi)001:869: gar ni khyug khyug mdzad par bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:870: de la sems ni zin pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:872: po brjod cing sgra rol mo'i yang bsgrags //
NK033(gi)001:874: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta a bi pra sa la /
NK033(gi)001:876: lus dang ngag dang yid gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:877: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags gsum 'byung //
NK033(gi)001:880: yid bde gsal mi rtog gang rung zhig 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:882: bcu pa byin rlabs rnam gsum ni //
NK033(gi)001:883: dang po bum dbang bskur ba la //
NK033(gi)001:884: slob ma'i spyi bo'i gtsug tu ni //
NK033(gi)001:885: rdo rje rgya gram bzhag byas te //
NK033(gi)001:886: ni btso ma gser lta bu //
NK033(gi)001:888: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa //
NK033(gi)001:889: lte ba gyis de la yi ge badz+ra a ti ba ti s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK033(gi)001:891: lce yi steng du rgya gram bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:892: a ni dus mtha'i me lta bu //
NK033(gi)001:895: lce ni rab badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa mi s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:897: snying khar rdo rje rgya gram bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:898: h'u sngon rgya gram gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)001:900: lcags kyi rdo rje rgya gram la //
NK033(gi)001:901: lte ba h'u gis badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa mi s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:903: de nas me tog dor la pra brtag go //
NK033(gi)001:904: dkyil 'khor shar phyogs su phyag rgya lnga'i man+dala gyi steng du slob ma bzhag la /
NK033(gi)001:905: bum pa spyi bor bzhag byas te //
NK033(gi)001:906: ngag tu tshigs 'di dbyangs su brjod //
NK033(gi)001:908: dbang bskur 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)001:909: sangs rgyas kun gyi bum pa'i dbang //
NK033(gi)001:910: sangs rgyas kun gyi phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK033(gi)001:911: sangs rgyas kun tu dbang bsgrub phyir //
NK033(gi)001:912: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)001:913: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:917: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rigs rnam pa lnga'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:918: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:919: rdo rje'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:920: rin po che'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par pad+ma'i
NK033(gi)001:921: rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par las kyi rigs kyi
NK033(gi)001:922: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:926: pad+ma k+aa la sha h+r+aih karma k+aa la sha +aah
NK033(gi)001:927: sku rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK033(gi)001:928: / sprul pa sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:929: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:930: chos kyi sku'i dbang dang ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i
NK033(gi)001:931: dbang dang gsang ba'i sku'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK033(gi)001:935: pad+ma lo tsa ni h+r+aih karma lo tsa ni +aah
NK033(gi)001:936: ye shes rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK033(gi)001:937: cig / chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:938: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:939: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:940: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:941: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:942: gzung ba rang bzhin med pa sku'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:943: 'dzin pa rang bzhin med pa gsung gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:944: de nyid gang du yang ma grub pa thugs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:945: ces bum dbang bskur la bum pa'i khrus gsol ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:947: sangs rgyas kun gyis khrus gsol ba //
NK033(gi)001:948: ye shes chu bo khrus kyi rdzing //
NK033(gi)001:949: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK033(gi)001:950: bkra shis bum pa spyi blugs bzang //
NK033(gi)001:951: dbang bskur thams cad 'dir gsol cig /
NK033(gi)001:952: dbang bskur 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)001:953: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK033(gi)001:954: gsang ba gsum las byung ba yi //
NK033(gi)001:955: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin par bya //
NK033(gi)001:956: phung po lnga ni rnam dag cing //
NK033(gi)001:957: nyon mongs lnga ni sbyong bar byed //
NK033(gi)001:958: ye shes lnga yi ngo bo nyid //
NK033(gi)001:959: dpal ldan sku yi dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)001:960: badz+ra a d+hi s+t+wam sat+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK033(gi)001:961: badz+ra a d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa mi s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:962: badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa mi s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:964: de nas gsang lho sgor sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i thig le'i man+dala gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)001:966: ka p+aa la spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)001:967: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK033(gi)001:968: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK033(gi)001:969: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:970: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir gsol cig /
NK033(gi)001:972: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:973: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK033(gi)001:974: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK033(gi)001:975: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK033(gi)001:976: rgyu drug sems can kun bsgral phyir //
NK033(gi)001:977: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi ste //
NK033(gi)001:978: bdud rtsi dam pa'i dbang bskur gyis //
NK033(gi)001:979: lce rang gi yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)001:980: rdo rje chang gi can gyi bsgoms te //
NK033(gi)001:981: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)001:982: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)001:983: k+aa ya sid+d+hi +amoh lce yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)001:984: rdo rje can gyi +aah bsgoms te //
NK033(gi)001:985: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)001:986: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)001:987: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah lce yi dam tshig rdo rje las //
NK033(gi)001:988: rdo rje can gyi h+aum bsgoms te //
NK033(gi)001:989: bdud rtsi 'bru lngas byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)001:990: zos pas byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK033(gi)001:992: sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:993: gsung chang gis mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:994: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:995: de nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi blud pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:996: rdo rje ka p+aa la'i khar bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)001:998: rdo rje 'di ni rdo rje che //
NK033(gi)001:999: rdo rje rgyal po rab tu bzang //
NK033(gi)001:1000: rdo rje rab tu 'bar ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1001: dag pa'i bdud rtsir byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)001:1002: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:1004: gzhan la smra bar ma byed cig /
NK033(gi)001:1005: a la la hoh rta ma rta 'jol /
NK033(gi)001:1006: rta ma yang 'jol gsum bstim mo //
NK033(gi)001:1007: nub sgor byang sems dkar dmar gyi thig le'i man+dala
NK033(gi)001:1008: gyi steng du de nas thig le'i dbang bskur te
NK033(gi)001:1010: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK033(gi)001:1011: byang sems thig ler rab sbyar nas //
NK033(gi)001:1012: dag cing gsal la dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:1013: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK033(gi)001:1014: 'di la yang dag ngos bzung med //
NK033(gi)001:1015: bu khyod la ni dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:1016: bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1017: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:1023: bam d+ai pa su khi ni /
NK033(gi)001:1024: hohgan+d+he tsit+ta hoh k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)001:1025: byang sems thig le dkar po rnam par dag pa
NK033(gi)001:1026: ni zla ba shar ba lta bu'i dbang thob par
NK033(gi)001:1027: gyur cig / byang sems thig le dmar po rnam
NK033(gi)001:1028: par dag pa ni nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i
NK033(gi)001:1031: sku bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1032: a la la hoh gsung bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1033: a la la hoh thugs bde ba'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1034: a la la hoh zhes byang sems thig le'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)001:1035: bcu gcig pa tshe dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1036: de nas dang po tshe 'dzab tshe bum dang bcas pa la /
NK033(gi)001:1038: tshe'i bum pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)001:1040: skal ldan dbang mchog lha yi lung //
NK033(gi)001:1041: bdud rtsi gang rgya sman gyi lung //
NK033(gi)001:1042: rin chen zla gam dbang gi lung //
NK033(gi)001:1044: rin chen sna lnga'i bum pa ru //
NK033(gi)001:1045: rdo rje tshe yis bkang nas kyang /
NK033(gi)001:1046: rin sna bdun chen rgyan gyis klubs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)001:1047: bu yi spyi bor dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:1048: bu khyod tshe dbang gnas par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1049: b+h+r+aum h+aum b+h+r+aum t+r+aam b+h+r+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum +aah b+h+r+aum /
NK033(gi)001:1050: de nas bkra shis brjod cing tshe bstim /
NK033(gi)001:1051: bcu gnyis pa zhing khams bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1053: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1054: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:1055: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:1056: badz+ra he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1057: rdo rje mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:1058: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1059: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1060: lho phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1061: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:1062: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:1063: rat+na he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1064: rin chen mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:1065: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1066: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1067: nub phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1068: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:1069: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:1070: pad+ma he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1072: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1073: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1074: byang phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1075: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:1076: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:1077: karma he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1078: las kyi mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:1079: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1080: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1081: dbus phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1082: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:1083: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK033(gi)001:1084: bud+d+ha he ru ka yi dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1085: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro bde ba che //
NK033(gi)001:1086: bde ba chen pos byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1087: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1089: bcu gsum pa tshul shing gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1091: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK033(gi)001:1092: bden pa gnyis la yang dag bsten //
NK033(gi)001:1093: de bzhin kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:1094: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1095: sgra dang tshig ni kun rdzob yin //
NK033(gi)001:1096: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK033(gi)001:1097: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1099: byang sgor gur gum gyi chus rdo rje rgya gram
NK033(gi)001:1100: bris pa'i steng du tshig dbang bskur de nas tshig
NK033(gi)001:1101: dbang rin po che 'di brjod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1103: e ma ngo mtshar rmad skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:1107: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)001:1108: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK033(gi)001:1109: skyes tsam nyid las skye ba med //
NK033(gi)001:1110: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK033(gi)001:1111: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)001:1113: skye 'gag med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK033(gi)001:1114: skye med kyi ngang du spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1115: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1116: a skye med ha 'gag med ho gnas med zhes dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)001:1117: de nas bcu bzhi pa sgom thag gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1119: byams dang snying rje'i thugs mnga' zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1120: sangs rgyas phrin las bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1121: bde ba'i bka' nan 'di bcings nas //
NK033(gi)001:1122: chos dang chos nyid sgoms par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1123: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:1125: bco lnga pa sgom rten gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1127: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin chos sku'i gdung //
NK033(gi)001:1128: chos rje 'od dpag med pa bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1129: bde ba'i lus la rab brten nas //
NK033(gi)001:1130: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1131: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:1133: skabs 'dir byin bla ma'i gyis 'jug zhal las shes /
NK033(gi)001:1135: bcu drug pa mkha' 'gro la gnyer las gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1138: zhing las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1139: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)001:1140: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1141: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:1142: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)001:1143: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:1144: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1145: mkha' 'gro ma yi bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:1146: mkha' la gshegs ma mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1148: las las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1149: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)001:1150: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1151: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:1152: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)001:1153: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:1154: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1155: mkha' 'gro ma yi bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:1159: chang ngam mar nag tu sbyar la /
NK033(gi)001:1160: mo thod mtshan ldan du blugs la sol ba'i me la ye shes pa 'bebs dus su bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:1161: de'i dus su mkha' 'gro ma 'du bar nges so //
NK033(gi)001:1164: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs 'bring po bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:1165: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1166: gdod nas dag pa'i rang bzhin ngo bo nyid //
NK033(gi)001:1167: nyams su blang ba'i lam gyi rim pa bstan pa la /
NK033(gi)001:1168: dang po kho nar ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:1169: dag pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:1170: smin pa grol bar byed pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:1171: grol ba mthar phyin pa rdo rje'i tshig lam dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:1172: de la dang po ma dag pa dag par byed pa la gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:1173: phyi rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung dang /
NK033(gi)001:1174: nang rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:1175: phyi rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:1176: byin rlabs kyi dus kyi bum pa 'cha' ba la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1177: nang rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung la /
NK033(gi)001:1178: rang he ru ka mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po gsal bar bsgom la /
NK033(gi)001:1179: sku mdog smug nag phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:1180: g.yon pa na dngul gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)001:1181: yum swasti badz+ra ma sku mdog smug nag g.yas pas gtso bo la 'khyud pa /
NK033(gi)001:1182: g.yon pa thod khrag zhal du stob pa /
NK033(gi)001:1183: de lta bu gcig bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:1184: de'i ngang las chos nyid stong pa nyid du wal gyis sgom la nyal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1185: nangs par nyi ma ri rtse la shar tsa na langs la khrus bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1190: e bam ram yam d+ha ra shud+d+he /
NK033(gi)001:1192: chu la sngags nyi shu rtsa gcig btab la khrus bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1194: rang gi bdud rtsi dri chu dang po la gtor ro //
NK033(gi)001:1196: lus sems gnyis su med par shel sgong dag pa ltar song bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:1197: lus sems gnyis kyi khrus de dag kyang smin tu mi btub pas /
NK033(gi)001:1198: dag pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa la 'jug ste /
NK033(gi)001:1199: dang po lus dang ba'i sgo nas thal mo sbyar te /
NK033(gi)001:1200: lha phyag dang skor ba dang man+dala dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:1201: ngag dang ba'i sgo nas dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba bya zhing /
NK033(gi)001:1202: rtsa ba'i bla ma la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:1203: yi dam lha yi bzlas pa yang bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1204: sems dang ba'i sgo nas bde gsal mi rtog gnyis
NK033(gi)001:1205: med kyi shes pa la lhan ne lhang nge bzhag
NK033(gi)001:1206: go // ma dag pa'i skyon cis lan na /
NK033(gi)001:1207: rang gi sems nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:1208: sems can ma rig pa la las kyi skyon yod
NK033(gi)001:1209: pas las kyi rnam par smin pa'i sgrib pa dang
NK033(gi)001:1210: gnyis / sems can rnams la shes bya shes byed kyi sgrib pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:1211: sems can rnams bag la chags pas /
NK033(gi)001:1212: la bag chags kyi sgrib pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:1214: da yang smin pa de grol du mi btub pas smin pa grol bar byed pa la /
NK033(gi)001:1215: dang po man+dala dpe chung bzhin bri /
NK033(gi)001:1216: de nas man+dala byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1217: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su yi ge gu ser po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1218: ngag tu gu lam man+dala zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1219: shar du yi ge ke dkar po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1220: ngag tu ke ke ru man+dala zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1221: lho ru bee mthing kha gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1222: ngag tu bee d+aur+ya man+dala zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1223: nub tu pam dmar po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1224: ngag tu pam pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1225: byang du e ljang khu gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1226: ngag tu in+d+ra n+ai la man+dala zhes brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1227: dbus kyi lte ba la ba ti badz+ra zhes pas sngon dmar rdo rje'i gdan bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1230: lho dmar mthing nub ser dmar byang sngo ljang dbus ljang ser /
NK033(gi)001:1231: ma s+aur+ya man+dala b+h+r+aum bi shwa /
NK033(gi)001:1232: a tsan+d+ra man+dala b+h+r+aum bi shwa /
NK033(gi)001:1234: zhes pas nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1236: de'i thog tu thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba a mri tas bran la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:1237: de'i thog tu me long la sin d+hu ras /
NK033(gi)001:1238: lam bi shwa d+ha ni d+h+rika /
NK033(gi)001:1242: me long zur la mngar gsum gyi ril bu spra tshug tsam pa bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:1243: de nas rang he ru ka bsgoms la /
NK033(gi)001:1244: snying kha nas 'od zer 'phros mkha' la spyod ma'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1246: mngal las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1247: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)001:1248: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1249: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)001:1250: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)001:1251: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:1252: gang sgrub pa la mi gnas gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1253: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:1260: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la //
NK033(gi)001:1261: ye shes lha yi dbang babs pas //
NK033(gi)001:1262: bka' brgyud ma chad pa yi babs //
NK033(gi)001:1264: bla ma lha la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1265: byin gyi rlabs kyi chog sgrig 'di //
NK033(gi)001:1266: gang gis bskul nas su yis bkod //
NK033(gi)001:1267: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs /
NK033(gi)001:1268: 'dzeng rdo rje pra b+has tshigs bcad du bsdebs pa rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:1269: byin rlabs kyi dus su byang sems dkar dmar gyi skyobs sbyar ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1270: de la dang po byang sems dkar po'i skyobs ni /
NK033(gi)001:1274: da byid dkar po chig thub dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:1275: ru ma byang sems thig le dkar po dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:1276: ka ra dkar po dang drug po de cha mnyam la mar gyi rta byas la sbyar ro //
NK033(gi)001:1277: de dar dkar po ru dril /
NK033(gi)001:1278: de nas yang dar dmar po ru dril lo //
NK033(gi)001:1279: dmar po sbyor ba'i skyobs la /
NK033(gi)001:1281: me tog r+aa ga dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:1282: pad+ma rin po che r+aa ga dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:1284: ru ma dmar cha r+aa ga dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:1285: bu ram dang drug sbyar ro //
NK033(gi)001:1287: de yang dar dkar pos dril lo //
NK033(gi)001:1288: de ni byang sems dkar dmar gyi skyobs kyi gdams ngag zhal las zhus pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:1289: byin rlabs kyi dus su mkha' 'gro ma'i spos sbyor ni /
NK033(gi)001:1292: bya sha zan gyi klad pa /
NK033(gi)001:1301: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs brgyud bskul te /
NK033(gi)001:1305: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK033(gi)001:1307: 'od zer bum pa'i nang du babs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:1308: las 'od zer 'phros kha dog lnga zhu ba'i 'od zer ljags las thod par babs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:1309: +aahdakara smug zhu ba'i thugs kyi 'od zer me long thog tu babs par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1310: h'u las 'od zer kha dog lnga zhu bas dam
NK033(gi)001:1311: tshig gi bdud rtsi dang ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK033(gi)001:1313: de yan chad kyis dkyil 'khor dang /
NK033(gi)001:1316: me long byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK033(gi)001:1318: de nas slob ma'i bgegs sum b+ha nis bskrad la /
NK033(gi)001:1319: skyabs sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa nas bshad pa bzhin /
NK033(gi)001:1321: de nas slob mas slob dpon dag ni dpa' chen po //
NK033(gi)001:1322: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK033(gi)001:1324: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1326: de nas bla mas ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1331: +aah'i 'od zer la phog pas 'dar zhing 'phro bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1332: ngag tu de nas slob dpon gyis /
NK033(gi)001:1333: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:1335: de nas slob ma'i lte bar a dmar po /
NK033(gi)001:1336: spyi bor ham dkar po mgo mthur du bstan pa
NK033(gi)001:1337: a las me 'bar ba me lces ham zhu bas
NK033(gi)001:1338: khog pa bdud rtsis dkar mer gyis khengs par bsam
NK033(gi)001:1339: / ngag tu yang a ham bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:1341: snying kha'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas mdun gyi
NK033(gi)001:1342: nam mkha' la ye shes kyi d+aa ki ma sku
NK033(gi)001:1343: mdog dmar ba / dur khrod kyi chas brgyad sogs rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:1344: skra grol ba g.yas d+aa ma ru /
NK033(gi)001:1346: ba ti smug po'i sham thabs can /
NK033(gi)001:1347: gar khyug khyug byed par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1348: a ham yang des 'dren par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1349: ngag tu bzlas pa las kyi sngags /
NK033(gi)001:1350: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta a bi pra sa la /
NK033(gi)001:1352: de nas shar phyogs su rnam lnga'i man+dala gyi steng du dbang bskur /
NK033(gi)001:1353: sangs rgyas kun gyi bum pa'i dbang /
NK033(gi)001:1354: sangs rgyas kun gyi byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1355: bu khyod la ni bskur bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:1356: dpag tu med pa'i don dang ldan //
NK033(gi)001:1357: rigs mchog phyag rgya lnga ldan pas //
NK033(gi)001:1358: bdag gis khams gsum dag gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1363: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah bud+d+ha k+aa la sha te /
NK033(gi)001:1364: badz+ra k+aa la sha te h'u /
NK033(gi)001:1365: rat+na k+aa la sha te t+r+aam /
NK033(gi)001:1366: pad+ma ka la sha te h+r+aih karma k+aa la sha te +aah bud+d+ha lo tsa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1369: pad+ma lo tsa ni h+r+aih karma lo tsa ni +aah
NK033(gi)001:1370: gzung ba rang bzhin med pa sku'i dbang thob par
NK033(gi)001:1371: gyur cig / 'dzin pa rang bzhin med pa gsung gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1372: de nyid gang du'ang ma grub pa thugs kyi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1374: dkyil 'khor gyi lho sgor sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i
NK033(gi)001:1375: thig le'i man+dala gyi steng du thod pa spyi bor
NK033(gi)001:1376: bzhag la / rang byung gdod nas dag pa ste //
NK033(gi)001:1377: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK033(gi)001:1378: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dbang //
NK033(gi)001:1379: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK033(gi)001:1380: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi mchog /
NK033(gi)001:1381: sku gsung thugs kyi sman mchog 'di //
NK033(gi)001:1382: dam tshig ma nyams sangs rgyas chu //
NK033(gi)001:1383: dam tshig nyams na dmyal ba'i chu //
NK033(gi)001:1385: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:1388: zhal du gsol du gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:1389: sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1390: gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1391: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:1392: dkyil 'khor gyi nub sgor byang sems thig le'i man+dala gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)001:1393: byang chub sems kyi thig le'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1395: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med las //
NK033(gi)001:1396: byang sems thig le rab sbyar te //
NK033(gi)001:1397: dag cing gsal ba dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:1398: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK033(gi)001:1399: 'di la yang dag ngos bzung med //
NK033(gi)001:1400: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:1403: ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra sat+wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)001:1404: de nas tshul shing gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1405: dkyil 'khor gyi byang sgor gur gum gyi chus rdo rje rgya gram bris te /
NK033(gi)001:1406: de'i thog tu slob ma la tshig dbang rin po che'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1408: khyod la yang dag don gcig ston //
NK033(gi)001:1409: rtsol dang bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK033(gi)001:1410: rgyu 'bras med pa'i mthar phyin yin //
NK033(gi)001:1411: sngags tshig bral ba'i nus pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:1412: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon yin //
NK033(gi)001:1413: 'ching bral rtogs pa'i lta ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:1414: rtog 'dzin spangs pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK033(gi)001:1415: dbyings kyi tshul la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1416: stong nyid bde ba'i man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:1417: dam pa'i bde ba sngon du bstan //
NK033(gi)001:1418: bde ba chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:1419: gcig pur 'dug pa'i bde chen yin //
NK033(gi)001:1420: bde ba chen po mi 'bral bzung //
NK033(gi)001:1421: bde ba rgyas pa'i dbang thob ste //
NK033(gi)001:1422: zhing khams bde la bde longs spyod //
NK033(gi)001:1423: bde ba'i tshul la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1424: ye shes 'khyil ba rdo rje bum //
NK033(gi)001:1425: bde ba chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:1426: ye shes lnga yi bde ba rgyas //
NK033(gi)001:1427: rang byung ye shes rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:1428: rig pa'i ye shes skur gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:1429: gang snang rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK033(gi)001:1430: rang rig ye shes rgyun mi chad //
NK033(gi)001:1431: rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:1432: ye shes nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)001:1433: ye shes tshul la gnas par bya //
NK033(gi)001:1435: 'di la yang dag ngos bzung med //
NK033(gi)001:1437: lus ngag dge ba bya rtsol med //
NK033(gi)001:1439: gnas dang ldan pa bstan pa med //
NK033(gi)001:1440: yul du nam yang 'gag pa med //
NK033(gi)001:1441: longs spyod ldan yang chags pa med //
NK033(gi)001:1442: chos nyid tshul la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:1446: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin chos sku'i gdung //
NK033(gi)001:1447: chos rje 'od dpag med pa bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1448: bde ba'i lung la rab brten nas //
NK033(gi)001:1449: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1450: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:1451: sgom thag gtad la 'di skad do //
NK033(gi)001:1453: byams dang snying rje'i thugs mnga' zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1454: sangs rgyas phrin las bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1455: bde ba'i bka' nan 'di bcings pas //
NK033(gi)001:1456: chos dang chos nyid bsgom bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:1457: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:1458: d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu +aah sgom thag gtad pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1459: de nas slob dpon a ha ho'i bzhengs phyag spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:1460: gyi thugs ka nas 'od kyi gong bu gcig thon /
NK033(gi)001:1461: slob ma'i snying gar thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1464: de nas yang dag gi lha tshogs la tshogs kyis mchod /
NK033(gi)001:1465: chos 'di'i bka' skyong ba'i mkha' 'gro gsum dang /
NK033(gi)001:1466: chos skyong gzhan la yang tshogs dang gtor mas mchod do //
NK033(gi)001:1470: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i sgom tshul bla ma'i man ngag rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:1472: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs bsdus pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:1474: zam pa'i byin rlabs bsdus pa las /
NK033(gi)001:1475: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:1476: dang po sa phyogs gtsang ma ru /
NK033(gi)001:1478: snam bu gtsang ma'i steng du /
NK033(gi)001:1479: me tog tshom bu lnga bkram la /
NK033(gi)001:1480: dbus su dpal gyi gtor ma dang ban+d+ha chang gis bkang la a mri tas bran la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:1481: d+aa ki ma gsum bsdus pa'i ba ling gcig bya /
NK033(gi)001:1482: zhun chen mar me yod na shin tu bzang /
NK033(gi)001:1483: spyi'i p+au dza lngas mtha' bskor la /
NK033(gi)001:1485: tshogs kyi p+au dza ci 'byor ba gcig bshams /
NK033(gi)001:1486: de ni rten rdzas bshams pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1487: de nas khrus byas bgegs bskrad slob ma rnams /
NK033(gi)001:1488: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha la ha la h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:1491: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bsdus pa bya /
NK033(gi)001:1492: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK033(gi)001:1493: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1494: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1495: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1496: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK033(gi)001:1497: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK033(gi)001:1498: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK033(gi)001:1499: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)001:1500: dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:1501: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:1502: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK033(gi)001:1503: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK033(gi)001:1504: bskul ba'i sa las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)001:1505: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK033(gi)001:1506: mya ngan mi 'da' bzhugs par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1507: ma grol ba rnams rnam dgrol grol //
NK033(gi)001:1508: sems can mya ngan 'das la dgod //
NK033(gi)001:1509: bdag la gnas pa'i lus 'di ni //
NK033(gi)001:1510: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la 'bul //
NK033(gi)001:1511: tshe rabs bsags pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK033(gi)001:1512: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK033(gi)001:1513: de nas spyi gtor byin gyis brlabs la 'byung po spyi la sbyin pa bya /
NK033(gi)001:1515: dngos gzhi la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:1517: sbyor ba ni mtshams bcad cing /
NK033(gi)001:1518: de nas mchod gtor 'di rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK033(gi)001:1519: bla ma yi dam d+aa ki gsum mchod //
NK033(gi)001:1520: de nas cho ga'i dngos gzhi mngon rdzogs yab yum du //
NK033(gi)001:1521: gsal he ru ka yab yum /
NK033(gi)001:1522: btab bzlas pa cung zhig bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1523: de nas cho ga dngos la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:1524: byin rlabs dang dbang bskur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:1525: dang po slob ma'i gnas gsum spyi bo mgrin pa snying ga /
NK033(gi)001:1531: byin phebs pa'i rtags gsum lus mi g.yo ngag mi smra yid mi rtog pa gang rung zhig /
NK033(gi)001:1533: de nas dbang bzhi bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1534: dpal gtor lhar gsal spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:1535: gsang ba gsum las byung ba yi //
NK033(gi)001:1536: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi dbang //
NK033(gi)001:1537: bu khyod la ni bskur ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1538: sku yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1539: sh+r+ai badz+ra b+aee r+ao ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK033(gi)001:1540: ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri bud+d+ha a lus la
NK033(gi)001:1544: rat+na a rna ltag g.yas b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK033(gi)001:1545: pad+ma a ltag khung du b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a
NK033(gi)001:1546: rna ltag g.yon b+hi shiny+tsa +aahzhesa pas de nas he
NK033(gi)001:1547: ru ka 'od du zhu slob ma'i lus la thim
NK033(gi)001:1548: pas lha'i lus ngo bor gyur par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:1549: mtshan ma dbyibs kyi rnal 'byor te //
NK033(gi)001:1550: lha dbang phyi bum pa'i lus la bskur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:1551: bdud de nas rtsi lhar gsal spyi bor bzhag la //
NK033(gi)001:1552: gsang ba gsum las byung ba yi //
NK033(gi)001:1553: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi dbang //
NK033(gi)001:1554: bu khyod la ni bskur ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1555: gsung gi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1556: sh+r+ai badz+ra w+aa ka ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra 'di skad brjod /
NK033(gi)001:1557: kro d+hi shwa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK033(gi)001:1558: zhes lha yi thugs ka'i sngags kyi 'od zer thugs slob ma'i kar thim /
NK033(gi)001:1560: sngags kyi phreng bar gyur par bsam la /
NK033(gi)001:1561: sngags bzlas pa'i lung ni lan gsum dpog /
NK033(gi)001:1562: bya ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor te //
NK033(gi)001:1563: ngag dbang ngag la de ni gsang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:1565: bdud de nas rtsi spyi bor yang bzhag la 'di skad do //
NK033(gi)001:1566: gsang ba gsum las byung ba yi //
NK033(gi)001:1567: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi dbang //
NK033(gi)001:1568: bu khyod la ni bskur ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1569: thugs kyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1570: sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK033(gi)001:1571: zhes pas mngon rdzogs yab yum de //
NK033(gi)001:1572: gnyis su dbyer med byang chub sems su de nas zhu //
NK033(gi)001:1573: lce bdud rtsi yi steng du bzhag pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:1574: lus slob ma'i sems bde bas gang bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:1575: sid+d+hi a la la hoh zhes bdud rtsi lan gsum blud /
NK033(gi)001:1576: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor te /
NK033(gi)001:1577: chos dbang sems la bskur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:1579: de nas 'di skad brjod par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:1580: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK033(gi)001:1581: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)001:1582: skye 'gag med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK033(gi)001:1583: chos nyid ngang du spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1585: a ni skye med mi rtog brda //
NK033(gi)001:1586: ha ni 'gag med gsal ba'i brda //
NK033(gi)001:1587: ho ni gnyis su med pa'i brda //
NK033(gi)001:1588: 'i ni dbyer mi phyed pa'i brda //
NK033(gi)001:1589: spros bral don gyi rnal 'byor te //
NK033(gi)001:1590: de kho na nyid kyi dbang bskur des dbang bzhi pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1592: rjes la tshogs kyi p+au dza 'bul //
NK033(gi)001:1593: rnal 'byor rol bar pa la ma mo //
NK033(gi)001:1594: cing lhag ma'i gtor ma btang //
NK033(gi)001:1597: he ru ka mngon rdzogs yab yum gyi //
NK033(gi)001:1598: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK033(gi)001:1599: phrin las lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal //
NK033(gi)001:1601: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen las //
NK033(gi)001:1602: dngos grub 'byung bar bsam la rol //
NK033(gi)001:1603: skyu dpal bshos mtha' bskor gyi /
NK033(gi)001:1604: gtor tsho dang d+aa ki ma'i gtor ma gtsang sar btang bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1605: gshegs su gsol dang bkra shis dang smon lam gdab //
NK033(gi)001:1606: mi don dmigs bsngo ba'i rgyas tshig gis gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:1607: de ni rjes kyi rim pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:1608: zam pa'i byin sgom tshul bla ma'i /
NK033(gi)001:1611: gsum pa sgom sgrub nyams len gyi skor la /
NK033(gi)001:1614: cha lag gi skor dang gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:1616: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa las bla ma brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs rgyas pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:1618: ma nor ma bla ma'i gsol 'debs bya ba de yin no //
NK033(gi)001:1620: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid dang //
NK033(gi)001:1621: dus gsum sangs rgyas thugs dang dbyer mi phyed //
NK033(gi)001:1622: brgyud pa'i bla ma spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1623: gu ru d+aa ki ni h+aum h+aum sa many+dzah zhes
NK033(gi)001:1624: brjod pas mdun gyi bar snang la bla ma d+aa
NK033(gi)001:1625: ki thibs kyis byon par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:1626: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis sprul pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:1627: bdag pos ma bzung phyi nang gsang ba'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:1628: nam mkha' gang bar blo yis rab sprul te //
NK033(gi)001:1629: thugs rje chen po'i dbang gis bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1630: chos dbyings rnam dag zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1631: chos sku spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)001:1632: skal ldan don du gzugs skur snang //
NK033(gi)001:1633: kun tu bzang po la phyag mtshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1634: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)001:1636: 'od snang gzhi med longs spyod sku //
NK033(gi)001:1637: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1638: rang snang dag pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1639: sprul sku phrin las mthar phyin cing //
NK033(gi)001:1640: log rtog dri ma kun sel ba'i //
NK033(gi)001:1641: sems dag lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1642: dur khrod gser gling he chen nas //
NK033(gi)001:1643: rigs byed sprul sku mkha' 'gro'i gtso //
NK033(gi)001:1644: lha yi dbang thob brda' la 'byongs //
NK033(gi)001:1645: dga' rab rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1646: yon tan 'byung ba'i gnas mchog na //
NK033(gi)001:1647: sprul skus byin brlabs dri ba mkhas //
NK033(gi)001:1648: the tshom kun spangs o rgyan byon //
NK033(gi)001:1649: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1650: na len+d+ra yi byang phyogs na //
NK033(gi)001:1651: sgra dang rtsod pas mu stegs zlog /
NK033(gi)001:1652: nyi zla lta bus gzhan don mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:1654: sgrags kyi yang rdzong dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1655: dka' thub spyod pas sgra bsgyur mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:1656: thang khab sprul sku skal ldan gzigs //
NK033(gi)001:1657: bee ro tsa na la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1658: stag rtse mkhar gyi dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1659: smon lam dag pas rjes dang mjal //
NK033(gi)001:1660: mkha' 'gros byin rlabs gnas lugs rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:1661: mi pham mgon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1662: seng ge brag gi yang dgon na //
NK033(gi)001:1663: sdom pa gsum ldan rnal 'byor pa //
NK033(gi)001:1664: rig 'dzin sa bzhi bgrod mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1665: byang chub rgyal mtshan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1666: gnas mchog seng ge'i yang rdzong na //
NK033(gi)001:1667: bslab pa mthar phyin dgongs pa lon //
NK033(gi)001:1668: shes bya gzhi med thugs su chud //
NK033(gi)001:1669: za ngam rin chen la phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)001:1670: grub thob bkra shis dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1671: bla mas byin brlabs brda' don 'phrod //
NK033(gi)001:1672: chos nyid don rtogs dngos grub thob //
NK033(gi)001:1674: phug po lha ri'i gtsang na ri bo che bya ba yod /
NK033(gi)001:1676: sku bzhi'i don rtogs mngon du gyur //
NK033(gi)001:1677: zad par skye mched rdzu 'phrul ston //
NK033(gi)001:1678: bya nyang chub grags pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)001:1679: phug phyung lha ri'i rtse mo na //
NK033(gi)001:1680: rtogs pa mngon gyur 'od gsal sku //
NK033(gi)001:1681: rlung lnga dbang thob mkha' spyod gshegs //
NK033(gi)001:1683: phug chung zu ru'i dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1684: rgyud sde'i chos la thos bsam mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:1685: bla ma'i gdams ngag sgro 'dogs chod //
NK033(gi)001:1686: ye rba sgom shes byang chub la phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)001:1687: 'dzeng stod dpal gyi dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1688: brda' bzhi'i don rtogs rig 'dzin pa //
NK033(gi)001:1689: gsang spyod mthar phyin gzhan don brtson //
NK033(gi)001:1690: d+harma 'dzeng po d+hi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1691: gar bzhugs chos kyi dben gnas nas //
NK033(gi)001:1692: mtshan ldan bla mas rjes su bzung //
NK033(gi)001:1693: brda' bzhis skal ldan 'dren mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1694: dz+ny+aa na gzigs ye shes dbang po /
NK033(gi)001:1696: la kha gtsug lag khang chen na //
NK033(gi)001:1697: bslab pa gsum ldan sh+aakya'i sras //
NK033(gi)001:1698: rang gzhan don grub 'gro ba'i dpal //
NK033(gi)001:1699: pun+ye pra mkhan po ngur pa bsod nams 'od /
NK033(gi)001:1701: la kha sngags sde'i dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1703: thos bsam sgrub pa tshul bzhin mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:1704: rdo rje dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)001:1705: 'phrul nang go ri'i dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1706: bslab pa gsum ldan gzhan don che //
NK033(gi)001:1707: sde snod dgongs shing brda' bzhi rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:1708: byang chub mtha' bzhi 'bum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1709: bdag sogs rmongs pa'i sems can la //
NK033(gi)001:1710: brda' don sgron mes snang mdzad nas //
NK033(gi)001:1711: 'khrul pa chos skur rtogs pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:1712: skye med phyag rgya che thob shog /
NK033(gi)001:1715: gzhon nu'i dpal 'dzin sbas pa'i don rnyed pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1716: rje dga' rab rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1717: dpal bo gcig pur bzhugs kyang brtse ldan spyod pa dpa' //
NK033(gi)001:1718: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1719: ma h+aa tsi nar legs 'tsho yun ring gnas //
NK033(gi)001:1720: rje sh+r+ai sing ha'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1721: mang pos bkur ba'i bka' spyod nyams su len //
NK033(gi)001:1722: rje bee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1723: gdams pa'i bka' babs d+aa ki'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1724: rje mi pham mgon po'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1725: rang yul spangs nas chos phyir srog mi lta //
NK033(gi)001:1726: rje byang chub rgyal mtshan sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1727: bdag sogs long ba'i mig gyur dgos 'dod de //
NK033(gi)001:1728: rje rin chen dbyig gi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1729: srid pa'i 'byung gnas 'du 'dzi chos brgyad spangs //
NK033(gi)001:1730: rje gsal ba mchog gi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1731: nad kyi chu klung drod kyi nyi mas skems //
NK033(gi)001:1732: rje byang chub grags pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1733: 'chi bdag bdud bcom gnas lugs ngang la bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:1734: rje shes rab 'byung gnas sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1735: zhabs kyi ze'u 'bru gus pas spyi bor len //
NK033(gi)001:1736: rje ye shes 'byung gnas sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1737: 'dod don spangs nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1738: rje d+harma bo d+hi'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1739: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal //
NK033(gi)001:1740: bka' srung mkha' 'gro'i gtso mo chen mo gsum //
NK033(gi)001:1741: sku mdog dmar po khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)001:1742: g.yas pa cang te'u chos nyid sgra sgrogs gsal //
NK033(gi)001:1743: g.yon pas thod khrag nyon mongs rtsad nas gcod //
NK033(gi)001:1744: kha t+w+aam rtse gsum dug gsum 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK033(gi)001:1745: sbas pa'i gar mdzad rnal 'byor byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1746: bka' srung mkha' 'gro gsum la phyag 'tshal bstod ////
NK033(gi)001:1748: chos kyi dbyings las sprul pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NK033(gi)001:1749: dngos med 'ja' tshon lta bur skur ston cing //
NK033(gi)001:1750: brda' dang sgra yis chos ston pa //
NK033(gi)001:1751: badz+ra sat+wa sems dag lha yi bu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1752: mkha' 'gro mang pos mchod pa'i lus bsgyur zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1753: skye 'gags med pa'i chos nyid thugs su gsal //
NK033(gi)001:1754: nyi ma'i dkyil ltar chos brda' ston mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1755: rje dga' rab rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1756: rje btsun byin brlabs dur khrod gnas su byon //
NK033(gi)001:1757: chos nyid mngon sum 'gyur med nyi ma'i dkyil ltar rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:1758: b+he ta'i gling na 'gro ba'i don la bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:1759: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1760: rje btsun byin brlabs b+he ta'i gling du byon //
