NK033(gi)001:1761: chos nyid skye med nam mkha'i dkyil ltar rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:1762: rdo rje gdan na chos skur ston mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1763: sh+r+ai sing ha'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1764: bod kyi mun pa thams cad sel mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1765: chos nyid snying po man shel ltar rtogs pas //
NK033(gi)001:1766: thugs rje'i rtsal gyis 'dzam gling khyab mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1767: bee ro tsa na'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1768: skal ldan byin brlabs chos nyid snod gyur pa //
NK033(gi)001:1769: dug gsum 'chi ba bcud len 'bras bu bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:1770: chos nyid zab mo dbang bzhis nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:1771: rjee mi pham mgon po'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1772: dka' ba spyad nas tsha ba'i rong du byon //
NK033(gi)001:1773: zab mo'i don rtogs bde gsal nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:1774: rig 'dzin sku brnyes 'gro ba'i don la bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:1775: rje ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1776: 'khor bas 'jigs shing shes rab me bzhin 'bar //
NK033(gi)001:1777: bde gsal mi rtog nyams myong mthar phyin pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1778: 'jam dpal sku bzhin gzhon nu'i skur ston pa //
NK033(gi)001:1779: rje za ngam rin chen dbyig gi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1780: rig 'dzin sa thob skye med don rtogs pas //
NK033(gi)001:1781: dus gsum 'gyur med chos nyid ngang la gnas //
NK033(gi)001:1782: sgyu lus lhag med phung po mngon sangs rgyas //
NK033(gi)001:1783: rje khu 'gyur gsal ba mchog gi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1784: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa rab tu 'jig mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1785: rje btsun thugs zin chos nyid nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:1786: phug po'i ri la lhag med mngon sangs rgyas //
NK033(gi)001:1787: rje btsun byang chub grags kyi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1788: ting 'dzin rtsal 'byongs yon tan sna tshogs ston //
NK033(gi)001:1789: 'gro don ston mdzad brda' nyid sna tshogs ston //
NK033(gi)001:1790: chos sku gcer bu ston mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1791: rje btsun shes rab 'byung gnas sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1792: las dang skal bar ldan pa'i dad pa can //
NK033(gi)001:1793: skye med chos sku rgyud la gsal mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1794: thugs rje nyi ma bzhin du gsal mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1795: rba bsgom ye shes byang chub sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1796: tha mal chen por bzhugs mdzad cing //
NK033(gi)001:1797: brjod med kyi ngang la gnas mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1798: nyon mongs kyi dri ma mi mnga' zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1800: rje d+harma bo d+hi'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1801: nyon mongs zad pas rje btsun zhal mjal zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1802: rje btsun thugs rjes chos nyid snod du gzigs //
NK033(gi)001:1803: chos nyid zab mo'i don rnams rgyud la shar //
NK033(gi)001:1804: rje ye shes dbang phyug sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1805: bcud kyi snying po don gyi gtso bo'i chos //
NK033(gi)001:1806: rig 'dzin sangs rgyas rnams kyi brda' yis bstan //
NK033(gi)001:1807: rtogs ldan gang zag rnams kyi snyan du brgyud //
NK033(gi)001:1808: bdud rtsi bde chen rab tu skyil mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:1809: phug chen bsod nams 'od kyi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1810: bla ma dam pa rnams kyi rig 'dzin sras //
NK033(gi)001:1811: gsang sngags rgyud sde ma lus mkhyen mdzad cing //
NK033(gi)001:1812: bdud rtsi'i bcud snying grub thob pa //
NK033(gi)001:1813: phug chen badz+ra shwa ra'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1814: gzhon nur rab byung tshul khrims rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK033(gi)001:1815: sde snod gsum dang 'phags pa'i nor gyis phyug /
NK033(gi)001:1816: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs snyan brgyud gdams par ldan //
NK033(gi)001:1817: rgyal ba'i sras gyur byang chub 'bum gyi sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1818: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen nas //
NK033(gi)001:1819: bka' srung gi mkha' 'gro gtso mo gsum //
NK033(gi)001:1820: sku mdog dmar mo khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)001:1821: g.yas pa cang te'u chos nyid sgra sgrogs gsal //
NK033(gi)001:1822: g.yon pa thod khrag nyon mongs rtsad nas gcod //
NK033(gi)001:1823: kha t+w+aam rtse gsum dug gsum 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK033(gi)001:1824: dur khrod rus pa'i rgyan gyis sku la brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:1825: gsang ba'i gar mdzad rnal 'byor byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:1826: bka' srung mkha' 'gro gsum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:1827: gsol ba snying gi dkyil nas 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1828: byin rlabs thugs kyi dkyil nas zhu //
NK033(gi)001:1829: lus la bde bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1830: ngag la nus par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1831: sems la rtogs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1832: rdzogs chen snyan brgyud kyi gsol 'debs so ////
NK033(gi)001:1833: kun gzhi rig pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK033(gi)001:1834: mi 'gyur dag pa ye shes lnga //
NK033(gi)001:1835: chos kyi sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1836: rje kun tu bzang pos byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1837: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)001:1838: 'ja' tshon ltar snang gzhi med gsal //
NK033(gi)001:1839: longs spyod sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1840: rje rdo rje sems dpas byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1841: skye med bar snang yangs pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1842: 'gags med lha sku snang tshul shar //
NK033(gi)001:1843: sprul pa'i sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1844: sems dag lha'i bus byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1845: dur khrod gser gling dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1846: lha las sprul nas gdul byar byon //
NK033(gi)001:1847: theg chen rigs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1848: dga' rab rdo rjes byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1849: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer nas //
NK033(gi)001:1850: dpa' ba'i shugs kyis dgongs pa lon //
NK033(gi)001:1852: rje 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1853: rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs nas //
NK033(gi)001:1854: rtsod pa tshar gcod bstan pa bsrungs //
NK033(gi)001:1855: log lta sel la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1856: rje sh+r+ai sing has byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1857: sgrags kyi yang rdzong dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1858: dka' thub spyod pas gdams pa lon //
NK033(gi)001:1860: rje bee ro tsa nas byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1861: stag rtse mkhar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1862: skal bar ldan pas rje dang mjal //
NK033(gi)001:1863: dgongs pa gtad la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1864: rje mi pham mgon pos byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1865: wa seng ge brag gi dgon pa na //
NK033(gi)001:1866: dam tshig gtsang bas sku tshe bsrings //
NK033(gi)001:1867: lhag med gshegs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1868: rje byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1869: seng ge yang rdzong dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1870: bla ma'i 'dab tu sgrub pa mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:1871: dgung du yal la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1872: rje za ngam rin chen gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1873: bla mas byin rlabs dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1874: gcig brgyud gdams pa'i tshul bzhin bsgrubs //
NK033(gi)001:1875: dbyings su dag la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1876: rje khu 'gyur gsal mchog gis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1877: ri bo chen po'i dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1878: rlung la dbang thob zad par 'byongs //
NK033(gi)001:1880: rje byang chub grags kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1881: phug chung lha ri'i rtse mo nas //
NK033(gi)001:1882: dka' thub mthar phyin rig pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:1883: lhag med gshegs la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1884: rje shes rab 'byung gnas kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1885: phug chung zu ru'i dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1886: brda' yi rig pas dwangs snyigs 'byed //
NK033(gi)001:1888: rje ye shes byang chub kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1889: dwangs lung 'dzeng stod dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1890: brgyud pa'i bka' babs rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:1892: rje rgyal ba 'dzeng ston gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1893: dwags po zangs dkar gyi dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1894: 'dzeng d+harma bo d+hi'i thugs kyi sras //
NK033(gi)001:1896: rje skye tshe ye shes dbang phyug gis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1897: la kha phug chen dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1898: don rnams rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK033(gi)001:1899: shes rgya can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1900: rje ru bsod nams 'od kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1901: phug chen dgon pa'i zhol khang nas //
NK033(gi)001:1902: bka' brgyud rnams kyi gdams pa 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:1903: grub thob sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1904: rje badz+ra shwa ras byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1905: 'phrul snang go ri'i dgon pa nas //
NK033(gi)001:1906: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs kyi sras //
NK033(gi)001:1907: gdams pa can la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1908: rje byang chub 'bum gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1909: mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:1910: dbyer med dbyings dang mnyam pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:1911: yi dam lha la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1912: dpal chen he ru ka yis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1913: sprin nag 'dus pa'i gzhal yas nas //
NK033(gi)001:1914: rna brgyud gdams pa'i bka' skyong ba'i //
NK033(gi)001:1915: ma bzhin byams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1916: mkha' 'gro sde gsum gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1917: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum //
NK033(gi)001:1918: rtsa ba gsum la gsol ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:1919: byin gyis rlobs par mdzad du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1920: khyed la byin rlabs zhu ba ni //
NK033(gi)001:1921: ma rig mun pa sel ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1922: rang rig rang gsal byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1923: bag chags 'khrul pa gcod pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:1924: mi rtog chos nyid du byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1925: sdug bsngal bde bar bsgyur ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1926: zag med bde chen du byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1927: chos rnams gcig tu go ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:1928: dbyer mi phyed par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1929: dbyer med dbyings la mnyam pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:1930: chos kyi sku ru byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1931: chos sku 'gags pa med pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:1932: longs spyod sku ru byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1933: thugs rjes 'gro don mdzad pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:1934: sprul pa'i sku ru byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1936: dbyer med rang sa zin par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:1937: bdag gis gsol ba 'di btab pas //
NK033(gi)001:1938: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1940: 'di skabs khyung tshang pa dpal ldan blo gros kyis
NK033(gi)001:1941: mdzad pa'i bsdus pa kun bzang rdor sems ma zhes
NK033(gi)001:1942: pa'i gsol 'debs shig yod par gsungs kyang dpe la
NK033(gi)001:1943: ma byung ngo // yan lag bdun pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:1944: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK033(gi)001:1945: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:1946: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:1947: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:1948: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK033(gi)001:1949: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK033(gi)001:1950: dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:1951: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:1952: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK033(gi)001:1953: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK033(gi)001:1954: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK033(gi)001:1955: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK033(gi)001:1956: bskul ba'i sa las bzhengs nas su //
NK033(gi)001:1957: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK033(gi)001:1958: ma grol ba ni rnam grol zhing //
NK033(gi)001:1960: bdag la gnas pa'i lus 'di ni //
NK033(gi)001:1961: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la 'bul //
NK033(gi)001:1962: tshe rabs bsags pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK033(gi)001:1963: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK033(gi)001:1964: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK033(gi)001:1965: thob nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams pham byas nas //
NK033(gi)001:1966: rga nad 'chi ba'i rba klong 'khrugs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:1967: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK033(gi)001:1968: rdo rje zam pa'i bdun rnam dag rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:1973: dge ba la rjes su yi rang ba /
NK033(gi)001:1975: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba 'debs pa /
NK033(gi)001:1976: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:1978: klu sgrub kyis dpag med bzhi ldan du gsungs te /
NK033(gi)001:1979: sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa'i spyan sngar /
NK033(gi)001:1980: lus dpag tu med par sprul /
NK033(gi)001:1981: sems can dpag tu med pa'i don du /
NK033(gi)001:1982: phyag dpag tu med par 'tshal bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:1983: mchod pa 'bul ba la drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:1984: rdzas rim par bshams pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:1985: bdag pos ma bzung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:1989: mos pa'i stobs kyis dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:1991: stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags te /
NK033(gi)001:1996: rjes su yi rang ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:1997: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i spyan sngar /
NK033(gi)001:1998: bdag gzhan gyi don du dge ba'i rtsa ba dang
NK033(gi)001:1999: mchod pa 'di lta bu 'bul ba a re dga'
NK033(gi)001:2001: sangs rgyas rnams kyis sems can gyi don du g.yel
NK033(gi)001:2002: ba med par chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar gsol
NK033(gi)001:2003: ba gdab bo // mya chos sku skye med kyi bde bas /
NK033(gi)001:2004: ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:2005: kun tu bzang po dang 'jam dpal gyi bsngo ba ltar bla med du bsngo'o //
NK033(gi)001:2006: dge ba rgya cher bsngo ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2007: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:2009: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon sum du sbyar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2010: da ltar gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di na ci mchis pa 'di dag dang /
NK033(gi)001:2011: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba da rung yid la 'byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2012: dge ba'i rtsa ba ci bgyis pa de dag thams
NK033(gi)001:2013: cad gcig tu bsdus te bzlum nas dge ba'i rtsa
NK033(gi)001:2014: ba rgya cher bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK033(gi)001:2017: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad dang /
NK033(gi)001:2018: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK033(gi)001:2019: sems dpa' rnams dang 'phags pa thams cad bdag la
NK033(gi)001:2020: dgongs su gsol / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK033(gi)001:2021: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2022: da ltar gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon sum du gyur pa 'di na ci mchis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2023: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba da rung yid la 'byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2024: gzhan gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba ci bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2025: rjes su yi rang bar bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2026: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag thams cad gcig tu
NK033(gi)001:2027: bsdus te bsdoms nas bla ma yi dam la 'bul
NK033(gi)001:2028: lo // de las kyang dpag tu med pa 'phel ba 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:2029: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK033(gi)001:2030: sems dpa' dang 'phags pa thams cad la 'bul lo
NK033(gi)001:2031: // dge ba'i rtsa ba 'phel ba la gnas par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:2032: mi zad par ba gyi ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2033: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po thams cad dang /
NK033(gi)001:2034: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK033(gi)001:2035: sems dpa' rnams dang 'phags pa thams cad bdag la
NK033(gi)001:2036: dgongs su gsol / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK033(gi)001:2037: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon sum du sbyar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2038: da ltar gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di na ci mchis pa 'di dag dang /
NK033(gi)001:2039: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba da rung yid la 'byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2040: gzhan gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba ci bgyis pa la rjes su yi rang bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2041: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag thams cad gcig tu bsdus te /
NK033(gi)001:2042: bsdoms nas rigs drug gi sems can thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)001:2043: don du bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba mi zad
NK033(gi)001:2044: par gyur cig / yongs su mi zad par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:2045: dpag tu med pa mi zad par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:2046: de dag thams cad la lan gsum gsum phyag gsum gsum bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2047: bla ma 'dzeng gi bsngo ba'i phyag len rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:2048: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:2049: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ki ni /
NK033(gi)001:2050: rdo rje zam pa'i gdams pa ma smin pa smin
NK033(gi)001:2051: par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi spyod pa ni
NK033(gi)001:2052: / de yang bdag gis khams gsum gyi sems can
NK033(gi)001:2053: thams cad kyi don du chos bya dgos snyam pa
NK033(gi)001:2054: zhe thag pa nas snying rje chen po rab tu
NK033(gi)001:2055: / bsgom mo // de nas lus dang bas phyag 'tshal /
NK033(gi)001:2056: ngag dang bas bzlas brjod bya /
NK033(gi)001:2057: yid dang bas bsam gtan la gnas par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2058: de la lus dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2059: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes lan gsum brjod cing se gol bsnol mar gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:2060: des bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro 'phags pa thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar byon par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:2061: de nas rang gi thugs khar kha dog lnga dang ldan pa gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:2062: de la bdag gis thal mo sbyar nas yod pa de'i nang du 'od zer song bas /
NK033(gi)001:2063: sor mo'i sul rnams rin po cher khra phung gi song bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:2064: de nas lag pa deng byas pas bla ma yi
NK033(gi)001:2065: dam 'phags pa thams cad la 'bul bar bsam zhing
NK033(gi)001:2066: zhabs la mgo gtug tu song bar bsam pas sku
NK033(gi)001:2067: gsung thugs kyi 'od zer gyis bdag gi sgrib pa
NK033(gi)001:2068: thams cad bud nas nag nyil nyil song bar bsam
NK033(gi)001:2069: mo // des lus dkar tse na song nas sems
NK033(gi)001:2070: sems nyid du gyur par bsam zhing phyag 'tshal lo
NK033(gi)001:2071: mo // // ngag nas kyang 'di skad du brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:2072: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spangs pa dang
NK033(gi)001:2073: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid dbyings dang
NK033(gi)001:2074: ye shes gnyis su med pa la bdag phyag 'tshal
NK033(gi)001:2076: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gsung rab yan lag
NK033(gi)001:2077: bcu gnyis 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad yang dag
NK033(gi)001:2078: pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa rnams la bdag
NK033(gi)001:2080: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun sa chen po la rab tu
NK033(gi)001:2081: bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
NK033(gi)001:2082: phyir mi ldog pa rnams la bdag phyag 'tshal zhing
NK033(gi)001:2083: skyabs su mchi'o // nyon mongs nad kyis gdung ba la //
NK033(gi)001:2084: chos kyis gdung ba sel mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:2085: yon tan thams cad rgyud la sbyor mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:2086: dus gsum bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2087: de gnyis su med pa'i 'od kyi rang bzhin du
NK033(gi)001:2088: gyur te me long la has btab pa bzhin du
NK033(gi)001:2089: rim par 'dus nas thig le la 'dus so //
NK033(gi)001:2090: rgyal ba thams cad dbyer med dbyings mnyam yang //
NK033(gi)001:2091: bsten bkur bdag gis mchod cing dbu la bkod //
NK033(gi)001:2092: dngos grub rnam gnyis myur du ster mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:2093: rigs lnga he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2094: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK033(gi)001:2095: 'dod par rgyug pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK033(gi)001:2096: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:2097: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2098: dug gsum las kyi rlung nag 'khor ba las ldog cing //
NK033(gi)001:2099: nyon mongs tha ba'i gnas nas byang chub myu gu bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:2100: sred dang lta phyir 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK033(gi)001:2101: bcom ldan lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2102: ngag dang ba'i sgo nas snying po brjod pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2103: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs nor bu'i mchog ldan gyis
NK033(gi)001:2104: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)001:2105: thugs kyi bcud bsdus pa'i snying po yin gsungs so
NK033(gi)001:2106: // ma ni badz+ra pad+me yin pa 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:2108: zhes yun ring du bsring la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig gam bdun brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:2109: de'i chos kyi rang sgras bde bar gshegs pa rnams
NK033(gi)001:2110: kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul zhing dgyes par bsam
NK033(gi)001:2111: zhing sems can thams cad kyi sdig sgrib dag cing
NK033(gi)001:2113: yid dang ba'i sgo nas bsam gtan la gnas pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2114: bde gshegs bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro spyan drangs
NK033(gi)001:2115: te 'od kyi rnam par bsdus te bla ma dang
NK033(gi)001:2116: yi dam lha la rim pas 'dus par bsam mo
NK033(gi)001:2117: // bla ma'i thig le yi dam la 'dus /
NK033(gi)001:2118: yi dam thugs ka'i h'u la thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:2123: zla tshes thig le la thim /
NK033(gi)001:2124: thig le de smin mtshams kyi thad ka'i nam mkha' bsam la /
NK033(gi)001:2125: +aahmh'u byas pas thig le rang gi spyi bo'i rtsa
NK033(gi)001:2126: a wa d+hu ti nas mar la thim par bsam
NK033(gi)001:2127: mo // de'i dus na chos nyid rgyud la 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:2128: sgom pa bdag po la gtad pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2131: slob dpon gyi zhal nas sgom pa bdag po la
NK033(gi)001:2132: gtad pa bya ba ye shes kyi ngang la gtad
NK033(gi)001:2133: pa la zer ba yin no gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:2134: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas so //////
NK033(gi)001:2135: nyams len gyi snying po rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i brgyud pa tha ma'i man ngag bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:2136: de kho na ma sems nyid de sangs rgyas kyis ma mdzad /
NK033(gi)001:2137: nor ma bcos bsam 'das gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i don chos sku'o //
NK033(gi)001:2139: brjod med tshig gi tha snyad bral bas /
NK033(gi)001:2140: ngang la sems kyi don de lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:2141: phyag gzung 'dzin gyi dri mas ma gos pas na /
NK033(gi)001:2143: nyon mongs pa rang bzhin gyis mi gnas pa bsam
NK033(gi)001:2144: pas sems nyid sangs rgyas su ngo shes pas ma
NK033(gi)001:2145: nor / da ltar nyams su len pa'i dus su blo'i bsam pas sgom du med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2146: yid kyis bcos su med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2147: ngo shes pas nyon mongs pa las gdod nas nyon mongs pa rang bzhin gyis mi gnas pas /
NK033(gi)001:2148: chos sku de nyid skyon dang bral ba nyi ma'i snying po lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2149: dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyi //
NK033(gi)001:2150: nyid kyi so so rang la gnas pa'i chos nyid kyi don bstan no //
NK033(gi)001:2151: ngo bo nyid kyis don bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2155: don gtan la 'bebs pa la gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:2156: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2157: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2158: re dogs med pa'i dbyings la gtad pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2160: rig 'dzin brdas brdas mig gi yul du bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2162: gang zag gdams ngag gis ngag gis rna ba'i dbang por blugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2164: de la rig 'dzin sangs rgyas pa'i rigs 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)001:2166: spyir rgya gar gyi yul na gling chen po dgu yod de /
NK033(gi)001:2167: shar phyogs na b+ham ga la /
NK033(gi)001:2171: shar lho mtshams na khang bu'i gling /
NK033(gi)001:2172: lho nub mtshams na zangs gling /
NK033(gi)001:2173: nub byang mtshams na za hor gyi gling /
NK033(gi)001:2174: byang shar mtshams na ka ma ru'i gling /
NK033(gi)001:2175: dbus na rdo rje gdan dang dagu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2176: de la rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs /
NK033(gi)001:2180: me tog u dum wa ra'i gling /
NK033(gi)001:2181: brag phug gser gyi yu ba can /
NK033(gi)001:2182: sprin nag po 'dus pa'i gseb na /
NK033(gi)001:2183: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje de /
NK033(gi)001:2184: mkha' 'gro ma chos kyi dbyings las /
NK033(gi)001:2185: rnams la chos ston cing bzhugs pa la /
NK033(gi)001:2186: dus nam zhig nyi ma'i rtse shar la skye ba med pa'i ngang las /
NK033(gi)001:2187: skye ba'i nam mkha' stong pa las /
NK033(gi)001:2188: cho 'phrul du dpal dbyings las ye shes shar rdo
NK033(gi)001:2189: rje sems dpa' snang 'od kyi sku ba'i gzugs su
NK033(gi)001:2190: grub la reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa gcig
NK033(gi)001:2191: gzigs nas / de'i dus su bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK033(gi)001:2192: rdo rje sems dpas slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i
NK033(gi)001:2193: spyi bor phyag bzhag nas a ha ho'i zhes dbang
NK033(gi)001:2194: gzigs nas / bskur ba'o // gzigs pa tsam gyis
NK033(gi)001:2195: 'dzum pa mdzad pas chos sku dbyings ye dga' rab
NK033(gi)001:2196: rdo rjes shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs so
NK033(gi)001:2197: gzigs nas / bskur ba'o // // de nas slob
NK033(gi)001:2198: dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis chos nyid kyi don
NK033(gi)001:2199: skad cig ma la rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang
NK033(gi)001:2200: rgya bar yod bya ba gsan nas dka' ba'i spyod
NK033(gi)001:2201: pa sna tshogs pa lo gcig tu lam 'phrang na
NK033(gi)001:2202: gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams dang mkha' 'gro mi
NK033(gi)001:2203: bsrun pa yod pas thag ring bas lo gcig 'gro
NK033(gi)001:2204: gzigs nas / bskur ba'o // // dgos so // mdzad nas byon /
NK033(gi)001:2205: de nas zhal mjal slob dpon gyi zhal nas nga
NK033(gi)001:2206: ni 'di na yod pas rnyed par dka' ba yin
NK033(gi)001:2207: pa la 'jam dpal bshes gnyen khyod las 'phro dang
NK033(gi)001:2208: ldan pa yin no gsungs skad /
NK033(gi)001:2209: nas lo gcig tu nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum
NK033(gi)001:2210: bskor ba dang lha phyag phul nas tshegs chung la
NK033(gi)001:2211: don che ba 'bad pa med par 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK033(gi)001:2213: zla ba ngo re la gsol ba 'debs shing lo gcig tu bzhugs pa la /
NK033(gi)001:2214: slob dpon gyi zhal nas ci yang mi gsungs nas
NK033(gi)001:2215: da yang shi la bsdad dgos snyam nas ka p+aa
NK033(gi)001:2216: li nas spu gri bton nas rke la brdeg kha
NK033(gi)001:2217: ma la slob dpon gyi zhal nas 'jam dpal bshes
NK033(gi)001:2218: gnyen khyed ci 'dod pa yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2219: bdag chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:2220: tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams pa zhu byas pas /
NK033(gi)001:2221: s+aur+ya yo ni zhes brda' bstan pas /
NK033(gi)001:2222: chos nyid nyi ma'i snying po ltar rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:2223: nyi ma'i snying po la bltas pas dus gsum du
NK033(gi)001:2224: 'du 'bral med pa gsal 'grib med pa de bzhin
NK033(gi)001:2225: du rtogs so // de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen de /
NK033(gi)001:2226: lho phyogs gyad kyi yul be ta'i gling shing dra ba gtsug dgu yod pa'i tshal /
NK033(gi)001:2228: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du gshegs so //
NK033(gi)001:2229: de nas slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has chos spyi chos
NK033(gi)001:2230: spyi ni bu ram ma zos par bu ram gyi
NK033(gi)001:2232: dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don ni bu ram
NK033(gi)001:2233: gyi yon tan kyang 'chad la bu ram zos pas
NK033(gi)001:2235: skad cig mas rtogs pa tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya
NK033(gi)001:2236: ba yod bya ba gsan nas dka' ba'i spyod pa
NK033(gi)001:2237: sna tshogs pa lo gcig sa'i bu ga nas phar
NK033(gi)001:2238: phyin pas zla ba drug na brtol /
NK033(gi)001:2240: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang mjal
NK033(gi)001:2241: nas slob dpon gyis rdzu 'phrul bstan te rmon pa
NK033(gi)001:2242: dang / byi'u mchil pa bdun dang /
NK033(gi)001:2243: bud med kyi lag pa g.yon pa la gdu bu lnga /
NK033(gi)001:2244: de lta bu la sogs pa sh+r+ai sing ha la bstan no //
NK033(gi)001:2245: de nas lo gcig tu nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du man+dala dang /
NK033(gi)001:2247: phyag phul nas zla ba ngo re la zhu ba'i
NK033(gi)001:2248: don re phul sh+r+ai sing has nam phyed na rdo
NK033(gi)001:2249: rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bton pa la
NK033(gi)001:2250: yang brda' bstan / rdul phyags kyang da rung byung /
NK033(gi)001:2251: nas lo gcig tu bzhugs pa la ci yang mi
NK033(gi)001:2252: gsungs nas da yang 'gro dgos de tsho brdar ma
NK033(gi)001:2253: go bas ngal zhing chad nas de nas slob dpon
NK033(gi)001:2254: gyis shing thog rdog gsum byin te zos pas na
NK033(gi)001:2255: bas snga ma tsho yang brdar ma go //
NK033(gi)001:2256: byang chub kyi shing klag sha'i 'bras bu smin pa rdog po gsum byin no //
NK033(gi)001:2259: slob dpon gyi zhal nas sh+r+ai sing+ha khyod ci 'dod pa yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2260: bdag chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid skad cig
NK033(gi)001:2261: ma gcig la rtogs pas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya
NK033(gi)001:2262: ba'i gdams pa zhu byas pas a ba d+ha ra
NK033(gi)001:2263: zhes brda' bstan pas chos nyid rnam dbyer mi phyed
NK033(gi)001:2264: pa'o // nam mkha'i mkha' 'gags pa med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2266: de nas rdo rje gdan rmad du byung ba'i gnas dpal na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du gshegs so //
NK033(gi)001:2267: de nas mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan gyis rgya gar gyi yul nas /
NK033(gi)001:2268: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don skad
NK033(gi)001:2269: cig ma gcig la rtogs pas tshe gcig gis 'tshang
NK033(gi)001:2270: rgya ba yod bya ba gsan nas /
NK033(gi)001:2271: gtsang legs grub dang bee ro tsa na gnyis len du btang bas /
NK033(gi)001:2272: bshad dka' rnams bstan nas legs grub song ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2273: bee ro tsa nas bee ro tsa na'i thugs la
NK033(gi)001:2274: 'dis chos nyid kyi don skad cig ma la rtogs
NK033(gi)001:2276: dang po thos pa'i shes rab sgra 'ba' zhig /
NK033(gi)001:2277: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab sgra don phyed pa /
NK033(gi)001:2278: tha ma don du 'dug kyang bdag cag la rgyal
NK033(gi)001:2279: pos chad pa bcad nas 'gro bas snyam nas bzhugs
NK033(gi)001:2280: so // bdag gis ni ma go'o zer nas slar yang bsdad do //
NK033(gi)001:2281: de nas bee ro tsa nas bdag la chos spyi dang /
NK033(gi)001:2282: rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don chos nyid skad cig
NK033(gi)001:2283: ma gcig la rtogs pas tshe 'di nyid la 'tshang
NK033(gi)001:2284: rgya ba gcig zhu byas pas /
NK033(gi)001:2285: san d+ha ra zhes brda' bstan pas chos nyid man shel ltar rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:2286: ngo bo gang du yang ma grub rkyen ci yang snang bar rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:2287: de yan chad rig 'dzin brdas grol lo //
NK033(gi)001:2288: de nas bod yul du rdzu 'phrul gyis byon no //
NK033(gi)001:2289: de ltar bka' babs dang po mnga' bdag la babs so //
NK033(gi)001:2290: de nas rgyal mo tsha ba'i shod du rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la babs so //
NK033(gi)001:2291: de nas rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du spang mi
NK033(gi)001:2292: pham mgon po rgyal mo stag rtse mkhar na bzhugs
NK033(gi)001:2293: so // lo brgyad cu rtsa lnga lon pa gcig la brda' mig gi yul du bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2294: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs nas bstan no //
NK033(gi)001:2295: des khams nas chos 'tshol du phyin pa'i ngan lam
NK033(gi)001:2296: byang chub rgyal mtshan la slar yang khams su byon
NK033(gi)001:2297: nas / brda' dang mig gi yul /
NK033(gi)001:2300: des za ngam gsum po de khams kyi wa seng
NK033(gi)001:2301: ge brag tu gcig rting la gcig phung po lhag
NK033(gi)001:2304: des khu 'gyur gsal ba mchog la bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2305: des gtsang nyang byang chub grags pa la bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2306: khams su byon nas gdams ngag zhus te gtsang gi
NK033(gi)001:2307: ri bo cher phung po lhag med du sangs rgyas
NK033(gi)001:2308: so // des nyang shes rab grags slob dpon nyang
NK033(gi)001:2309: shes rab grags pa gtsang na gang bar phug po
NK033(gi)001:2310: so // cher byon / slar log nas gtsang du bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:2312: des la kha phug po che'i bsgom ye shes byang chub la bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2313: des yang phug chung zur ra ru bsgoms pas mi dkar po gcig gnam du song zer skad /
NK033(gi)001:2314: des bla ma skye tshe ye shes dbang phyug la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:2315: des mkhan po ngu chen po la /
NK033(gi)001:2317: de'i sh+aakya'i dge slong byang chub 'bum pa la 'di rnams ni gang zag gdams ngag gis grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2319: des mtha' bzhi'i ban chung gzhon nu byang chub bdag la gnang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2321: brda' don dgrol ba'i man ngag sbyin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2322: rdo rje'i tshig lam sems kyi lde mig sbyin pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2324: 'dzin med ngang la mi gnas la //
NK033(gi)001:2325: g.yo 'dzin rlung gi man ngag sbyin pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:2326: sems nyid mi brtan spros chen la //
NK033(gi)001:2327: bde ba thig le'i man ngag sbyin pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2332: de la bem po'i rlung gtan la mi 'bebs /
NK033(gi)001:2333: rig pa'i rlung gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2334: rig pa'i rlung brdas ston pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2335: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag cing ma g.yos pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2336: de yang yid ches pa'i lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:2338: ka ra na bcings yon tan gyis //
NK033(gi)001:2339: lus ngag yid gsum g.yo mi 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:2340: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag cing ma g.yos pa'i brdas rig pa'i rlung mi 'gul bas /
NK033(gi)001:2342: de chad pas 'khor bar lus len mkhan med do //
NK033(gi)001:2343: de ni gnad kyi gdams ngag zab mo'o //
NK033(gi)001:2345: de ni thabs zab mo brten pa las chos skur rtogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2346: de yang yid ches pa'i lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:2347: rtsa ba'i rgyud nam mkha' che las /
NK033(gi)001:2348: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK033(gi)001:2349: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK033(gi)001:2351: rna brgyud 'di nyid kyi bzhed kyis /
NK033(gi)001:2352: bde chen lam du 'jug pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:2353: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long bstan //
NK033(gi)001:2355: yang de'i man ngag gis mig mi 'gul bar thad ka la zim me blta bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2356: de yis rnam par rtog pa thams cad rgyun chad do //
NK033(gi)001:2358: rtsa ma 'gul bas rlung mi bskyod /
NK033(gi)001:2359: rlung mi bskyod pas yid kyi 'gyu ba chad de /
NK033(gi)001:2361: skye ba phyis mi len pa'i gdams ngag kyang de la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2362: de ni man ngag gis yid ches pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2363: da ni mdo nas gsungs pa'i /
NK033(gi)001:2364: lung yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK033(gi)001:2365: gnya' mig rna rtser dbab pa /
NK033(gi)001:2366: shing gang tsam blta zhing 'gro la sems 'khrul med //
NK033(gi)001:2368: de'i dus su dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pas gsal ba'i brda' /
NK033(gi)001:2369: mig ma 'dzum pas phyi'i snang ba gsal /
NK033(gi)001:2371: g.yos pas mi rtog pa'i brda' /
NK033(gi)001:2373: yang de'i dus na 'og sgo yid tsam 'then pas bde ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)001:2374: bde ba la zag bcas dang zag med do //
NK033(gi)001:2375: zag med de brdas bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2376: 'og sgo yid tsam 'then pas spyi gshang ba'i sgo btsum nas gyen la yid tsam drangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2377: bo'i gtsug nas rkang pa'i mthil yan chad du lus yod du mi tshor ba'i bde ba skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2378: de yang byams pas zhus pa'i le'u shes rab kyi
NK033(gi)001:2379: pha rol tu phyin pa nas zag pa med pa'i
NK033(gi)001:2380: bde ba chen po zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2381: rdo rje'i tshig lam la gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:2382: rten med par rig pa rang grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2383: rkyen dang bral ba'i snang ba rang dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2384: de la rten med pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2385: sems nyid stong pa nam mkha' lta bu gcig la yang mi brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2387: phyi'i yul la rtog pa ma zhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2388: re dogs med pa la gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:2389: bsam brjod bral ba'i ting 'dzin mchog /
NK033(gi)001:2390: de bzhin nyid du mya ngan 'das //
NK033(gi)001:2391: zhes pas de la bsam brjod dang bral ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2392: brda' bstan pa'i dus mno bsam gyis bsgom du med /
NK033(gi)001:2393: yid la mi byed pas ting 'dzin gyi mchog go //
NK033(gi)001:2394: de bzhin nyid ni bsam brjod dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin de nyid kyi ngang las sangs rgya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2395: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyang de bzhin du sangs rgya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2396: don gtan la phebs pa la gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:2397: dbang ngang gis rdzogs pas sgom sgrub dge ba'i chos la mi ltos /
NK033(gi)001:2398: sku rang chas su gyur pas dge sdig gnyis las grol /
NK033(gi)001:2399: don gcig tu rtogs pas rtog dpyod las 'das pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2400: dbang ngang gis rdzogs pa ni lus kyis brda' bstan pas phyi bum pa'i dbang rdzogs /
NK033(gi)001:2401: mi rtog pa shar bas nang gi dbang rdzogs /
NK033(gi)001:2402: bde ba skyes pas gsang ba'i dbang rdzogs /
NK033(gi)001:2403: zhal gyi gdams ngag thos pas tshig dbang rin po che rdzogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2404: dbang de rnams sems nyid la 'dus pas rgyal thabs
NK033(gi)001:2405: rin po che spyi blugs kyi dbang rdzogs de tsa
NK033(gi)001:2406: na dge ba'i chos la ltos mi dgos so //
NK033(gi)001:2409: sems nyid 'bral ba med pas chos skur rang chas /
NK033(gi)001:2410: chos sku la ye shes 'char bas longs sku rang chas /
NK033(gi)001:2411: ye shes kyis gzhan don mdzad pas na sprul sku rang chas so //
NK033(gi)001:2412: don gcig tu rtogs pas ni chos thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)001:2413: mtha' chos kyi sku la thug pas theg pa gzhan
NK033(gi)001:2414: la rtog dpyod kyi de tsa na dge sdig ni
NK033(gi)001:2415: blo las skyes pas dge sdig gnyis las grol /
NK033(gi)001:2417: des don gtan la phebs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2418: 'di ni rgyal thabs rin chen ste //
NK033(gi)001:2419: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol //
NK033(gi)001:2420: 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste //
NK033(gi)001:2421: sangs rgyas sa la sbyor ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2422: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa brgyud pa tha ma'i
NK033(gi)001:2423: man 'di spang mi pham mgon po'i gsung yin min
NK033(gi)001:2425: bee ro tsa na bdag 'dra yis //
NK033(gi)001:2426: rdzogs chen brgyud pa tha ma yi //
NK033(gi)001:2427: rna brgyud dgongs pa bkrol ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:2428: phyag rgya chen po thob par shog /
NK033(gi)001:2431: po chen po'i phyag dpe las brgyud pa las bris byang chub 'bum gyis /
NK033(gi)001:2437: phyin ci ma log rtogs pa'i ye shes dang //
NK033(gi)001:2438: spros bral mkha' snang dag pa'i ngang bzhugs pa //
NK033(gi)001:2439: dus gsum bla ma rnams dang yi dam lha //
NK033(gi)001:2440: lhun grub bde chen sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2441: de la dam pa rin po che de'i gsung gi 'od zer /
NK033(gi)001:2442: zhal gyi da la nas nyi zla mkha' snang dag pa bzhin 'od phyung nas /
NK033(gi)001:2443: dug lnga ye shes snang zhing 'char bar byed pa /
NK033(gi)001:2444: gdams pa gsal ba'i yig chung 'di ru dgod //
NK033(gi)001:2445: de la dam pa rin po che'i zhal nas /
NK033(gi)001:2446: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa la gdams pa sna brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:2447: de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i gdams pa rnam pa gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:2448: ngo mtshar can gyi gdams pa rnam pa gsum /
NK033(gi)001:2449: brda' bzhi'i 'dug tshul bstan pa dang bzhi bya bar bla ma'i zhal nas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2450: de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i gdams ngag zhal la dam por mchi /
NK033(gi)001:2452: ltas brda rang la brtags pa dang 'chi ltas byung na bslu ba gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:2455: de la 'chi ltas brtag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2456: tshangs pa'i skud pa chad na 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:2457: mkha' 'gro ma'i brda' skad yal na 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:2458: ye shes kyi gzi mdangs yal na 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:2459: chu shing gi mkhar po sgron yal na 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:2460: nam mkha' dag pa'i nyi ma la rgyab bstan nas bltas pas mgo med na 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:2461: rkang lag la sogs pa'i yan lag ma tshang na ltas ngan yin no //
NK033(gi)001:2462: 'chi ltas de rnams byung na 'pho ba mi bya 'chi bslu bya /
NK033(gi)001:2464: lag pa g.yon pa'i mthil du bdud rtsi mchil ma blugs te /
NK033(gi)001:2466: de la sngags 'di lan bdun brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:2468: ga te ga te p+aa ra ga te p+aa ra sam ga te b+ho d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:2470: de lces blangs te mid pas tshe 'phel zhing rgyal ba'i yum yid la bya ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:2472: des ma bzlog kyang 'chi bslu bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:2473: de lta bu lan gsum byas te /
NK033(gi)001:2475: de yang 'pho ba la gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:2476: rten 'brel khyad par can la brten nas longs sku la 'pho ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2477: sprul pa'i sku la 'pho ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2478: thabs khyad par can la brten nas chos nyid kyi dbyings su 'pho ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2479: de la dang po na ma gcig shing sgur por bzhog la /
NK033(gi)001:2480: de la rigs drug gi sa bon /
NK033(gi)001:2481: ahn+ri su tri pre du bris la /
NK033(gi)001:2482: rang gi sngas su btsugs la blta ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2483: gzhan tshe 'phos na bstan la sngas su gzhugs gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2484: gnyis pa ni shing gi rtse la mar glan /
NK033(gi)001:2485: mar gyi rtse la de bzhin gshegs pa'i ring bsrel bzhag la /
NK033(gi)001:2486: sna bug g.yon du bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:2487: dbugs kyis kun tu rgyal ba'i nang du drang zhes bla mas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2489: stan la 'dug la lus drang po'i 'dug stangs su byas te /
NK033(gi)001:2490: lag pa mnyam bzhag byas la shes pa rig pa'i
NK033(gi)001:2491: rlung gis d+hu tir bcug la lus je dgye byas
NK033(gi)001:2492: la / rgyab tu grogs la 'dzin du bcug /
NK033(gi)001:2493: rlung rig pa'i rlung gis mar zhabs yar la bskul la /
NK033(gi)001:2494: d+hu ti la drangs la spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga la 'don zhes bla mas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2495: de yang 'chi nges na bya ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:2496: ye shes kyi 'pho ba zhes bya /
NK033(gi)001:2497: chos nyid kyi 'pho ba zhes bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:2498: g.yas pa thabs g.yon pa shes rab /
NK033(gi)001:2499: dus kyi brda' dang gsum 'dzom na legs te /
NK033(gi)001:2500: de ni tshe'i dus byas pa'i dus su mi dmigs
NK033(gi)001:2501: pa'i chos sku skye med la 'pho ba zhes bya
NK033(gi)001:2502: ba rje'i zhal nas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2503: snang ba'i 'khyer lugs la gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:2504: nyin mo snang ba sna tshogs lam du khyer ba /
NK033(gi)001:2505: nub mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2506: de la nyin mo 'di ltar snang ba mig gi
NK033(gi)001:2507: dbang po la sogs par sna tshogs kyi snang ba
NK033(gi)001:2508: 'di / 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba 'di mi 'gags te /
NK033(gi)001:2509: ji ltar snang yang gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams
NK033(gi)001:2510: cad la sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs
NK033(gi)001:2511: 'di mi gnas shing mi rtog pas gnyis su ma
NK033(gi)001:2512: grub pas chos nyid kyi rnam par dag pa rig
NK033(gi)001:2513: pa gcig pas gcig chod kyis snang ba lam du
NK033(gi)001:2514: 'khyer gsung ngo // nub mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2515: rig pa'i ngo bo de rten gang la mi 'cha' ste /
NK033(gi)001:2516: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de bde
NK033(gi)001:2517: gsal mi rtog dbyer mi phyed pa'i ngang du nyal
NK033(gi)001:2518: zhes gsungs te / de yang nyal kha langs khar
NK033(gi)001:2519: mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i yi ge bzhi bsgrags gsungs
NK033(gi)001:2520: zhes gsungs te / / yi ge bzhi ni ha
NK033(gi)001:2521: ri ni sa zhes lan bdun nam gnyis bzla zhes
NK033(gi)001:2522: dam pa'i zhal nas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2523: de gnyis ni sbyor lam pa'i dus su shes par bya ba'i don to //
NK033(gi)001:2524: ngo mtshar gyi gdams ngag rnam pa gsum ni ngo sprad kyi rnam pas te /
NK033(gi)001:2525: gang na sems gzhi stong pa la sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis kyis so //
NK033(gi)001:2526: de ni snang stong gnyis med snga phyir ma song bas bral du mi 'dod do //
NK033(gi)001:2527: 'di ni snang la rang bzhin med pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:2529: de ltar snang ba dang stong pa'i dbye bsal ma shes par /
NK033(gi)001:2530: slob dpon gyis stong pa sbom yor du bstan /
NK033(gi)001:2531: slob mas stong ngo snyam du bzung bas /
NK033(gi)001:2532: dge ba la sogs pa thams cad kyi stong pa la mi gnod kyi zer nas longs spyad /
NK033(gi)001:2533: stong pa gsha' ma kha nas zer gin stong pa sangs ye nas rgyas pa skad zer nas /
NK033(gi)001:2534: sdig pa mi dge ba mtha' dag la mi 'dzem /
NK033(gi)001:2535: 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad la sogs pa byed de /
NK033(gi)001:2536: stong pa yin zer zhing gzung 'dzin slar cher song ba des lan no //
NK033(gi)001:2537: de yang rdo rje zam pa'i lugs kyi gnas lugs
NK033(gi)001:2538: la lam bsgrod du med de gnas de yang ji
NK033(gi)001:2540: dge ba'i chos la mi ltos par ngo sprad pa ni chu'i zla ba lta bur snang /
NK033(gi)001:2541: chu'i nang na snang yang btsal na mi rnyed de /
NK033(gi)001:2542: chu'i zla bar ngo sprad pa de ni /
NK033(gi)001:2544: de skyes bu stobs dang ldan pas btsal yang mi rnyed /
NK033(gi)001:2545: de bzhin du sems nyid chu zla lta bur gsal /
NK033(gi)001:2546: yang btsal na mi rnyed pas stong ste /
NK033(gi)001:2548: gsal ba de tsam nas stong /
NK033(gi)001:2549: de yang rig pa dang stong pa gnyis med du gnas te /
NK033(gi)001:2550: 'bad rtsol dang bral ba de la sbyor lam stong pa zhes bla mas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2552: 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste //
NK033(gi)001:2553: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol //
NK033(gi)001:2554: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK033(gi)001:2556: sangs rgyas pa'i stong pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2557: de nyid rnam pa gsum du ngo sprad /
NK033(gi)001:2558: kun tu bzang po'i de nyid ni /
NK033(gi)001:2559: kun tu bzang po'i de nyid /
NK033(gi)001:2560: rig stong dbyer med kyi de nyid /
NK033(gi)001:2561: de bzhin dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med de /
NK033(gi)001:2562: ming gi rnam grangs yin no //
NK033(gi)001:2563: de ltar sa lam bsgrod du med par yid ches pa'i gdams ngag yin /
NK033(gi)001:2564: bsgom yod bsgom med gnyis las /
NK033(gi)001:2566: de ci'i phyir na rig pa'i rlung des ye shes rang ga ma nyams su myong ba ste /
NK033(gi)001:2567: de yang sangs rgyas kyi sa na ye shes rgyun ma chad par 'dod zhes bla mas gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2569: ye shes la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:2571: gnyug ma'i ye shes gnyis bla mas bzhed de /
NK033(gi)001:2572: lam gyi ye shes bya ba de bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la zer te rgyun chad /
NK033(gi)001:2575: ye shes med zer ba de yin /
NK033(gi)001:2576: gnyug ma'i ye shes bya ba de rgyun ma chad /
NK033(gi)001:2578: ye shes med na yon tan 'phel med byang chub med //
NK033(gi)001:2579: rgya mtsho 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas chos kyang med par 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:2581: don la sangs rgyas pa'i stong pa bya ba de
NK033(gi)001:2582: stong pa phyam chad pa lta bu ma yin te
NK033(gi)001:2583: / 'dod pa zad pa bya ba mtshan ma yid
NK033(gi)001:2584: 'jog pa de med pas don la sems nyid ngo
NK033(gi)001:2585: shes pa'i don de la zer zhes bla mas gsung
NK033(gi)001:2587: dam pa rin po che'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2588: bla ma la sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes 'jog pa'i gang zag gis ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK033(gi)001:2589: ci 'byor ba'i tshogs dang yo byad bshams te /
NK033(gi)001:2590: de'i dus su byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:2591: gu ru yang bsgom gsungs te /
NK033(gi)001:2593: bsgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab //
NK033(gi)001:2595: bsgom bya dang bsgom med kyi mtshan ma ni med gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2596: 'o na ji ltar zhus pa las /
NK033(gi)001:2597: 'dzin pa med pa'i gnas nas spongs //
NK033(gi)001:2598: 'dzin pa rlung gi man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:2600: sems nyid mi brtan spros chen la //
NK033(gi)001:2601: bde ba thig le'i man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:2603: rlung de ngos 'dzin dgos pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2604: de la gnyis las bem po'i rlung mi 'dzin rig pa'i rlung 'dzin gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2605: de gang na gnas na sems la'o gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2606: de la d+hu tir tshud pa'i dus yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2608: sna sgo g.yon nas rgyu ba'i dus su tshud pa yin gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2609: de lta bu yang brda' bzhi'i 'dug tshul la brten
NK033(gi)001:2610: nas dbang po'i sgo ma bkag cing ma g.yos pa
NK033(gi)001:2612: de yang nyams su len pa'i dus su 'di ltar ro //
NK033(gi)001:2613: dang po lus sems kyi gnad gsal /
NK033(gi)001:2615: tha ma bying ba gseng ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2616: dang po lus kyi gnad gsal ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2617: lus la mi bde ba rnams bsal /
NK033(gi)001:2619: nyi ma la sdod snying mi 'dod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2620: zas che chung ran pa de rnams so //
NK033(gi)001:2621: bar du brda' bzhi'i 'dug tshul bcos pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2622: mig sna'i rtse mo mthong tsam du dbab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2623: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang mi reg pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2624: kha smyug ma 'bring po shong tsam du cung zhig deng nge bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2626: dbugs sna bug g.yon nas 'gyu tsam na bsgom pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2627: dbang po dang lus mi g.yo ba rnams so //
NK033(gi)001:2628: tha ma bying ba gseng ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2629: bsgom tsam na 'ong ma bsgom tsam na mi 'ong ba'i bar gyi bying nas 'dug pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:2630: ting nge 'dzin dang 'bral mi phod pa la sogs
NK033(gi)001:2631: pa byung ba'i dus su 'dug sa yang yang spos
NK033(gi)001:2632: la bsgom / 'dug sa spos pa'i sar ting nge 'dzin skye'am mi skye bltas te /
NK033(gi)001:2633: de yang lus bde ba'i 'dug tshul byas te /
NK033(gi)001:2634: yang dag lta stangs sna rtse la'o //
NK033(gi)001:2635: zer bas sna rtse la lta ba'i tshul du byas la /
NK033(gi)001:2636: gnya' shing gang tsam la gtad la bya gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2637: de yang dbang po'i sgo ma bkag cing ma g.yos pa las 'byung ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:2638: ma bkag pa ni gsal ba yin la /
NK033(gi)001:2639: ma g.yos pas ni dran med kyi rtog pa thams cad 'gag ste /
NK033(gi)001:2640: de yang tha snyad du brjod na /
NK033(gi)001:2641: gsal ba la stod pa'i rgyas thebs pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2643: sems nyid mi brtan spros chen la //
NK033(gi)001:2644: bde chen thig le'i man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:2646: zag bcas dang zag med las /
NK033(gi)001:2648: las rgyal brten pa'i bde ba gsang sngags dbang gsum pa'i bde ba lta bu yin te /
NK033(gi)001:2649: gzhan la rag lus pas 'dir mi bzhed gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:2650: zag med kyi bde ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2652: ka ra na bcings yon tan gyis //
NK033(gi)001:2653: srid pa gsum po g.yo mi 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:2655: chos nyid de la srid pa gsum gyi bde ba 'byung zhing /
NK033(gi)001:2656: de nyid rtog pa'i dbang du mi g.yo zhing /
NK033(gi)001:2657: de gsum zil gyis mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:2658: yon tan de yod pas ka ra na bcings /
NK033(gi)001:2659: de'i dus su a long bag tsam 'dzum 'og rlung cung zad 'then no //
NK033(gi)001:2660: de drag na rtsol bsgrub ches pas /
NK033(gi)001:2661: cung zad 'then pas bde yin gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2662: de ltar na tha mal gyi shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:2665: gnyug ma nyams su myong ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2666: de ltar bsgom pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:2669: zhi ba dpa' bo'i 'dug stangs byas la /
NK033(gi)001:2671: g.yon cung zhig bskum la sgom thag gis 'khyud par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2672: ma bde tsa na g.yas g.yon spo bar bya /
NK033(gi)001:2673: lag pa g.yon lag pa g.yas pas bsgom shing thogs
NK033(gi)001:2674: nas mchan khung du gtad nas sgom rten phyin phyogs
NK033(gi)001:2675: su gzugs la lag pa g.yon pas g.yas pa'i nywa
NK033(gi)001:2677: stan ma bde na go bzlog par bya /
NK033(gi)001:2679: rjes la mkha' 'gro ma gsum la gtor ma btang /
NK033(gi)001:2680: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:2681: dang po bsgom khar sems bskyed bya /
NK033(gi)001:2682: bla ma rnams la gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)001:2683: sngon du 'gro ba sems can thams cad byang chub thob par bya /
NK033(gi)001:2684: de'i don du bdag gis bsgom par bya /
NK033(gi)001:2685: brgyud pa'i bla ma la mos gus kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)001:2686: tha ma bsgom pa las byung ba'i dge ba sems can gyi don du bsngo /
NK033(gi)001:2687: dam pa'i bka' dang rtogs ldan thun mong ma yin pa'i gdams ngag rnams /
NK033(gi)001:2688: dmar khrid zhal las blangs kyin bsgom pa 'di //
NK033(gi)001:2689: skal ldan gsol ba 'debs phyir yi ger bkod //
NK033(gi)001:2690: gal te 'khrul zhing nongs pa rnams //
NK033(gi)001:2691: bla ma rje btsun rnams la mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:2692: snyan brgyud nyams su blangs pa'i dmar khrid 'di //
NK033(gi)001:2693: dbang po yang rab rnams dang 'phrad par shog /
NK033(gi)001:2694: snyan brgyud rin po che bka' nas snyan du brgyud
NK033(gi)001:2695: pa skas kyi rim pa lta bu dgongs pa'i nyams
NK033(gi)001:2696: bsgrigs mu tig rtsar la brgyus pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:2697: brda' bzhis ngo sprod lag mthil du gter mthong ba 'dra ba lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:2698: tshig la yid ches pa bod du med pa gser gyi phreng ba lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:2699: yid ches the tshom 'dzol sa med pa bya thi ba tshang du 'gro ba lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2700: dam pa rin po che'i snyan brgyud rdo rje zam
NK033(gi)001:2701: pa'i gdams pa dmar khrid lag tu blangs pa'i rim
NK033(gi)001:2702: pa rdzogs so ////// snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i
NK033(gi)001:2703: nyams khrid sgom gyi yi ge gsal ba'i sgron ma
NK033(gi)001:2704: pa rdzogs so ////// bzhugs / bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:2705: chos nyid kyi don skad cig gis rtogs shing tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya bar 'dod pas /
NK033(gi)001:2706: dang po mi skye ba skye bar byed pa'i gnad ni sgom thag brkyang khru gang dang sor bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:2707: sgom rten la yang tshad de tsam pa zhig go //
NK033(gi)001:2708: 'dug stangs la snga dro kha nub tu blta /
NK033(gi)001:2709: pus mo g.yon pa sa la dbab /
NK033(gi)001:2710: g.yas pa bsgreng pa'i pus mo la sgom thag 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:2711: sgom rten gzhogs g.yon ngos kyi sta zur ngos nas lag pa gnyis kyis bzung bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2712: dgong mo kha shar du blta /
NK033(gi)001:2713: pus mo g.yas pa sa la dbab /
NK033(gi)001:2714: g.yon pa bsgreng ba'i pus mo'i khar sgom thag 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:2715: sgom rten g.yas ngos kyis sta zur du blta'o //
NK033(gi)001:2716: nyin gung la dus kyi gnad mi 'ong bas mi bsgom gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:2717: gnyis pa skyes pa brtan par byed pa'i gnad ni /
NK033(gi)001:2718: brda' gnyis kyi sgo nas nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:2719: dus kyi brda' dang gnad kyi barda'o //
NK033(gi)001:2720: dus kyi brda' sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi ston pas da res mi ston /
NK033(gi)001:2721: 'o na da res mi ston yang ji lta bu gcig yin na /
NK033(gi)001:2723: dus kyi brda' ni bstan shes yang snang /
NK033(gi)001:2725: gnad kyi brda' ni yongs gyur nas //
NK033(gi)001:2726: yongs gyur gnyis la mi gnas te //
NK033(gi)001:2728: de la dus kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:2729: rlung a wa d+hu tir tshud pa'i dus so //
NK033(gi)001:2730: a wa d+hu ti la lnga yod de /
NK033(gi)001:2731: spyi bor gtsug tor gyi a wa d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:2732: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi a wa d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:2733: snying ga shes rab kyi a wa d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:2734: lte ba sprul pa'i a wa d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:2735: gsang ba bde chen gyi a wa d+hu ti dang lnga yod pa las /
NK033(gi)001:2736: de rnams gang du tshud kyang rung ste /
NK033(gi)001:2737: de'i rtags su rlung sna bug g.yon pa nas rgyu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2738: de'i dus su gnad kyi brda' bzhis nyams su blangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2739: dang po gsal ba'i gnad kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:2740: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag ste /
NK033(gi)001:2741: de'ang sna'i rtse mo mtho gang tsam gyi thad kar blta ste /
NK033(gi)001:2742: dbang po ma bkag par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:2743: des rgyud la ji lta bu gcig 'char na /
NK033(gi)001:2744: sems nyid rang gi ngo rang gsal zhig 'ongs /
NK033(gi)001:2745: de yang dran pa dang bcas pa'i gsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:2747: 'di dran med kyi gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2748: de la ming 'dogs na gsal ba zer ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2749: gnyis pa mi rtog pa'i gnad kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:2750: dbang po ma g.yos par mig gi 'bras bu mi 'gul bar tsen gyis bzhag pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2751: des rgyud la ji ltar du 'char na sems nyid rang gi ngo bo rang gsal ba /
NK033(gi)001:2753: blo'i rtog pa ci yang mi 'gyu ba gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:2754: de ni gsal ba la stong pas rgyas thebs pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2755: gsum pa bde ba'i gnad kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:2756: dbang po ma bkag cing ma g.yos pas kyang 'og rlung rang bzhin gyis zin /
NK033(gi)001:2757: a long rang bzhin gyis btsum gyis 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2759: des lus yod pa mi mngon pa'i bde ba gcig skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2760: bzhi pa dbyer mi phyed pa'i gnad kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:2761: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang mi reg par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:2762: de yang bshad pa snga phyir byung yang /
NK033(gi)001:2763: nyams su len pa'i dus su 'og rlung cung zad 'then /
NK033(gi)001:2764: lce rtse gang la yang ma reg par dbang po'i sgo ma bkag cing ma g.yos par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:2769: dbyer mi phyed pa tsam gyi mtha' la mi gnas pa zhig rgyud la 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:2770: de yang gsal ba'i gnad kyi brda' ste /
NK033(gi)001:2771: dbang po ma bkag pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2772: mi rtog pa'i gnad kyi brda' ste /
NK033(gi)001:2773: dbang po ma g.yos pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2774: bde ba'i gnad kyis 'og rlung zin pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2775: dbyer mi phyed gnad kyi brda' ste /
NK033(gi)001:2776: lce rtse gang la yang ma reg pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:2777: de yang gnad kyi brda' dang pos gsal ba gcig
NK033(gi)001:2778: byung ba de dran med kyi gsal ba yin te
NK033(gi)001:2779: / rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2780: sems nyid rang gi ngo bo rang gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2781: de la 'od gsal zer ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:2782: gnad gnyis pas rnam rtog 'gyu 'phro bar chad nas ci yang yid la mi 'gyu ba /
NK033(gi)001:2783: ci yang mi rtog pa dran med gcig 'ong ste /
NK033(gi)001:2784: de la mi rtog pa zer ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2785: mi rtog pa de rang gi sems dag pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:2786: bla mas bstan pa'i chos nyid rnam par dag pa bya ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2787: de la gsal ba la stong pas rgyas thebs bya ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2788: gnad kyi brda' gsum pas lus sems bral nas lus
NK033(gi)001:2789: yod pa mi mngon pa'i bde ba cig 'byung ste
NK033(gi)001:2790: / de la zag pa med pa'i bde ba bya ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:2791: de la stong pa'i ro bde bar shar ba zer ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:2792: gnad kyi brda' bzhi pas bde ba /
NK033(gi)001:2794: mi rtog pa gsum po de dbyer mi phyed pa gcig 'byung ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:2795: de yang rgya gang du yang ma chad pa /
NK033(gi)001:2796: phyogs gang du yang ma lhung ba /
NK033(gi)001:2797: de gsum ngo bo gcig tu 'dug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2798: 'bras bu'i dus su yang rim pas sku bzhi 'byung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2799: mig sna rtser gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2801: mu stegs tshangs gnas gyen la blta //
NK033(gi)001:2802: zhi ba po ni mthur du blta //
NK033(gi)001:2803: khro bo'i lta stangs thad khar blta //
NK033(gi)001:2804: yang dag lta stangs sna rtse'o //
NK033(gi)001:2806: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2808: mig ma btsum pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK033(gi)001:2810: seng ge'i lta stangs zhes su bshad //
NK033(gi)001:2811: dbang po ma g.yos pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2813: ka ran bcings pa na yon gyis //
NK033(gi)001:2814: srid pa gsum po g.yo mi 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:2820: dang po ni steng lha'i srid pa /
NK033(gi)001:2822: bar mi'i srid pa dang gsum yid la mi 'gyu ba gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:2826: de gnyis ka yid la mi 'gyu ba gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:2831: dbyer mi phyed ngo snyam pa yang yid la mi byed pa gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:2832: 'og rlung cung zad 'then pas lus sems gnyis bral nas zag pa med pa'i bde ba gcig skye /
NK033(gi)001:2833: de'i lung yang phar phyin byams zhus le'u nas /
NK033(gi)001:2834: gang lus yod du mi tshor ba'i bde ba de ni zag pa med pa'i bde ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2835: bla na med pa'i bde ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2838: lce rtse gang la yang ma reg par bzhag pas /
NK033(gi)001:2841: bde ba gsum dbyer mi phyed pa gcig rgyud la skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2843: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK033(gi)001:2844: yang dag mtha' la rnam par gnas //
NK033(gi)001:2845: bdag med seng ge'i sgra dang ldan //
NK033(gi)001:2846: mu stegs ri dwags ngan 'jigs byed //
NK033(gi)001:2848: brtan pa gong nas gong du bogs 'byin par byed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2849: sgom gyi skyon sel ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:2850: sems nyid dang chos nyid la skyon mi 'ong yang /
NK033(gi)001:2851: lus 'byung ba bzhi las grub pas /
NK033(gi)001:2852: 'byung ba cha ma snyoms na lus la nad 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:2854: de yang sa shas che na lus lci /
NK033(gi)001:2857: nyal snying 'dod gtam smra snying mi 'dod /
NK033(gi)001:2858: rlung shas che na 'gro ba dang smra ba la dga' /
NK033(gi)001:2860: chu shas che na bying 'thib shes pa 'dar dran pa med par gnyid du 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2861: me shas che na rgod pa dang 'aphro'o //
NK033(gi)001:2862: de tsho gang shas che yang sgom mi chags so //
NK033(gi)001:2863: rlung shas che na snga dro rlung gi dus su sa bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2864: rkang pa'i mthe bong gcig thog tu gcig bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)001:2865: lag pa gnyis dpung pa la 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:2866: mtheb chen gnyis kyis dpung pa'i nang rtsa gnyis mnan te /
NK033(gi)001:2869: des lus gru gu ltar bsgril lo //
NK033(gi)001:2870: lta stangs ni thur la blta ste /
NK033(gi)001:2871: lte ba na sa lam ser po'am /
NK033(gi)001:2872: yang na thig le ser po gcig la shes pa gtad do //
NK033(gi)001:2873: rlung shas chung du yin na thun gcig gis 'gro ste /
NK033(gi)001:2875: phyi dro chu'i dus su me chu shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:2877: 'dug stangs rkang pa brkyangs pa la sogs gang bde bya /
NK033(gi)001:2882: lte bar yi ge ram dmar po la shes pa gtad /
NK033(gi)001:2884: rig pa de spyi bo nas yar la zang zang thon par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:2885: rang gi spyi bo na khru gang gi sar yi
NK033(gi)001:2886: ge ram mam thig le dmar po la sems gtad
NK033(gi)001:2887: de bsgom mo // lan bdun bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2888: des skyon las grol te ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2889: srod la me'i dus su chu me shas che na bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2890: rkang pa rdo rje skyil krung bya /
NK033(gi)001:2892: lta stangs ni ri thang mtshams las mtho bar blta /
NK033(gi)001:2893: lte bar chu yi yi ge bam la gtad /
NK033(gi)001:2894: de bas kyang shes pa rang so la bzhag gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:2895: des kyang skyon las grol te ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2896: nam sa shas che na phyed yol nas nyi ma
NK033(gi)001:2897: ma shar gyi bar sa'i dus su rlung bsgom pa
NK033(gi)001:2898: ni / rdo rje skyil krung mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya bya /
NK033(gi)001:2900: rang gi lte ba'i thad kar yi ge yam ljang gu'am /
NK033(gi)001:2901: thig le ljang khu la sems gtad la bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:2902: des skyon las grol te ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:2903: kun gyi gegs sel rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i 'dug stangs bya /
NK033(gi)001:2904: snying kha'am lte bar kha dog lnga pa bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:2906: de ltar sgom gyi skyon bsal zhing nyams su blangs pas /
NK033(gi)001:2908: sgom nyams dang po rtse gcig sgyu ma lta bu'i nyams shar ba'i dus /
NK033(gi)001:2909: nags la me mched pa dang 'dra ste /
NK033(gi)001:2910: dper na nags la me mched pa de /
NK033(gi)001:2911: dang po chung ngu las je che je che la nags thams cad la me 'bar /
NK033(gi)001:2912: de nas me de je chung je chung la tha ma rang zhi nas med par 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2913: de bzhin du rtags lnga po yang dang po chung ngu las che cher 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2914: de nas phyis je med la tha ma yal 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2915: de'ang sgom gyi skyon bsal zhing brda' gnyis kyi sgo
NK033(gi)001:2916: nas bsgom pas las dang po pa la chos nyid
NK033(gi)001:2917: yad yud tsam brang breng tsam 'byung /
NK033(gi)001:2918: rjes la snang ba thams cad sgyu ma lta bur rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:2921: gzugs ni sgyu ma lta bu'o nas rnam pa thams
NK033(gi)001:2922: cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du sgyu ma lta
NK033(gi)001:2924: mkhyen pa nyid las lhag pa'i chos gzhan zhig yod na'ang sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2926: de yang yun ring du bsgoms pas rjes la 'bar ba lta bu'i rtags 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:2927: de yang kha dog la nges pa med do //
NK033(gi)001:2928: dkar po lta bu la mtshon na /
NK033(gi)001:2929: dkar po chung ngu gcig la dkar phreng ba'am /
NK033(gi)001:2930: dkar khyug la dkar skem pa lta bu gcig 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2931: de je che je che la /
NK033(gi)001:2935: mjug tu yul khams thams cad dkar yal la dkar po 'ba' zhig tu 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:2938: kha dog bzhi po yang de dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:2939: de nas zla ba shar ba lta bu'i rtags 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:2943: de nas yul khams thams cad zla ba gsal po lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2944: de nas nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i rtags 'char lugs gong dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:2945: 'di'i dus su nyin mtshan bye brag mi phyed pa 'ong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2946: 'di nas rang gi lus la grib ma mi 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2947: de nas sprul pa sku'i zhing khams mthong ba 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:2948: dang po rang gi yi dam gang yin pa gcig zhal mthong ba gcig 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:2949: rjes shes la yang dang yang du mthong /
NK033(gi)001:2950: de nas 'jug tu snang ba dang dngos po 'di thams cad yi dam du 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:2951: de yang dngos po che ba dang sbom pa thams cad yi dam che ba dang sbom pa /
NK033(gi)001:2952: chung ba dang phra ba thams cad yi dam chung ba dang phra bar mthong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:2953: de yun ring du gnas de yang dag nas 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:2954: 'di'i dus su gzung ba rang bzhin med par rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:2955: de nas longs sku'i zhing khams mthong ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:2956: rjes shes bar snang thams cad yi dam gyis khengs pa 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:2957: 'di'i dus su nad zhi ba la sogs smon lam ci btab 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:2958: 'di'i dus su 'dzin pa rang bzhin med par rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:2959: rtags de rnams byung ba dang ma byung ba la dga' mi dga' mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:2960: de nas rjes thob la nyams gnyis pa du ma ro gcig stong pa nyid kyi nyams 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:2961: de yang phyi'i yul drug stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:2964: gzugs stong pa nyid do la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:2965: nang gi sems lnga stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK033(gi)001:2966: 'dod chags la sogs pa lnga stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:2969: 'dod chags stong pa nyid la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:2970: dpe ni mtsho la kha ba bab pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:2971: de'i dus na mngon par shes pa lnga 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:2972: lha'i mig gi mngon par shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:2973: sa 'og sa steng sa bla rnam pa gsum mthong ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:2974: lha'i rna ba'i mngon par shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:2975: sa 'og sa bla sa steng gsum gyi sems can shig gi skad tshun chod thos pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2976: gzhan gyi sems shes pa sems la ci 'gyu ba shes pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2977: 'pho ba dang skye ba shes pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2981: shi nas gang du skye shes pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2982: rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon par shes pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:2983: lus shing bal ltar yang ba /
NK033(gi)001:2984: sa la byi ba ltar 'dzul ba /
NK033(gi)001:2986: chu la bying ba med par 'gro ba /
NK033(gi)001:2987: lus kyi bkod pa du mar sprul nus pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2989: nam mkha' la 'phur shes te bya bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:2990: chu la mi bying ste sa la byi ba bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:2991: sa la 'dzul te chu la bya nya 'dra ba bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:2994: gcig tu sprul nas mang por 'gyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:2995: mang por sprul nas gcig tu sdud shes pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:2997: de nas nyams gsum pa spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i nyams 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:2998: brda' gnyis la mi ltos par mnyam bzhag rjes thob med /
NK033(gi)001:3000: dpe nam mkha' dag pa la nyi ma shar ba lta bu ste /
NK033(gi)001:3001: sems nyid gnyis 'dzin gyi mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3002: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i nyams khrid sgom gyi yi ge gsal ba'i sgron me rin po che /
NK033(gi)001:3003: 'dzing d+harma b+ho d+his slob dpon 'o la badz+ra sam sid+d+hi kirti la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3004: des slob dpon 'dzing jo sras la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3005: des gzigs ye shes dbang po la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3006: des dpal ldan ru pa chen po la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3007: des ru ston 'jam pa'i dbang phyug la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3008: des go ram pa byang chub 'bum la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3009: des mtha' bzhi pa gzhon nu byang chub la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:3011: sgom gyi khrid rim bco lnga pa rgyud lung man ngag dang mi 'gal ba bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:3013: dmar khrid du bstan pa 'di la /
NK033(gi)001:3014: dang po mi skye ba skye bar bya ba'i thabs bstan pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:3015: skyes pa brtan par bya ba'i thabs bstan pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:3016: de la bying rgod kyi skyon byung na bsal thabs bstan pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:3017: de ltar nyams su blangs pas nyams rnam pa gsum ji ltar 'char lugs bstan pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:3018: de lta bu'i skyon med de bsgom pa la tshe
NK033(gi)001:3019: thung na mi 'grub pas bcud len la brten nas
NK033(gi)001:3020: tshe'i rig 'dzin bzhi ji ltar bsten par bstan pa
NK033(gi)001:3021: dang lnga / de ma grub kyi bar du shi
NK033(gi)001:3022: na ngan song du skye dogs yod pa bsrung ba
NK033(gi)001:3023: dang bskrad pa'i sbyor bas ngan song gi sgo dgag
NK033(gi)001:3024: dang lnga / pa dang drug / mtho ris thar pa'i lam bstan pa dang bdun /
NK033(gi)001:3025: tshe ring bar byung yang lus la na tsha dang /
NK033(gi)001:3026: sems la sdug bsngal byung na bsgom mi 'ong bas
NK033(gi)001:3027: he ru ka mchog gi dngos grub blang ba'i thabs
NK033(gi)001:3028: kyi sgo nas de gnyis mi 'ong bar bstan pa
NK033(gi)001:3029: dang brgyad / phyi'i 'byung ba chen po la rtsal
NK033(gi)001:3030: sbyangs pa'i phyir zad par gyi ting nge 'dzin la
NK033(gi)001:3031: dngos grub blangs pa dang dgu /
NK033(gi)001:3032: na tsha dang sdug bsngal zad par bcu la dbang
NK033(gi)001:3033: thob kyang zas nor gyis mi 'tsho na d+aa ki
NK033(gi)001:3034: gsum la brten nas thun mong gi dngos grub bsgrub
NK033(gi)001:3036: zas nor gyis 'tsho yang bar du gcod pa'i dgra
NK033(gi)001:3037: bgegs byung na d+aa ki gsum la brten nas mngon
NK033(gi)001:3038: spyod kyi phrin las bstan pa dang bcu gcig /
NK033(gi)001:3039: 'di'i brgyud pa phung po lhag med du gshegs pa sha stag yod kyang /
NK033(gi)001:3040: rgya la bsgom yun thung ste lhag med du ma song na /
NK033(gi)001:3041: 'chi ltas brtags pa bstan pa dang bcu gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:3042: rtags byung nas 'chi ba bslu bar bstan pa dang bcu gsum /
NK033(gi)001:3043: ma bslus na 'pho ba bya bar bstan pa dang bcu bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:3044: de ltar 'phos nas bar do'i snang ba 'char ba srid pas /
NK033(gi)001:3045: bar do'i gdams ngag bstan pa dang bco lnga'o //
NK033(gi)001:3047: 'o la'i ban+desa zhus pa go ba ri pa'i thugs dam bdag la gnang ba lags so //////
NK033(gi)001:3048: snyan brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa'i sgom
NK033(gi)001:3049: khrid kyi lag len 'o la jo sras kyi bcud
NK033(gi)001:3050: rgya sgom gyi snod du blugs pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:3051: bla ma he ru ka dang ni //
NK033(gi)001:3052: bka' srung mkha' 'gror bcas rnams la //
NK033(gi)001:3053: rab tu gus pas phyag 'tshal nas //
NK033(gi)001:3054: dam pa'i gsung bzhin ma nor bri //
NK033(gi)001:3055: de la rnal 'byor pa bla ma la gus shing
NK033(gi)001:3056: byin rlabs kyis rgyud smin cing gdams pa thob nas
NK033(gi)001:3057: 'jig rten gyi bya ba la mi dga' zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3058: bdag dang sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i
NK033(gi)001:3059: byang chub la dgod par 'dod pa'i rten gyi gang
NK033(gi)001:3060: zag gis gnas yid dang mthun zhing dben pa'i gnas
NK033(gi)001:3061: su 'dug nas / de la dang po mi skye ba skye bar byed pa'i gnad ni /
NK033(gi)001:3062: sgom thag bltab la brkyang khru gang dang sor bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:3063: sgom rten la'ang tshad de tsam zhig go //
NK033(gi)001:3064: 'dug stangs la snga gro kha nub tu blta /
NK033(gi)001:3065: pus mo g.yon pas la dbab /
NK033(gi)001:3066: g.yas pa bsgreng ba'i pus mo'i khar sgom thag 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:3067: sgom rten gzhogs g.yon ngos kyi sta zur ngos nas lag pa gnyis kyis bzung bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3068: dgong mo kha shar du blta /
NK033(gi)001:3069: pus mo g.yas pa sa la dbab /
NK033(gi)001:3070: g.yon pa bsgreng ba'i pus mo'i khar sgom thag 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:3071: sgom rten g.yas ngos kyi sta zur la lta'o //
NK033(gi)001:3072: nyin gung la dus kyi gnad mi 'ong bas mi sgom gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:3073: gnyis pa skyes pa brtan par byed pa'i gnad ni /
NK033(gi)001:3074: brda gnyis kyi sgo nas nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:3077: dus kyi brda sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi dus su ston pas da res 'dir mi ston /
NK033(gi)001:3078: 'o na der ston yang bshad na ji lta bu gcig yin na /
NK033(gi)001:3080: dus kyi brda ni shes byas nas //
NK033(gi)001:3081: gnad kyi brda ni yongs gyur nas //
NK033(gi)001:3082: yongs gyur gnyis la mi gnas te //
NK033(gi)001:3084: de la dus kyi brda ni rlung a ba d+hu tir tshud pa'i dus so //
NK033(gi)001:3085: a ba d+hu ti la lnga yod de /
NK033(gi)001:3086: spyi bo gtsug tor gyi a ba d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:3087: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi a ba d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:3088: snying ga shes rab kyi a ba d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:3089: lte ba sprul pa'i a ba d+hu ti /
NK033(gi)001:3090: gsang ba bde chen gyi a ba d+hu ti dang
NK033(gi)001:3091: lnga yod pas de rnams gang du tshud kyang 'dra
NK033(gi)001:3092: ste / de'i rtags su rlung sna bug g.yon nas rgyu'o //
NK033(gi)001:3093: de'i dus su gnad kyi brda bzhis nyams su blang ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:3094: dang po gsal ba'i gnad kyi brda ni /
NK033(gi)001:3095: dbang po ma bkag ste de yang sna'i rtse mo
NK033(gi)001:3096: mtho gang tsam gyi thad kar bltas te dbang po
NK033(gi)001:3098: des rgyud la ji lta bu zhig 'char na sems
NK033(gi)001:3099: nyid rang gi ngo bo rang gsal ba gcig 'ong
NK033(gi)001:3100: / de'ang dran pa dang bcas pa'i gsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:3102: 'di dran med kyi gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3103: de la ming 'dogs na gsal ba zer ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3104: gnyis pa mi rtog pa'i gnad kyi brda ni /
NK033(gi)001:3105: dbang po ma g.yos par mig gi 'bras bu mi
NK033(gi)001:3106: g.yo ba mi 'gul bar tsen la bzhag pa yin
NK033(gi)001:3107: / de las rgyud la ji ltar du 'char na /
NK033(gi)001:3108: sems nyid rang gi ngo bo rang gsal ba sal
NK033(gi)001:3109: le ba blo yi rtog pa ci yang mi rgyu
NK033(gi)001:3110: ba gcig yong / de ni gsal ba la stong pas rgyas thebs pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3111: gsum pa bde ba'i gnad kyi brda ni /
NK033(gi)001:3112: dbang po ma bkag cing ma g.yos pas kyang 'og rlung rang bzhin gyis zin /
NK033(gi)001:3113: a long kha rang bzhin gyis btsum gyis 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3115: des lus yod du mi mngon pa'i bde ba gcig skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3116: bzhi pa dbyer mi phyed kyi brda ni /
NK033(gi)001:3117: lce'i rtse mo gang la'ang mi reg par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:3118: de yang bshad pa snga phyir byung yang nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:3120: lce rtse gang la'ang ma reg par dbang po'i sgom bkag cing ma g.yos par bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:3121: des bde ba gsal ba mi rtog pa dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK033(gi)001:3122: dbyer mi phyed tsam gyi mtha' la yang mi gnas pa zhig rgyud la 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:3123: de'ang gsal ba'i gnad kyi brda de dbang po ma bkag pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3124: mi rtog pa'i gnad kyi brda de dbang po ma g.yos pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3125: bde ba'i gnad kyi brda de 'og rlung zin pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3126: dbyer mi phyed kyi gnad kyi brda de lce rtse gang la'ang ma reg pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3127: de'ang gnad kyi brda dang pos gsal ba gcig 'byung
NK033(gi)001:3128: ba de dran med kyi gsal ba de yin te
NK033(gi)001:3129: / rang bzhin gyis gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3130: sems nyid rang gi ngo bo rang gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3131: de la 'od gsal zer ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3132: gnad kyi brda gnyis pas rnam rtog 'gyu 'phro bar chad nas ci yang yid la mi rgyu ba /
NK033(gi)001:3135: de la mi rtog pa zer ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3136: mi rtog pa de rang gi sems dag pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3137: bla mas bstan pa'i chos nyid rnam par dag pa bya ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3138: de la gsal ba la stong pa'i rgyas thebs pa zer ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3139: gnad kyi brda gsum pas lus sems bral nas yod du mi mngon pa'i bde ba zhig 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:3140: de la zag pa med pa'i bde ba bya ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3141: de la stong pa'i ngo bde bar shar ba zer ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3142: gnad kyi brda bzhi pas bde ba gsal ba mi
NK033(gi)001:3143: rtog pa gsum po de dbyer mi phyed pa gcig
NK033(gi)001:3145: de'ang rgya gang du'ang ma chad la phyogs gang du'ang ma lhung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3146: de gsum ngo bo gcig tu 'dus pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3147: 'bras bu'i dus su yang rim pas sku bzhi 'byung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3148: mig sna rtser gtad pa ni dus 'khor las /
NK033(gi)001:3149: mu stegs tshangs gnas gyen du blta //
NK033(gi)001:3150: zhi ba po ni mthur du blta //
NK033(gi)001:3151: khro bo'i lta stangs thad kar blta //
NK033(gi)001:3152: yang dag lta stangs sna rtse'o //
NK033(gi)001:3154: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pa ni rdzogs chen las /
NK033(gi)001:3155: mig ma btsum pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK033(gi)001:3157: seng ge'i lta stangs zhes su brjod //
NK033(gi)001:3159: dbang po ma g.yos pa ni dus 'khor las /
NK033(gi)001:3160: ka ra na bcing yon tan gyis //
NK033(gi)001:3161: srid pa gsum po g.yo mi 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:3167: dang po ni steng lha'i srid pa /
NK033(gi)001:3169: bar mi'i srid pa gsum ka yid la mi 'gyu ba gcig yong /
NK033(gi)001:3170: gnyis pa ni rtog pa gcig shar bas gcig 'gags /
NK033(gi)001:3172: gnyis ka yid la mi byed pa gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3173: gsum pa ni bade'o snyam pa'am gsal lo snyam pa'am
NK033(gi)001:3174: mi rtog go snyam pa'am dbyer mi phyed do snyam
NK033(gi)001:3175: pa yang yid la mi byed pa gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3176: 'og rlung cung zad 'then pas lus sems bral nas zag pa med pa'i bde ba gcig skyes /
NK033(gi)001:3177: de'i lung yang phar phyin byams zhus le'u las /
NK033(gi)001:3178: gang lus yod du mi tshor ba'i bde ba de ni zag pa med pa'i bde ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3179: bla na med pa'i bde ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3182: lce rtse gang la ma reg par bzhag pas bde
NK033(gi)001:3183: ba gsal ba mi rtog pa gsum dbyer mi phyed
NK033(gi)001:3186: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK033(gi)001:3187: yang dag mtha' la rnam par gnas //
NK033(gi)001:3189: brtan pa gong nas gong du bogs 'byin par byed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3190: sgom gyi skyon sel bar byed pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3191: sems nyid dang chos nyid la skyon mi 'ong yang /
NK033(gi)001:3192: lus 'byung ba bzhi las grub pas 'byung bzhi cha ma snyoms na lus la nad 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3194: de'ang sa shas che na lus lci rgyu ba ngan /
NK033(gi)001:3197: rlung shas che na 'gro ba dang smra ba la dga' /
NK033(gi)001:3199: chu shas che na bying 'thib shes pa 'dar dran pa med par gnyid du 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3200: me shas che na dran pa gsal rgod pa dang 'aphro'o //
NK033(gi)001:3201: de tshe gang shas che yang sgom mi 'ong bas /
NK033(gi)001:3202: rlung shas che na snga dro rlung gi dus su sa bsgom ste /
NK033(gi)001:3203: rkang pa'i mthe bo gcig thog tu gcig bzhag ste lag pa gnyis dpung pa la 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:3204: lag pa'i mtheb chen gnyis kyis dpung pa'i nang rtsa gnyis mnan te gru mo pus mo la 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:3206: des lus gru gu ltar 'dril lo //
NK033(gi)001:3207: lta stangs ni mthur la blta /
NK033(gi)001:3208: lte ba nas lam ser po'am /
NK033(gi)001:3209: yang na thig le ser po gcig la gtad do //
NK033(gi)001:3210: rlung shas chung na thun gcig gis chog ste ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3211: phyi dro chu'i dus su me bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3212: 'dug stangs rkang pa brkyang ba la sogs gang bde bya /
NK033(gi)001:3217: lte bar yi ge ram dmar po la shes pa gtad /
NK033(gi)001:3219: rig pa de spyi bo nas yar zang zang thon /
NK033(gi)001:3220: rang gi spyi bo nas khru gang gi sar yi
NK033(gi)001:3221: ge ram ma ma thig le dmar po la sems
NK033(gi)001:3224: des skyon las grol te ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3225: srod la me'i dus su chu bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3226: rkang pa rdo rje skyil krung bya /
NK033(gi)001:3228: lta stangs ni ri thang mtshams las mtho la blta /
NK033(gi)001:3229: lte bar chu yi yi ge bam la gtad /
NK033(gi)001:3230: de bas kyang shes pa rang sor bzhag gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:3231: des kyang skyon las grol nas ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3232: nam phyed yol nas nyi ma shar ba'i bar sa'i dus su rlung sgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3233: rdo rje skyil krung mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya bya /
NK033(gi)001:3235: rang gi lte ba'i thad kar yi ge yam ljang
NK033(gi)001:3236: gu'am thig le ljang khu la sems gtad la sgom
NK033(gi)001:3237: mo // des skyon las grol te ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3238: kun gyi gegs sel rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i 'dug stangs bya /
NK033(gi)001:3239: snying kha'am lte bar kha dog lnga pa bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:3241: de ltar sgom gyi skyon bsal zhing bsgom pas nyams rnam pa gsum 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3242: sgom nyams dang po rtse gcig sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK033(gi)001:3243: nyams shar ba'i dus su nags la me mched pa
NK033(gi)001:3244: dang 'dra / dper na nags la me mched pa
NK033(gi)001:3245: de dang po chung ngu las je che je cher
NK033(gi)001:3247: de nas me de je chung je chung la tha ma rang zhi nas med nas 'gro /
