NK033(gi)001:3248: de bzhin du rtags lnga po yang dang po chung ngu las je cher 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3249: de nas je med la tha ma yal nas 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3250: de yang sgom gyi skyon bsal zhing brda gnyis kyi sgo nas bsgoms pas /
NK033(gi)001:3251: las dang po pa la chos nyid yad yud brang breng tsam 'byung /
NK033(gi)001:3252: rjes la snang ba thams cad sgyu ma lta bur rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:3253: sgyu ma lta bur gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:3255: rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:3256: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:3257: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid las lhag pa'i chos gzhan zhig yod na'ang sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:3259: de'ang yun ring du bsgoms pas rjes la 'bar ba lta bu'i rtags 'char /
NK033(gi)001:3260: de yang kha dog la nges pa med de dkar
NK033(gi)001:3261: po lta bu gcig la mtshon na dkar po chung
NK033(gi)001:3262: ngu la dkar phreng ba'am dkar khyug la dkar skem
NK033(gi)001:3264: de je che je che la me long tsam phub tsam yul tsam /
NK033(gi)001:3265: mjug tu yul khams thams cad dkar yal la dkar po 'ba' zhig tu 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:3267: de nas yang de yal nas 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3268: kha dog bzhi ka yang de dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:3269: de nas zla ba lta bu'i rtags 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3270: dang po me long tsam de nas phub tsam de
NK033(gi)001:3271: nas yul khams thams cad zla ba gsal po lta
NK033(gi)001:3272: bu'o // de nas nyi ma lta bu'i rtags 'char lugs gong dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:3273: 'di'i dus su nyin mtshan bye brag mi phyed pa 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3274: 'di nas rang gi lus la grib ma mi 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:3275: de nas sprul pa sku'i zhal mthong ba 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:3276: dang po rang gi yi dam gang yin pa gcig zhal mthong /
NK033(gi)001:3277: rjes shes la yang dang yang du mthong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:3278: de nas mjug tu snang ba'i dngos po 'di thams cad yi dam du 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3279: de yang dngos po che ba dang sbom pa thams cad yi dam che ba dang sbom pa /
NK033(gi)001:3280: chung ba dang phra ba thams cad yi dam chung ba dang phra bar 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:3283: 'di'i dus su gzung ba la rang bzhin med par rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:3284: de nas longs sku'i zhal mthong ba ni rjes shes
NK033(gi)001:3285: bar snang thams cad yi dam gyis khengs par 'byung
NK033(gi)001:3286: ste / 'di'i dus su nad zhi ba la sogs pa smon lam ci btab 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:3287: 'di'i dus su 'dzin pa la rang bzhin med par rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:3288: rtags de rnams byung ba dang ma byung ba la dga' ba dang mi dga' ba mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3289: de nas rjes thob la nyams gnyis pa du ma ro gcig stong pa nyid kyi nyams 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3290: de yang phyi yi yul drug stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:3293: gzugs stong pa nyid do la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:3294: nang gi sems lnga stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK033(gi)001:3295: 'dod chags la sogs pa lnga stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:3298: 'dod chags stong pa nyid la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:3299: dpe ni mtsho la kha ba babs pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:3300: de'i dus na mngon par shes pa lnga 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:3301: lha'i mig gis mngon par shes pas 'og /
NK033(gi)001:3303: sa bla rnam pa gsum mthong ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3304: lha'i rna ba'i mngon par shes pa sa 'og sa
NK033(gi)001:3305: steng sa bla gsum gyi shig gi skad tshun chod
NK033(gi)001:3306: thos pa'o // gzhan gyi sems shes pa'i mngon par shes pa sems la ci 'gyus shes pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3307: 'chi 'pho ba dang skye ba shes pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3311: shi nas gang du skye shes pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3312: rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon par shes pa ni lus shing bal ltar yang ba /
NK033(gi)001:3313: sa la byi ba ltar 'dzul ba /
NK033(gi)001:3315: chu la bying ba med par 'gro ba /
NK033(gi)001:3316: lus kyi bkod pa du mar sprul nus pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3318: nam mkha' la phur shes te bya bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3319: chu la mi bying ste sa la byi ba bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3320: sa la 'dzul te chu la nya bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3323: gcig tu sprul nas mang por 'gyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3324: mang por sprul nas gcig tu sdud pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3326: de nas nyams gsum pa spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i nyams 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3327: brda gnyis la mi ltos par mnyam zhag rjes thob med /
NK033(gi)001:3328: sems nyid chos nyid du dag /
NK033(gi)001:3329: dper na nam mkha' dag pa la nyi ma shar ba lta bu ste /
NK033(gi)001:3330: sems nyid gnyis 'dzin gyi mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3331: gdams ngag rgyal po rna brgyud kyi //
NK033(gi)001:3332: sgom khrid bla ma'i gsung bzhin bkod //
NK033(gi)001:3333: dge rtsa sems can don du ni //
NK033(gi)001:3334: sems nyid ngang la gnas gyur shog /
NK033(gi)001:3335: sgom khrid yi ge bla ma'i gsung bzhin du bris pa lags so //
NK033(gi)001:3338: de la sngags 'chang 'o la jo sras kyis zhus /
NK033(gi)001:3339: de la bdag rgya sgom gyis zhus so //
NK033(gi)001:3341: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i khrid yig skal bzang mig 'byed bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:3342: ye nas lhag pa'i chos sku chen po ni //
NK033(gi)001:3343: gang gis mngon du mdzad pa ku m+aa ra //
NK033(gi)001:3344: bla ma dam pa'i zhabs kyi pad+mo la //
NK033(gi)001:3345: yan lag mchog gi gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:3346: gang gi zhal las 'ongs pa'i snyan brgyud ni //
NK033(gi)001:3347: yi ge bri bar bya ba min na'ang //
NK033(gi)001:3348: dran pa'i ngal ba cung zad gso phyir du //
NK033(gi)001:3349: zin bris 'di brjod mkha' 'gros bzod mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)001:3350: de la rdzogs pa chen po'i chos skor la /
NK033(gi)001:3353: man ngag gi sde gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:3354: phyag chen zhi byed sogs sems sde dang mthun /
NK033(gi)001:3355: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa klong sde yin yang sde gsum kar bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:3356: de yang rdo rje zam pa zhes pa /
NK033(gi)001:3357: rdo rje sngags kyi khyad chos yin te /
NK033(gi)001:3358: slob dpon la rdo rje'i slob dpon dang /
NK033(gi)001:3359: slob ma la rdo rje'i slob ma /
NK033(gi)001:3360: chos la'ang rdo rje'i tshig sogs kyis btags pa bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3362: sems sde dang man ngag gi sde gnyis klong sdes sbrel bas zam pa zhes bya ba'am /
NK033(gi)001:3363: da ltar gyi lus 'di ma spangs par 'ja' lus
NK033(gi)001:3364: su sgyur thub pas lus gnyis sbrel bas zam pa
NK033(gi)001:3366: de lta bu'i snyan brgyud nyams su len pa la /
NK033(gi)001:3367: bsgom don sems la bkod pa /
NK033(gi)001:3368: sgom khrid lag tu blangs pa /
NK033(gi)001:3369: sgom 'bras tshad la dbab pa dang gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:3371: 'dir zab gsal gnyis med gcig tu bstan pas /
NK033(gi)001:3372: chos thams cad gtan la phebs pa dbang po shin tu rnon po'i chos yin cing /
NK033(gi)001:3373: de yang dang por lhag mthong ston pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:3374: da ltar gyi sems spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad
NK033(gi)001:3375: dang bral bar bsgom pas snang ba sna tshogs su
NK033(gi)001:3377: ngo bo nyid kyi skur 'gyur pa bshad pa'i go don sems la bkod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3379: ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung /
NK033(gi)001:3380: dag pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum las kyi bya ba /
NK033(gi)001:3381: smin pa grol bar byed pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs /
NK033(gi)001:3382: grol ba mthar phyin par byed pa rdo rje'i tshig lam dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:3383: dang po la phyi rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung dang /
NK033(gi)001:3384: nang rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:3386: tho rangs langs zin pa dang dri bzang gi chu la /
NK033(gi)001:3390: e ram bam d+ha ra shud+d+he a a a s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:3391: sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:3392: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:3393: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:3394: zhes pa nyi shu rtsa gcig btab la khrus bya /
NK033(gi)001:3395: dri chu bar pas kyang khrus dang cung zhig 'thung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:3396: de ltar byas pas dri ma dag /
NK033(gi)001:3397: lus shel sgong ltar gsal sing song bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:3398: nang rgya mtsho rtsa ba'i yig chung la dri chu
NK033(gi)001:3399: bar pa'i khrus la nang rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung
NK033(gi)001:3400: du gsungs shing / spyir 'di la yig cha rgyas pa zur du yod do //
NK033(gi)001:3402: dbang gi skabs su bum chus khrus byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3403: gnyis pa sgo gsum las kyi bya ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3406: sems spros bral du 'jog pa dang gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:3409: de'i steng du sna tshogs pad+ma /
NK033(gi)001:3410: de'i steng du zla ba dang nyi ma /
NK033(gi)001:3411: de'i steng du rang nyid skad cig gis he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po /
NK033(gi)001:3412: sku mdog smug nag khro chags kyi rnam pa /
NK033(gi)001:3413: phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa dpung pa'i thad du 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:3414: g.yon yum swa ti badz+ra la 'khyud nas dngul dkar gyi dril bu bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:3415: thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang /
NK033(gi)001:3416: rgyan cha sna tshogs pas brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:3417: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil krung lhod pa byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:3418: yum yang sku mdog smug nag phyag g.yas pas yab
NK033(gi)001:3419: kyi g.yon phyogs nas 'khyud cing g.yon thod khrag yab
NK033(gi)001:3420: kyi zhal du stob pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin cing zhabs
NK033(gi)001:3421: sems skyil lam / 'khyud pa gang rung bya /
NK033(gi)001:3422: rgyan gtso bo dang mthun pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3423: rang mngon rdzogs rgyal por gsal ba'i dpral bar /
NK033(gi)001:3424: mgrin par +aah snying gar pad 'dab kyi ze'u 'bru'i steng du nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK033(gi)001:3428: de'i mtha' nang bskor du rdzogs rim gyi sngags /
NK033(gi)001:3431: rgyab tu hoh g.yon du 'i bzhi po stan la
NK033(gi)001:3432: khab btsugs pa bzhin langs thabs su yod pa klog
NK033(gi)001:3433: pa'i tshul gyis ci nus bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:3435: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:3436: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:3437: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:3438: zhes pa bskyed rim gyi sngags yin pas gong bzhin klog /
NK033(gi)001:3439: yi ge rnams 'od kyi gong bur gsal ba las 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)001:3440: mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma yi dam sangs rgyas
NK033(gi)001:3441: dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dpag tu med pa
NK033(gi)001:3442: spyan drangs / gang gi drin gyi dang /
NK033(gi)001:3445: thams cad rdzogs pa'i byang chub phyir bsngo'o'i bar dang /
NK033(gi)001:3448: thun 'jog khar snying ga'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)001:3449: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten 'od du zhu /
NK033(gi)001:3450: nang bcud kyi sems can la thim /
NK033(gi)001:3451: de gser gyi sa gzhi la /
NK033(gi)001:3456: thod skam phyag mtshan rnams sku la /
NK033(gi)001:3458: mas nas yar thim pas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK033(gi)001:3466: de dmigs med du song ba'i spros bral gyi ngang du gnas par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3468: dge ba 'di yis myur du bdag /
NK033(gi)001:3469: mngon rdzogs rgyal po 'grub gyur nas //
NK033(gi)001:3470: sogs kyis bsngo ba yang bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3471: gnyid nyal khar mngon rdzogs yab yum 'od kyi gong bur bsam la nyal lo //
NK033(gi)001:3472: gsum pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la /
NK033(gi)001:3478: thun mong ma yin pa gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:3481: bskyed rim gsal la yun thung bar bya /
NK033(gi)001:3483: pa gor bee ro tsa nas spang mi pham mgon
NK033(gi)001:3484: po la gnang bar tha snyad de 'dra med na'ang
NK033(gi)001:3485: / snyan brgyud kyi gdams pa gzhan las /
NK033(gi)001:3487: nyams su len pa'i gnad drug bshad pa las /
NK033(gi)001:3491: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:3498: rgya che ba nam mkhar spar bas bzung ba dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:3499: dang po la don dam pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3502: sems nyid zab gsal gnyis med yin la /
NK033(gi)001:3504: gang du gtad pa'i nam mkha' yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:3505: las dang po ba'i dus su gnyis pa la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:3507: dang por a dkar po yin zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3508: gnyis pa du ba la sogs pa'i stong gzugs ji snyed byung ba rnams yin /
NK033(gi)001:3511: gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa'i sems dang gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:3512: lus kyi gnad gzir ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:3513: lus skyil krung cung zhig tsog pur byas la /
NK033(gi)001:3514: lag mthil gnyis dpyi zur gnyis nas mthil sa la phabs pas /
NK033(gi)001:3515: mthil bzhis la phab pa zhes bya /
NK033(gi)001:3516: 'di la seng ge'i 'dug stangs zhes kyang bya /
NK033(gi)001:3518: rlung rang babs su 'jog pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3519: gtad pa'i 'ben la gzugs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3521: lta stangs hur pa byas la yun thung bar 'jog /
NK033(gi)001:3522: de nas lha mi'i sems bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3523: sna'i thad kyi mtho phyed dang de'i tshod kyi nam
NK033(gi)001:3524: mkhar a dkar po chung la sran lkog phyed tshal
NK033(gi)001:3525: tsam mam / ci rigs la dmigs pa hril bsgril la /
NK033(gi)001:3526: ji tsam gsal gsal gyi bar la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:3527: yang bying rmug yongs la khad 'dug na /
NK033(gi)001:3528: dmigs pa med par lhod de bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:3529: de ma thag tu gong bzhin sgom /
NK033(gi)001:3530: legs par gsal snang byung rjes /
NK033(gi)001:3531: a med par de'i thad ka'i nam mkha' de la
NK033(gi)001:3532: sems ji gnas bzhag cing spros pa med par yang
NK033(gi)001:3533: yang blta ba ni byang chub sems dpa'i sgom pa'o
NK033(gi)001:3534: // de'i rjes su mi 'gyur ba'i gzhi bca' ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:3535: chos thams cad spros bral nam mkha' lta bur bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:3536: de las sems gzhan ma yin cing /
NK033(gi)001:3537: sems kyang de las gzhan ma yin par thag chod de /
NK033(gi)001:3539: chos rnams nam mkha' 'drar shes te //
NK033(gi)001:3540: nam mkha'i rang bzhin de ni sems bzung bya //
NK033(gi)001:3541: sems de sems ma yin par byas gyur na //
NK033(gi)001:3542: de ni bla med byang chub myur thob 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:3545: sngon 'gro gsal la yun thung bar byas rjes /
NK033(gi)001:3546: pa gor bee ro tsa nas /
NK033(gi)001:3547: spang mi pham la gnang ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3553: dus ni nyin gung mtshan gung la sgom mi skye bas mi sgom zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3554: snga dro kha nub tu bltas la /
NK033(gi)001:3555: phyi dro kha shar du blta /
NK033(gi)001:3556: rlung g.yon phyogs nas rgyu dus bya zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3557: ma rgyu na gzhog g.yas phab la cung zhig nyal ba dang g.yon la rgyu bas de dus bya /
NK033(gi)001:3558: de la yang ma skyes pa skyed par byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3559: bskyed pa bogs 'don par byed pa gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:3561: lus snga dro pus mo g.yon pa sa la phab /
NK033(gi)001:3565: mig sor bcu drug pa'i thad kyi nam mkhar lta stangs bya /
NK033(gi)001:3566: phyi dro lus gnad de las ldog cing kha shar la blta'o //
NK033(gi)001:3568: mig dang nge blta ba kun rdzob gsal ba'i brda /
NK033(gi)001:3569: de'i ngang nas stong gzugs sna tshogs snang ba don dam pa gsal ba'i brda1 /
NK033(gi)001:3570: mig 'bras mi 'gul ba kun rdzob kyi mi rtog pa'i brda /
NK033(gi)001:3571: de'i stobs kyis mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin skye ba don dam pa'i mi rtog pa'i brda2 /
NK033(gi)001:3572: 'og rlung cung zad 'then pa kun rdzob bde ba'i brda /
NK033(gi)001:3573: de'i dus su brjod du med pa'i sems bde ba skye ba don dam pa'i bde ba'i brda3 /
NK033(gi)001:3574: lce gang la'ang ma reg par gnas pa kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i brda /
NK033(gi)001:3575: de dus sems skad cig ma'i steng du bde gsal
NK033(gi)001:3576: mi rtog pa gsum dbyer med du stong pa'i sems
NK033(gi)001:3577: la ldan pa don dam pa'i dbyer med brda 4zhes
NK033(gi)001:3578: bya ste / bde gsal mi rtog stong pa'i ngang //
NK033(gi)001:3579: zhes pa'ang 'di lta bu gcig gi dus la nges par dgos so //
NK033(gi)001:3580: 'di dus bla mas gdams pa 'di las zab pa yod re zhes mna' bskyel ba'i dus /
NK033(gi)001:3581: slob mas mgo 'jog byed pa'i dus yin /
NK033(gi)001:3582: sems gsal stong du shar ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3583: dam pa sangs rgyas rtsa ba zin pa zer /
NK033(gi)001:3584: de ltar bsgom pas stong gzugs kha dog sna tshogs
NK033(gi)001:3585: su 'char bas gang shar gyi steng du bsgom pa
NK033(gi)001:3586: yin te stong gzugs gang byung yang /
NK033(gi)001:3587: chos sku 'grub pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK033(gi)001:3588: spyir snang ba thams cad sems can la nyon mongs
NK033(gi)001:3589: pa las snang ba a 'thas ma dag pa'i snang
NK033(gi)001:3590: ba / rnal 'byor pa la ting nge 'dzin nyams kyi snang ba /
NK033(gi)001:3591: sangs rgyas la dag pa'i snang ba chos sku 'ba' zhig tu snang ba yin la /
NK033(gi)001:3592: da ltar gyi gzugs sgra dri ro'i las snang thams cad dang /
NK033(gi)001:3593: stong pa nyid kyi gzugs brnyan chu la chu bzhag dang /
NK033(gi)001:3594: mar la mar bzhag gi tshul du yod pa la /
NK033(gi)001:3595: man ngag 'di dang rdo rje'i rnal 'byor yan lag
NK033(gi)001:3596: drug pa lta bus btsan thabs su nyams su blangs
NK033(gi)001:3597: pas stong gzugs gsal bar snang ba yin cing /
NK033(gi)001:3598: ma blangs dus byung ba 'dres mar snang /
NK033(gi)001:3599: las snang byung na de la a 'thas su zhen pas 'khor ba'i rgyu byed /
NK033(gi)001:3600: stong gzugs shar ba'i steng du mnyam par bzhag na las snang dag ste /
NK033(gi)001:3601: ye shes kyi snang ba skye ste chos sku'i ngang du gnas pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3602: de yang zung 'jug rab tu mi gnas pa'i dbu ma'i lugs kyi /
NK033(gi)001:3603: las snang log kyang stong gzugs mi log pas /
NK033(gi)001:3604: sangs rgyas la stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa la sogs
NK033(gi)001:3605: yon tan thams cad zung 'jug gi ye shes de
NK033(gi)001:3606: la gsal mdangs su ldan pa yin gyis /
NK033(gi)001:3607: tha dad pa'i tshul ma yin /
NK033(gi)001:3608: snang med rab tu mi gnas pa'i lugs kyis /
NK033(gi)001:3609: sangs rgyas pa'i tshe snang ba thams cad log ste
NK033(gi)001:3610: stobs sogs ci yang med pa'i snum zad mar me
NK033(gi)001:3611: lta bu / las zad chos zad rang bzhin med
NK033(gi)001:3612: tsam gyi stong nyid kho na gnyis ka dpe sbrul
NK033(gi)001:3613: lta bu / la mdzad de / sbrul gyi 'jigs pa'i sar thag khra sbrul du 'khrul pa'i tshe /
NK033(gi)001:3614: zung 'jug gi dbu ma ba 'khrul pa log pa'i tshe snang ba thag khra yong gsung /
NK033(gi)001:3615: snang ba med pas de'i tshe snang ba thag khra dang 'khrul pa gnyis ka med par bzhed /
NK033(gi)001:3616: dwags po'i bka' brgyud pa zung 'jug gi dbu ma dang mthun pas /
NK033(gi)001:3617: lhan cig skyes pa zhes pa chos gang dang gang gi gshis /
NK033(gi)001:3618: stong pa dang gsal ba lhan cig skyes pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3619: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes la ji lta ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:3621: dang po chos thams cad rang bzhin stong nyid rtogs pa la bya /
NK033(gi)001:3622: gnyis pa chos thams cad kyi stong nyid ma yin dgag rtogs pa'i cha la zer /
NK033(gi)001:3623: des na stong gzugs sna tshogs 'char ba 'di la /
NK033(gi)001:3625: stong nyid mig gis mthong ba gal che /
NK033(gi)001:3626: bem po'i stong nyid kyi sa lam mthar thug mi chod gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:3627: skyes pa bogs 'don par byed pa la /
NK033(gi)001:3628: bye brag 'byung pa so so'i rlung bsgom pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3630: dang po 'byung ba che'i rlung cha snyoms par gang
NK033(gi)001:3631: rung re re'i rlung shed che nas rlung kha rengs
NK033(gi)001:3633: de yang sa shas che na lus lci /
NK033(gi)001:3638: rlung shas che na 'gro ba dang smra ba la dga' /
NK033(gi)001:3641: dran pa med par gnyid du 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3642: me shas che na rgod pa dang 'phro /
NK033(gi)001:3643: de tsho gang shas che yang sgom mi chags pas /
NK033(gi)001:3644: rlung shas che na snga dro rlung gi dus sa sgom ste /
NK033(gi)001:3645: rkang pa'i mthe bong gcig thog tu gcig bzhag ste /
NK033(gi)001:3646: lag pa gnyis dpung pa la 'khyud /
NK033(gi)001:3647: lag pa'i mtheb chen gnyis kyi dpung pa'i nang rtsa gnyis mnan te /
NK033(gi)001:3651: lta stangs mthur la blta ste /
NK033(gi)001:3652: lte ba sa ser po lci ba gcig la'am /
NK033(gi)001:3653: thig le ser po gcig la sems gtad de /
NK033(gi)001:3656: thig le la rlung sems thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:3657: lan gcig gnyis kyi ting nge 'dzin skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:3658: phyi dro chu'i dus me sgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3659: 'dug stangs rkang pa brkyang bskum gang bde bya /
NK033(gi)001:3665: spyi bo nas mtho gang tsam na ram yig dmar
NK033(gi)001:3666: po'am thig le dmar po tsha zhing bsreg pa la
NK033(gi)001:3667: sems gtad / rlung 'jam pa gcig lte 'og rngub /
NK033(gi)001:3668: ma thub par gtong dus spyi gtsug tu bug pa
NK033(gi)001:3669: ha re ba nas rlung sems thon thig le la
NK033(gi)001:3670: thim par bsam / lan gsum bzhi tsam gyis chog /
NK033(gi)001:3671: srod me'i dus su chu bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3674: bam yig dkar po'i chu'i rang bzhin can gcig la sems gtad /
NK033(gi)001:3678: rlung sems lte ba'i thig le la thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:3679: lan gsum gyi ting nge 'dzin skye /
NK033(gi)001:3680: tho rangs sa'i dus su rlung bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3681: lus gnad lta stangs byings dang 'dra bar byas /
NK033(gi)001:3683: yam ljang gu rlung gi rang bzhin la sems gtad /
NK033(gi)001:3684: rlung shugs che bar rngubs la /
NK033(gi)001:3685: lte ba'i 'og gi thig le la rlung sems thim par bsam pa lan gsum tsam bya /
NK033(gi)001:3686: spyi'i gegs sel ba rkang pa gshibs lag pa gnyis bsnol spyi gtsug tu bkab /
NK033(gi)001:3688: lte ba'i thad du kha dog lnga ldan zhig la sems gtad /
NK033(gi)001:3689: rlung gcig rngubs lte ba'i la rlung sems thim par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:3690: de ltar byas pas zla ba lta bu'i rtags 'char /
NK033(gi)001:3691: de'ang dang por me long tsam /
NK033(gi)001:3694: de nas yul khams thams cad zla ba lta bu'i nang du 'char /
NK033(gi)001:3695: de nas nyi ma lta bu'i rtags sogs gong dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:3696: 'di'i skabs su nyin mtshan gyi bye brag mi phyed pa 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3697: de nas rang lus la grib ma mi 'byung /
NK033(gi)001:3699: re kh+aa nag po yungs 'bru tsam gyi nang du
NK033(gi)001:3700: dang po rang gi yi dam gang yin gcig gi
NK033(gi)001:3701: zhal mthong / rjes shes la'ang de bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3702: de nas snang ba'i dngos po gang yin thams cad yi dam gang yin du 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3703: dngos po che ba dang chung ba /
NK033(gi)001:3704: yi dam che ba dang phra ba thams cad 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:3705: yun ring du gnas nas yal 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:3706: de dus yul gzung ba rang bzhin med par rtogs /
NK033(gi)001:3707: de la nag po skra tsam mthong ba la stong nyid mngon sum pa zhes bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:3708: de re che re mang dang /
NK033(gi)001:3709: re zung 'byung ba la nyams gong 'phel /
NK033(gi)001:3710: de brtan por song ba la rig pa tshad la phebs pas /
NK033(gi)001:3711: re khwa de sbrul 'gros dang 'dra ba 'byung ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3712: chos rje rang byung rdo rjes /
NK033(gi)001:3713: rig pa lu gu rgyud ces gsungs te /
NK033(gi)001:3714: rig pa gsal dwangs nyid yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:3715: re kh+aa skra'i rtse tsam gyi nang du srid gsum dang /
NK033(gi)001:3717: de sems spros bral yin par shes pa la chos
NK033(gi)001:3718: nyid zad sar 'khyol ba zhes bya ba yin no
NK033(gi)001:3719: // yungs 'bru tsam gyi nang du srid gsum 'char ba la snang ba 'phros te /
NK033(gi)001:3720: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dpag tu med par phyin /
NK033(gi)001:3723: de yang de lta bu byas pa'i go chod pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3724: 'di lta bu la don dam pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:3725: gong gi rgya che ba'i nam mkha' spar bas bzung ba zhes bya ba dang don gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:3726: de yang don la sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams de
NK033(gi)001:3727: dag tu phyin pa med par rang rig sems gsal
NK033(gi)001:3732: gsum pa rjes la rgyun du bskyang ba'i nyams len ni /
NK033(gi)001:3733: nyin mo snang ba rgya yis 'debs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3734: mtshan mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa gnyis las /
NK033(gi)001:3737: bsre ba bzhi'i sgo nas nyams su blangs ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3738: dang po gnyid khra lhag gis sad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3739: sngar bzhin mngon rdzogs rgyal po rang nyid bsgom la /
NK033(gi)001:3741: nang rgya mtsho khrus dmigs pas byas la /
NK033(gi)001:3742: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad e wam
NK033(gi)001:3743: m+aa y+aa zhes pa'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlab snyam
NK033(gi)001:3745: ngag tu yang tshar kha yar 'don /
NK033(gi)001:3746: de nas zhwa gyon dus bla ma spyi gtsug tu 'bral med du bzhugs par mos pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3747: gos gyon dus sra ba brtan pa rdo rje'i gos yin snyam pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3748: ske rag la'ang rdo rje'i ka nan dang /
NK033(gi)001:3749: zas la longs spyod dus rang nyid he ru ka ser po sngar bzhin bsam la /
NK033(gi)001:3750: mgrin par e wam m+aa y+aa zhes pa'i sngags bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:3751: bla ma yi dam sangs rgyas byang sems thams cad mchod snyam pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3752: gzugs thams cad gzugs kyi lha mo dang /
NK033(gi)001:3756: reg bya thams cad de dang de'i lha mor mos te /
NK033(gi)001:3757: bla ma yi dam mchod par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:3758: skabs su bar do yin nam ma yin brtags pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3759: da lta'i snang tshul dang khyad ci 'dug /
NK033(gi)001:3760: de yang bar do la brtags thabs drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:3761: gnas gcig tu bar do'i sems can yun ring du mi 'dug ste /
NK033(gi)001:3763: de bzhin du lus la grib ma dang rkang rjes mi 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:3764: bde sdug ci yin kyang yun mi brtan /
NK033(gi)001:3765: rmi lam ltar snang ba 'gyur rkyen /
NK033(gi)001:3766: mi yin 'phro la khyi ru 'gro ba la sogs srid /
NK033(gi)001:3767: bar do dang rmi lam brtags pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:3768: bag chags sbyong sla ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3769: da ltar bag chags sbyong ba lcags me la bsregs pa dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:3771: rmi lam shing me la bsregs pa dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:3772: srol ba lus yod pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:3773: bar dor ras bal bsregs pa dang 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:3774: thal ba yang mi lus par bar do longs sku'i zhing khams zer /
NK033(gi)001:3776: gnyis pa bsre ba bzhi'i sgo nas nyams su blang ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3777: snang ba dang gsal ba bsre ba /
NK033(gi)001:3778: rtog pa dang mi rtog pa bsre ba /
NK033(gi)001:3779: sdug bsngal dang bde ba bsre ba /
NK033(gi)001:3780: sna tshogs dang dbyer med bsre ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3782: snang ba ci shar yang sems stong gsal de'i rang mdangs su bltas la de'i ngang la bzhag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3785: rig pa mig tu bcug pa'i tshul gyis /
NK033(gi)001:3786: mig 'bras mi 'gul ba la sems gtad de 'jog pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3788: sdug bsngal gyi rnam pa gang byung yang /
NK033(gi)001:3789: de'i ngo bo la sems bzhag nas /
NK033(gi)001:3790: sngar gyi 'og rlung cung zad 'then pa'i lus yod du mi tshor ba'i bde ba de dang basre'o //
NK033(gi)001:3792: sems skad cig ma'i steng du bde gsal mi rtog pa gsum dbyer med du yod pas /
NK033(gi)001:3793: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de'i rgya
NK033(gi)001:3794: las ma 'das par thag bcad de dran pa'i rgyun
NK033(gi)001:3795: skyong ba'o // gnyis pa mtshan mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3796: gnyid la 'gro la khad du rang gi snying gi dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:3797: de'i dbus su gdan ser po gcig gi steng du he ru ka ser po gcig sngar bzhin bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:3799: e wam m+aa y+aa zhes pa 'od zer gyi rnam par bsgom ste /
NK033(gi)001:3800: gnyid du 'gro ba dang dus mtshungs par yig 'bru
NK033(gi)001:3801: rnams 'od zer gyi rnam pas he ru ka la
NK033(gi)001:3802: thim / de yang 'od zer gyi rnam par gyur
NK033(gi)001:3803: te de'i ngang la nyal ba dang rmi lam zin
NK033(gi)001:3805: las kyi 'brel ba chod pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:3806: bzhi pa grol ba mthar phyin par byed pa rdo rje'i tshig lam la /
NK033(gi)001:3807: mi 'gyur ba'i gzer bzhi gdab pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:3808: a skye ba med pa'i don gyis blta ba'i tshul gtad pa /
NK033(gi)001:3809: ha 'gag pa med pa'i don gyis brda bzhi bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)001:3810: ho mi 'gyur ba'i don gyis gzer bzhi gdab pa /
NK033(gi)001:3811: 'i sna tshogs pa'i don gyis sems kyi bzhag thabs bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3813: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems nyid
NK033(gi)001:3814: gdod ma'i ye shes kyi rang gdangs su thag chod
NK033(gi)001:3815: pa / dper na rdzing la 'phur ba'i bya rog bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3817: de lta bu'i chos nyid las skad cig kyang mi yengs pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:3818: dpe ni mda' mkhan bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3820: lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi kar blta ba las ma
NK033(gi)001:3821: yengs bzhin du bde sdug btang snyoms gsum la blang
NK033(gi)001:3822: dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:3823: dpe ni byis pa bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3829: skye ba med pas gnyug ma /
NK033(gi)001:3830: gdod ma nas gnas pas tha mal gyi shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:3831: mthar 'gag pa'i gnas med par so ma /
NK033(gi)001:3832: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu thams cad 'byung bas lhug pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:3833: dpe ni rang thag chu skor bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:3834: gsum pa bsgom 'bras tshad la dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:3835: de ltar thugs nyams su bzhes pas /
NK033(gi)001:3836: rnal 'byor ba'i ting nge 'dzin la nyams gsum phye ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:3837: rtse gcig sgyu ma lta bu'i nyams /
NK033(gi)001:3838: ro gcig stong pa nyid kyi nyams /
NK033(gi)001:3839: spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i nyams gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:3841: sgom pa'i stobs kyis du ba la sogs pa'i stong
NK033(gi)001:3842: gzugs ji snyed shar ba rnams snang la rang bzhin
NK033(gi)001:3843: med par rjes la'ang nges shes 'dren nus pa'i myong
NK033(gi)001:3844: ba brtan por song ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3846: sngar gyi stong gzugs rnams dang las snang gi gzugs
NK033(gi)001:3847: rnam snang ba nyid nas spros pa'i mtshan ma thams
NK033(gi)001:3851: snang stong ro gcig gi zung 'jug tu shar ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:3853: re kh+aa nag po skra'i khyon gyi tshad tsam la /
NK033(gi)001:3854: srid pa gsum dang dus gsum gyi bkod pa dang snang ba shar zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3855: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dpag tu med par phyin nas /
NK033(gi)001:3856: chos nyan pa sogs bsags sbyang dpag tu med pa byed nus pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:3857: 'di lta bu la don dam pa'i rnal 'byor pa zhes bya zhing /
NK033(gi)001:3858: gong gi rgya che ba'i nam mkha' spar bas bzung ba dang don gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:3859: de ltar lam 'dir zhugs nas dam tshig dang sdom pa ma nyams na /
NK033(gi)001:3860: tha ma'ang skye ba bdun la sangs rgyas te /
NK033(gi)001:3862: gal te lam du zhugs pa 'chi bar gyur pa de'i tshe gzhan pa de'i skye gzhan la'o //
NK033(gi)001:3865: skye ba bdun gyi mthar thug pa /
NK033(gi)001:3866: brtson 'grus dang ldan pa ma yin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:3867: yang dag par ye shes ma bsgom yang nges pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3869: nya lcags kyus zin pa dang 'dra bar ye shes
NK033(gi)001:3870: myur du skye bar bcom ldan 'das kyi nges pa'o
NK033(gi)001:3871: // dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i gsung gi snying po mchog /
NK033(gi)001:3872: snyan brgyud bdud rtsi'i thig pa blo gros bum pa gang /
NK033(gi)001:3873: skal ldan gdug bya'i lus stobs rgyas byed 'di /
NK033(gi)001:3874: blo yi nus dang sbyar te cung zad yi ger
NK033(gi)001:3875: zhwa dmar spyan snga chos kyi grags pas mdzad pa'o
NK033(gi)001:3877: de las byung ba'i rnam dkar dge ba des //
NK033(gi)001:3878: ma gyur nam mkha'i mtha' klas sems can rnams //
NK033(gi)001:3879: rdo rje theg pa'i lam bzang 'dir zhugs nas //
NK033(gi)001:3880: tshe 'di nyid la rdo rje 'chang thob shog /
NK033(gi)001:3883: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i skor la ///
NK033(gi)001:3885: he ru ka r+aa he ru ka yab yum sgrub pa'i gzhung /
NK033(gi)001:3886: dza bi ha ra sad+ha na /
NK033(gi)001:3888: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po sgrub thabs /
NK033(gi)001:3891: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:3892: bskyed rim rdzogs rim zung du 'jug pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:3893: mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i sgrub thabs bshad //
NK033(gi)001:3894: gu lang dbus rin chen gser brdal ba'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:3895: nyi ma zla ba pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang /
NK033(gi)001:3896: gzhal yas de nang rdo rje'i gdan gru gsum bsnol
NK033(gi)001:3897: ma zur drug la rdo rje med par de nyid
NK033(gi)001:3900: e bsnol de'i steng du chos 'byung gru gsum /
NK033(gi)001:3901: zur drug yig 'brur lte ba la'o //
NK033(gi)001:3903: bud+d+ha mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:3904: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku sngo ser //
NK033(gi)001:3905: rin chen rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:3906: ba ti sku la sngon po'i sham thabs can //
NK033(gi)001:3907: dbu skra cung zad mthur du 'phyang //
NK033(gi)001:3908: zhi ba'i mdangs la cung zhal zad khro //
NK033(gi)001:3909: g.yas phyag na rdo rje gser gyi rtse dgu pa bsnams pa //
NK033(gi)001:3910: g.yon phyag na dngul dkar gyi dril bu 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:3911: pa zhabs skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)001:3912: phyag de gnyis kyis yum swasti badz+ra la 'khyud //
NK033(gi)001:3914: yum bde stobs zhes byang sems ma rdo rje zhes bya /
NK033(gi)001:3916: yab dang 'khril sbyor phyag gnyis yab kyi gnya' gong du 'khyud //
NK033(gi)001:3917: sku mdog ser po yab dang 'dra dbu skra grol //
NK033(gi)001:3918: bdag nyid de ltar yab yum /
NK033(gi)001:3920: rdo rje gdan dang e bsnol lte ba la /
NK033(gi)001:3926: de'i mtha'am rgya yig gis bskor ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:3928: shin tu gsal bar bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)001:3929: de yi zhing khams bstan 'di rnams ni don ngo
NK033(gi)001:3930: bo gcig la gadulabya'i snang ba la he ru ka
NK033(gi)001:3933: shar phyogs dkar la lho phyogs mthing //
NK033(gi)001:3934: nub ni dmar la byang phyogs ljang //
NK033(gi)001:3938: bskyed tshul gong 'dra yab badz+ra he ru ka yum dkar //
NK033(gi)001:3940: lho phyogs bee d+aur+ya zhing khams mthing ga la //
NK033(gi)001:3941: bskyed tshul gong 'dra yab rat+na he ru ka yum mthing //
NK033(gi)001:3943: nub phyogs pad+ma r+aa ga la zhing khams dmar po la //
NK033(gi)001:3944: bskyed tshul gong 'dra yab pad+ma he ru ka yum dmar //
NK033(gi)001:3948: bskyed tshul gong 'dra yab karma he ru ka yum ljang //
NK033(gi)001:3950: de dag thams cad bskyed tshul ni //
NK033(gi)001:3951: cho ga'i yan lag ma yin te //
NK033(gi)001:3952: skad cig dran rdzogs tsam gyis ni //
NK033(gi)001:3953: rnam pa lha la rang bzhin med //
NK033(gi)001:3954: mtshan nyid spros pa thams cad bral //
NK033(gi)001:3955: brda bzhi'i steng nas nyams su blang //
NK033(gi)001:3956: rjes la sgyu ma lta bur ldang //
NK033(gi)001:3959: thugs ka'i la sngags 'dis bskor bar bsam la /
NK033(gi)001:3960: sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:3961: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:3962: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:3963: mi mi dang gdong ma 'phrad par sgrub na mkha' spyod dngos grub thob bo gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:3964: tshig bar ma chod par bzlas //
NK033(gi)001:3965: de la skyo bar gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)001:3966: bla ma dang yi dam dang mkha' 'gro dang gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:3967: gtor ma 'bul phyir mchod pa dang bstod pa dang
NK033(gi)001:3968: bshags yi ge brgya pa la sogs bdun rnam dag
NK033(gi)001:3969: bya / de nas spyod lam bya /
NK033(gi)001:3971: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub ni //
NK033(gi)001:3973: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i sgrub yang dag thugs kyi gsang /
NK033(gi)001:3974: thabs slob dpon a wa d+hu chos skyong gi rgyal po /
NK033(gi)001:3975: ti pa rdo rje chos kyis chos kyi rdo rje /
NK033(gi)001:3976: mdzad pa 'di yongs su rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:3979: dpal he ru ka mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po nyi
NK033(gi)001:3980: ma dang zla ba dang gzhal yas khang na bzhugs
NK033(gi)001:3982: shar nas bltas pas sku mdog dkar po /
NK033(gi)001:3983: kee ru lta bu'i dkar po'i mdog lta bu zhal
NK033(gi)001:3984: gcig phyag gnyis pa phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu
NK033(gi)001:3985: pa bsnams pa / g.yon na ka p+aa la klad
NK033(gi)001:3986: khrag gis bkang ba rdo rjes gyen pa yod pa'i
NK033(gi)001:3987: rtse mo dgu ni theg pa rim pa dgu dang
NK033(gi)001:3989: b+han+d+ha'i nang du btsug pa'i rtse mo dgu ni sa dgu rim gyis non pa'i rtags so //
NK033(gi)001:3990: dkrug cing zhal du gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:3991: dur khrod kyi chas dang rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:3992: zhabs kyis bgegs pho mo dri za byi chings su mnan pa /
NK033(gi)001:3993: lho nas bltas na sku mdog bee d+aur+ya'i mdog lta
NK033(gi)001:3994: bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa phyag mtshan gong dang
NK033(gi)001:3995: 'dra'o // zhabs brkyang g.yon bskum g.yas bgegs gshin rje /
NK033(gi)001:3996: pho mo byi chings su mnan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:3997: nub phyogs nas bltas pas pad+ma r+aa ga'i mdog lta
NK033(gi)001:3998: bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa phyag mtshan gong dang
NK033(gi)001:3999: 'dra'o // zhabs brkyang bskum bgegs klu pho mo byi chings su mnan pa /
NK033(gi)001:4000: byang nas bltas pas in+d+ra n+ai la'i mdog lta bu
NK033(gi)001:4001: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa phyag mtshan gong dang 'dra'o
NK033(gi)001:4002: // zhabs brkyang bskum bgegs gnod sbyin pho mo byi chings su mnan pa /
NK033(gi)001:4003: dbus nas bltas pas gu lam gser btso ma'i mdog
NK033(gi)001:4004: lta bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa brkyang bskum bgegs
NK033(gi)001:4005: lha chen pho mo byi chings su mnan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4006: de dag ni zhal mdog khros pa dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4007: de ni mtshan ma dbyings kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:4008: phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor bsgom pa ni de'i thugs kar sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba na /
NK033(gi)001:4014: 'a ljang gu de'i mtha' ma g.yas bskor du /
NK033(gi)001:4015: +amo sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4016: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4018: de ni phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor ces bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4019: zab pa chos kyi rnal 'byor bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4020: de kho na rnam pa lha'i rnam pa /
NK033(gi)001:4021: rang bzhin skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:4022: nyams myong bde ba chen po /
NK033(gi)001:4023: de nyams su shar ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4024: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4025: de'i yum swasti badz+ra bde ba stobs ldan ma ni /
NK033(gi)001:4026: sku mdog mthing ga zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
NK033(gi)001:4027: rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:4028: thod pa dum bu'i ske rags can spyi bo na
NK033(gi)001:4029: zla phyed kyi steng na sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan
NK033(gi)001:4030: pa phyag g.yas na thod pa'i d+aa ma ru bkrol
NK033(gi)001:4031: ba / phyag g.yon pas bdud rtsi'i b+han+d+ha dang kha t+w+aam ka dku la brten te bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:4032: rdo rje gdan gyi zur drug la phag mo /
NK033(gi)001:4037: tsan+di ka rnams g.yon bskor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4038: de dag gi phyag mtshan ni gtso mo dang mthun no //
NK033(gi)001:4039: zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum pa'i rting pas mtshan ma bkag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4040: g.yas brkyang ba'i mthe bong gis nyon mongs pa can
NK033(gi)001:4041: gyi yid kyi bag chags sogs byed kyi snod lha
NK033(gi)001:4042: mo dus mtshan ma sku mdog ljang gu rgyan thams
NK033(gi)001:4043: cad kyis spras pa nyon mongs pa'i yid bslu bar
NK033(gi)001:4045: de zhabs kyi mtheb chen gyis mnan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4046: de ni mtshan ma dbyibs kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:4047: phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK033(gi)001:4048: de'i thugs ka na gzhi dwangs ma don gyi snying po dwangs ma kun 'dus kyi thig le /
NK033(gi)001:4056: am pam ham yam h+r+aim m+aam hrem h+r+aim h'u h'u phata phata la g.yon bskor du 'khor ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:4057: de ni phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:4058: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK033(gi)001:4059: de nyid rnam pa lha'i rnam pa /
NK033(gi)001:4060: rang bzhin skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:4061: nyams myong bde ba chen por shar ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4062: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:4063: slob dpon chen po nyi ma'i seng ge'i 'od las
NK033(gi)001:4064: mtshan du bsgyur ba dpal a ba d+hu ti pa
NK033(gi)001:4065: chen po rdo rje chos kyis gsungs pa /
NK033(gi)001:4066: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po yab yum gyi sgrub thabs /
NK033(gi)001:4067: nyams su blang ba'i chos rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:4070: dus kyi brda' sna bug g.yon pa nas rlung rgyu ba'i dus so //
NK033(gi)001:4071: gnad kyi brda' rgyal chen rol pa'i 'dug stangs yi dam gyi lha bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:4073: mig sna rtser gsal ba'i brda /
NK033(gi)001:4077: lce dbyer mi phyed pa'i brda' /
NK033(gi)001:4078: ya rkan la ma reg pa /
NK033(gi)001:4079: lus mi 'gul mi rtog pa'i brda' /
NK033(gi)001:4081: bde ba gsal ba mi rtog pa dbyer mi phyed pa gcig mi skye mi srid /
NK033(gi)001:4082: dpal chen po sku mdog ser po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:4083: phyag g.yas pas gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK033(gi)001:4085: yang na ka p+aa la bdud rtsis bkang ba rdo rjes dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:4086: dur khrod chas brgyad kyi sku la brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:4088: lha chen pho mo byi chings su mnan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4090: sku mdog yab dang mthun pa /
NK033(gi)001:4091: yang na sku mdog mthing ka g.yas thod rnga bkrol ba /
NK033(gi)001:4092: g.yon b+han+d+ha bdud rtsis gang ba yab la stob pa /
NK033(gi)001:4093: yab kyi thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' lha mo brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:4094: byang phyogs kha che'i gling nas sing+ga la'i yul gyi
NK033(gi)001:4095: rgyal po gzhon nu dpal gyi sras rgyal po nyi
NK033(gi)001:4096: mi'i seng ge'i 'od kyi yang dag thugs kyi sgrub
NK033(gi)001:4097: par dur khrod so sa gling du bsgrubs pas /
NK033(gi)001:4098: zhag bdun nas mngon rdzogs rgyal po rten gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa zhal gzigs /
NK033(gi)001:4101: yum mo swasti badz+ra bde ba stobs ldan ma rten
NK033(gi)001:4102: gzhan yas khang dang bcas pa zhal gzigs nas mtshan
NK033(gi)001:4103: bsgyur te dpal a wa d+hu ti pa chen po
NK033(gi)001:4104: rdo rje chos bya bar bsgyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:4105: de'i sras seng ge zla ba mkha' spyod du gshegs skad do //
NK033(gi)001:4106: des mtshan ri dwags rab tu gsal ba la bstan /
NK033(gi)001:4107: des rab zhi lo ts+tsha ba chos kyi shes rab la bstan /
NK033(gi)001:4108: des rkan blo gros dbang phyug la /
NK033(gi)001:4109: des rba sgom ye shes dbang phyug la /
NK033(gi)001:4110: des rgyal ba 'dzeng ston pa la /
NK033(gi)001:4111: des skye tshe ye shes dbang phyug la /
NK033(gi)001:4112: des bla ma ru ba chen po la /
NK033(gi)001:4114: des go ri ba blo ldan byang chub 'bum la /
NK033(gi)001:4115: des mtha' ston gzhon nu byang chub bdag la gnang ba lags so //
NK033(gi)001:4116: de la dang po'i zhal gdams /
NK033(gi)001:4117: sems gnas lugs de ma skyes na /
NK033(gi)001:4118: lta stangs kyis 'tshol ba gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:4119: gnas lugs rgyud la skyes tsam na //
NK033(gi)001:4120: blo bcas bcos mi byed pa gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:4121: nyams myong nang nas skyes tsam na //
NK033(gi)001:4122: rang gcig pur sdod pa gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:4123: dran pa glo bur ba byung tsam na //
NK033(gi)001:4124: de la skyon du mi lta ba gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:4125: don thog tu tha snyad stor tsa na //
NK033(gi)001:4126: de la the tshom mi za ba gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:4127: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i nyams kyi skyugs pa yin par gada'o ////
NK033(gi)001:4131: rin po che dbang gi man ngag nas /
NK033(gi)001:4132: nyi zla pad+ma brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK033(gi)001:4133: de nang rdo rje'i gdan steng du //
NK033(gi)001:4134: bud+d+ha mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:4136: nyi ma dang zla ba kha sbyar ba'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:4137: he ru ka mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:4138: g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK033(gi)001:4139: g.yon shel gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)001:4140: sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:4141: yum swasti badz+ra sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba la /
NK033(gi)001:4143: gzigs tshul rig 'dzin du gzigs pa /
NK033(gi)001:4144: bzhugs tshul zhi ma khro ru bzhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4145: de ni sha khrag lus po lta bu min te /
NK033(gi)001:4147: rang bzhin skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:4148: nyams myong bde ba chen po /
NK033(gi)001:4149: mtshan nyid gnyis su med pa /
NK033(gi)001:4150: bsam tshul skad cig dran rdzogs su bsgom pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4151: de ni bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug go //
NK033(gi)001:4152: +amo zhi ba'i sngags sh+r+ai badz+ra he ru ka h'u h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4153: 'gro drug g.yang sa gcod zhal gdams pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:4154: gsang ba'i dgra gsum bsad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4155: shing pa shing bal bu khug par skyes pa la zer gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:4156: la sha zhes bya ba bstan ma rang khug tu
NK033(gi)001:4157: skyes pa'i sna la yi ge k+shum bya ba bris
NK033(gi)001:4158: la / de'i logs la a n+ri su tri pre du bya ba bri'o //
NK033(gi)001:4159: de yang yi ge g+hi wang gi chus bri'o //
NK033(gi)001:4160: de bzhin du byas pa'i shing bu de mi dang
NK033(gi)001:4161: phyugs la sogs pa 'chi ba'i tshe sna bug g.yas
NK033(gi)001:4162: pa bkag la / bcom ldan 'das grong kha'i tshe
NK033(gi)001:4163: gzims lugs byas nas shi na nges par ngan song
NK033(gi)001:4166: shing rkam pa sha zhes bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:4167: seng ldeng la yi ge ha sa ni ri zhes bya ba rko mar bris la /
NK033(gi)001:4171: gu gul dkar po'i chu blugs la /
NK033(gi)001:4172: kha dog bsgyur la rang ske la gzhogs g.yon dngos su gdags so //
NK033(gi)001:4173: rang gi grib ma la gzhan gyis 'gom du mi rung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:4174: spyir yang thams cad la mi 'gong gsungs so //////
NK033(gi)001:4175: rin po che dbang gi man ngag ces pa bskyed
NK033(gi)001:4176: rdzogs zung 'jug gi gdams pa he ru ka mngon
NK033(gi)001:4177: rdzogs rgyal po'i yang dag gi phrin las sgrub pa
NK033(gi)001:4178: dngos gzhi tshogs lung dang bcas pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:4179: bcom ldan 'das he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal mngon rdzogs yab yum gyi sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)001:4182: gnas dben par dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)001:4183: mchod pa rnam pa lnga bdud rtsi ba ling rak+ta bshams la /
NK033(gi)001:4185: skyabs 'gro dang byams pa snying rje byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK033(gi)001:4186: de nas lung rnam pa bdun gyis nub gcig gis phrin las gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4187: dang po bgegs bsrung ba 'bar ba mtshams kyi lung du mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4188: bdag nyid dpal chen du gsal bar bskyed de /
NK033(gi)001:4190: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)001:4191: yang dag don la mi brtson zhing //
NK033(gi)001:4192: 'byung po dam med thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)001:4193: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK033(gi)001:4195: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:4196: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)001:4197: mtshon cha rang dpal he ru ka'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)001:4199: phyogs mtshams thams cad ra ba dang gur du gyur pa'i phyi ma me ri'o //
NK033(gi)001:4201: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:4205: k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:4206: a ko ta ya mut+ga ra h'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:4208: zhes mtshon cha lngas mtshams bcad /
NK033(gi)001:4211: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)001:4212: rdo rje'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:4213: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la //
NK033(gi)001:4214: rdo rje sa gzhi gcal du bkram //
NK033(gi)001:4215: bar snang rdo rje'i sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK033(gi)001:4217: rdo rje'i glog 'khyug khyugs se khyug /
NK033(gi)001:4218: rdo rje'i thog 'bebs lams se lam //
NK033(gi)001:4219: rdo rje'i me 'bar ya la la //
NK033(gi)001:4220: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK033(gi)001:4221: phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)001:4222: thams cad rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK033(gi)001:4223: rdo rje gtams pa'i gzhal yas 'dir //
NK033(gi)001:4225: chu la zags pa'i gsang med cing //
NK033(gi)001:4227: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4230: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:4231: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)001:4232: rdo rje 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams /
NK033(gi)001:4234: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla bre la /
NK033(gi)001:4236: steng yang ral gri'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)001:4238: steng yang phur pa'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)001:4240: steng yang dbyug tho'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)001:4242: me'i mtshams kyang de bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:4243: e ram phata ram dz+wa la ram /
NK033(gi)001:4244: zhes pas 'bar ba me'i dbus su bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:4245: de nas khro bo'i mtshams bcad par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:4247: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4248: dbus phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4249: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)001:4251: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)001:4252: khro mo'i sprul pa sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)001:4253: ma tshogs dbang phyug bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)001:4256: rgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)001:4257: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4260: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4261: shar phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4262: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)001:4264: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)001:4265: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)001:4266: ma tshogs dbang phyug bar snang gang //

NK033(gi)001:4273: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4274: lho phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4275: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)001:4277: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)001:4278: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)001:4279: ma tshogs dbang phyug bar snang gang //

NK033(gi)001:4283: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4286: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4287: nub phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4288: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //

NK033(gi)001:4291: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //

NK033(gi)001:4296: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4299: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4300: byang phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:4301: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //
NK033(gi)001:4303: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)001:4304: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)001:4305: ma tshogs dbang phyug bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)001:4308: rgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)001:4309: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4312: khro bos bar mtshams med par gtams par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:4314: nga ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:4315: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4316: chos rnams ye nas rang bzhin stong pa la //
NK033(gi)001:4317: rnam rtog 'khrul pa 'byung ba'i gzhi med de //
NK033(gi)001:4318: bgegs kyang rang gi sems las byung //
NK033(gi)001:4319: stong pa nyid kyis mtshams bcad do //
NK033(gi)001:4320: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK033(gi)001:4321: chos kyi dbyings las ma 'da' zhig /
NK033(gi)001:4322: stong pa nyid kyis rgyas gdab //
NK033(gi)001:4324: gnyis pa tshogs bsags sgrib sbyong gi lung du bshags pa tha mal pa dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK033(gi)001:4326: mdun gyi nam mkha' la yi dam lha tshogs bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:4330: mdun du chos skyong bsam la bshags pa bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:4332: dus gsum bde gshegs rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)001:4333: mtshan nyid don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4334: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK033(gi)001:4335: dam tshig mos gus chung ba mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4336: yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi bsnyen sgrub tshad du ma bskyal mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4337: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi mchod bstod gzhung ma
NK033(gi)001:4338: skyong ba ma sring mkha' 'gro rnams kyi gtor ma
NK033(gi)001:4339: dus su ma theng chos skyong srung ma rnams kyi
NK033(gi)001:4340: dam rdzas tshang bar ma bsags mthol mched dang lcam
NK033(gi)001:4341: dral rnams kyi dam tshig brtse gdung chung ba dus
NK033(gi)001:4342: gsum pha ma rnams kyi drin lan lan gyis ma
NK033(gi)001:4343: lon khams gsum sems can rnams kyi theg chen byang
NK033(gi)001:4344: sems chung ba zhes bshags pa dang bzod gsol bya'o
NK033(gi)001:4345: // gsum pa mchod rdzas byin gyis brlabs pa'i lung du byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4346: sman +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:4347: raka gtor +aahmh'u ma h+aa ba ling+ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:4348: +aahmh'u ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+dala h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:4350: ma gsum byin gyis brlabs so //
NK033(gi)001:4351: bzhi pa bdag nyid rtsa ba'i lung du yang dag mngon rdzogs zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la /
NK033(gi)001:4352: dang po ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4354: 'di tshe sangs rgyas bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4355: sku gsum de bzhin nyid sa la goms par bya //
NK033(gi)001:4356: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK033(gi)001:4357: dmigs pa med pa'i don cig bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:4360: kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK033(gi)001:4361: thams cad du ni khyab par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:4366: ba'i tshogs ni bsam par bya //
NK033(gi)001:4370: bam chu lam gser sum ri rab /
NK033(gi)001:4371: ram me b+h+r+aum gzhal yas khang /
NK033(gi)001:4374: 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK033(gi)001:4375: mngon par dga' ba'i rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)001:4376: nyi zla pad+ma 'od kyi kha sbyor nang //
NK033(gi)001:4377: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba yi //
NK033(gi)001:4386: mngon rdzogs rgyal po bud+d+ha sku mdog phyag mtshan yum dang mthun /
NK033(gi)001:4388: zhal gcig mchan khung na kha t+w+aam ga bsnams ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:4390: yab yum gnyis med bdud rtsi zhal du stob //
NK033(gi)001:4391: 'bar ba'i gar dgu khro tshul rdzogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4393: lam man+da la gdan nyi zla pad ma /
NK033(gi)001:4397: ma swur+ya man+da la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od dang bcas /
NK033(gi)001:4399: ba ti tish+tha man+da la chos 'byung dmar po /
NK033(gi)001:4401: b+h+r+aum pad+ma'i ge sar 'od zer lnga pa /
NK033(gi)001:4403: ke kha dog lnga pa shar ke ke ru dkar po /
NK033(gi)001:4405: bee d+aur+ya lho bee d+aur+ya sngon po /
NK033(gi)001:4407: pad+ma r+aa ga man+da la h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4409: in+d+ra n+ai la man+da la byang in+d+ra n+ai la ljang /
NK033(gi)001:4411: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru yab dpal chen /
NK033(gi)001:4412: ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi yum shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4413: badz+ra shar sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4414: rat+na lho sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4415: pad+ma nub sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4416: karma byang sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4417: rigs lnga yab yum koo r+ai sing ha sgo ma dbang phyug /
NK033(gi)001:4418: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4419: dpal chen he ru ka dur khrod chas brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:4420: de yang phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga nas bltas pas /
NK033(gi)001:4421: rigs lnga ru mngon pa la sangs rgyas rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa la dbus rnam snang /
NK033(gi)001:4422: don he ru ka gcig tu rdzogs pas na mngon rdzogs /
NK033(gi)001:4423: che zhing gong na med pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4424: de nas 'og min gnas nas ye shes sems dpa' spyan drang ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4426: 'og e bsnol zur drug la +aaham h+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum ham /
NK033(gi)001:4427: phag mo drug gi ngo bor bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4428: min bde gshegs pho brang nas //
NK033(gi)001:4430: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4431: e h+ya he bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4432: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4434: de nas bdag dam tshig sems dpas lha ye shes sems dpa' la phyag bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4435: mdun gyi nam makharabazhugasa pa la gtso bo la gtso bos 'khor la 'khor gyis /
NK033(gi)001:4437: mi gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa la //
NK033(gi)001:4438: bdud 'dul khro tshogs dag gi sku sprul pa //
NK033(gi)001:4439: bcom ldan dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK033(gi)001:4440: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:4441: a la la hoh a ti p+au hoh phra t+aits+tsha hoh ya mi /
NK033(gi)001:4444: lha ye shes pa dgyes nas sku gsung thugs kyis
NK033(gi)001:4445: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i lus ngag yid gsum la
NK033(gi)001:4446: byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4447: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i spyi bor ye shes sems dpa' bstim mo //
NK033(gi)001:4448: de nas bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4449: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK033(gi)001:4450: ye shes thugs rje bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4451: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru 'khor dang bcas //
NK033(gi)001:4452: dngos grub stsol phyir brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4453: gtso bo la gtso bo thim /
NK033(gi)001:4454: 'khor la 'khor thim pas gzi brjid nus pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4457: de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4459: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK033(gi)001:4460: bcom ldan dpal gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK033(gi)001:4461: sku gsum gnyis med bde chen rgya //
NK033(gi)001:4462: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4463: sku gsung thugs gnyis su med pa'i bde ba thugs su chud pa'i dngos grub /
NK033(gi)001:4464: a la la hoh zhes so //
NK033(gi)001:4465: de nas rigs lnga'i he ru ka la bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4467: dbus phyogs gu lang ser po gser gyi zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:4468: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:4469: bud+d+ha he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:4470: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4471: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:4472: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)001:4473: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)001:4474: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)001:4475: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)001:4476: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4477: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:4478: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4479: shar phyogs ke ke ru dkar po'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:4480: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:4481: badz+ra he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:4482: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4483: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:4484: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)001:4485: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)001:4486: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)001:4487: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)001:4488: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4489: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:4490: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4491: lho phyogs rin chen bee d+aur+ya sngon po'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:4492: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:4493: rat+na he ru 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:4494: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4495: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:4496: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)001:4497: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)001:4498: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)001:4499: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)001:4500: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4501: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:4502: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4503: nub phyogs pad+ma r+aa ga dmar po'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:4504: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:4505: pad+ma he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:4506: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4507: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:4508: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)001:4509: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)001:4510: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)001:4511: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)001:4512: de yang mi 'chab gnong pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4513: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes pa //
NK033(gi)001:4514: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4515: byang phyogs in+d+ra n+ai la ljang gu'i zhing khams na //
NK033(gi)001:4516: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:4517: karma he ru ka 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:4518: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4519: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:4520: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs su //
NK033(gi)001:4521: rang sems byang chub sems su ma 'byongs pas //
NK033(gi)001:4522: bdud rtsi chen po lags par ngo ma shes //
NK033(gi)001:4523: dngos grub chen po lags par zhal ma 'dzom //
NK033(gi)001:4524: de yang mi 'chab gnong ba'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4525: mthol bshags bzod pa dang du yar bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:4526: mi sgrib tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4527: de nas phyi'i mchod pa rnam pa lnga 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4528: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4529: badz+ra push+pe me tog dbu la /
NK033(gi)001:4533: badz+ra d+h+au pe bdug spos shangs la /
NK033(gi)001:4534: badz+ra +aa lo mar me spyan la /
NK033(gi)001:4535: ke badz+ra gan+d+he dri chab thugs khar /
NK033(gi)001:4536: badz+ra nee wi zhal zas zhal la /
NK033(gi)001:4537: d+y+aee badz+ra shap+da rol mo snyan la /
NK033(gi)001:4539: mngon rdzogs yab yum 'khor bcas la //
NK033(gi)001:4540: mchod pa 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4541: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4542: badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma de rnams rim pas 'agre'o //
NK033(gi)001:4543: rang he ru ka'i thugs kha nas mchod pa'i lha mo 'phros mchod pas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4545: de nas bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs pa'i sman mchod 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4546: bdud rtsi'i 'dzab bgrang la sman phud re sbreng la mchod pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:4548: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)001:4549: 'byung ba'i bcud bsdus 'bras bu bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK033(gi)001:4550: yum chen m+aa ma k+ai ru byin brlabs nas //
NK033(gi)001:4551: rgya mtsho chu klung mtsho bran man chad nas //
NK033(gi)001:4552: zil pa'i thig pa'i brlan gyi bcud bsdus te //
NK033(gi)001:4553: 'bru bcud stong la sbyar ba'i dza gad dpal bos bkang //
NK033(gi)001:4554: dus gsum rgyal ba yab yum mchod pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4555: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK033(gi)001:4556: 'gro ba ma lus thugs rjes bzung ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4557: nyon mongs dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK033(gi)001:4558: ji snyed bla ma yi dam dang //
NK033(gi)001:4560: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK033(gi)001:4561: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4562: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyi zhal du +aahmh'u /
NK033(gi)001:4563: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:4565: bcom ldan dpal chen yab yum dang /
NK033(gi)001:4566: lha mo brgyad kyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4569: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:4571: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal du +aahmh'u /
NK033(gi)001:4572: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4576: dpa' bo 'bru gsum tshul du ni //
NK033(gi)001:4577: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'di //
NK033(gi)001:4578: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4579: sku gsung thugs mnyes nas thod pa'i nang du dngos grub +aahh+aum byung /
NK033(gi)001:4580: rang gi mtheb srin gyis blangs la lce thog tu
NK033(gi)001:4581: bzhag pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par
NK033(gi)001:4582: bsam mo // +aahh+aum k+aa ya spyi bor /
NK033(gi)001:4585: sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta snying khar sid+d+ha h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4586: zhes bdud rtsi lce thog tu mtheb srin gyis blangs nas lan gsum bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:4587: de nas gtor ma'i p+au dza 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4588: dbang bzhi'i dus na rnal 'byor pa'i chas /
NK033(gi)001:4591: dam rdzas kyi chas rnams bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4595: dpal chen yab yum mchod pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4596: ma sring rgya mtsho ma lus brten pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4597: rdo rje slob dpon rgyal thebs king ka ra //
NK033(gi)001:4598: mched lcam 'dus pa'i g.yar dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4599: rin chen tshang ba'i gtor gzhong chen po ru //
NK033(gi)001:4600: zhal zas bdud rtsi sha chen dang //
NK033(gi)001:4601: rak+ta dmar dang dkar gyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:4603: zhing khams rgyas par bkang nas 'bul lags na //
NK033(gi)001:4604: sngags bdag chen pos byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4605: zhes gtor mar sman rag sbreng ngo //
NK033(gi)001:4606: brgyud pa'i bla ma ma rig pa'i mun sel /
NK033(gi)001:4607: rnam rtog thams cad sel bas so //
NK033(gi)001:4608: rnams kyi zhal du ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4609: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4610: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4611: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4612: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4613: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4614: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4615: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4616: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4617: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4618: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4622: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:4624: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:4625: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4626: de yang ma h+aa ni chen po /
NK033(gi)001:4628: kha ram snga mas stong gsum bdud rtsir bsgyur /
NK033(gi)001:4629: kha ram phyi mas bdud rtsi dang bcud kyi dngos po thams cad tshur la bsdus /
NK033(gi)001:4630: kh+aa hi zhes pas gang la 'bul ba rnams kyis zhal du stob par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4631: de rnams gtor ma'i mchod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4632: de nas rak+ta'i bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'bul bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4634: sngar byin gyis brlabs pa de /
NK033(gi)001:4635: chang phud dang sbyar te 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4637: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dgongs pa bsgrub pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4638: ma sring rgya mtsho ma lus brten pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4639: dpal chen ma mo'i thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4640: pad+ma zil thig dri dang sbyar ba yis //
NK033(gi)001:4641: dung chen dmar gyis bkang ba'i rak+ta 'di //
NK033(gi)001:4642: mnga' bdag chen pos bzhes la byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)001:4643: zhes pas gtor mar sbreng ngo //
NK033(gi)001:4646: thugs rje chags pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK033(gi)001:4647: 'gro ba'i don la dmigs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:4649: bla ma bde gshegs mkha' 'gro dang //
NK033(gi)001:4650: chos skyong srung ma ma lus la //
NK033(gi)001:4651: brtse ba'i sems kyis 'bul lags kyi //
NK033(gi)001:4652: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4653: ma h+aa rak+ta la kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:4655: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po phul bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:4657: de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4659: dpal chen yab yum gsal gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:4660: mi gnas dpal chen mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:4661: lha mo brgyad kyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)001:4662: rnam dag chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4663: sgyu ma'i phyag rgyar gsal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:4664: ces yi ge brgya pa tshar gcig brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:4665: de nas kha bskang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4667: ye shes mkha' 'gro'i dbang phyug khro rgyal gtso //
NK033(gi)001:4668: dpal chen he ru ka ni mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)001:4669: dus drug chos kyi sku las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4670: thugs dang 'gal bar mchis na bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4671: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)001:4672: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)001:4673: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)001:4674: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po ni chos nyid thugs su chud //
NK033(gi)001:4675: ma rig dbang gis de ltar ma rtogs kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4676: mi dge log pa'i las rnams ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)001:4677: bstan pa srung ba rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4678: 'da' ka khas blangs dam las g.yel gyur te //
NK033(gi)001:4679: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4680: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol /
NK033(gi)001:4681: sbyor sgrol mchod pa ting 'dzin ma bshams te //
NK033(gi)001:4682: kro d+hi shwa ri'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4683: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4684: rdzas dang phyag rgya mngon du ma gyur te //
NK033(gi)001:4685: koo r+ai ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4686: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4687: sha khrag mchod pa gzhung bzhin ma bshams pas //
NK033(gi)001:4688: sing ha ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4689: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4690: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ma gsal te //
NK033(gi)001:4691: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi yi thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4692: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4693: yo byad tshogs nas tshogs kyi phud nyams pas //
NK033(gi)001:4694: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4695: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4696: tshogs la rol nas lhag ma ma lus pas //
NK033(gi)001:4697: ma mo brtan ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4698: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4699: sku bskyed khro bo'i lus su ma gyur te //
NK033(gi)001:4700: sngags 'jug pho nya'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)001:4701: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4705: don lnga pa yang dag thugs kyi mngon rdzogs rgyal po la 'dzab dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4706: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i lung du ru lu'i 'dzab yang dag bsgrubs pas /
NK033(gi)001:4708: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK033(gi)001:4709: ru lu dbyangs drug bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:4710: de yang tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul /
NK033(gi)001:4711: za hor rgyal po'i dbyangs kyi skad /
NK033(gi)001:4713: rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgra /
NK033(gi)001:4715: 'khun cing gdung ba'i dbyangs dang drug go //
NK033(gi)001:4717: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro ti sku'i bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)001:4719: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:4720: pad+ma gsung sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4721: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4723: rat+na yon tan karma phrin las /
NK033(gi)001:4724: bzlas pa byed pa'i dus su gsal la dod par bzlas pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:4725: dus bzhir bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi'i tshul du ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral bar byed pa yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:4726: dang po bsnyen pa la bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)001:4731: de nas thun gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)001:4732: thun gsum pa la sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)001:4733: de nas sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK033(gi)001:4734: dbang bzhi'i sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la /
NK033(gi)001:4735: bla ma'i man ngag bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi bsnyen pa bya /
NK033(gi)001:4736: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4737: ru lu ru ru h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4739: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4740: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4742: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4743: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4745: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4746: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4748: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4749: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4751: de la 'di btags la bargya'am stong bzlas la /
NK033(gi)001:4752: a a sarba tath+aa ga ta ya h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:4753: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:4755: de nas me long gi nang du'am steng du yi ge a ham dkar dmar gnyis bsam par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4756: de yan chad sgrub thabs kyi dngos gazhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:4757: skabs 'dir bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum gyi gtor chog zur du bkol ba ltar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4759: drug pa za ba tshogs kyi lung du tshogs 'bul ba la don bdun te /
NK033(gi)001:4760: tshogs rnam pa gsum gyi sta gon bya ba /
NK033(gi)001:4761: bsang thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dri ram yam kham /
NK033(gi)001:4763: sbyangs thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dngos po dang mtshan ma med par sbyangs pa /
NK033(gi)001:4764: byin rlabs nor bu 'dod yon bdud rtsi gsum /
NK033(gi)001:4765: rnam pa gsum gyis khyad par gyi rdzas su brlabs pa /
NK033(gi)001:4766: spro thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dmigs pa so sor bzung ba /
NK033(gi)001:4767: dbul thabs rnam pa gsum gyis bdag gi don sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)001:4768: sbyangs thabs rnam pa gsum gyis bdag gi phrin las bcol ba dang bdun no //
NK033(gi)001:4769: byin rlabs kyi khyad par nor bu 'dod yon bdud rtsi gsum du byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK033(gi)001:4770: lha tshogs spyan drangs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:4771: mi dmigs mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)001:4772: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4773: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK033(gi)001:4774: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4776: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK033(gi)001:4777: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK033(gi)001:4778: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' dag dang //
NK033(gi)001:4779: ma mo'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK033(gi)001:4780: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK033(gi)001:4781: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4782: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:4787: ram ram ram ni ye shes me yin te //
NK033(gi)001:4788: me yi snying po ram zhes bya //
NK033(gi)001:4789: ram las ye shes me byung bas //
NK033(gi)001:4790: bag chags ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK033(gi)001:4792: yam yam yam ni ye shes rlung yin te //
NK033(gi)001:4793: rlung gi snying po yam zhes bya //
NK033(gi)001:4794: yam las ye shes rlung byung bas //
NK033(gi)001:4795: bag chags ma lus gtor bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:4797: kham kham kham ni ye shes chu yin te //
NK033(gi)001:4798: chu yi snying po kham zhes bya //
NK033(gi)001:4799: kham las ye shes chu byung bas //
NK033(gi)001:4800: bag chags ma lus bkru bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:4802: lhag mthong gi me yis bsregs //
NK033(gi)001:4803: ye shes kyi rlung gi gtor //
NK033(gi)001:4804: zhi gnas kyi chu yis bkrus so //
NK033(gi)001:4805: byin gyis rlabs thabs gsum ni /
NK033(gi)001:4808: bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po dri ma med par byin gyis brlabs so //
NK033(gi)001:4809: bsgral ba dgra bgegs kyi dug lnga /
NK033(gi)001:4813: 'di ni shes rab ral gri ste //
NK033(gi)001:4814: rin chen gter kha 'byed pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4816: dri med bdud rtsi 'byung ba dang //
NK033(gi)001:4817: dgra bgegs srog rtsa gcod pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4818: dug lnga rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4819: srog can rgyu dang srog med rgyu //
NK033(gi)001:4820: 'di ni srog med can rgyu yin te //
NK033(gi)001:4821: snying rje med pas bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:4823: tshogs phud tsho gsum du bcad de /
NK033(gi)001:4824: dang po g.yas zhal dkar ba la dmigs la zhi ba'i lha tshogs la mchod /
NK033(gi)001:4825: gnyis pa g.yon dmar ba la dmigs la thugs rje gshe ba'i lha la bshags /
NK033(gi)001:4826: gsum pa dbus mthing kha la dmigs la khro bo
NK033(gi)001:4827: rngams pa'i lha tshogs la stob par bya ba'i dang
NK033(gi)001:4830: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba 'di //
NK033(gi)001:4831: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK033(gi)001:4832: dbang po lnga yi longs spyod mkho dgur ldan //
NK033(gi)001:4833: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK033(gi)001:4834: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4836: gnyis pa thugs rje la dmigs nas bshags pa byas nas dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4838: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK033(gi)001:4839: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK033(gi)001:4840: lus kyis srog bcad sdig pa dngos su bgyis //
NK033(gi)001:4841: ngag gis rdzun smras gzhan la ngan du brjod //
NK033(gi)001:4842: sems kyis blo nor log par bsam la sogs //
NK033(gi)001:4843: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)001:4844: bkram pa'i lha tshogs rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4845: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)001:4846: de yi bka' 'khor gnas pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)001:4847: 'di 'dra dmyal sogs shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK033(gi)001:4848: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4850: gsum pa zhal dbus ma mthing ba la dmigs te
NK033(gi)001:4851: khro bo khrag 'thung gi tshogs la stob pa bya
NK033(gi)001:4853: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK033(gi)001:4854: khams gsum ma lus za ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4855: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:4857: nga ni khra 'thung chen po ste //
NK033(gi)001:4858: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:4859: dmar chen po la rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK033(gi)001:4860: 'khor gyi ma tshogs rnams dang rol //
NK033(gi)001:4861: dpal chen khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:4862: khro rgyal khrag 'thung rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4863: g.yo 'gul thams cad bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:4864: gzugs rnams thams cad he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:4865: koo r+ai la sogs za byed rnams //
NK033(gi)001:4866: sing ha la sogs gsod byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4867: rta gdong la sogs 'ching sdom tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4868: dbang phyug la sogs bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4869: pho nya la sogs 'joms byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4870: choms shig 'khor ba rtsad nas chom //
NK033(gi)001:4871: ha ha ru lu mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4872: zhes zhal du bstab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:4873: de nas tshogs zan tha ma des dgra bgegs kyi ling ga byas la bsgral ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4874: sdang dgra gdon bgegs su dmigs te /
NK033(gi)001:4875: gnod byed kyi dug zhi bar byed pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:4876: nyon mongs pa dug lnga ru dmigs la /
NK033(gi)001:4877: snying dkar nag mtshams sam 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod par bsam la bsgral te /
NK033(gi)001:4879: 'khor gyi dmag tshogs dam tshig can //
NK033(gi)001:4880: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4881: slob dpon la ni brnyas byed cing //
NK033(gi)001:4882: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed dang //
NK033(gi)001:4883: snying nas slob dpon smod byed rnams //
NK033(gi)001:4884: ma thogs myur du drag tu khug /
NK033(gi)001:4886: khro chung zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK033(gi)001:4887: mtshon cha'i rgyal po lcags kyu yis //
NK033(gi)001:4888: 'og min dga' ldan lha yul nas //
NK033(gi)001:4889: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:4891: khro chung mang po 'phros nas dgra bgegs gang na
NK033(gi)001:4892: yod pa lcags kyus bzung nas gzugs de la thim
NK033(gi)001:4893: par bsam mo // de nas rang nyid lha'i nga
NK033(gi)001:4894: rgyal dang ldan pas bar chad bsal ba'i phyir mtshon
NK033(gi)001:4895: cha sna tshogs kyis ling+ga de gtub la /
NK033(gi)001:4896: khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams la bstab par byas te /
NK033(gi)001:4899: 'jigs byed chen po'i tshul ston pa //
NK033(gi)001:4900: dpal chen dgu dang yum chen dgu //
NK033(gi)001:4901: gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK033(gi)001:4902: koo r+ai'i tshogs dang sing ha'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4903: sgo ma'i tshogs dang spor ma'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4904: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug chen mo'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:4905: phung po dpal gyi zhal du stabs //
NK033(gi)001:4906: 'byung ba yum gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4907: rnam shes koo r+ai'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4908: yul ni phra men zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4909: yan lag sgo ma'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4910: rus pa mkha' 'gro'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4911: khrag ni ma mo'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4912: sha ni pho nya'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4913: srog ni king chen zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4914: lhag ma 'khor gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)001:4915: yas kyi bdud g.yos mchod par bzhes //
