NK033(gi)001:4916: mas kyi sri langs mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4917: pha khu'i rgan sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4918: ma bu'i byung 'dre mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4919: bu tsha'i phung sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4920: rnal 'byor dam sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4921: sdang ba'i dgra rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4922: gnod pa'i bgegs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4923: sngags kyi sngags zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4924: chos kyi chos zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4925: bon gyi bon zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4926: rgya 'dre stong mtshams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4927: rmi lam ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4928: mtshan ma ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4929: sbyor ba rtsub pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4930: lo skag zla zur mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4931: za skag bdud zhag mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4932: mi mthun phyogs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)001:4933: mchod bzhes dam skongs mthu rtsal dngos grub stsol //
NK033(gi)001:4934: zhes ling+ga gtub pa de gtor mar dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:4935: bdun pa lhag ma mjug sdud kyi lung du lhag ma bsdu zhing gtor ma'i mjug bskyang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:4936: de la phud dang lhag ma'i mtshams sbyar ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4938: bcom ldan dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK033(gi)001:4939: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:4940: mi shigs sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4941: chags med pad+ma 'dra ba'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:4942: ma chags gsung gi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4943: 'gro drug thugs rjes sgrol ba'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:4944: skye med thugs kyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4945: 'gro drug smin mdzad bde ba'i don 'grub pa //
NK033(gi)001:4946: phrin las rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:4947: zhes brjod la mig btsum nas /
NK033(gi)001:4948: dmod bor la gtor ma'i nang nas gcig dngos grub blangs pas /
NK033(gi)001:4949: sha la babs na mthu che /
NK033(gi)001:4954: de nas rigs dbye ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:4955: mar gyi gnas bdun la mchod /
NK033(gi)001:4956: gnas ma dag gi shod lang+ka /
NK033(gi)001:4964: mgron dma' ba mar gyi gnas bdun la longs spyod dman pa lhag ma byin la /
NK033(gi)001:4965: byan mo'i tshul du brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4966: bran phud lhag par gsum bsre /
NK033(gi)001:4968: ya rkan ma rkan gnyis su rta mgrin yab yum gnyis bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:4969: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems dkar dmar bdud rtsir phab ste /
NK033(gi)001:4970: gtor ma bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs /
NK033(gi)001:4971: mo dang g.yog mo'i tshul du brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:4974: lhag ma byin gyis brlabs la /
NK033(gi)001:4975: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK033(gi)001:4976: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4978: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:4979: 'jig rten las kun khyed la bcol //
NK033(gi)001:4980: bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:4982: 'jig rten bya ba las grub pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4984: da dung 'jig rten rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'jig rten
NK033(gi)001:4985: las kun bcol ba'i las rnams phyogs bcur mgyogs pa'i
NK033(gi)001:4986: las byed pa'i // pho nya sum brgya drug cu yang //
NK033(gi)001:4987: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i ta krita lcam mor zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4988: 'bar ma chen mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4989: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i sha khrag zhal du gsol byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4990: dur khrod dregs pa'i ma bdun yang //
NK033(gi)001:4991: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i rgyal chen sring mor zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4992: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams kyang //
NK033(gi)001:4993: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i ri rab rmangs nas 'degs byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4994: dbang gi gru 'degs chen mo bzhi //
NK033(gi)001:4995: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i pha rol dmag dpung 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4996: dmag gi rgyal mo mched bzhi yang /
NK033(gi)001:4997: da dung rnam lnga'i 'jig rten bcol ba'i chos skyong srung mar dam bcas pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:4998: bod khams brtan ma bcu gnyis kyang //
NK033(gi)001:5000: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)001:5001: 'jig rten las kun khyed la bcol //
NK033(gi)001:5002: bcol ba'i las kun sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:5003: badz+ra ka la sa pa si b+h+yo //
NK033(gi)001:5005: de nas gtor ma tsho gsum du bgos te chos dbyings kyi gtor ma gter du sbed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:5007: thugs rje rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:5008: snang srid mtshan ma'i bye brag kun //
NK033(gi)001:5009: snod kyi 'jig rten dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)001:5010: snod kyang bcud kyi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)001:5011: snod bcud skye ba med par sba //
NK033(gi)001:5012: srid pa za byed gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)001:5013: rtsi shing bdud rtsi rang byung ste //
NK033(gi)001:5014: 'byung ba lnga dang rigs lnga yang //
NK033(gi)001:5015: chos nyid stong pa'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)001:5016: nyon mongs dug lnga'i ngo bo yang //
NK033(gi)001:5017: ye shes lnga yi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)001:5018: ma rig 'khrul pa'i log rtog kyang //
NK033(gi)001:5019: mnyam snang chen po'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)001:5020: rdzas rnams byang chub sems su bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:5021: sngags mkhan theg mchog rgyal por bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:5022: gnyis med gter du sba bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:5023: phyag rgya lnga yi rgya yis gdab //
NK033(gi)001:5024: de ltar sbas pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)001:5025: yab yum lnga yi phyag sbrel la //
NK033(gi)001:5026: lu gu rgyud kyi bro brdung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:5027: gtor ma cha gcig po de /
NK033(gi)001:5028: dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu gter du sba'o //
NK033(gi)001:5031: dngos grub 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:5032: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i mi zad pa'i gter du sba'o //
NK033(gi)001:5033: de nas ye shes rol pa'i gtor ma sbyin sreg tu 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5034: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro rnams me thab kyi gzhal yas khang du bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:5035: me mchod dam sbyin sreg tu byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5036: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i zhal du tshogs dang mchod pa dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:5037: thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor ma sa phyogs legs par dri spos dang /
NK033(gi)001:5038: dri mchog bzang po ru man+dala legs pa gcig byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5039: de'i steng du gtor ma bzhag la /
NK033(gi)001:5040: 'gro ba sems can gyi don du bdag gis phan
NK033(gi)001:5041: thogs par bya ba'i phyir ram phrin las rnam bzhi'i
NK033(gi)001:5042: don grub par bya ba'i phyir gtor ma bskyang ba
NK033(gi)001:5044: shar nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)001:5045: shar phyogs rdo rje rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:5046: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:5047: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:5048: dkar mo dung gi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)001:5049: phyag na dung gi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:5050: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)001:5051: khyod kyis zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)001:5053: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)001:5054: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:5056: lho nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)001:5057: rin chen rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:5058: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:5059: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:5060: ser mo gser gyi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)001:5061: phyag na gser gyi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:5062: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)001:5063: khyod kyis rgyas pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)001:5065: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)001:5066: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:5068: nub nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)001:5069: pad+ma rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:5070: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:5071: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:5072: dmar mo bse yi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)001:5073: phyag na bse yi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:5074: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di yongs la //
NK033(gi)001:5075: khyod kyis dbang gi las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)001:5077: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)001:5078: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:5080: byang nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)001:5081: las kyi rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:5082: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:5083: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:5084: sngon mo g.yu yi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)001:5085: phyag na g.yu yi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:5086: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)001:5087: khyod kyis drag po'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)001:5089: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //
NK033(gi)001:5090: bgegs rnams bsrung la rkyen rnams bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:5091: ces gtor ma sa gtsang sar spungs /
NK033(gi)001:5092: dri ma yal bar du sdud du mi gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:5093: gtor ma'i snod de rnams cha gsum du phye la /
NK033(gi)001:5094: cha gcig ma bshal bar kha yar la bstan la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:5095: nang du nas sam me tog gis bkang la /
NK033(gi)001:5097: des bkra shis pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)001:5098: cha gcig bshal chu phyir dor /
NK033(gi)001:5099: bshal chu la re ba'i yi dwags tshim zhing kho thag chod pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)001:5100: cha gcig mi bshal ba kha sbubs la /
NK033(gi)001:5101: dgra bgegs ting nge 'dzin gyis bkug la 'og tu bcug ste /
NK033(gi)001:5102: bro brdungs la mnan pa bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5103: bar chad zhi nas dgra bgegs mi ldang ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)001:5104: las kyi mjug bsdu bro brdung mnan pa byed pa'i dus su byin dbab cing /
NK033(gi)001:5106: dang po byin dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:5107: a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK033(gi)001:5108: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:5110: 'phags mchog thugs rje can gyi dus la bab //
NK033(gi)001:5111: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)001:5112: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)001:5113: byin chen dbabs pa'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)001:5114: mthu chen mthu rtsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)001:5115: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)001:5116: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)001:5117: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)001:5118: bdag cag las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:5120: de nas bro brdung ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5121: gtor gzhong kha sbubs pa'i 'og tu dgra bgegs bkug la /
NK033(gi)001:5123: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)001:5124: kun kyang bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:5125: bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam //
NK033(gi)001:5126: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)001:5127: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)001:5128: khro chung sprul pas bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)001:5129: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbyings na rol //
NK033(gi)001:5130: lta ba'i ngang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:5131: bro ni bar chad med pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)001:5132: tshangs pa'i dbyangs su 'dren pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:5133: glu ni bar chad med par blangs //
NK033(gi)001:5134: dkyil 'khor rang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:5136: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5137: nyon mongs lnga la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5138: dug lnga'i steng du sman lnga shar //
NK033(gi)001:5139: nga rgyal sa la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5140: nga rgyal spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)001:5141: 'dod chags chu la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5142: 'dod chags spangs nas bde chen shar //
NK033(gi)001:5143: zhe sdang me la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5144: zhe sdang spangs nas stong nyid shar //
NK033(gi)001:5145: phrag dog rlung la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5146: phrag dog spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)001:5147: gti mug nam mkhar bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5148: gti mug spangs nas ye shes shar //
NK033(gi)001:5149: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5150: khri gdugs brgya shar stong shar bas //
NK033(gi)001:5151: ye shes nyi ma gcig shar dro //
NK033(gi)001:5152: shar tsam nyid nas nub pa med //
NK033(gi)001:5153: nga ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:5154: rkang pa g.yas pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5155: rnal 'byor pho sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)001:5156: rkang pa g.yon pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5157: rnal 'byor mo sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)001:5158: rkang pa gnyis kas bro brdung pas //
NK033(gi)001:5159: rgyab nyan rkun bu mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)001:5160: rmig pa lcags kyis bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)001:5161: sa bdag sa srin mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)001:5162: sba'am de ni mi sba ru //
NK033(gi)001:5163: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du sba //
NK033(gi)001:5164: mnan nam de ni mi mnan na //
NK033(gi)001:5165: ri bo chen po'i rmang du mnan //
NK033(gi)001:5166: bskal pa brgyar yang ma ldang zhig /
NK033(gi)001:5168: brgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)001:5170: s+t+wam b+ha rak+sha m+aa ra ya nan /
NK033(gi)001:5173: glu gar bro la sogs pa'i bkra shis pa'i rol mo bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5174: rang don la ye shes pa mi gshegs /
NK033(gi)001:5175: gzhan don la ye shes pa gshegs so //
NK033(gi)001:5176: dam tshig gi lha gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa thugs kar bsdu /
NK033(gi)001:5183: de nas rdzogs rim brda' bzhi la gsal btab /
NK033(gi)001:5187: mngon rdzogs rgyal po yang dag gi gzhung gi phrin las rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:5188: bde ba stobs ldan ma'i sgrub thabs bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:5189: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:5191: sku gsung thugs kyi gdams ngag 'di la don gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:5192: dang po nyams myong skye ba'i dus dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:5193: nyams dang gzi mdangs bskyed pa'i dus dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:5194: bar chad sel ba'i dus dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:5196: rang nyid rnal 'byor ma dkar dmar bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:5197: nyams dang gzi brjid bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:5198: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge 'bru gsum spyi bor
NK033(gi)001:5199: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i lte ba la
NK033(gi)001:5200: ser po / lce pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi lte ba la +aahdamara po /
NK033(gi)001:5201: snying gar rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte ba la h+aum mthing ka gcig bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:5204: skad mo skad la rig pa gtad /
NK033(gi)001:5205: snang ba la ched 'dzin mi bya /
NK033(gi)001:5206: gnyis pa ni rnal 'byor dmar mo bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:5208: skad mo skad gdangs dang ldan pa la rig pa gtad /
NK033(gi)001:5209: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK033(gi)001:5210: gsum pa bar chad sel ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5211: rang nyid rnal 'byor ma nag mor skad drag po thog lta bu la shes pa gtad /
NK033(gi)001:5212: sku gsung thugs lam du blang /
NK033(gi)001:5214: brtul shugs kyi spyod pa lam du slongs /
NK033(gi)001:5215: sku gsung thugs kyi gdams pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:5216: rang byung bde ba che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:5218: rnal 'byor bde chen nyams su blangs //
NK033(gi)001:5219: tsit+ta rang gi rin ceen 'bar ba'i nang //
NK033(gi)001:5220: e bsnol a lo rang byung /
NK033(gi)001:5222: pad+ma rdo rje me rtse ltar gnas /
NK033(gi)001:5224: mtshon byed yi ge e bam ham mam hrim h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5226: tshogs drug don gyi snying po la //
NK033(gi)001:5235: mo'i sngags kyis 'od zer rgyun du bskul //
NK033(gi)001:5237: rdzas kyis mkha' 'gro ma rnams mnyes par bya /
NK033(gi)001:5238: byin rlabs dngos grub rgyun du 'byung //
NK033(gi)001:5239: skal ldan rnams kyis nyams su longs //
NK033(gi)001:5240: bde ba stobs ldan ma'i sgrub thabs //
NK033(gi)001:5241: mi g.yo mgon pos gsungs pa +thii //////
NK033(gi)001:5242: rdo rje zam pa'i mkha' 'gro rnam gsum gyi sgrub thabs bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:5246: dga' rab rdo rjes bka' la btags nas /
NK033(gi)001:5247: de nas rim par brgyud pa'i don //
NK033(gi)001:5249: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i bka' srung gi //
NK033(gi)001:5250: mkha' 'gro ma ni yin par bzhed //
NK033(gi)001:5251: mkha' la spyod ma'i mkha' 'gro ni //
NK033(gi)001:5252: rin chen rigs kyi bka' srung ni //
NK033(gi)001:5253: mkha' 'gro ma ni yin pa ste //
NK033(gi)001:5254: rnal 'byor pa yi dbul ba sel //
NK033(gi)001:5255: 'dod pa'i gter bdag kho na ste //
NK033(gi)001:5256: mkha' la gshegs ma phrin las kyi //
NK033(gi)001:5257: bdag mo kho na yin pa ste //
NK033(gi)001:5258: mdor na mkha' 'gro rnam gsum yin //
NK033(gi)001:5259: dam pa'i chos kyi srung ma'o //
NK033(gi)001:5260: de la mkha' 'gro ma bsgrub par 'dod pas /
NK033(gi)001:5262: gsang ba'i dbang zhu ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:5266: de la dang po gsang ba'i dbang zhu ba ni drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:5274: dur khrod dam ri khrod du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5275: man+dala mda' gang gru bzhi pa /
NK033(gi)001:5277: dbus chos 'byung dmar po gru gsum pa /
NK033(gi)001:5281: de'i khar thod pa mtshan ldan /
NK033(gi)001:5283: de nas rdzas bsags pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:5284: thod pa'i nang du chang dang byang sems dkar dmar /
NK033(gi)001:5285: bdud rtsi a mri ta blugs /
NK033(gi)001:5286: me long la sin+d+hu ras chos 'byung bri /
NK033(gi)001:5289: d+aa ki 'bar ba'i gdong can sku mdog mthing ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:5290: gcer bu spyan gsum skra grol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5291: thod phreng dang rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:5301: g.yon rin po che'i rkyal bu /
NK033(gi)001:5302: rgyan rin po ches brgyan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:5305: sku mdog dmar mo phyag g.yas gri gug /
NK033(gi)001:5307: dur khrod chas kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:5308: chos 'byung gi zur gsum du h+r+aihgasuma las bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:5309: de nas sngags bzlas pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:5310: mkha' 'gro spyi yi snying po bzlas pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:5311: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru h+r+aing h+r+aingah rat+na su ru r+aa ga /
NK033(gi)001:5312: ru ti h+r+aihh+aum ha sa ma ni ri /
NK033(gi)001:5313: pad+ma su ru r+aa ga ru ti h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5315: karma d+ha ki a be sha ya mo ha ni a d+ha ni stam b+ha ni h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5316: de ltar bzlas pa zhag gsum mam bdun bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:5317: bdag gi sku gsung thugs su /
NK033(gi)001:5319: yi ge'i dbang ni bgegs dang shes pa 'thibs na bya /
NK033(gi)001:5321: +aah h+aum ho ham h+r+aih klad pa dung khang du kha mthur la bltas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5323: snying khar h+aum kha mthur la bltas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5324: lte bar ho kha gyen la bltas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5325: spyi gtsug tu ham kha mthur la bltas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5326: gsang bar h+r+aihkha gyen la bltas pa bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:5328: gtor ma gtong na gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:5332: tshogs sha chang zan la sogs pa 'byor tshad bshams /
NK033(gi)001:5333: ram yam kham gsum gyis bsreg sbyangs bkru ba bya /
NK033(gi)001:5336: h+r+aihg+ha ta ya sarba dush+tana h+r+aimhphata s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5337: ha h+r+aihho ha ha hi hi phem phem phem /
NK033(gi)001:5338: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:5340: gtor ma phyi rol tu btang /
NK033(gi)001:5341: thod pa'i bdud rtsi sha chang rang gi bza' btung bya /
NK033(gi)001:5342: de ni gsang ba'i dbang zhu ba'i man ngag go //
NK033(gi)001:5343: gzhan dbang du bsdu ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5344: bdag rang yi dam lha'i nga rgyal byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5345: mdun du d+aa ki ma gsum bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:5346: d+aa ki ma gsum gyi thugs ka nas h+r+aihdamara po las 'od ljang gu 'phros /
NK033(gi)001:5347: bsgrub bya gang yin gyi snying khar yi ge n+ri bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5348: de las 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la hrimhgisa mtshan pa
NK033(gi)001:5349: gcig g.yon bskor du 'khor bar bsam zhing sngags 'di
NK033(gi)001:5350: bzlas so // rat+na d+aa ki ni su ru ru
NK033(gi)001:5351: ga ru ti h+r+aimhha sa ni ri pra men ku
NK033(gi)001:5352: ru h+r+aim h+r+aimh zhes mi tshig gis bar ma chod
NK033(gi)001:5353: bzlas so // par bzlas so // des 'dod pa'i don 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:5356: dri chen dri chu dmar chen m+aam sa dang //
NK033(gi)001:5357: rdo rje zil pa mdangs chen dang ni lnga //
NK033(gi)001:5358: dam rdzas lnga po ye nas gnyis su med //
NK033(gi)001:5359: sems can rnam par dag pa'i spyod yul te //
NK033(gi)001:5360: gnyis su med pa'i khrus chen 'di //
NK033(gi)001:5361: nyin mtshan kun tu spyod par bya //
NK033(gi)001:5363: smin mtshams su thig le bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5366: mtshams kyi dus su bsrung ba'i 'khor lo gdags /
NK033(gi)001:5367: ba ling la brtson par bya /
NK033(gi)001:5368: bar chad sel ba'i sngags ni /
NK033(gi)001:5369: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha dz+wa la ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:5370: badz+ra tsakra yak+sha mu le tsu le rak+sha rak+sha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:5371: 'khor lo bris la lus la gdags /
NK033(gi)001:5372: sngags ni gong mas bskrad do //
NK033(gi)001:5373: d+aa ki ni gsum gyi sgrub thabs slob dpon dga'
NK033(gi)001:5374: rab rdo rjes dur khrod gser gling he chen brdal
NK033(gi)001:5376: 'bar ba'i gdong can bka' yi gtso mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:5377: mkha' la spyod ma rin chen mkha' 'gro ma //
NK033(gi)001:5378: rnal 'byor pa yi dbul ba sel //
NK033(gi)001:5379: mkha' la gshegs ma phrin las mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:5380: mkha' 'gro ma yi dam tshig tu //
NK033(gi)001:5381: yug sa mo dang dme can bsrung //
NK033(gi)001:5382: 'di ni kun la med pas gsang la spyad par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5383: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa'i d+aa ki'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:5385: rgyu rkyen bzlas brjod kyi sngags bstan pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:5386: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK033(gi)001:5387: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK033(gi)001:5388: brjod pa las kyi sngags dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:5389: dang po rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags ni /
NK033(gi)001:5390: spyi gtsug tu 'od zer dkar po gcig las zla ba'i dal gcig tu bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5391: de las chu las chu bur rdol ba bzhin du dkar po gcig lhag gis byung bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5392: lce'i steng du 'od zer dmar po gcig las pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa dmar po gcig bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5393: de'i ze'u 'bru la chu las chu bur rdol ba bzhin du +aahdakara po gcig bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5394: snying gar 'od zer mthing ka gcig las rdo rje rgya gram gcig bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5395: de'i lte ba la chu las chu bur rdol ba
NK033(gi)001:5396: bzhin du h'u dkar po gcig lhag gis byung bar
NK033(gi)001:5397: bsam mo // de ni rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:5398: bskyed pa rkyen gyis sngags ni /
NK033(gi)001:5399: spyi gtsug gi a ba d+hu ti na mar ham
NK033(gi)001:5400: dkar po mu tig gi thig pa 'dra ba gcig
NK033(gi)001:5401: mgo mthur la 'phyang ba klad pa la reg ge
NK033(gi)001:5403: lte ba la +aahdamara po mchong bcag pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:5404: reg bya tsha ba dmar ba gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5405: reg bya'i rtse mos ham bzhus te ye shes kyi
NK033(gi)001:5406: thig le dkar po tsa ra ra babs par bsam
NK033(gi)001:5407: / lus bde bas khengs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5408: de ni bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:5409: bzlas brjod las kyi sngags ni /
NK033(gi)001:5410: rang gi snying kha nas 'od zer dmar po gsum 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)001:5411: mdun gyi nam mkha' la mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo sku gcer bu skra grol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5412: rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:5413: phyag g.yas pas thod pa'i d+aa ma ru 'khrol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5414: phyag g.yon na ka p+aa la bdud rtsis bkang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5415: rnam pa lha'i rnam pa tsam la /
NK033(gi)001:5416: rang bzhin skye ba med pa nyams myong bde ba chen po'o //
NK033(gi)001:5424: de ni bzlas brjod las kyi sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:5425: sngags de rgyun du bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:5427: d+aa ki mngon spyod kyi dngos grub blang ba'i sgrub pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:5429: dza lan d+ha ra sa tha bi ra nir g+ha ta sho gan na pa swa am na yad /
NK033(gi)001:5430: sh+r+ai na ba ta pi ta ya na sha trum
NK033(gi)001:5431: na gra ha sarba yo ga sid+d+hi pra do mu
NK033(gi)001:5434: dz+aa lan d+ha ri'i gnas rnam par bsgyur ba /
NK033(gi)001:5435: dpal gnas pa'i gzhung lugs las /
NK033(gi)001:5436: 'di ni dpal gyi mi mo zhabs kyi /
NK033(gi)001:5438: rnal 'byor pa thams cad la dngos grub ster ba'i gzhung lugs so //
NK033(gi)001:5439: dpal khrag 'thung gi rgyal po he ru ka mngon rdzogs /
NK033(gi)001:5441: dpal chen khrag 'thung rigs lnga gang yang rung ba'i /
NK033(gi)001:5442: po'i bsam gtan dang ldan pas /
NK033(gi)001:5443: mi bskyod rang gi pas gdong dang kha lag bkru zhing /
NK033(gi)001:5444: kha lhor bltas la bdud rtsi a mri ta'i ril bu khar gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:5445: lngas kha bkang sha chen ste /
NK033(gi)001:5446: dang po la zur stegs bu mnga' gang gru bzhi
NK033(gi)001:5447: pa byas la zlum po e ni nyis 'gyur brtsigs
NK033(gi)001:5448: / gsum pa kha dog dmar po byas la mdog ni dkar dang ljang dang mthing /
NK033(gi)001:5449: gru chad bzhi po thur du rdo sol byug /
NK033(gi)001:5451: thod pa dum bu'i nang du tsha ba'i mar khus me sbar la /
NK033(gi)001:5452: de'i dbus su 'bar ba'i dzahls 'bar ba'i gdong can /
NK033(gi)001:5453: d+ha las mkha' la gshegs ma /
NK033(gi)001:5454: da las mkha' la spyod ma /
NK033(gi)001:5455: mdog dang phyag rgya thams cad gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:5457: gdong gcig ma la mig gsum ma sku mdog dmar
NK033(gi)001:5458: la lag pa bzhi pa g.yas brkyangs pas gnas pa
NK033(gi)001:5459: / g.yon bskum pa'i rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:5460: gzhan gnyis kyis gri khug dang thod pa mi'i rgyu ma sha khrag gis bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:5462: stag gi lpags pas smad dkris shing /
NK033(gi)001:5464: mi mgo'i do shal byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5465: kha nas mad'i me 'bar bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5466: shar gyi zur kam las bskyed pa /
NK033(gi)001:5467: du bya rog gdong can ma mdog nag mo gdong gcig ma la phyag gnyis ma /
NK033(gi)001:5468: phyag gnyis kyis ro 'i rkang pa nas /
NK033(gi)001:5469: bzung nas sos 'drad cing gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5470: ro'i steng na g.yas brkyangs pas gnas pa gcig gzhan gtso mo dang mthun gsum ka bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5471: bden bral gyi phyogs su lce spyang gi gdong can ma dzam las bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:5473: phyag gnyis kyis ro 'i rked pa nas /
NK033(gi)001:5475: ro'i steng na g.yas brkyangs pas gnas pa gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5476: rlung lha'i phyogs su khyi'i sho las /
NK033(gi)001:5477: gdong can ma du ba'i mdog can lag pa gnyis kyi ro 'i mtshan ma bzung nas za ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:5478: ro'i steng na g.yas brkyangs pas gnas par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:5479: de bsgom nas bdag nyid khrag 'thung gi rnam par byas nas go bgo bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5480: skra lhug par byas la bsrung ba'i don du khrag
NK033(gi)001:5481: dang khu ba bsres la thig le dpral ba dang
NK033(gi)001:5482: mgrin pa dang snying kar bku bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5483: sha chen gyis bdug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5484: ru lu he ru kas rang bsrung /
NK033(gi)001:5486: tsit+ta b+ha b+h+yi ma na phreng ya a sa la /
NK033(gi)001:5487: de nas rang nyid mchod mchod rdzas dang rang ci za ba'i phud kyis /
NK033(gi)001:5489: de nas gdug pa can tshar bcad pa'i phyir zhe sdang bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:5490: lha mo 'bar ba'i gdong can rang nyid khrag 'thung
NK033(gi)001:5491: gi skur byas pa'i thugs kha'i sa bon las 'od
NK033(gi)001:5492: zer lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)001:5494: g.yog mo gsum spyan drang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:5498: ha sta dang kun gyi g.yab mos 'bod do //
NK033(gi)001:5499: ma la sogs pa spyan drangs par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:5503: si sh+r+ai spyan drangs pa'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:5504: he ru ka dzah d+ha ra sa na pa ke ro na g+h+ri h+na a gad dza s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5505: sngon du brjod pas dal zur gsum du bkug la /
NK033(gi)001:5506: chang dang sha chen dang khrag gis brlan par byas
NK033(gi)001:5507: pa'i me tog la sogs pa rnams kyi mchod par
NK033(gi)001:5508: bya'o // dz+wa la 'bar ba'i gdong ba /
NK033(gi)001:5512: da ha na mkha' la spyod /
NK033(gi)001:5513: mu khi gtso mo la mchod /
NK033(gi)001:5514: p+au dza gri h+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5516: ka mu khi kam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5517: dzam su khi mu lce sbyang gi mgo /
NK033(gi)001:5519: shwa na mu khyi gdong can ma /
NK033(gi)001:5521: p+au dza gri g.yog mo gsum po mchod /
NK033(gi)001:5523: de ltar rab tu mchod nas /
NK033(gi)001:5524: de nas bstod pa bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:5526: 'gro don chags pa'i dbang gi sku //
NK033(gi)001:5527: sku mdog dmar mo 'bar ba'i gdong //
NK033(gi)001:5528: ral pa dmar po byi ru'i lan tshar can //
NK033(gi)001:5529: phyag gnyis rdo rje mda' gzhu 'gengs pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:5530: thabs bstod pa 'di man chad mchan yig tu 'dug /
NK033(gi)001:5531: dang shes rab gnyis med thugs rje yis //
NK033(gi)001:5532: nyon mongs dug tshogs bsgral nas dbyings su sdud //
NK033(gi)001:5533: lhag ma gnyis ni gri dang b+han+d+ha bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:5534: 'khor ba rtsad gcod snying khrag dron mo gsol //
NK033(gi)001:5535: dus ngan tha ma'i sems can gdul dka' bas //
NK033(gi)001:5536: gsod pa nyi tshes 'dul mdzad 'bar ba'i gdong //
NK033(gi)001:5537: sgrol byed dpa' mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:5538: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i phra men ma //
NK033(gi)001:5539: bya rog mgo dang spyang ki khyi yi dbu //
NK033(gi)001:5540: bud med chags pas 'dul bar dbang che bas //
NK033(gi)001:5541: 'khor ba'i ro dang dug gsum rol mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:5542: dgra bgegs tshar gcod mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:5545: khrag mchod rdzas sha khrag dang rang ci za ba'i phud /
NK033(gi)001:5546: dang sha la sogs pas 'jigs byed ma la sogs pa la gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5548: sa man+ta be ra ba gtor ma'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:5549: ba ling+ta gri h+na ma ma ka ma sa ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5550: brtsam pa nas las ma rdzogs kyi bar du bka'
NK033(gi)001:5551: rgyas kyi phyag gzhug tu las la sbyor tsa na
NK033(gi)001:5552: / thod pa'i mu tras phrin las 'di bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5553: rgya bcas la sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5554: de ltar rab tu mchod nas sngon du bsnyen pa 'bum phrag gcig /
NK033(gi)001:5557: a byin chen mo mthu mo che //
NK033(gi)001:5558: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:5559: dam tshig gsang ba'i tshul bstan ma //
NK033(gi)001:5560: dbang phyug tsakra'i gtso mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:5561: bran pho bran mo dang 'khol la /
NK033(gi)001:5562: brnag pa 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK033(gi)001:5563: dam tshig tshul bzhin da skyongs la //
NK033(gi)001:5564: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:5566: de la sngags ni 'di yin no //
NK033(gi)001:5567: gtso mo gsum ka gcig tu dril ba'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:5571: mu khe dza la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:5572: ka ka 'di g.yog mo gsum gyi mu khi kam /
NK033(gi)001:5573: dzam su khi mu khi dzam /
NK033(gi)001:5574: shwa na mu khi sham h+aum dzah zhes bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:5575: de ltar bsnyen pa bya de ltar nyin gsum mtshan gsum bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5577: zhing dus bzhir mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5579: de nas drag po'i las la sbyor ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5580: 'byung po'i nyin zhag la nyi shu gnyis nas stong man chad du /
NK033(gi)001:5581: dgra bsad pa bsgrub bya'i rjes kyi sa blangs te /
NK033(gi)001:5584: dur khrod kyi ras la 'chad par 'gyur ba'i 'khrul 'khor bris la /
NK033(gi)001:5586: lte ba mu khyud dang bcas pa'i bar du tsakra rtsibs brgyad rtse mo nang du bstan pa bri /
NK033(gi)001:5587: tsakra dz+ny+aa ya ri ma adz+ny+aa h+na gri ru gu /
NK033(gi)001:5588: phata phata phata h+aum s+ya mas ya da hri /
NK033(gi)001:5591: ya ra m+aa ya ra m+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5592: trum sha khi mu la da la d+ha la dz+wa /
NK033(gi)001:5596: de dril la gzugs kyi snying khar gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:5597: gzugs de'i snying khar gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5602: snying khar tsher ma gla ba'i tsher ma'am /
NK033(gi)001:5604: btsugs la thod pa'i klo'am mon gyi /
NK033(gi)001:5605: nang du ling+ga la dgug gzhug yang yang bya /
NK033(gi)001:5607: rang nyid kyis mda' gzhu bzung ste mad'i rtse mo
NK033(gi)001:5608: la da du ra'i khu ba byug la bsgrub bya'i
NK033(gi)001:5609: gzugs brnyan la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig sngags 'dis
NK033(gi)001:5610: bsnun lha mos dgra bkug cing gsod par bsam mo
NK033(gi)001:5612: sngags brgya tsho re re'am yang na /
NK033(gi)001:5616: mu khi sha trum bsad pa'i thun ni nyungs kar
NK033(gi)001:5617: nyungs nag dug dang khrag dang lcags phye zangs phye
NK033(gi)001:5618: la sogs pa'i thun rdzas rnams /
NK033(gi)001:5619: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:5623: sa ma s+ya h+aum phata phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:5630: khros pa'i sems kyis drag tu bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5631: de nas dur khrod du bsreg sbyin sreg byed na lha mo gsum por rang bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:5635: khrag sna tshogs dang rang ci za ba'i phud kyis mchod /
NK033(gi)001:5636: gta' gsum ka'i gtor ma gsum cha gcig bsreg /
NK033(gi)001:5637: sum cha gcig phral gtor du'o //
NK033(gi)001:5639: dus bzhi la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5640: khung byas la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5641: dgra'i gzugs brnyan gri gug gis dum bur byas la khros pa'i sems kyis bsreg par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5642: mnan pa'i ling ro rnams ro khung du mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:5645: +amo a ka nan zhes drag tu bzlas la mnan sbyin sreg byas pa'i thal ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:5649: de thod ngan du bcug la ro ras kyis dkris pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:5650: re bas dril la ro khung du mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:5651: mnan pa'i dus su mnan pa'i sngags de bazla'o //
NK033(gi)001:5654: ji srid dbang du bya ba la sogs pa bcu gnyis kyi mthar thug par gyur pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:5655: dbang du gyur na 'o mas thod pa bkang la de'i nang du bstsal la /
NK033(gi)001:5656: sh+aan+tim sa ma m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:5657: ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa'i mtha' can gyis bkru bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5658: 'di 'di man mchan bur 'dug te dkyus lags par 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:5660: bsad pa gong ma rang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:5663: dgug am ku sha dzahpa dang /
NK033(gi)001:5667: rengs par lte ba la gzer /
NK033(gi)001:5669: phur snying la seng ldeng gi /
NK033(gi)001:5673: rmongs snying la khyi khrag par bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:5678: thams cad du spyi'i phag khrag bya khrag /
NK033(gi)001:5679: longs spyod nyams par bya ba dang bcu gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:5680: de ma yin na mtha' 'dis 'chi bar 'gyur ba the tshom mi za'o //
NK033(gi)001:5681: 'dir sngon du bsnyen par gyur pa la /
NK033(gi)001:5685: mu khe m+aa ra ya phata /
NK033(gi)001:5686: 'dis 'chi bar 'gyur ba la the tshom mi za'o //
NK033(gi)001:5687: sngags dz+wa ha na mu khe s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5689: 'di nyid kyis sbyin sreg kyang bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5690: kha che'i mkhan po dz+ny+aa sh+r+ai sid+ha na badz+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:5691: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong bee ro tsa na /
NK033(gi)001:5692: shes rab grags kyis bsgyur ba rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:5693: mkha' 'gro ma'i mngon spyod kyi dngos grub blang ba bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:5694: mkha' 'gro ma'i d+aa ki'i longs spyod bsgrub pas /
NK033(gi)001:5695: mngon spyod kyi las ni gzhung na gsal /
NK033(gi)001:5697: rdzas la rin po che yig zugs byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5698: de'i nang du gter chen po'i gzugs dung g.yas 'khyil /
NK033(gi)001:5699: bcug la de'i nang du rin po che sna lnga dang /
NK033(gi)001:5702: rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas bya /
NK033(gi)001:5703: de nas sems byang chub kyi bskyed la d+aa ki ma la 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)001:5704: de nas rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)001:5705: mdun du kam dkar po gcig gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5706: de yongs su gyur pa las dur khrod chen po gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5707: de nas de steng ni ri ti zhes brjod pas /
NK033(gi)001:5708: keng rus kyi ri rab gcer bu gsum la gdan ro gdan dang bcas pa bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5709: de'i steng du yi ge dz+wa d+ha ra gsum bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5710: yi ge de gsum las mkha' 'gro ma gsum bsam ste zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK033(gi)001:5711: g.yas dang po rdo rje sdigs mdzub /
NK033(gi)001:5712: 'og ma d+aa ma ru bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:5713: g.yon dang po kha t+w+aam ka brkyang ba'i tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:5714: 'og ma na ka p+aa li bdud rtsis bkang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5715: sku gcer bu skra grol ba /
NK033(gi)001:5716: thod pa dum bu'i ske rags byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5717: rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:5718: ro'i steng na rgyal po rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:5719: pheem bi ra zhes mkha' la gshegs nas /
NK033(gi)001:5720: sprin nag po 'dus pa'i nang na bzhugs par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5721: de nas mkha' 'gro ma gsum gyi thugs ye shes
NK033(gi)001:5722: kyi 'od zer mkha' 'gro ma sde gsum la phog
NK033(gi)001:5723: / mkha' 'gro ma gsum gyi thugs ye shes kyi
NK033(gi)001:5724: 'od zer phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la phog pas sangs
NK033(gi)001:5725: rgyas kyi thugs ye shes kyi 'od zer mdun gyi
NK033(gi)001:5726: bam b+h+r+aum ma la phog pas /
NK033(gi)001:5727: bam b+h+r+aum ma la pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi ge sar
NK033(gi)001:5728: gyi steng na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK033(gi)001:5729: che gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5730: de'i nang na gter chen po las dgos 'dod kyi re ba thams cad 'byung bar bsam la /
NK033(gi)001:5731: de nas snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:5732: dz+wa la ha na d+ha ha na da ha na /
NK033(gi)001:5734: dgos 'dod kyi re ba ster ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:5735: dang po rang gi nyams len phul ba lags so //
NK033(gi)001:5736: bka' brgyud 'dzin pa'i don byed shog /
NK033(gi)001:5738: sgrub pa las sbyor gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:5740: man+dala dang po la zur gsum pa /
NK033(gi)001:5742: dam de'i dbus su rdzas dgram pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:5750: gtor ma khrag dang sha la sogs pas /
NK033(gi)001:5755: bzlas pa thems nas sgrub pa las sbyor bya ba la bdun te /
NK033(gi)001:5756: ling+ga bca' ba bsgrub bya'i rjes /
NK033(gi)001:5760: bstan pa bya ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:5761: thun gyis brab pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:5762: phur bus gdab pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:5763: mda' rgyag rang nyid kyi mda' gzhu /
NK033(gi)001:5765: sbyin de nas dur khrod du /
NK033(gi)001:5767: mnan pa bya ba dang bdun no //
NK033(gi)001:5768: nang ri me yis gtor ba 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:5771: rtags la me dgra phyogs su 'gro ba 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:5773: sha khrag la sogs pa byung na phyi'i rtags so //
NK033(gi)001:5774: ling+ga dang po dgra bo lha dang phral ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:5779: khyi lud rnams kyi dud pas bdug la dabye'o //
NK033(gi)001:5781: dz+wa la na gtso mo gsum gcig tu dril ba'i sngags gong bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:5782: 'di gtso mo gsum po so sor bkral ba'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:5783: mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihmh'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:5785: d+ha ha na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:5787: da ha na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:5788: ka 'di g.yog mo gsum gyi sngags /
NK033(gi)001:5790: dzam su khi mu khe dzam /
NK033(gi)001:5791: shwa na mu ke sham h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:5792: zhag gsum gsum na 'bum bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)001:5796: de 'dra ba tsho gsum gsum bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5797: lar zhag dgus 'grub pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:5798: bu dang 'dra zhag gsum gsum na las sbyor re re rdzogs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5799: ba las gzhan la spel du mi rung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:5800: nub dgu la gsum zhun gyi me mar btang /
NK033(gi)001:5805: nyi shu gnyis nas 'byung po'i nyin zhag yin /
NK033(gi)001:5810: mo gsum la sna tshogs pa'i gtor ma bya /
NK033(gi)001:5814: g.yog khra yi mgo can ma /
NK033(gi)001:5815: mo gsum la snying sna khra'i snying /
NK033(gi)001:5816: kh+aa ta'i snying spyang ki'i snying du srog snying bris la gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:5819: dang po zhag bdun snying gi nang du d+au ki'i srog dang /
NK033(gi)001:5821: d+aa ki 'di yang mngon spyod do //
NK033(gi)001:5822: d+aa ki sde gsum nyams su blangs pa'i dus su sha chen gyi mar me btang ste /
NK033(gi)001:5823: skyes dar ma'i snying gi zhun mar /
NK033(gi)001:5826: gcan gzan gyi snying gi zhun mar ro //
NK033(gi)001:5827: de nas 'bod pa btags la zhag bdun bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:5829: sh+r+ai sing has bee ro tsa na la gnang nas
NK033(gi)001:5830: da lta yan chad du brgyud pa ma chad pa
NK033(gi)001:5831: lags so // rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i bka' srung lags so //
NK033(gi)001:5832: bu slob gzhan dang pho khyad yod pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:5835: dza lan d+ha ra sa tha bi ra ni ra g+ha ta sho ga na /
NK033(gi)001:5840: sha trum na gra ha sarba yo ga sid+d+hi pra do mu la a ma na ya /
NK033(gi)001:5842: dza lan d+ha ra'i gnas rnam par bsgyur ba /
NK033(gi)001:5843: dpal gnas pa'i gzhung lugs las /
NK033(gi)001:5844: 'di ni dpal gyi mi mo zhabs kyi dngos grub
NK033(gi)001:5845: dgra tshar bcad pa 'i gdams ngag ga bur g+hi
NK033(gi)001:5846: wang gla rtsi nal bu'i sha khrag tshil chen a
NK033(gi)001:5847: mri ta rdzas drug po de'i phye mar spos dkar
NK033(gi)001:5848: dang sbyar nas rgya sol du ba med pa la
NK033(gi)001:5849: bsreg na d+aa ki sprin 'thib pa bzhin 'ong ngo
NK033(gi)001:5850: // d+aa ki ma'i spos sbyor ro //
NK033(gi)001:5851: rnal 'byor pa thams cad la dngos grub ster ba'i gzhung lugs so //
NK033(gi)001:5852: dpal he ru ka mngon rdzogs khrag 'thung rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:5853: 'byung po'i nyin zhag la dgra bsad par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:5855: bskyod pas gdong dang kha lag la sogs pa bkru zhing ste /
NK033(gi)001:5856: kha lho phyogs su blta zhing /
NK033(gi)001:5859: bsgrub bya'i rkang rjes kyi sa blangs te /
NK033(gi)001:5860: bag phye dang bsres la dgra'i gzugs brnyan bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5861: dur 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad sngags sde brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:5862: khrod kyi ras la 'chad par 'gyur pa'i 'khrul 'khor bris la gzugs de'i snying khar gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5868: snying khar gla ba'i tsher ma'am skyer tsher /
NK033(gi)001:5869: tsher ma btsugs la thod glo'am mon gyi /
NK033(gi)001:5870: pa'i nang du gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5875: mad'i rtse mo da thang khrom pa du ra'i khu bas byugs la /
NK033(gi)001:5876: sngags 'di lan nyi shu rtsa gcig gis dgra bo'i gzugs la /
NK033(gi)001:5878: dz+wa la d+ha la da la mu khi sha trum m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:5881: hri da ya sa ma s+ya h'u phata phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:5882: gu ru gri h+na dz+ny+aa a ma ri ya dz+ny+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5889: khros pa'i sems kyis drag 'di yan chad bsgrub pa'i gzhung yin no //
NK033(gi)001:5890: 'di man chad las kyi sgrig yin /
NK033(gi)001:5892: de nas bsgrub pa'i dur khrod du bsreg khung brub khung byas la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5893: dgra bo'i gzugs brnyan la gri gug gis dum bu dum bur byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5894: brub khung du khros pa'i sems kyis bsregs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5895: de 'khrul 'khor d+aa ki ma la bsnyen sngags bsad sngags dang btags la sbrel ba bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:5897: ji srid du dbang du bya ba la sogs pa
NK033(gi)001:5898: bcu gnyis kyis mthar thug par 'gyur ba'am dbang du
NK033(gi)001:5899: gyur pa na / 'o mas thod pa bkang la de'i nang du btsal la /
NK033(gi)001:5900: sh+ain+tam m+aa ra sa ma ya ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa'i mtha' can gyis bkru bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5901: de ltar ma yin na mtha' 'dis mchi ba la the tshom mi za'o //
NK033(gi)001:5902: 'dir sngon du bsnyen par gyur pa /
NK033(gi)001:5906: mu khi sh+ain+tam m+aa ra ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa phata /
NK033(gi)001:5907: 'dis 'chi bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK033(gi)001:5908: sngags de nyid kyis sbyin me lhar mkha' 'gro gsum bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:5910: dang po dal zur gsum pa kha dog dmar por byas la /
NK033(gi)001:5911: de'i dbus su thod pa'i dum bu'i nang du mar
NK033(gi)001:5912: khus mar me spar de'i dbus dz+wa d+ha da las
NK033(gi)001:5913: / su 'bar ba'i gdong gsum ka sku'i cha byad gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:5914: can bsam par bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:5915: gdong gcig ma la mig gsum ma /
NK033(gi)001:5919: lag bzhi g.yas brkyangs pas gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5920: rtsa sku'i ba'i lag pa gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'dzin snying kha nas tshur la /
NK033(gi)001:5922: gzhan gnyis kyis gri gug dang thod pa mi'i rgyu ma dang sha khrag gis bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:5924: stag gi pags pa'i smad sku'i dkris shing ro'i steng na gnas pa'i mi mgo'i do shal byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5925: kha nas me mkha' 'gro ma gsum ka de tshugs bsam /
NK033(gi)001:5928: du bya rog gdong can ma /
NK033(gi)001:5929: sku mdog nag mo gdong gcig ma /
NK033(gi)001:5931: ro'i steng na zhabs g.yas brkyangs pas gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:5932: phyag gnyis kyis ro bzung nas sos 'drad cing za rkang pa nas /
NK033(gi)001:5935: bral phyogs su lce spyang gdong can ma /
NK033(gi)001:5937: phyag gnyis kyis mi ro bzung nas rtsi'u chung nas khrag 'jib pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:5938: lhag ma ni sngon bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:5940: lha'i phyogs su khyi gdong can ma sku mdog dud kha'i mdog can /
NK033(gi)001:5941: phyag gnyis kyis ro bzung nas za ba sngar lhag ma /
NK033(gi)001:5943: de ltar bsgoms nas bdag nyid khrag 'thung gi rnam par bya bas go cha bgo bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5944: skra lhug par byas la bsrung ba'i don du khrag
NK033(gi)001:5945: dang khu ba bsres la thig khrag les dpral rang
NK033(gi)001:5946: gi ba dang / snying kha zhag dang /
NK033(gi)001:5947: mgrin par bku thal chen bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5948: sha chen gyis bdug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5949: he ru ka'i rang bsrung ba /
NK033(gi)001:5950: ru lu ru lu h+aum tsi ti h+aum b+h+yo 'di la mi 'dra ba snang /
NK033(gi)001:5952: ma de phreng ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5953: de nas rang ci za bas /
NK033(gi)001:5955: de nas gdug pa can tshar bcad par bya ba'i phyir zhe snying rje zer /
NK033(gi)001:5957: lha mo 'bar ma'i gdong can ma la sogs pa
NK033(gi)001:5958: spyan sa bon las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu'o
NK033(gi)001:5962: da ha na he dzam si sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK033(gi)001:5963: dzahd+ha ra sa na pa ke ro sha na g+h+rih+na
NK033(gi)001:5964: / a gad dzah a gad tsha /
NK033(gi)001:5966: sngon du brjod pas dal zur gsum par chang dang
NK033(gi)001:5967: sha chen dang khrag gis can byugs par byas pa'i
NK033(gi)001:5968: steng du me tog la sogs pa rnams kyis mchod
NK033(gi)001:5969: par bya'o // dz+wa la ha na /
NK033(gi)001:5973: mu khe p+au dza g+h+rih+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5975: kam ka mu khe kam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5976: dzam su khi mu khe dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5977: shwa na mu khe sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5978: mu kha p+au dza g+h+rih+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5979: de ltar rab tu mchod byas nas /
NK033(gi)001:5980: khrag dang sha la sogs pa yis /
NK033(gi)001:5981: dngos grub gong na med pa 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:5982: 'jigs byed ma la sogs pa la gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5983: u nan 'di la mi 'dra ba snang /
NK033(gi)001:5984: ta be ra ba ya ba lim nu ha na ma ma ka ram he pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:5985: des ni gtor ma dbul bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5986: de ltar rab tu mchod nas sngon du 'bum phrag gcig gis bsnyen par byas na 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:5988: dz+wa la ha na d+ha ha na da ha na gtso mo gsum gyi sngags /
NK033(gi)001:5989: mu khe dza la na la ni h+r+aihmh'u phata /
NK033(gi)001:5990: gtso mo gsum gyi snying po 'bum phrag tu bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:5991: de nas g.yog mo gsum gyi sngags 'adi'o //
NK033(gi)001:5993: dzam su khi mu khi dzam /
NK033(gi)001:5994: shwa na mu khi sham h+aum dzah g.yog mo gsum
NK033(gi)001:5995: gyi snying po khri bzlas na mkha' 'gro ma dngos
NK033(gi)001:5996: su 'ong ngo // gtso bo nas ma rdzogs kyi bar du kem rus thod pa'i phyag rgya /
NK033(gi)001:5997: kyi phyag rgya bcas la sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:5998: mnan pa ni ling ro rnams ro khung du mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:6002: kha che'i mkhan po dz+ny+aa sh+r+ai sing ha na badz+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:6003: bod kyi lo ts+aa bee ro tsa na /
NK033(gi)001:6004: ba dge slong shes rab grags kyis bsgyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:6005: de nas gang zag la rim gyi bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6007: 'di'i 'di man chad las sgrigs yin no //
NK033(gi)001:6008: mgo mjug tu dbang du bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6012: rmugs par mgo la dug shing gis bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6013: rengs par bya ba lte bar gzir /
NK033(gi)001:6015: phur snying la seng ldeng gi /
NK033(gi)001:6017: ngag phrog pa lce ru dug gis /
NK033(gi)001:6019: rmongs par snying la khyi khrag bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6020: zha bar bya ba rkang pa /
NK033(gi)001:6024: thams cad du spyi'i phag khrag bya khrag longs spyod nyams par bya ba ste bcu gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:6027: dam rdzas dgram pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:6029: ye shes pa'i lha spyan drangs la bstim pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:6033: bzlas pa thems nas las la sbyar ba dang brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:6034: las la sbyar ba la bdun te /
NK033(gi)001:6035: ling ga bca' ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:6036: thun mtshams su mnan pa bya ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:6037: thun gyis brab pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:6038: phur bus gdab pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:6040: sbyin sreg bya ba dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:6042: sngags brgya tsho re re la'am /
NK033(gi)001:6043: yang na nyi shu rtsa gcig mda' re la bsnun no //
NK033(gi)001:6048: lcags phye la thun rdzas bya /
NK033(gi)001:6050: de nas 'bod pa btags la bdun bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:6051: bcu bzhi nas zhag bdun gsang sngags bzlas pa las la sbyar ro //
NK033(gi)001:6052: ma mo mkha' 'gro yis dgra bkugs nas gsol bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:6053: dam tshig tshul bzhin du skyong la bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod /
NK033(gi)001:6054: a phyi chen mo mthu mo che //
NK033(gi)001:6055: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:6056: dam tshigs gsang ba'i tshul ston ma //
NK033(gi)001:6057: dbang phyug brgya rtsa brgyad kyi gtso mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:6058: bdud cha gnyis dang srin po bran pho srog bdag 'khol //
NK033(gi)001:6059: brnag pa 'di la rtags phyung zhig /
NK033(gi)001:6060: dam tshig tshul bzhin da skyong la //
NK033(gi)001:6061: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:6062: ces las bcol ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:6067: dz+ny+aa ya ri ma a dz+ny+aa h+na gri ru gu phata phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:6068: h'u s+ya ma sa ya da hri /
NK033(gi)001:6073: ya ra m+aa ya ra m+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6075: khi mu la da la d+ha la dz+wa /
NK033(gi)001:6077: lte ba la ling ga bri /
NK033(gi)001:6078: 'khor lo'i rtse mo nang du bstan /
NK033(gi)001:6079: rtse mo'i bar du dgra bo'i ming rus bri /
NK033(gi)001:6081: dri ma la gzugs byas la de'i snying khar 'khrul 'khor gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:6085: sha khrag la sogs pa byung na phyi rtags drod mer song ba la 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:6088: lha dang dbral ba khyi mo /
NK033(gi)001:6097: sbyin sreg byed na lha mo rang bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:6103: rang ci za ba'i phud kyis mchod do //
NK033(gi)001:6104: de nas ling ga gtubs la snod bkang la khros pa'i sems kyis thab tu bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:6105: gta' gtor gsum cha gcig mnan /
NK033(gi)001:6108: de nas ling ga gtubs la snod bkang la /
NK033(gi)001:6109: khros pa'i sems kyis thab tu bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:6111: ba la gzugs byas shing 'khrul 'khor de'i snying khar bcas la mnan par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6112: mnan pa ni ngan thod du bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:6113: ro ras sam re bas dril la ro khung du mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:6114: mnan pa'i dus su srung ba'i sngags de bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:6115: mchod pa nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum bazla'o //
NK033(gi)001:6117: nya dang dus bzhi la bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:6118: zhag gsum na 'bum tsho thon par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6119: las sbyor bu dang 'dra ba las gzhan la spel du mi rung /
NK033(gi)001:6125: stegs bu mda' gang gru bzhi zlum po e ni nyis 'gyur rtsig /
NK033(gi)001:6126: mdog ni dkar dang ljang dang mthing //
NK033(gi)001:6127: dbus ni nag po gru chad bzhi ni thur du rkos /
NK033(gi)001:6130: ni rtse mo nang du bstan pa bri /
NK033(gi)001:6131: bar bar du ni che ge mo'i ming rus bri /
NK033(gi)001:6132: de dril gzugs dgra'i kyi snying khar gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:6133: mkha' 'gro ma ngan sngags su bsgrub pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:6134: snyan brgyud kyi srung ma yin //
NK033(gi)001:6135: khyad par du sgrub rdzas bla ma'i zhal las dris /
NK033(gi)001:6136: rgya 'di gong ma rnams dang 'dra la khad kyis
NK033(gi)001:6137: mi 'dra ba mang bas gzhung sor bzhag byas yod
NK033(gi)001:6139: gar skad d+aa ki mngon spyod /
NK033(gi)001:6141: de wi tsan+di k+aa yo ga sha trum t+aa re karma na mah bod skad du /
NK033(gi)001:6142: lha mo gtum mo sgrol mas rje btsun sgrol ma'i gsung gi sprul pa /
NK033(gi)001:6143: rnal 'byor pa'i dgra sgrol bar byed pa'i las zhes bya ba /
NK033(gi)001:6144: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:6146: tshogs dgra bo bsad dpal mkha' 'gro ma /
NK033(gi)001:6147: pa'i las 'di brtsam ste dang por dpal chen po'i rigs lnga khrag 'thung gang yang rung ba'i /
NK033(gi)001:6149: mi bskyod pas gdong dang kha lag bkrus la /
NK033(gi)001:6150: zhing lpags kyi gdan la bsdad la /
NK033(gi)001:6151: kha nub lhor bstan te khros pas bdud rtsi'i ril bu'am sha chen mur zhing /
NK033(gi)001:6154: zhing lpags kyi steng du sha chen gyis dal zur gsum pa bris te /
NK033(gi)001:6155: dbus su thod pa'i nang du mar khrag tshil gyi mar me spar la /
NK033(gi)001:6156: mar me'i dkyil du h+r+aihls byung ba'i lha mo gtum
NK033(gi)001:6157: mo sku mdog dmar mo gcer bu spyan gsum pa
NK033(gi)001:6159: zhal gcig pa phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:6162: rus pa'i rgyan du ma dang sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:6163: phyag g.yas pa na ral gri me 'bar ba 'debs pa'i tshul du gdengs pa /
NK033(gi)001:6164: g.yon pa thod pa ka p+aa la 'gyings bag gi
NK033(gi)001:6165: tshul gyis khams gsum gyi snying khrag dron mo gsol
NK033(gi)001:6166: ba / stag gi sham thabs can /
NK033(gi)001:6167: ro'i steng na g.yon brkyangs pas bzhugs shing me 'bar
NK033(gi)001:6168: 'khrugs pa'i steng na 'gyings pa 'jigs pa'i rta gad
NK033(gi)001:6169: dang bcas par bsgom par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6171: las me'i phyogs su bya rog gi gdong can ma nag mo /
NK033(gi)001:6172: phyags gnyis ro'i yan lag brkyangs nas /
NK033(gi)001:6174: dzam las bden bral phyogs su spyang gdong ma dmar ser /
NK033(gi)001:6175: phyag gnyis kyis ro bzung nas mgrin pa'i khrag 'thung bar byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6176: sham las rlung gi phyogs su khyi'i gdong can ma
NK033(gi)001:6177: sku mdog ljang nag lag pa gnyis kyis ro bzung
NK033(gi)001:6179: ma dper 'dir khyi gdong ma chad dam snyam zhes
NK033(gi)001:6180: mchan btab pa bzhin tshig 'di nyid 'og gi mngon
NK033(gi)001:6181: rtogs las btus te 'dir bcug pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:6183: de rnams kyang rgyan cha lugs gtso mo dang mthun pa /
NK033(gi)001:6184: g.yon brkyangs pas ro la bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:6185: de nas bdag nyid dpal khrag 'thung gi nga rgyal gyi go cha bgo bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6187: khrag dang khu ba bsres pas gnas gsum du thig le byas la /
NK033(gi)001:6188: sha chen gyis bdug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6189: tsi ti b+hu ta ma ni pri ya ya s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6190: de de nas rang nyid la mchod par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:6191: nas lha mo gtum mo la mchod par bya ste
NK033(gi)001:6192: sngags 'di sa ye shes kyi lha mo spyan drangs
NK033(gi)001:6193: par byas / dzam d+aa ki mam ni ti tsu b+hi sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:6194: dz+ny+aa ham dzi ri ri sham ba ni ba ga ri na kam /
NK033(gi)001:6195: e hi a gad dza ha /
NK033(gi)001:6196: zhes brjod pas sngar gyi dal la bkug la /
NK033(gi)001:6197: chang dang sha chen dang khrag gis brlan pa'i me tog la sogs pas mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6198: dzam mam mu khe d+hi p+au dza g+h+ri h+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6200: ka mu khi kam p+au dza g+h+r+ai h+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6202: su khi mu khi dzam p+au dza g+h+ri h+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6204: na mu khi sham p+au dza g+h+ri h+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6205: de ltar rab tu mchod nas khrag dang /
NK033(gi)001:6206: sha la sogs pas 'di man chad mchan /
NK033(gi)001:6207: 'jigs byed ma la gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6208: mu na min tam b+he ra b+hi ya ba ling+ta
NK033(gi)001:6209: g+h+ri h+na ma ma kas+ya pa ta ya s+w+aa h+aa
NK033(gi)001:6211: gtso bo nas 'jigs byed man chad du /
NK033(gi)001:6212: thod rlon gyi phyag rgyas dbul bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6213: de nas sngags bzlas par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:6214: sku tsan d+he k+she h+r+aihdzah gsung ma ham ni mu ki phatah s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6215: thugs dzam mam ni lam mu lu ni hrim s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6216: de dag gsum bdun 'bum du bsnyen pa bya zhing dus bzhir mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6217: de nas drag po'i las bya ste 'byung po'i nyin zhag la dur khrod kyi dal gru gsum pa /
NK033(gi)001:6218: khrag chen gyis dmar por byas la /
NK033(gi)001:6219: bsgrub bya'i rkang rjes chu 'gram bra shing so ba la thal chen khrag /
NK033(gi)001:6223: bag phye dang bsres la ske tshe yungs kar yungs nag /
NK033(gi)001:6224: dang lan tsha rnams la ling ga byas la de'i 'khrul 'khor h'u h'u bri /
NK033(gi)001:6227: zhing ras la khrag chen pos tsakra zur gsum pa bris la /
NK033(gi)001:6229: de'i zur gsum la sngags dang m+aa ra ya'i ming thams cad lar /
NK033(gi)001:6230: dang sbyar ba bri bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6231: de'i snying khar gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6232: dri chen dri chu khrag dang gshang lci bkus la /
NK033(gi)001:6233: gdug pa'i sems kyis snying khar tsher ma gzugs so //
NK033(gi)001:6234: thod pa'i nang du gan rkyal mgo lhor bstan la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:6235: rang nyid mda' gzhu bzung ste /
NK033(gi)001:6236: da du ra'i khu bas byugs la bsgrub bya'i gzugs brnyan la lan nyer gcig bsnun par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6237: de nas yang g.yas su ral gri thogs te /
NK033(gi)001:6238: g.yon pas ling ga bzung la /
NK033(gi)001:6239: ral gri la lan brgya rtsa brgyad du sngags bzlas shing dum bu stong du gtub par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6240: sngags la dzam mam mu khi sha trum m+aa ra ya tshin d+ha tshin d+ha /
NK033(gi)001:6245: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:6247: de nas gong gi thab khung du /
NK033(gi)001:6248: dur khrod kyi mgal du ma dang dug shing tsher ma can la me spar te /
NK033(gi)001:6249: khros pa'i sems kyis sngags gong ma bzlas shing bsreg par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6250: de ltar zhag bdun gyi bar du byas na dgra de nyid du 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:6252: ling ga thab khung du bsro bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6253: de la sngags brgya rtsa brgyad dus gsum du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6254: gal te 'dud par gyur na chu med pa'i 'o
NK033(gi)001:6255: mas ling ga dang thod pa bkru bar bya ste
NK033(gi)001:6256: / a mri ta h'u sh+aan+tim sa ma ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6257: de ltar ma byas na de nyid du 'chi ba la the tshom med do //
NK033(gi)001:6258: de la sogs te dbang du bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6264: bsad pa la sogs bcu gnyis kyi mtha' sbyar ba'i man ngag shes par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6265: lha mo gtum mo'i sgrub thabs dpal mi mo zhabs kyi rim pa las byung ba /
NK033(gi)001:6266: a na tsa na ti ka u bdun /
NK033(gi)001:6268: kha che'i slob dpon chen po dz+ny+aa na badz+ra zhal snga nas /
NK033(gi)001:6269: bod kyi dge slong smon lam byang chub kyis zhus te /
NK033(gi)001:6270: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba lha byang chub pas bsgyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:6271: kha che 'bring wa ba ti'i dpe la zhu gtugs byas nas /
NK033(gi)001:6272: kha che'i jo bo ma h+aa badz+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:6273: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba mar ngo chos kyi dbang phyug gis kyang gtan la phab pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6274: dge slong smon lam byang chub kyis ston pa ye
NK033(gi)001:6275: shes bla ma la d+aa ki dpang du btsugs te
NK033(gi)001:6276: / mi spel bar dam bcas te gnang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:6278: lha mo gtum mo la dgyes pa'i bstod pa /
NK033(gi)001:6280: de ba tsan d+he he he su dra /
NK033(gi)001:6282: lha mo gtum mo la dgyes pa'i bstod pa /
NK033(gi)001:6284: 'jig dus me ltar 'od dpung klong dkyil na //
NK033(gi)001:6285: dbang drag las mdzad gtum mo khro gnyer can //
NK033(gi)001:6286: drag mo chen mo 'jigs pa'i gzugs can ma //
NK033(gi)001:6287: sgrol ma dpal mo 'bar ba me yi gdong //
NK033(gi)001:6288: sku mdog dmar mo bskal pa'i me lta bu //
NK033(gi)001:6289: 'bar bas stong gsum bsreg mdzad tsan+di ka /
NK033(gi)001:6290: byi ru'i ral pa g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil /
NK033(gi)001:6291: 'jigs pa 'dul phyir nyi zla'i spyan gyis gzigs //
NK033(gi)001:6292: rngam zhing gtsigs pa'i zhal gyi brda' skad can //
NK033(gi)001:6293: sbrul dang rus pa'i phreng bas lus brgyan cing //
NK033(gi)001:6294: phyag g.yas ral gri me 'od 'bar ba 'debs //
NK033(gi)001:6295: srid gsum sgrol mdzad snying khrag dron mo rngubs //
NK033(gi)001:6296: snod mchog b+han d+ha bsnams pa'i khrag 'thung ma //
NK033(gi)001:6297: gdug pa mtha' dag dbyings su sgrol mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:6298: stag dang zhing gi lpags pa gos su gyon //
NK033(gi)001:6299: dur khrod brgyad na gnas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK033(gi)001:6300: 'byung po ro langs 'jigs pa'i gad mo can //
NK033(gi)001:6301: mang pos bskor ba'i dbus na 'gying mdzad cing //
NK033(gi)001:6302: bam chen ro yi gdan la brkyangs bskum bzhugs //
NK033(gi)001:6303: drag mo mi thub drag shul dbang drag sku //
NK033(gi)001:6304: srid gsum dgra bgegs rtsad nas 'joms mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:6305: gtum mo 'bar ba'i gdong la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6306: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i phra men ma //
NK033(gi)001:6307: mkha' la spyod pa'i mkha' 'gro bya rog gdong //
NK033(gi)001:6308: rnam dag skyon gyi ma gos sku mdog nag /
NK033(gi)001:6309: ye shes mtshon chas rgyu 'dren khrag mtsho gsol //
NK033(gi)001:6310: shes bya'i bag chags gcod mdzad ka ka ma //
NK033(gi)001:6311: rdo rje khwa gdong sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6312: gzung 'dzin dngos po za byed spyang ki'i gdong //
NK033(gi)001:6313: zhing chen khog pa khong nas dkrugs cing gsol //
NK033(gi)001:6314: mkha' 'gro rtags snyoms sna tshogs 'od ldan ma //
NK033(gi)001:6315: drag po'i las mdzad za byed shwa na ma //
NK033(gi)001:6316: rdo rje spyang gdong sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6317: khyi gdong dug gsum za byed gtsang rme med //
NK033(gi)001:6318: btang snyoms gzung 'dzin mtshan ma med par rtogs //
NK033(gi)001:6319: phyag gnyis gar gyis dgyes mdzad zhing chen rol //
NK033(gi)001:6320: rnam rtog skyon bral ku ku mu kha ma //
NK033(gi)001:6321: rdo rje khyi gdong sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6322: da ha ni mu khi dzam mam na mu ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6325: yo ga sarba sha trum ga ta pra ti sid+d+hi kar+m+aa na ma /
NK033(gi)001:6327: rnal 'byor pa thams cad kyi dgra tshar gcod pa'i dngos grub kyi las zhes bya ba /
NK033(gi)001:6328: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:6330: nyin zhag la dgra bsad par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:6331: mi bskyod pas gdong dang kha lag bkrus la /
NK033(gi)001:6332: kha lhor bltas la bdud rtsis kha bkang ste /
NK033(gi)001:6333: bsgyur bya'i rkang rjes kyi sa blangs sa'am phyi sa /
NK033(gi)001:6335: bag phye dang bsres la dgra'i gzugs bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6336: dur khrod kyi ras la 'chad par 'gyur ba'i 'khrul 'khor bris la /
NK033(gi)001:6337: de'i snying gar gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6338: dri chen dri chu dang khrag gis bku zhing snying khar tsher ma btsugs la /
NK033(gi)001:6339: thod pa'i nang du gzhug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6340: rang nyid kyi mda' glang ma'am /
NK033(gi)001:6346: bsgrub bya'i gzugs brnyan la lan nyer gcig tu bsnun par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6348: sha trum m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:6351: h+r+ai da ya sa ma s+ye h+aum phata phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:6352: gu ru gri h+na dz+ny+aa na a ma ri ya dz+ny+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6353: de nas dur khrod du bsreg khung byas la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6354: dgra'i gzugs brnyan gri gug gis dum bur gtubs la khros pa'i sems kyis bsreg par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6356: ji srid dbang du bya ba la sogs pa bcu gnyis kyi mthar thug par nyams par gyur pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:6358: 'o mas thod pa yongs su bkang ba de'i nang
NK033(gi)001:6359: du bstsal te sh+ain+tam sa ma ya ku ru s+w+aa
NK033(gi)001:6360: h+aa / zhes bya bas bkru bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6361: de ltar ma yin na mthar 'dis 'chi bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK033(gi)001:6363: ma h+aa na mu khe ya s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6364: 'dis 'chi bar 'gyur ba la the tshom mi za'o //
NK033(gi)001:6365: sngags de nyid kyis sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6366: dang por dal zur gsum pa kha dog dmar por byas la /
NK033(gi)001:6367: de'i dbus su thod pa dum bu'i nang du mar khus mar me sbar la /
NK033(gi)001:6368: de'i dbus su 'bar ba'i gdong can ma bsam par bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6369: gdong gcig ma la mig gsum ma /
NK033(gi)001:6373: rtsa ba'i lag gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:6374: lhag ma gnyis kyis gri gug dang /
NK033(gi)001:6375: thod pa mi'i rgyu ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:6376: sha khrag gis bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:6378: stag gi lpags pas smad dkris shing ro'i steng na gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:6379: mi mgo'i do shal byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:6380: kha nas me 'bar ba bsam par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6381: shar gyi zur du bya rog gi gdong can ma
NK033(gi)001:6382: mdog nag pa lag pa gnyis kyis mi ro bzung
NK033(gi)001:6384: ro yi steng na g.yas brkyang gis gnas bar bsam par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6385: bden bral gyi mtshams su lce spyang gi gdong can ma ser mo /
NK033(gi)001:6386: lag pa gnyis kyis ro bzung nas rke nas khrag 'jib pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6387: rlung gi mtshams su khyi gdong can ma sku mdog dud kha'i mdog can /
NK033(gi)001:6388: phyag gnyis kyis ro bzung nas za ba /
NK033(gi)001:6390: de ltar bsgoms nas rang nyid dpal khrag 'thung gi cho gas go cha bgo bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6392: bsrung ba'i don du khrag dang khu ba bsres pa'i thig les dpral ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6395: sha chen gyis bdug par byas la /
NK033(gi)001:6396: tsi ti b+hu ta ma ni pri ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6397: de nas rang nyid mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6398: de nas gdug pa can tshar bcad par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6400: lha mo 'bar ba'i gdong can ma spyan drangs par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:6401: dzam ma ni ti tsu b+hi sngags thams cad la mi 'dra ba yang snang /
NK033(gi)001:6403: sh+r+ai he ru ka dz+ny+aa ham d+ha dze hee ni
NK033(gi)001:6404: sarba na ba ka ri na g+h+ri hri na a
NK033(gi)001:6405: gad tsha ya a gad tsha ya dza s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6406: sngon du brjod pas dal zur gsum par chang dang
NK033(gi)001:6407: sha chen dang khrag gis brlan par byas pa'i me
NK033(gi)001:6408: tog la sogs pa rnams kyis mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6409: dzam mam ma mu khi bu dzam g+h+ri h+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6410: ka ka mu ki kam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6411: dzam su khi mu khi dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6412: shwa na mu khi sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6413: de ltar rab tu mchod nas /
NK033(gi)001:6414: khrag dang chu la sogs pas 'jigs byed la gtor ma sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6415: u nan ta b+he ra ba ya ba ling+ta g+h+ri h+nam ma ka t+yam sad d+ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6416: gtso bo nas ma rdzogs kyi bar du kem rus kyi phyag rgyas sbyin par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6417: sngon du 'bum phrag gcig gis bsnyen pa byas na 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:6418: de la sngags ni 'di yin te /
NK033(gi)001:6419: dzam lam lam na bri ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6420: ma h+aa na khye h+yi dza la na mam lam ni h+r+aihs+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6421: ma h+aa na mu khe dzam lan /
NK033(gi)001:6422: lam la ne h'u h'u phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:6423: dbang 'dis mgo mjug tu am gu bam /
NK033(gi)001:6425: dgug dzahh+aum bam hoh pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:6429: rengs par bya lte ba la gzer /
NK033(gi)001:6431: phur snying la seng ldeng gis /
NK033(gi)001:6440: zha rkang lag bar bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6443: thams cad phag khrag dang bya khrag gis /
NK033(gi)001:6444: du spyi'i longs spyod nyams par bya ba ste bcu gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:6445: kha che'i mkhan po dz+ny+aa na badz+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:6446: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong shes rab kyis bsgyur ba'o ////
NK033(gi)001:6449: don phrin las chags pa'i dbang gi sku //
NK033(gi)001:6450: sku mdog dmar mo 'bar ba me yi gdong //
NK033(gi)001:6451: ral pa dmar po byi ru'i lan tshar can //
NK033(gi)001:6452: phyag gnyis rdo rje mda' gzhu 'gengs pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6453: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med thugs rje yis //
NK033(gi)001:6454: nyon mongs dug tshogs bsgral nas dbyings su sdud //
NK033(gi)001:6455: lhag ma gnyis ni gri dang b+han d+ha bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:6456: 'khor ba rtsad gcod snying khrag dron mo gsol //
NK033(gi)001:6457: dus ngan tha ma'i sems can gdul dka' bas //
NK033(gi)001:6458: gsod pa'i nyi tshes 'dul mdzad 'bar ba'i gdong //
NK033(gi)001:6459: sgrol byed dpa' mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6460: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i phra men ma //
NK033(gi)001:6461: bya rog dbu dang spyang ki khyi yi dbu //
NK033(gi)001:6462: bud med chags pas 'dul bar dbang che bas //
NK033(gi)001:6463: 'khor ba'i ro dang dug gsum rol mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:6464: dgra bgegs tshar gcod mdzad pa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6466: bcom ldan 'das dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:6467: 'byung po'i nyin zhag la dgra bo bsad pa'i cho ga 'di brtsam ste /
NK033(gi)001:6468: de la dang po sgrol ma'i sprul pa tsan+di ka yi nga rgyal blangs te /
NK033(gi)001:6469: bdag shin tu khros pas zhing lpags kyi stan la 'dug ste /
NK033(gi)001:6470: mi bskyod pas gdong bkrus la /
NK033(gi)001:6472: lag par ral gri dang thod pa thogs te /
NK033(gi)001:6475: lho phyogs su kha bltas la /
NK033(gi)001:6476: bsnyen pa'i dus su 'bum bzlas te bsnyen pa la /
NK033(gi)001:6477: mdun du zhing lpags la khrag chen gyis dal zur gsum pa bris te /
NK033(gi)001:6478: dbus su thod pa'i nang du mar me spar la /
NK033(gi)001:6479: mar me'i dkyil du h+r+aihls byung ba'i lha mo sku mdog dmar mo /
NK033(gi)001:6480: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa mche ba gtsigs pa thod pa'i dbu rgyan can /
NK033(gi)001:6481: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:6482: phyag g.yas na ral gri g.yon na thod pa dgra bo'i khrag 'thung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:6483: me'i phyogs su kam las bya rog gi gdong pa can sku mdog nag mo /
NK033(gi)001:6484: phyag gnyis kyis ro blangs nas snying 'dren par byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6485: srin po'i mtshams su spyang gdong ma dzam las sku
NK033(gi)001:6486: mdog dkar dmar phyag gnyis kyis ro blangs nas mgrin
NK033(gi)001:6488: rlung gi mtshams su sham las khyi'i gdong ljang ku /
NK033(gi)001:6489: phyag gnyis kyis ro blangs nas za bar byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6490: de dag ni rgyan dang cha lugs dang /
NK033(gi)001:6491: gdan ni gtso mo dang mthun no //
NK033(gi)001:6492: de nas ye shes kyi lha mo spyan drangs la
NK033(gi)001:6493: sngar bshad pa'i zur gsum pa'i dal du mchod par
NK033(gi)001:6495: da ni drag po'i las bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:6496: bsgrub bya'i rdzas rkang rjes kyi sa dang /
NK033(gi)001:6499: rkee tshe dang lan tsh+wa rnams la ling ga byas te /
NK033(gi)001:6502: khrag chen gyis zur gsum pa bris pa /
NK033(gi)001:6504: zur la m+aa ra ya bris la /
NK033(gi)001:6505: ling gar gshang lci bkus la gdug pa'i sems kyis snying gar tsher ma gzugs so //
NK033(gi)001:6506: thod pa'i nang du gan rkyal du mgo lhor bstan la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:6508: zi ra nag pos brab cing /
NK033(gi)001:6509: sngags bzlas la ral gri'i char dbab pa'i bro brdungs bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6510: mdun du thab khung zur gsum pa brkos te /
NK033(gi)001:6511: dur khrod kyi mgal du ma mam shing tsher ma can la me spar te /
NK033(gi)001:6512: lag pa g.yon du ling ga blangs la /
NK033(gi)001:6513: g.yas su ral gri thogs te /
NK033(gi)001:6514: ral gris ling ga gtub cing thab khung du sngags
NK033(gi)001:6515: 'di bzlas shing ling ga'i dum bu re re bsreg
NK033(gi)001:6516: go // de ltar zhag gi bar du byas na dgra bo de nyid du 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:6517: 'di la the tshom du mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6519: ling ga brub khung du bsro bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6520: bzod par gsol zhing zhu na /
NK033(gi)001:6522: rang gi dpral bar khrag gis thig le byas te /
NK033(gi)001:6523: bdag dang dal la mchod pa lngas gtso la /
NK033(gi)001:6525: de nas sngags la 'dis ye shes lha mo spyan drangs par byas te /
NK033(gi)001:6526: dzam ma mu ham dzah si sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK033(gi)001:6527: ma ga ta d+ha dze ri ni sha sa na
NK033(gi)001:6528: ba ga ro nam gram e he a gad dzahdzahs+w+aa
NK033(gi)001:6531: ya mu khi p+au dza g+h+rih+na s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6532: ka bya rog ka mu khi kam p+au dza g+h+rih+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6533: dzam su khi spyang ki mu khe dzam p+au dza grih+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6535: mu khi sham p+au dza g+h+rih+na s+w+aa dee gsum mchod pa'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:6537: tsan+da kam dzam ma mu khi h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6538: snying kha la rak+sha yak+sha se na dz+aa dz+aa dz+aa phata phata phata /
NK033(gi)001:6540: dza bi mu tam b+hi an d+ha mu ka m+aa ra ya h+aum h+aum ha ha /
NK033(gi)001:6541: na mo b+ha ga wa te ro sha na ya
NK033(gi)001:6542: sha t+r+aum m+aa ra ya ga da dz+aa dz+aa ya
NK033(gi)001:6543: s+w+aa h+aa / dza ma bsad pa /
NK033(gi)001:6544: mu khi che ge mo sha t+r+aum m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:6552: h+r+aihkam dzam sham dze te pu ta me ni tre ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6555: tshul gyis ral gri b+han d+ha 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:6556: 'jig rten sgrol phyir rak+sha'i spyan gyis gzigs //
NK033(gi)001:6557: sku mdog dmar mo bskal ba'i me lta bu //
NK033(gi)001:6558: 'bar ba stong gsum bsreg mdzad tsan+di ka /
NK033(gi)001:6559: gtum mo mi bzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK033(gi)001:6560: mkha' la spyod pa'i d+aa ki bya rog dang //
NK033(gi)001:6561: zhes pa la sogs pa g.yog mo gsum la bstod pa btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:6562: kha che'i mkhan po dz+ny+aa na tsan+d+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:6563: bod kyi lo ts+wa ba lha byang chub dam pas bsgyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:6564: gtum mo mi bzad ma sgrol ma'i sgrub thabs dpal
NK033(gi)001:6565: mi mo zhabs kyi rim pa las byung ba rdzogs
NK033(gi)001:6566: so ////// rdo rje zam pa'i d+aa ki ma sde gsum gyi sgrub pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:6569: sa tha bi ra ni ra g+ha ta shwa ga na /
NK033(gi)001:6571: na ya yad sh+r+ai na pa ta /
NK033(gi)001:6574: gra ha sarba yo ga sid+d+hi pra do mu kha /
NK033(gi)001:6577: dza lan d+ha ra'i gnas bsgyur ba /
NK033(gi)001:6578: dpal gnas pa'i gzhung lugs las /
NK033(gi)001:6579: 'di ni dpal gyi mi mo zhabs kyi dngos grub blangs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:6580: dgra tshar bcad pa'i gdams ngag /
NK033(gi)001:6581: rnal 'byor pa thams cad la dngos grub ster ba'i gzhung lugs so //
NK033(gi)001:6582: dpal khrag 'thung rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:6583: man ngag 'di la don rnam pa brgyad kyis bstan te /
NK033(gi)001:6584: de la dang po dal gyi 'dod lugs bca' ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:6585: dam rdzas dgram pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:6586: bka' skyong zhi ba dang khro mo dpon g.yog tu bskyed pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:6587: ye shes pa spyan drangs pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:6588: de la mchod pa bya ba dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:6589: gtor ma btang ba dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:6590: bzlas pa bya ba dang bdun /
NK033(gi)001:6591: bzlas pa thems nas las la sbyor ba dang brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:6592: de la dang po sgrub pa'i dal bca' thabs ni /
NK033(gi)001:6593: stegs bu mda' tshad gru bzhi la //
NK033(gi)001:6594: zlum po'i e ni sum 'gyur brtsigs //
NK033(gi)001:6595: dang po dbus kyi pho brang ni //
NK033(gi)001:6596: zhi bar byed na zlum po la //
NK033(gi)001:6597: rgyas par byed na rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:6598: dbang du byed na zla gam la //
NK033(gi)001:6599: drag por byed na gru gsum bya //
NK033(gi)001:6600: dang po zhi ba byed na ni //
NK033(gi)001:6601: dbus su zlum por byas pas su //
NK033(gi)001:6602: phrin las rnam bzhi tshang ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:6603: chang dang sha chen khrag chen gyis //
NK033(gi)001:6604: man+dala kun la byug par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6605: khrag dang ro sol bsres pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:6606: gru gsum logs la byug par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6607: dbus kyi zlum po de la yang //
NK033(gi)001:6608: rin po che dang rus pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:6609: phye ma khrag dang sbyar ba byug /
NK033(gi)001:6610: e bsnol zur drug nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6611: mi rus rta rus la sogs pas //
NK033(gi)001:6612: dur khrod tshul du 'gengs par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6613: zhi ba sgrub pa'i dus su ni //
NK033(gi)001:6614: dbus kyi zlum po'i steng du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6615: dpal gyi 'dzin gtor chen po bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:6616: gru gsum gong ma'i zur gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:6617: zhi ba dmar po'i 'bag gsum gzug /
NK033(gi)001:6618: 'og ma'i zur ni gsum po la //
NK033(gi)001:6619: sha chen khrag chen gtor ma dang //
NK033(gi)001:6620: zhun chen sman chen gtor ma dang //
NK033(gi)001:6621: dkar gsum mngar gsum gtor ma dang //
NK033(gi)001:6622: mkha' 'gro gsum la mchod par bshams //
NK033(gi)001:6623: dang po rang nyid bsgom pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6624: rgyu ni ma nor rtsa ba'i sngags //
NK033(gi)001:6625: lus ngag yid gsum smin par byed //
NK033(gi)001:6626: rang nyid mngon rdzogs rgyal por bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:6627: spyi bor gser gyi 'khor lo'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:6628: ni ser po rdog gis bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:6629: ljags thog pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK033(gi)001:6631: thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram steng //
NK033(gi)001:6632: h+aum ni mthing ga rdog gis bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:6633: yi ge gsum po gsal ba las //
NK033(gi)001:6635: 'od kyis mchod cing sdig pa sbyangs //
NK033(gi)001:6636: tshur 'dus rang gi lus ngag yid //
NK033(gi)001:6637: sdig sgrib ma lus dag par byas //
NK033(gi)001:6638: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NK033(gi)001:6639: bcom ldan dpal dang mnyam par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6640: gang snang rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK033(gi)001:6641: dag par byed cing sdig sel ba //
NK033(gi)001:6642: ma nor rtsa ba'i sngags yin no //
NK033(gi)001:6643: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags la ni //
NK033(gi)001:6644: thabs dang shes rab bskyed pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:6645: a ham mi yi sa bon ni //
NK033(gi)001:6646: rang nyid yi dam lhar bskyed pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:6647: lte bar a dmar spyi bor ham //
NK033(gi)001:6648: a ham gnyis la blo gtad nas //
NK033(gi)001:6649: ma yengs gsal bar bgrangs pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:6651: thig le dkar dmar mer gyis khengs //
NK033(gi)001:6652: bde ba phril phril shig shig bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:6653: gnyis su med par nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:6655: bde ba chen pos lus gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:6656: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK033(gi)001:6657: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags yin no //
NK033(gi)001:6658: bzlas brjod las kyi sngags la ni //
NK033(gi)001:6659: rang nyid yi dam lhar gsal ba'i //
NK033(gi)001:6660: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas gsum nas //
NK033(gi)001:6661: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK033(gi)001:6663: bka' skyong mkha' 'gro sde gsum gyi //
NK033(gi)001:6664: tsa ka li ni gsum la phog /
NK033(gi)001:6665: lha mo gsum du gyur pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6666: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog dmar //
NK033(gi)001:6667: d+aa ma ru dang kha t+w+aam bsnams //
NK033(gi)001:6668: rus rgyan dbu skra sil bur grol //
NK033(gi)001:6669: nam mkha' khyab pa gar byed cing //
NK033(gi)001:6670: dbu skra bsig cing rus rgyan dkrug /
NK033(gi)001:6671: khams gsum srid gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK033(gi)001:6672: lha 'dre mi gsum dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)001:6673: lhag ma ma lus mkha' 'gror gyur //
NK033(gi)001:6674: mer mer shig shig yun du bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:6675: brjod pa'i snying po 'di yin te //
NK033(gi)001:6676: +amo badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta a bi pra sa la /
NK033(gi)001:6677: de ltar brjod pa'i rang sgra yis //
NK033(gi)001:6678: 'jig rten khams kun gang bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6679: de nas bdag la tshur 'dus pas //
NK033(gi)001:6680: 'gro ba ma lus don mdzad nas //
NK033(gi)001:6681: lhag med bdag la thim par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6682: bdag kyang thugs kyi la thim //
NK033(gi)001:6683: +amo ni sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NK033(gi)001:6684: 'od kyi rang bzhin dbyings su yal //
NK033(gi)001:6685: bsam med dran med mi g.yo ba //
NK033(gi)001:6686: dmigs su med pa'i ngang la gnas //
NK033(gi)001:6687: las bzhi bral ba'i dngos grub thob //
NK033(gi)001:6688: 'da' ba med pa'i dam tshig bsrung //
NK033(gi)001:6689: rtog 'dzin spangs pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK033(gi)001:6690: yang dag mtha' la rnam par gnas //
NK033(gi)001:6691: bzlas brjod las kyi sngags yin no //
NK033(gi)001:6692: sngags zhes bya ba skyob pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:6693: bsam pa'i yul dang bral bas te //
NK033(gi)001:6695: bla na med pa'i gsungs pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:6696: chos nyid mkha' la ye shes shar //
NK033(gi)001:6698: kun la thugs rjes ma bzhin skyob //
NK033(gi)001:6699: zhi ba bsgrub pa'i man ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:6700: gtor ma bdag gzhan don du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6701: dus su byin rlabs byas nas dbul //
NK033(gi)001:6702: mkha' 'gro ma zhi ba ye shes su sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)001:6703: de ni mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa'o //
