NK033(gi)001:6705: bka' skyong mkha' 'gro sde gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:6706: thun mong dngos grub zhu ba ni //
NK033(gi)001:6707: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)001:6709: de steng bzhugs pa'i dam rdzas ni //
NK033(gi)001:6710: rdza'am shing ngam rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:6711: gang yang rung ba'i rgyu de la //
NK033(gi)001:6712: rin chen 'bar ba'i gzugs bcos la //
NK033(gi)001:6713: de yi nang du gzhug pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6714: gter chen gdung gi gzugs sam dngos //
NK033(gi)001:6715: g.yas su 'khyil ba'i ngo bo la //
NK033(gi)001:6716: rin chen lnga dang 'bru sna bdun //
NK033(gi)001:6717: bsgrub bya'i snying po 'di dag ni //
NK033(gi)001:6721: sid+d+hi h'u bris la gter chen du gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:6722: de nas rang don skyabs 'gro dang //
NK033(gi)001:6723: gzhan gyi don du sems bskyed bya //
NK033(gi)001:6724: rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas bya //
NK033(gi)001:6725: dbus kyi zlum po'i nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6726: thod pa mtshan dang ldan pa ru //
NK033(gi)001:6728: zlum po'i dkyil du bzhugs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:6729: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab //
NK033(gi)001:6731: dbul 'phongs kun dang bral bar nges //
NK033(gi)001:6732: bca' gzhi'i khog dbub bstan pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6733: gru bzhi mthing ka zlum po dkar //
NK033(gi)001:6734: gru chad rnams ni ljang khu la //
NK033(gi)001:6735: 'og ma nag po gong ma dmar //
NK033(gi)001:6736: dbus kyi zlum por bzhugs pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6737: rang nyid yi dam lhar bskyed pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:6739: chos 'byung de yi nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6740: yig 'bru kam gsum chad pa las //
NK033(gi)001:6741: chos 'byung dur khrod chen po'i steng //
NK033(gi)001:6742: kem rus sgyil po gsum du bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:6743: de yi nang du 'od zer las //
NK033(gi)001:6744: yi ge dz+wa d+ha da dang gsum //
NK033(gi)001:6746: zhu nas mkha' 'gro gsum du gyur //
NK033(gi)001:6747: bka' skyong mkha' 'gro sde gsum ni //
NK033(gi)001:6748: sku mdog dmar mo zhal gcig ma //
NK033(gi)001:6749: phyag gnyis cang te'u kha t+w+aam ka /
NK033(gi)001:6750: thod pa 'dod yon bdud rtsis bkang //
NK033(gi)001:6751: gar mdzad khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)001:6752: dngos grub ci 'dod bdag la ster //
NK033(gi)001:6753: de ltar bskyed la sngags 'di bzlas //
NK033(gi)001:6754: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta a bi pra sa la /
NK033(gi)001:6755: de skad brjod cing mkha' 'gro ma'i //
NK033(gi)001:6756: spos sbyor dud pa btang ba ni //
NK033(gi)001:6757: nal bu'i sha khrag tshil chen dang //
NK033(gi)001:6758: g+hi wang spos dkar a mri ta //
NK033(gi)001:6759: sol ba'i me la bsreg par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6760: de ltar byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK033(gi)001:6761: yi dam lha yi 'od zer de //
NK033(gi)001:6762: bka' skyong mkha' 'gro gsum la phog /
NK033(gi)001:6764: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas mnyes par byas //
NK033(gi)001:6765: sku gsung thugs kyi bcud bsdus nas //
NK033(gi)001:6766: pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:6767: dur khrod gzhal yas khang gi nang //
NK033(gi)001:6768: gter ni chen po'i ngo bo ste //
NK033(gi)001:6769: yi ge t+r+aam gyi dngos por bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:6770: de nyid gyur pa'i rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:6771: 'bar ba chen po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6772: de yi nang du yi ge ni //
NK033(gi)001:6773: bam dang b+h+r+aum ma gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6775: stong gsum 'jig rten ma lus pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:6776: rtsi dang bcud kyi dngos po kun //
NK033(gi)001:6777: lhag ma med par tshur bsdus nas //
NK033(gi)001:6778: dung ni g.yas su 'khyil ba ste //
NK033(gi)001:6779: yid bzhin nor bu gcig tu gyur //
NK033(gi)001:6780: de nas snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:6785: la na la ni h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6786: zhes bargya'am stong du brjod pa na //
NK033(gi)001:6787: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen las //
NK033(gi)001:6788: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:6789: gsol ba ci btab 'byung bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6790: mchod pa byas shing dgos 'dod zhu //
NK033(gi)001:6792: dbul dang bral bar the tshom med //
NK033(gi)001:6793: sgrub pa po'i dgos 'dod yo byad 'byor ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:6794: 'jig rten zas nor gyi dngos grub 'byung ba /
NK033(gi)001:6795: bla ma du ston badz+ra shwa ra /
NK033(gi)001:6796: rin po che'i phyag bzhes so //
NK033(gi)001:6797: de ni thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6799: log par lta ba'i dgra tshar bcad pa /
NK033(gi)001:6800: khro mo dpon g.yog tu byas pa'i man ngag ni /
NK033(gi)001:6801: de la dang po drag po'i dal e gru gsum bsnol ma la /
NK033(gi)001:6802: gong ma'i rtse mo dgra phyogs su bstan pa la /
NK033(gi)001:6803: phyi dur khrod kyi rang bzhin byas pa la /
NK033(gi)001:6804: nang dug dang ro sol gyis byug par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6806: mi grir shi ba'i snying gi nang du mkha' 'gro
NK033(gi)001:6807: ma gtso mo gsum gyi rtsa ba'i srog snying gi
NK033(gi)001:6808: sngags grog la bris la gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:6809: man+dala gyi kha'am e gru gsum gong ma'i zur la rten du gzugs so //
NK033(gi)001:6812: khyi'am 'phar ba'i snying gi nang du /
NK033(gi)001:6813: g.yog mo'i srog gi snying po bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:6815: man+dala gyi steng ngam e gru gsum 'og ma'i sta zur gsum du gzugs so //
NK033(gi)001:6816: gtso mo gsum la sha chen khrag chen gyi gtor ma zhun chen sman chen gyi gtor ma /
NK033(gi)001:6817: dkar gsum mngar gsum gyi gtor ma byas la /
NK033(gi)001:6818: gong ma'i zur gsum la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:6819: g.yog mo gsum la zhag gi gtor ma /
NK033(gi)001:6824: glang gi khrag dang gsum la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6825: gtso mo gsum la gri bo'i snying la sogs pa snying sna tshogs pas gtor ma brgyan par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6827: khra spyang ki khyi dang gsum gyi snying gis gtor rgyan bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6828: g.yog mo'i gtor ma de gsum kyang e gru gsum 'og ma'i zur gsum la bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:6829: yang na gtor ma de tsho man+dala gyi kha na phar dgram /
NK033(gi)001:6830: yi dam la 'dzin gtor dbal dang bcas pa can gcig /
NK033(gi)001:6831: gtor ma bdun po de gta' gtor du gzung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:6832: de ni dam rdzas dgram pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:6834: khro mo dpon g.yog bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6835: dang po mkha' 'gro ma zhi ba gsum ni /
NK033(gi)001:6836: rang nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK033(gi)001:6837: yi ge dz+wa d+ha da dang gsum 'phros pas //
NK033(gi)001:6838: gru gsum phyi yi zur gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:6839: mkha' 'gro zhi ba gsum po ni //
NK033(gi)001:6841: phyag g.yas pa rdo rje sdigs mdzub dang /
NK033(gi)001:6842: 'og ma d+aa ma ru bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:6843: g.yon pa kha t+w+aam ka brkyang tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:6844: 'og ma ka p+aa la bdud rtsis bkang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:6845: sku mdog dmar mo gcer bu la /
NK033(gi)001:6846: dbu skra sil bur grol ba /
NK033(gi)001:6847: thod pa dum bu'i ske rags byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:6848: rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:6849: mi ro dmar po'i gdan stengs su /
NK033(gi)001:6850: rgyal po rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK033(gi)001:6851: rang gis de ltar bsgom par bya /
NK033(gi)001:6852: tsa ka li yang gzugs par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6853: bar gyi brub khung zur gsum po la /
NK033(gi)001:6854: 'bar ba'i gdong can la sogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:6855: mkha' 'gro ma gsum po bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6856: rang nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK033(gi)001:6857: yi ge dz+wa d+ha da gsum las //
NK033(gi)001:6858: zhal gcig spyan gsum shin tu dmar //
NK033(gi)001:6859: sku mdog dmar mo phyag bzhi ma //
NK033(gi)001:6860: zhabs gnyis g.yon bskum g.yas brkyang ma //
NK033(gi)001:6861: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis mda' gzhu 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:6862: brnag pa'i dgra la mda' bsnun nas //
NK033(gi)001:6863: snying kha nas tshur za bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6864: de 'og gnyis kyis gri gug dang //
NK033(gi)001:6865: thod pa klad khrag bkang ba 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:6866: brnag par byed pa'i dgra de ni //
NK033(gi)001:6867: g.yas pas gri gug bsnun nas su //
NK033(gi)001:6868: g.yon pa'i thod pa'i nang du ni //
NK033(gi)001:6869: rgyu ma klad khrag bcas pas bkang //
NK033(gi)001:6870: dkrugs shing zhal du gsol bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6871: yan lag lhu tshigs sprul gyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)001:6872: stag gi lpags pas smad g.yogs dkris //
NK033(gi)001:6873: mi ro dmar po'i gdan la gnas //
NK033(gi)001:6874: mi mgo rlon pa'i do shal can //
NK033(gi)001:6875: kha nas me 'bar khrag la ldag /
NK033(gi)001:6876: gru gsum 'bar ba'i zur gsum la //
NK033(gi)001:6877: rang gi de ltar bskyed pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:6878: tsa ka li yang gzugs par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6879: dbus kyi brub khung zur gsum du //
NK033(gi)001:6880: g.yog mo las mkhan gsum bskyed pa //
NK033(gi)001:6881: shar du yi ge kem las ni //
NK033(gi)001:6882: bya rog gdong can tsan ti ka /
NK033(gi)001:6883: nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma //
NK033(gi)001:6884: ro steng zhabs g.yas brkyang bas mnan //
NK033(gi)001:6885: phyag gnyis dag gis bzung nas su //
NK033(gi)001:6886: brnag pa'i dgra bo de yi ni //
NK033(gi)001:6887: mgo nas 'thog cing za bar bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6888: lho nas yi ge dzam las ni //
NK033(gi)001:6889: lce spyang mdog can shwa na ma //
NK033(gi)001:6890: ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma //
NK033(gi)001:6891: ro steng zhabs gnyis brkyang ba'i mnan //
NK033(gi)001:6892: phyag gnyis kyis ni bzung nas su //
NK033(gi)001:6893: brnag pa'i dgra bo de yis ni //
NK033(gi)001:6894: rtse chung khrag ni 'jibs par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6895: nub byang yi ge d+ha las ni //
NK033(gi)001:6896: khyi gdong u ma de wa ni //
NK033(gi)001:6897: zhal gcig phyag gnyis dud pa'i mdog /
NK033(gi)001:6898: zhabs ni g.yas brkyang ro mnan nas //
NK033(gi)001:6899: phyag gnyis kyi ni dgra bzung nas //
NK033(gi)001:6900: brnag pa'i dgra bo de yi ni //
NK033(gi)001:6901: mtshan ma nas bzung 'drad par bsam //
NK033(gi)001:6902: de nas mkha' 'gro gtso mo dang //
NK033(gi)001:6903: g.yog mo spyang gdong gzugs la bstim //
NK033(gi)001:6904: gtso mo gsum gyi spyan 'dren dang //
NK033(gi)001:6906: sngon du rang nyid yi dam bskyed //
NK033(gi)001:6907: sku gsung thugs kyi bsnyen pa bskyal //
NK033(gi)001:6908: de yang rang nyid he ru ka /
NK033(gi)001:6909: mngon rdzogs rgyal po tshul bzhin bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:6910: ru lu'i bsnyen pa 'bum du bskyal //
NK033(gi)001:6911: de nas gtso mo 'bod pa'i sngags //
NK033(gi)001:6912: re re la ni gsum gsum ste //
NK033(gi)001:6913: zhag dgu'i bar du 'bod par bya //
NK033(gi)001:6916: sh+r+ai he ru ka dzah d+ha ra sa na ba ke ro na g+h+rih+na /
NK033(gi)001:6922: he dzam si sh+r+ai he ru ka dzah d+ha ra sa na ba ke ro na g+h+rih+na /
NK033(gi)001:6928: he dzam si sh+r+ai he ru ka dzah d+ha ra sa na bke ro na g+h+rih+na /
NK033(gi)001:6932: g.yog mo gsum gyi 'bod pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6934: ka mu khi kam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6935: dzam su lce spyang mgo can /
NK033(gi)001:6936: khi mu khe dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6938: mu khi sham h+aum dza s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6939: yi dam gyi thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bus /
NK033(gi)001:6940: o rgyan gyi yul sprin nag po 'dus pa'i dur khrod nas /
NK033(gi)001:6941: mkha' 'gro ma gtso mo dang g.yog mor bcas pa bskul nas /
NK033(gi)001:6942: rang dpal chen por bskyed pa'i mdun du spyan drangs nas bskyed pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:6943: tsa ka li brub khung la btsugs pa de la bstim par byas nas /
NK033(gi)001:6944: mkha' 'gro ma dngos su bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:6945: de nas gtso mo gsum la mchod pa dang gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6946: mdun gyi man+dala gyi kha ru me tog dang mchod pa dang gtor ma bkram pa de tsho la /
NK033(gi)001:6947: rang yi dam du bsgoms pas byin rlabs byas pa sngags 'dis 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)001:6948: dz+wa la na he mu kha he p+au dza ba ling+ta g+h+ri h+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6949: d+ha ha na mu kha he p+au dza ba ling+ta g+h+rih+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6950: da ha na mu kha he p+au dza ba ling+ta g+h+ri h+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6951: de nas g.yog mo gsum la gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6952: u na ta be u ti me ra b+ha la /
NK033(gi)001:6955: ba lim ta g+hu hen ma ma ka ra ram pa ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6956: zhes gtor ma dgra bo'i sha khrag tu dmigs la 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)001:6957: de nas sngon du he ru kas rang bsrung ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6958: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)001:6959: tsit+ti b+h+ya d+hu ma ne phre ya y+aa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:6960: de nas rang gi yi dam gyi lha la mchod pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6961: sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:6962: ma h+aa ba ling+ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes ci za bas mchod pa bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6963: de nas gtso mo gsum gyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6964: dz+wa la ha na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6965: d+ha ha na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6966: da ha na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:6967: de la gtso mo re re la zhag gsum gsum dagu'am /
NK033(gi)001:6968: bsnyen pa 'bum bskyal na zhal mngon sum du ston du 'ong ste /
NK033(gi)001:6970: g.yog mo gsum gyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:6972: dzam su khi mu khi mu ki dzam /
NK033(gi)001:6973: shwa na mu khi sham h+aum dzah g.yog mo gsum gyi bsnyen pa ni khri bzlas na /
NK033(gi)001:6974: mkha' 'gro ma mngon sum du las byed du 'ong ste ci bcol ba nyan no //
NK033(gi)001:6975: dang po gtso mo nas las kyi bya ba ma zin gyi bar du /
NK033(gi)001:6976: bka' thod pa rgyas kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK033(gi)001:6977: gtor ma byin la las bcol lo //
NK033(gi)001:6978: brgyad pa bzlas pa thems nas las la sbyar ba la bdun te /
NK033(gi)001:6979: de la dang po ling ga bca' ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:6980: rang gi lag pa dri chus dag par bkrus la /
NK033(gi)001:6981: chus bshal la ling+ga la dri ma mi 'go bar byas /
NK033(gi)001:6982: de nas rang he ru ka ru bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:6987: dur khrod dam ro bsregs pa'i sa dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:6989: skas ka rnying pa chags pa'i shing /
NK033(gi)001:6990: gru rnying pa zhig pa'i shing /
NK033(gi)001:6991: zam pa chag pa'i shing dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:6994: chu mig lkug pa'i chu la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6998: ser ba bab pa'i chu la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:6999: de tsho dang dgra bo de'i dri chen dri chu dang /
NK033(gi)001:7001: mtshon gri ru shi ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7005: bag zan nam sa spyin po dang bsres la /
NK033(gi)001:7006: dgra'i gzugs brnyan byas te dur khrod kyi ras la
NK033(gi)001:7007: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i 'khrul 'khor bris la gzugs de'i
NK033(gi)001:7009: dri chen dang dri chu dang khrag byug par bya zhing snying khar tsher ma btsug la /
NK033(gi)001:7013: rabs chad shi ba'i skra yis /
NK033(gi)001:7014: ro gnya' lag 'khyig pa'i tshul du byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7015: brub khung gi nang du gan rkyal du bsgyel lo //
NK033(gi)001:7016: klo'am mon gyi thod pa'i nang du gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:7018: dur khrod kyi zhing ras ras la ni /
NK033(gi)001:7019: la dug chu dang gri ru shi ba'i khrag gis /
NK033(gi)001:7020: tsakra rtsibs brgyad pa'i rtse mo nang du bstan par bris la ling+ga la gcod 'khor lo'i dbal gyis /
NK033(gi)001:7022: dbus kyi lte ba la ling ga bris la /
NK033(gi)001:7023: snying kha ru mi du yod kyi ming dang rus
NK033(gi)001:7024: bris la dri chu dang sha khrag sngar gyi thun
NK033(gi)001:7025: kyang byug go // 'khor lo'i rtsibs kyi bar kun tu dgra du yod pa'i ming rus bri'o //
NK033(gi)001:7026: rtsibs kyi nang du sngags 'di dgod do //
NK033(gi)001:7030: h+aum s+ya ma sa ya da hri /
NK033(gi)001:7038: la da la d+ha la dz+wa /
NK033(gi)001:7039: g.yog mo gsum gyi srog sngags dang bsad sngags bri'o //
NK033(gi)001:7040: de nas 'khor lo de sngar gyi ling ga de'i snying khar gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:7041: de nas rang nyid yi dam mkha' 'gro ma khros
NK033(gi)001:7042: pa'i gzugs kyis drag po'i ting nge 'dzin du byas
NK033(gi)001:7043: la / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK033(gi)001:7044: ang+ku sha dzah sa gang na 'dug pa de dbang du bsdus /
NK033(gi)001:7046: h+aum gis ling ga la dgra bo de tsho bstim /
NK033(gi)001:7047: bam gyis lcags sgrog gis bsdams //
NK033(gi)001:7049: de gsod pa la dga' bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:7050: sdang ba'i dgra bo la gnod pa skyel te d+aa ki ma rnams kyis gsod pas sdang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7052: ling+ga'i mgo la dug chu byug /
NK033(gi)001:7053: rengs par bya ba ni lte ba la skyer pa'i tsher ma gzer /
NK033(gi)001:7055: snying la seng ldeng gi phur pa gdab /
NK033(gi)001:7057: ngag phrog pa ni lce la btsan dug dang dug sna byug /
NK033(gi)001:7059: snying la khyi dang ba glang gi khrag byug /
NK033(gi)001:7061: yan lag la mdze pho'i khrag byug /
NK033(gi)001:7063: rna ba la lkug pa'i klad pa byug /
NK033(gi)001:7064: longs spyod nyams par bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7066: gtor byed bya'i khrag ling ga la byug /
NK033(gi)001:7067: de tsho thun yang brdeg go //
NK033(gi)001:7068: de nas ling+ga de lha dang bral ba'i thabs 'di tsho byed pa gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:7070: khyi lud de gnyis kyi du ba ling+ga la bdug
NK033(gi)001:7071: la kho rang gi 'go ba'i lha lnga sngon du
NK033(gi)001:7072: phral lo // de nas rang nyid skra bshig la he ru kas rang bsrung ba bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7073: de nas mkha' 'gro ma gtso mo dang g.yog mo 'bod pas spyan drangs /
NK033(gi)001:7074: srog snying gis bsad pa'i dus la bab par dgra bsad pa'i rtags thon par bgrangs /
NK033(gi)001:7075: zhun chen gyi mar me nub gsum /
NK033(gi)001:7077: rtsi'i mar me nub gsum btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7078: nub dgu po des 'grub par bshad do //
NK033(gi)001:7079: gtor ma drag tu btang la dmod bcol bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7080: nang rtags byung nas dgra la 'gror ma btub na /
NK033(gi)001:7081: gtor ma 'phral la mi btang bar /
NK033(gi)001:7083: gtor ma byin gyi byas la gtang rag tu khas blangs /
NK033(gi)001:7084: thun mtshams su las bcol zhing bstab pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7085: a phyi chen mo mthu mo che //
NK033(gi)001:7086: nad dang rims kyi bdag mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:7087: dam tshig gsang ba'i tshul bstan pa //
NK033(gi)001:7088: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad gtso mo ste //
NK033(gi)001:7089: bdud dang srin po g.yog mo srog bdag da khol la //
NK033(gi)001:7090: dgra bo bdag la brnag pa 'di la rtags phyungs shig /
NK033(gi)001:7091: dam tshig tshul bzhin skyongs la ni //
NK033(gi)001:7092: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)001:7098: snyan brgyud kyi srung mar khas blangs nas /
NK033(gi)001:7099: rang dam rang gis bcas pa yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:7100: dam tshig nyams na khyed rang tshig par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7101: bdag chos la gnas su mi ster ba /
NK033(gi)001:7102: bstan pa skyong du mi ster ba /
NK033(gi)001:7104: thun mtshams su bstab pa drag tu bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7105: de ru mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis /
NK033(gi)001:7106: brnag pa'i dgra bo gang na 'dug pa bkug nas /
NK033(gi)001:7107: mgo dang rkang lag la sogs pa nas tshur la /
NK033(gi)001:7108: sngar bskyed pa bzhin du sha zos khrag 'thung bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:7109: de nas rang nyid mkha' 'gro 'bar ba'i gdong can
NK033(gi)001:7110: la sogs pa gong bzhin du khro mo ru bskyed
NK033(gi)001:7111: la / mda' dang phur bus brdeg cing thang phrom gyi thun gyi brab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7112: rang nyid mda' gzhu bzung ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7113: 'od ma'i gzhu dang skyer pa'i mda' la /
NK033(gi)001:7114: d+ha du ra'i khu ba byug la /
NK033(gi)001:7131: sngags 'di tsho brgya rtsa brgyad dam nyi shu rtsa gcig la /
NK033(gi)001:7132: ling ga'i snying kha ru mda' re rgyag go //
NK033(gi)001:7133: srog rbad rbad bcad par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:7134: snying kha ru seng ldeng gi phur pa lan nyi shu rtsa gcig tu sngar bzhin du brdeg go //
NK033(gi)001:7139: gri thun gyis dum bur gtub bo //
NK033(gi)001:7140: khros pa'i sems kyis bsad sngags dang bcas par bsreg par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7145: shi ba la sogs pa sngar bzhin du gsal bar bsgom par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7146: de nas phyi rtags su lung ba 'ja' dang 'od kyis khengs pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:7147: sgra chen po 'brug dang thog rgyab pa 'dra ba 'ong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7148: nang rtags me mched pa dgra'i phyogs su song nas dgra'i grong khyer mes tshig pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:7150: nang du mar me'i 'od dam me 'bar ba'am /
NK033(gi)001:7151: dgra bo'i bla tshe bkug nas srog chags bsad nas /
NK033(gi)001:7152: sha khrag za ba 'ong ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:7153: rtags rdzogs nas bsad las zin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7154: las gzhug sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7155: sbyin sreg byed pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:7156: nya dang dus bzhi'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:7157: zhag gsum gsum na lan re byed pa de /
NK033(gi)001:7158: thebs zlog rtsis la dus bzang po la gtad la lan gsum du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7159: sbyin sreg byed pa'i 'dug sa de nas spos la
NK033(gi)001:7160: dur khrod du bsreg khung byas la sbyin sreg bya'o
NK033(gi)001:7161: // yang nang rtags bzang na gnas de nyid du sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7162: dang por dal gru gsum du /
NK033(gi)001:7167: mkha' 'gro ma gtso mo gsum dz+wa d+ha da gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:7168: brub khung nang du me lha bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7169: zhal gcig spyan gsum sku mdog dmar /
NK033(gi)001:7170: phyag bzhi zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum la /
NK033(gi)001:7172: gri gug thod pa mi'i rgyu ma dang klad khrag gis bkang ba /
NK033(gi)001:7173: sbrul dang stag gi pags pas brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)001:7174: mi ro'i steng na gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:7176: kha nas me 'bar bas dgra bsreg cing khrag dang zhag gi khu ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK033(gi)001:7177: gro snying rgyu mar bcas pa thod par dkrug cing zhal du gsol ba gsum bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:7179: shar zur du bya rog gdong can /
NK033(gi)001:7180: lho nub tu lce spyang gdong can /
NK033(gi)001:7181: nub byang du khyi'i gdong can /
NK033(gi)001:7182: yi ge kem dzam d+ha gsum las sku mdog nag mo /
NK033(gi)001:7185: brub khung gi zur gsum nas dgra bo'i mgo dang
NK033(gi)001:7186: rtse'u chung mtshan ma gsum las za 'drad byed cing
NK033(gi)001:7187: klad khrag 'thung zhing khu ba 'jibs par bsam mo
NK033(gi)001:7188: // lha mo dpon g.yog tsho sngags kyi 'bod /
NK033(gi)001:7191: bsad las byas nas dagra'am gzugs brnyan de la mda' rgyag /
NK033(gi)001:7193: thun gyi brab pa'i lhag ma de gri gug gam /
NK033(gi)001:7194: mi bsad pa'i gris dum bur gtubs la /
NK033(gi)001:7195: rang nyid he ru kar bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:7196: rang bsrung ba'i sngags 'di bgrang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7197: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:7198: tsit+ti b+h+ya d+hu ma ne phre ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:7199: de nas dpal chen bsgoms la thal chen tshom bu /
NK033(gi)001:7201: zhag gi zo ris byas te rang la bsrung bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7202: po'i thugs ka nas mchod pa'i lha mo bton la /
NK033(gi)001:7203: gtor ma byin gyis brlabs la /
NK033(gi)001:7204: 'dod yon gyis dpal chen po nyid la mchod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7205: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu yang gsol bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7206: de nas gdug pa can tshar bcad pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)001:7207: rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rjer bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:7208: lha mo dpon g.yog tsho yi dam dpal gyi thugs
NK033(gi)001:7209: ka nas 'od lcags kyu lta bus sprin nag po
NK033(gi)001:7210: 'dus pa'i gseb nas spyan drangs la /
NK033(gi)001:7211: me lha thab tu bskyed pa'i tsho la bstim pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7215: he dzam si sh+r+ai he ru ka dzahd+ha ra sa na pa ke ro na /
NK033(gi)001:7218: gtso mo gsum spyan drangs nas bstim pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7220: dzam su khi mu khi mu ki dzam /
NK033(gi)001:7221: shwa na mu khi sham h+aum dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:7222: des su g.yog mo gsum spyan drangs la bstim mo //
NK033(gi)001:7223: de nas srog snying bgrang la /
NK033(gi)001:7224: de'i rting la gtor ma 'bul ba'i sngags kyis mchod /
NK033(gi)001:7225: de'i gsham du bsad pa'i sngags kyis ling ga gtubs la snod bkang la /
NK033(gi)001:7226: khros pa'i sems kyis yi dam du bskyed la mchod rdzas dang /
NK033(gi)001:7234: rang ci za ba'i phud dang /
NK033(gi)001:7236: me lha d+aa ki ma dpon g.yog gi zhal du dbul zhing /
NK033(gi)001:7237: dgra'i rkang mthil dmar lhag ge zhal du song bar bsam zhing /
NK033(gi)001:7238: sbyin sreg gi sngags 'dis dbul zhing bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:7242: mu khe sh+ain+tamnga m+aa ra ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa phata /
NK033(gi)001:7244: dzam su khi mu ki dzam /
NK033(gi)001:7245: shwa na mu khi sham h+aum dza /
NK033(gi)001:7246: mu khi sh+aan+tinga m+aa ra ya ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:7247: de 'dra ma lan gsum du byas na dgra bo
NK033(gi)001:7248: du yod kyang 'chi ba la the tshom med do
NK033(gi)001:7249: // bargya'am stong du byas na tshangs pa'i lha bu'i tshe yang 'joms /
NK033(gi)001:7250: de nas gta' gtor cha gsum byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7251: cha gcig bsreg nas cha gcig 'phral gtor du btang la /
NK033(gi)001:7252: cha gcig las gzhug mnan pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7253: spyin sreg gi thal ba la brnag pa'i dgra bo'i gzugs byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7254: snying khar sngar bzhin du 'khor lo bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:7255: mnan pa'i sngags tsho bris la 'khor lo de ngan thod du bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:7256: ro ras sam re bas dril /
NK033(gi)001:7259: lha khang gi them pa'i 'og tu mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:7260: gnon pa'i dus su rang bsrung ba he ru ka'i sngags mang du bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:7261: gong du mchod pa nyid lan gsum du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7263: sbyin sreg dang mnan pa yang lan gsum du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7264: he dzam yan chad gsum kha dril nas /
NK033(gi)001:7265: shing bu la ni sh+r+ai he ru ka 'dogs pa lugs gcig yin no //
NK033(gi)001:7270: zhes drag tu bzlas la mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:7271: mtshams khongs su dgra shi na brub khung de rang gi nang du mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:7272: des ni las gzhug 'dus pa yin pas shin tu zab bo //
NK033(gi)001:7273: rdzogs chen brgyud pa tha ma'i gdams ngag rna brgyud
NK033(gi)001:7274: rin po che rdo rje zam pa'i bka' skyong d+aa
NK033(gi)001:7275: ki ma sde gsum la mchog gi dngos grub 'tshang
NK033(gi)001:7277: thun mong gi dngos grub zas nor 'du ba'i sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)001:7278: mthu'i dngos grub d+aa ki ma ngan sngags su bsgrubs nas dgra tshar bcad pa /
NK033(gi)001:7279: chos 'di skyong nges pa'i dam tshig can las gzhan
NK033(gi)001:7280: la ma byin gsungs nas bdag la gnang ba yin
NK033(gi)001:7281: no // d+aa ki'i chos ma 'khrugs pa 'di /
NK033(gi)001:7282: zhag dgus 'grub pa ston par kha che'i mkhan po dz+ny+aa na sh+r+ai sid+ha badz+ra dang /
NK033(gi)001:7283: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong shes rab bee ro tsa na /
NK033(gi)001:7285: d+aa ki'i sgrub pa rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:7289: slob dpon kun bzang rdo rje /
NK033(gi)001:7290: rje btsun sangs rgyas rdo rje /
NK033(gi)001:7291: skye tshe ye shes dbang phyug /
NK033(gi)001:7293: bla ma du ston chen po /
NK033(gi)001:7297: mthu dang sri'u gso ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7298: nor thams cad 'di las 'byung ba yin gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7299: d+aa ki ye shes lnga ru bsgrubs pas nyams dang rtogs pa 'phel ba /
NK033(gi)001:7300: d+aa ki gnod sbyin nor lhar bsgrubs pas zas nor longs spyod 'phel ba /
NK033(gi)001:7301: d+aa ki las kyi srin mor bsgrubs pas dgra bgegs tshang gcod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7303: d+aa ki gsang spyod kyi sgrub thabs bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:7304: dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:7305: mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang spyod sgrub pa 'di la don rnam pa gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:7307: nyams dang gzi mdangs bskyed pa'i dus /
NK033(gi)001:7308: bar chad sel ba'i dus dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:7309: de la dang po nyams skyong ba'i dus ni /
NK033(gi)001:7310: bdag rang rdo rje rnal 'byor ma dkar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
NK033(gi)001:7311: phyag g.yas na thod pa'i d+aa ma ru bkrol ba /
NK033(gi)001:7312: g.yon na kha t+w+aam ka dang ka p+aa la bdud rtsis bkang ba bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:7313: de'i spyi bo na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad
NK033(gi)001:7314: pa'i steng na +amo gser btso ma lta bu yod
NK033(gi)001:7315: pa / lce pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i steng na +aahdamara po mchong bcag pa lta bu yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7316: snying gar rdo rje rgya gram steng na h+aum mthing ga bee d+aur+ya lta bu yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7317: yi ge de gsum 'dar phri li li 'dug par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7318: snang ba thams cad rnal 'byor ma dkar mo lam gyis bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7320: dran rtog kyang thugs dang gsung du bsam zhing +amo
NK033(gi)001:7321: +aah h'u zhes pa'i ye ge gsum sbrel la bzlas
NK033(gi)001:7322: so // de nyams skyong ba'i dus so //
NK033(gi)001:7324: nyams dang gzi mdangs bskyed par byed pa'i dus ni //
NK033(gi)001:7325: bdag rang rdo rje rnal 'byor ma dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:7326: yi ge gsum dgod pa dang khyer so tsam snga ma dang 'dra ba la dang /
NK033(gi)001:7327: lta stangs steng du mthor btang ba'i chog go //
NK033(gi)001:7328: bar chad sel ba'i dus ni /
NK033(gi)001:7329: bdag rang rnal 'byor ma nag mor bsgom pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7331: zla ba gsum du ri khrod brten /
NK033(gi)001:7334: de'i bar du mkha' 'gro ma'i spos sbyor bya /
NK033(gi)001:7337: mi dang ma phrad na bar dor mkha' spyod la gshegs nges the tshom med gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7339: 'di mkha' 'gro sde gsum la brten pa yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:7340: thun bar du brda' bzhi lus kyi 'dug tshul gtum mo bzhin du byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7341: gsal ba'i brda' mig sna rtser blta /
NK033(gi)001:7342: bde ba'i brda' 'og rlung yid tsam 'then /
NK033(gi)001:7343: mi rtog pa'i brda' lus mi 'gul bar bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:7344: dbyer mi phyed pa'i brdas lce yar rkan mar rkan la ma reg pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7345: khyad par du sna bug g.yon nas 'gyu dus su bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:7346: de gnad dang dus kyi brda' yin no gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7347: la blta ba gal che gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7349: d+aa ki mkha' spyod sgrub pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:7350: dpal he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:7351: rdo rje mkha' 'gro la brten nas mkha' spyod sgrub pa'i thabs /
NK033(gi)001:7353: mkho ba'i yo ri khrod du bsgrub pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:7357: de nas yid dam lhar bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7358: nyi ma zla ba kha sbyor ba'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du /
NK033(gi)001:7359: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:7360: g.yas na gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK033(gi)001:7361: g.yon na shel gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)001:7362: sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:7363: yum dang 'khril sbyor du bzhugs pa bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:7364: rang de ltar bsgom pa'i mdun na mkha' 'gro ma gsum gar khyug khyug mdzad par bsgom zhing /
NK033(gi)001:7365: sngags 'di rgyun chad med par bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:7366: badz+ra su lam ma lam ma ma ru ru tsit+ta
NK033(gi)001:7367: a bi pra sa la +aahh+aum zhes mkha' 'gro ma'i
NK033(gi)001:7368: zhun chen gyi mar me ma chad par bya gsungs
NK033(gi)001:7369: / spos bsreg cing zla ba drug bsgrub na /
NK033(gi)001:7370: de nyid du mkha' spyod la gshegs par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7371: dam tshig tu mi dang gdong mi 'phrad /
NK033(gi)001:7373: mkha' spyod bsgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK033(gi)001:7375: sku mdog dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:7376: g.yas na thod pa'i d+aa ma ru /
NK033(gi)001:7377: g.yon na ka p+aa li dang kha t+w+aam ka bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:7378: zhabs g.yon brkyang g.yas bskum pa rus pa'i rgyan btags pa /
NK033(gi)001:7379: de lta bu gsum gsal ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:7380: gtor ma ma chag par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7381: de yang sha chen gtor ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7384: rtags ni bud med bzang mos glu len pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7385: gar byed pa byung na bzang /
NK033(gi)001:7386: sprang mo dang mdze mor byung na ngan no //
NK033(gi)001:7390: mi grir shi ba'i klad pa /
NK033(gi)001:7392: bya sha zan gyi sgo nga /
NK033(gi)001:7395: gu gul dkar po rnams spos hring bzang po dang sbyor ro //
NK033(gi)001:7397: de shug pa'i me la bsreg go //
NK033(gi)001:7398: mkha' spyod ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:7399: gsum pa cha lag gi skor la ///
NK033(gi)001:7400: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum gyi gtor chog bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:7401: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:7402: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7403: gtor ma'i snod ci 'byor ba'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:7404: zas ci 'byor pas gtor ma bshams la /
NK033(gi)001:7405: bla ma yi dam la dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:7406: mkha' 'gro ma la dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7407: zhing las skyes la sha lnga bdud rtsi lngas brgyan /
NK033(gi)001:7408: las las skyes la dkar gsum gyis brgyan /
NK033(gi)001:7409: sngags las skyes la a mri tas brgyan pa byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7410: de la sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7411: bdag gi snying khar +amo kha dog lnga dang ldan pa gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7412: de las ma dmar ser gcig lag pa g.yon pa'i
NK033(gi)001:7413: mthil du rgyangs kyis byung bar bsam ste gtor ma
NK033(gi)001:7414: la deng bya / yang +amo de las a dkar
NK033(gi)001:7415: po gcig lag pa g.yas pa'i mthil du rgyangs kyis
NK033(gi)001:7416: la deng bya / byung bar bsam / de yang gtor ma la deng bya /
NK033(gi)001:7417: yang +amo de las h+aum sngon po gcig lag pa
NK033(gi)001:7418: gnyis kyi mtheb chen sbrel ba'i bar du mgo mthur
NK033(gi)001:7419: la 'phyang ba gcig rgyangs kyis byung bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7420: de nas h+aum des gtor ma de dkrugs shing +aahh+aum
NK033(gi)001:7421: lan gsum brjod pas lag pa g.yon pa'i ma las
NK033(gi)001:7423: de las bdud rtsi dkar me re re byung bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7424: de +aahh+aum lan gsum brjod cing chos 'khor du dkrugs pas /
NK033(gi)001:7425: g.yas pa'i +aahls zla ba'i dkyil 'khor de las bdud rtsi dkar me re re byung bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7426: de las bdud rtsi ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa
NK033(gi)001:7427: de bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong spyan
NK033(gi)001:7428: drangs la mchod pa phul bas mnyes par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7429: de la sngags kyi byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7430: ma h+aa ba ling+ta te dzo ba ling+ta ba la ba ti gu h+ya sa ma ye sat+wa h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:7431: zhes lan bdun nam gsum brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:7432: phyag rgya mtheb chen sbrel te bskor /
NK033(gi)001:7433: de nas bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro spyan drang ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7434: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7435: gu ru d+aa ki ni h+aum h+aum sa m+aa dzah
NK033(gi)001:7436: de wa d+aa ki ni h+aum h+aum sa m+aa dzah
NK033(gi)001:7437: dz+wo ki d+aa ki ni h+aum h+aum sa m+aa dzah
NK033(gi)001:7438: gdan dbul ba / gu ru man+da la /
NK033(gi)001:7441: de nas gtor ma dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7442: gu ru d+aa ki ni ye e dam ba ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7443: d+he wa d+aa ki ni ye e dam ba ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7444: dz+wo ki d+aa ki ni ye e dam ba ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7445: de re re la lan gsum gsum brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:7446: de nas tshigs bcad kyis dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7447: byin gyis rlobs pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7448: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7449: rim pa dbang gi bla ma dam pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7450: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7451: shes rgyud grol ba'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7452: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7453: nges pa ston pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7454: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7455: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7456: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7457: badz+ra he ru ka'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7458: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7459: rat+na he ru ka'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7460: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7461: pad+ma he ru ka'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7462: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7463: karma he ru ka'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7464: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7465: he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7466: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7467: zhing las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma /
NK033(gi)001:7469: dur khrod chen po brgyad na gnas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7470: mkha' 'gro ma 'bar ba'i gdong can 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7471: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7472: las las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma /
NK033(gi)001:7473: bud+d+ha rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7474: rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7475: rin po che'i rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7476: pad+ma'i rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7477: las kyi rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:7478: mkha' la gshegs ma 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7479: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i mchod pa bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7480: sngags las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro ma /
NK033(gi)001:7483: sman mo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:7484: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:7489: mkha' 'gro ma mkha' la spyod ma 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK033(gi)001:7490: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i gtor ma bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)001:7491: gzhan yang bka' dang bstan pa bsrung zhing 'khor dang
NK033(gi)001:7492: gang zag skyong ba'i mgon po dam tshig can thams
NK033(gi)001:7493: cad la / dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i 'bar ba'i gtor ma 'di 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)001:7496: gtor ma'i cho ga yongs su rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:7499: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i mkha' 'gro'i spos sbyor ni /
NK033(gi)001:7502: bya sha zan gyi klad pa /
NK033(gi)001:7506: mar nag dang chang du blugs /
NK033(gi)001:7508: spos sbyor ba de ni mo thod mtshan ldan du blugs /
NK033(gi)001:7509: pho thod mtshan ldan gyi kha bkab /
NK033(gi)001:7511: rang yi dam gyi lhar bsgom la sngags gsum gyis
NK033(gi)001:7512: mkha' 'gro ma gsum mdun gyi nam mkha' la sprin
NK033(gi)001:7513: gtibs pa bzhin byon nas byin gyis brlabs par bsam
NK033(gi)001:7514: / des ni dngos su grub pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7516: g.yo rong gi slob dpon rdo rje dbang phyug la /
NK033(gi)001:7517: gnyags ha lo gdong pa'i dge bshes kyis zhus pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7519: 'di skabs lnga pa'i gsan yig tu mkha' 'gro'i mchod
NK033(gi)001:7520: gtor zhes pa snang rung dpe rgyun la mi gsal
NK033(gi)001:7521: /// bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK033(gi)001:7522: e a ral+li hoh zhes rang nyid rol lo //
NK033(gi)001:7525: lte bar mkha' 'gro ma rnams la mchod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7526: de nas zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:7527: kun bzang bde ba che la 'dud /
NK033(gi)001:7528: no pi ka rgyud a ti gsang ba 'dud pas gsung /
NK033(gi)001:7529: ka na e a ga ta rnams gcig tu spyan 'dren /
NK033(gi)001:7531: bam b+han+d+ha ga ta rnams gcig tu 'dus pa /
NK033(gi)001:7532: ma ma ga ta rnams gcig tu dgyes pa /
NK033(gi)001:7533: tra ti ya ya hi ma ga ta rnams phrin las brjod /
NK033(gi)001:7534: a dam tshig mu dra chags pa med pa'i dam tshig rjes su 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:7535: pamh phyag rgya chen po'i ye shes rdo rje lta bu'i dam tshig rjes su 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:7536: mam las kyi mu dra sku gsung thugs kyi phrin
NK033(gi)001:7537: las yongs su rdzogs pa'i dam tshig rjes su 'dzin
NK033(gi)001:7538: pa / ya chos kyi mu dra thabs dang shes
NK033(gi)001:7539: rab gnyis su dbyer med pa'i dam tshig rjes su
NK033(gi)001:7540: pa / 'dzin pa / sa ma ti ting nge
NK033(gi)001:7541: 'dzin rang gi sems nyid la brda' bzhi brtan par
NK033(gi)001:7542: pa / 'dzin pa / bya'o // ka pa sku
NK033(gi)001:7543: gsung thugs kyi chos thams cad ngo bor gnas pa
NK033(gi)001:7548: +aah gsung nye ba'i snying po rtag tu brjod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7549: h+aum byang chub sems dpa' gsung gi dbang phyug chos kyis gsungs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7550: 'di skabs byang sems dkar dmar sbyor thabs snang rung byin rlabs rgyas pa'i mjug na yod do //
NK033(gi)001:7551: yang lnga pa'i gsan yig tu chos dam tshig las
NK033(gi)001:7552: kyi mu dra gsum gyi sngags 'grel zhes pa de
NK033(gi)001:7553: gzhung 'dir dngos bstan ma byung bas gzhan nas byung
NK033(gi)001:7554: tshe bsab dgos /// 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi yi ge 'bru gcig pa'i cho ga /
NK033(gi)001:7555: tad+ya th+aa k+sh+nim gsang sngags yi ge 'bru gcig pa 'di rab tu gsang ba'i don te /
NK033(gi)001:7556: don thams cad grub par byed pa /
NK033(gi)001:7558: 'dis re ba thams cad yongs su skong bar byed pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:7560: gzungs bsdus nas phyungs pa yin no //////
NK033(gi)001:7562: drang srong rdzogs byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:7563: bcud len bdud rtsi'i sgrub thabs brjod par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:7564: bdud rtsi phul gang 'o ma dang phye mar bskol te 'o ma nyi tshe lus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7565: 'o ma de la nyin rer 'ju tshod kyis 'thung na /
NK033(gi)001:7566: zhag nyi shu rtsa bdun gsum gyis rgas pa med
NK033(gi)001:7567: cing lo bcu drug lon pa'i sha tshugs su 'gyur
NK033(gi)001:7568: zhing tshe lo stong thub par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7569: yang na bdud rtsi'i chu phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7570: rgya sran tshos pa'i khu ba phul brgyad dang /
NK033(gi)001:7571: mar phul gang phul brgyad gsum bkol bas brgyad du btang /
NK033(gi)001:7573: rnams bkol te mar nyi tshe lus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7574: grang du bcug pa sbrang rtsi bre phyed tsam dang sbyar te /
NK033(gi)001:7575: zla ba gcig bar du ran tshod du zos na yid gzhungs la /
NK033(gi)001:7576: lo bcu drug pa 'dra bar 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:7578: yang na bdud rtsi'i chu bskol te /
NK033(gi)001:7579: bcu drug cha lus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7580: mar bre bzhi til phul gang rnams bskol te /
NK033(gi)001:7581: mar nyi tshe lus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7583: rgas pa med cing thos pa mi brjed par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7584: yang na zla ba gcig gi bar du nang re bdud rtsi'i chu khyor ba re re 'thung na /
NK033(gi)001:7585: rgas pa med cing tshe lo lnga brgya thub par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7586: bdud rtsis zla ba gcig tu khrus byas na yang rgas pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7587: yang na zla ba gcig gi bar du nyin re bzhin snar blugs na yang gong dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:7588: bdud rtsi dngul chu brag zhun snar blugs na yang gong dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:7589: bdud rtsi dngul chu brag zhun gsum gcig tu mar dang sbrang rtsi dang sbyar nas /
NK033(gi)001:7590: lde gur byas nas zos na da phyin chad 'chi bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7591: de ni bdud rtsi'i mchog yin no //
NK033(gi)001:7592: mdor na mang du smos mi 'tshal te /
NK033(gi)001:7593: ji ltar bsgrub kyang sman bcud len yin te /
NK033(gi)001:7594: lo bcu drug lon pa'i sha tshugs dang 'dra bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7595: thos pa 'dzin cing yid gzhungs par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7596: bdud rtsi dngul chu rnam gnyis dang /
NK033(gi)001:7597: lag mthil na ra la bzhal ba'i rnam gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:7598: du brnyes na dngul chur 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:7599: gser zho gnyis tsam la byas pa'i snod du bzhag
NK033(gi)001:7600: ste khar bcug na lus mi snang bar 'gyur la
NK033(gi)001:7601: / gzhan gyi longs spyod kun la dbang zhing spyod /
NK033(gi)001:7602: nyi zla'i tshe dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7603: de ltar sman bcud len sbyar ba'i thabs ni 'di las sla ba med do //
NK033(gi)001:7604: zhes lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7605: drang srong zhi sred kyis kyang bshad do //
NK033(gi)001:7606: bcud len bdud rtsi'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:7607: bdud rtsi'i khu ba 'don pa ni zhal las shes so //
NK033(gi)001:7609: bdud rtsi'i khu ba 'don pa zhal gyi gdams pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7610: dang po rgyun spongs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7611: nas bzang po sbrus zhag bar /
NK033(gi)001:7614: de nas zhib par btags la /
NK033(gi)001:7615: nas phul re'i tshad mar en re btang /
NK033(gi)001:7616: tsam nyin mo sum yar bza' /
NK033(gi)001:7617: nam gung la re re mar en re bar /
NK033(gi)001:7619: de nas bdud rtsi de rdza phor sa la mi btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7623: de'i bar du skom du chang bzang po gsum yar du btang /
NK033(gi)001:7624: de'i bar du dri chu yang rdza gcig tu bsags /
NK033(gi)001:7625: de ltar zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bsags /
NK033(gi)001:7626: de nas dri chen skam po gar chang phul tshad
NK033(gi)001:7627: re re nub mo dang nam gung la yang btang
NK033(gi)001:7628: / de nas tsam sran ma tsam du brdung la /
NK033(gi)001:7629: de nas chang zhim pos kha phru btab la /
NK033(gi)001:7630: yibs rus dang mi sha tshon po'i rdor btab /
NK033(gi)001:7631: bdud rtsi a mri ta'i kha tshar btab pas bar chad bsrung /
NK033(gi)001:7632: de nas rdza ma zhabs su bug pa seng tsam phug pa gcig tu bardzanga /
NK033(gi)001:7633: de yang sor gcig tsam du ma khengs par byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7634: de nas bdud rtsi a mri ta'i sor gsum gyi
NK033(gi)001:7635: pho tshom gcig tsam gyi bag zan bzang pos nyes
NK033(gi)001:7636: brtsegs su byas la shin tu dam par byas la
NK033(gi)001:7639: de nas kha shin tu dam par bcad /
NK033(gi)001:7640: de rdza ma glo mchu can gcig gi khar bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:7641: de chus bkang la 'og tu me btang /
NK033(gi)001:7642: de nas yang skabs su bzhugs la mnan /
NK033(gi)001:7644: de nas ci ran tshes pa dang nyin zhag phrug gcig tu btso /
NK033(gi)001:7646: de nas kha zhag de snod du bsags /
NK033(gi)001:7648: de nas chu zhag gi dul nas chu /
NK033(gi)001:7650: dkar po gcig 'ong ba de la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7652: dri chu dang mnyam la gdu /
NK033(gi)001:7653: de nas dri chu tsam du btsos la /
NK033(gi)001:7655: de yang logs su tshags bya /
NK033(gi)001:7656: de nas cong bdud rtsi'i chu phul gang yod na /
NK033(gi)001:7657: cong zhi dang brag zhun ni phul gsum dang /
NK033(gi)001:7658: zhi nas tsam sran tsam du brdungs la btsos /
NK033(gi)001:7659: de brag zhun nas tsam sran tsam brdungs pa dang btso /
NK033(gi)001:7660: de nas gnyis mnyam la yang btso /
NK033(gi)001:7661: de nas gang rung cong zhi tsam du song ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7662: gcig tsam du song ba dang de gsum bsres la btso /
NK033(gi)001:7663: de nas mar khu tsam du song ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7668: gang la byed kyang bdud rtsi'i chu la sum ldab tu btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7678: rgya sran dkar po'i khu ba /
NK033(gi)001:7680: dkar po gcig thub dbang po lag pa'i khu ba phul do /
NK033(gi)001:7681: de rnams 'dul ba ni logs su gadu'o //
NK033(gi)001:7682: de rnams so so rang rang du bkrus nas skam po'am /
NK033(gi)001:7684: de gang la byed kyang chom chom du brdungs /
NK033(gi)001:7685: bskol gyin khu ba phul do ba snod gtsang ma gcig tu bsres la sman mar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7687: 'o mar bkol nas ngar chag nas btung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7688: chang gsar yod na legs gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7690: tsh+wa la sogs pa'i skyon spang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7691: nyi shu rtsa na thon no //
NK033(gi)001:7692: bcud len legs rdzogs zhes bya ba rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:7693: ltog kyang a kha nga mi za /
NK033(gi)001:7694: phag pa khra lug mig pa'i me tog kyang btang /
NK033(gi)001:7700: dom mkhris de tsho chu'i nang du blugs la lto stong la btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7701: ka ras nang re byi'u'i sgong re re btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7703: bcud len gyi lag len yin no //
NK033(gi)001:7704: des ni skye ba rgyun bcad do //
NK033(gi)001:7705: des nges par phyag rgya'i thig le 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7706: badz+ra shwa ra la byang chub 'bum gyis /
NK033(gi)001:7711: chad pa'i stong pa nyi tshe ba /
NK033(gi)001:7712: rtag pa de nyid de zhes bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:7713: shes pa smin mtshams kyi bar snang nye ba nam mkhar gtad la yun ring du bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:7714: mig lug pa snyam pa'am smin phrag tu skam pas 'byin pa snyam byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7715: lus zing zing byed na rlung nang du zhugs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7717: mig btsum la shes pa smin phrag tu gtad /
NK033(gi)001:7718: dran rtog rlung gis dran bskyod cing //
NK033(gi)001:7719: 'dzin med ngang la mi gnas la //
NK033(gi)001:7720: g.yo 'dzin rlung gi man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:7724: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi bcud len /
NK033(gi)001:7725: bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo /
NK033(gi)001:7726: phyi'i bcud blangs pa sman gyi m+au la dang /
NK033(gi)001:7727: nang gi bcud blangs pa sman gyi m+au la dang /
NK033(gi)001:7728: gsang ba'i bcud blangs pa sman gyi m+au la'o //
NK033(gi)001:7729: dang po rtsi'i bcud blangs pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:7730: de la rtsi ni dkar po chig thub phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7731: dbang po lag pa phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7732: ra mo shag dkar po phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7733: ba spru ba dkar po phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7734: bzhi po de grib skam byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7735: skam po phul re re ste phul bzhi chu bre do'i nang btsos la /
NK033(gi)001:7736: phul gsum du song ba dang btsag go //
NK033(gi)001:7737: de 'dra ba lan gsum du byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7738: de nas mar dkar gyi khu ba bre phyed kyi sbu ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7742: rgya sran btsos pa'i khu ba de dang mnyam pa /
NK033(gi)001:7743: de 'dres par dkrugs la rdza ma gcig tu tshags bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:7744: de nas lto gtsang bar snyoms par baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7745: gcig tu byas te sbyangs te zos na lo bcu drug lon pa ltar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7746: rtsi bzhi dang rgya sran btsos pa'i tshad ni /
NK033(gi)001:7747: chu bre do do la btsos pas chu phul gsum gsum du song ba dang btsag /
NK033(gi)001:7748: de nas dul ba'i tshad ni bu ram bsgor ba dang 'dra bas shes gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:7749: de'i bar du lto gtsang ba gal che gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:7750: sman dang lto gnyis ka che chung ma shor ba gal che gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:7751: chag tshad bar pa gcig la brtag pa gal che gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:7753: de la rdo'i m+au la ni /
NK033(gi)001:7755: brag zhun phul gang gangs chur bsing ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7756: de nas de gdus la logs su tshags bya /
NK033(gi)001:7757: de nas mar khu dwangs ma de dang mnyam sbrang rtsi dwangs ma de dang mnyam /
NK033(gi)001:7758: rgya sran btsos pa'i khu ba dang mnyam pa de
NK033(gi)001:7759: tsho 'dres par dkrugs la rdza ma gcig tu tshags
NK033(gi)001:7760: bya'o // de nas lto gtsang bar snyoms par baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7761: dam tshig tu bu ram 'bru mar tsam bsrung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7762: tshos pa'i tshad ni bu ram bsgor ba dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:7763: mar dang sbrang rtsi btso mi dgos gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7764: de ni rdo bcud blang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7765: chu la bcud blangs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7767: rang gi grib ma mi btang /
NK033(gi)001:7770: rdo chu ni phyag tshang khu bcad pa ni chu shing gis bcad /
NK033(gi)001:7772: 'dul ba ni ba glang dmar skya'i khrag gis 'dul lo //
NK033(gi)001:7775: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:7776: slob dpon 'dzeng gi zhal gdams dam pa jo sras kyis /
NK033(gi)001:7777: slob dpon kun bzang la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:7779: rdo rje zam pa'i bcud len 'di la don gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:7780: phyi'i bcud blang ba sman gyi rtsa ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7781: nang gi bcud blang ba sman gyi rtsa ba /
NK033(gi)001:7782: gsang ba'i bcud blang ba sman gyi rtsa ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7783: dang po rtsi'i bcud blang ba ste /
NK033(gi)001:7784: de la rtsi ni dkar po gcig thub phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7787: ba spru ba dkar po phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:7788: bzhi po grib skam byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7789: skam po phul re re phul bzhi po chu bre
NK033(gi)001:7790: do'i nang du btsos la phul gsum du song ba
NK033(gi)001:7791: dang btsag / de 'dra ba lan gsum byas la
NK033(gi)001:7792: de nas mar dkar gyi khu ba bre phyed kyi
NK033(gi)001:7793: dang btsag / wu ba dang / snyigs ma sangs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7796: rgya sran btsos pa'i khu ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7797: bzhi po cha mnyam pa gcig tu byas te sbyangs
NK033(gi)001:7798: nas zos na lo bcu drug lon pa'i na tshod
NK033(gi)001:7800: rtsi bzhi dang rgya sran btsos pa'i tshad ni chu
NK033(gi)001:7801: bre do la btsos pas phul gsum du song dus
NK033(gi)001:7802: btsags / de nas dul ba'i tshad ni bu ram bsgor ba dang 'dra bar shes gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7803: de'i bar du lto gtsang ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:7804: sman dang lto gnyis che chung ma shor ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:7805: chag tshad bar pa gcig la bya'o gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7806: 'o ma bskol ba ngar chag nas btung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7807: chang gsar 'jam yang btung du btub /
NK033(gi)001:7808: tsh+wa la sogs pa skyon spang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7809: de ni bdud rtsi'i bcud blang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7810: nang gi bcud blang ba rdo'i rtsi ni /
NK033(gi)001:7812: brag zhun phul gang gangs chur bsing ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7813: de nas de gdu la logs su tshag byas la /
NK033(gi)001:7814: de nas mar khu dwangs ma de dang mnyam /
NK033(gi)001:7815: sbrang rtsi'i dwangs ma de dang mnyam /
NK033(gi)001:7816: rgya sran btsos pa'i khu ba dang mnyam po de
NK033(gi)001:7817: tsho 'dres par dkrugs la rdza ma gcig tu tshag
NK033(gi)001:7818: bya'o // de nas lto gtsang ma la snyoms par baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7819: dam tshig tu bu ram 'bru mar snang /
NK033(gi)001:7821: tshos pa'i tshad ni bu ram bsgor ba bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:7822: mar dang sbrang rtsi btso mi dgos gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7823: de ni rdo la bcud blang ba'i rtsi'o //
NK033(gi)001:7824: gsang ba'i bcud blang ba'i rtsi ni chu la bcud blang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7828: rdo chu ni phyag tshang khu ba blang /
NK033(gi)001:7829: 'dul ba ni ba dmar skya'i khrag gis 'dul ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7830: de ni gsang ba'i bcud blang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7831: mu zi dang khong zi'i bcud blang ba 'dir ma gsung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7832: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas spang mi pham mgon po bsgres nas de yi don du gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:7833: bcud len lam gyi gdams ngag la phyi nang gsang ba gsum du byung ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:7834: 'di lam du 'khyer ba la de kho na nyid bsdus pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7835: gsang ba de kho na nyid nyams su blang ba
NK033(gi)001:7836: ni de la dang po rtsa ba rnams cha mnyam
NK033(gi)001:7837: par byas la zhib par btags /
NK033(gi)001:7838: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar du zas kyi rgyun spang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7839: de nas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu rtsa ba lnga po mar dang bcas te baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7840: de nas sman nang gi bcud blang ba sman gyi rtsi ni sha lnga /
NK033(gi)001:7842: ngang ngur bya rog shug gu gul gru rnams dang lnga'o //
NK033(gi)001:7843: mar dang bcas pas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig phyi'i rgyun spong /
NK033(gi)001:7844: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu 'o ma dang bcas pa baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7845: ba'i 'o ma phul re'i nang du bdun phul phyed phyed btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:7846: de rnams mthar phyin par bya ba ni de rnams
NK033(gi)001:7847: sbrang rtsi dang sbyar te mar gyi nying khu dang
NK033(gi)001:7848: spyad nas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gis mthar phyin
NK033(gi)001:7849: par 'gyur ro // de gang zag gi rgyud la nyams su blang ba ni zas gang 'phrod la /
NK033(gi)001:7850: dri ma 'bags sgo med par za ste /
NK033(gi)001:7851: bud med spangs te rgyun ngan pa bor te /
NK033(gi)001:7852: dang po rgyun spos pa'i rgyun de rdo leb steng du grib skams byas te /
NK033(gi)001:7853: de dang rtsa ba la rgyun gong bzhin du sgom ste /
NK033(gi)001:7855: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar la 'o ma dang bcas pa zos na phyi'i bcud blang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7856: de yang rnam snang gong bzhin skams te sbrang rtsi
NK033(gi)001:7857: dang mar dang bcas nas zos na mthar phyin par
NK033(gi)001:7858: 'gyur ro // sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga gu gul
NK033(gi)001:7859: ngang ngur bya rog rnam snang mar dang bcas pa
NK033(gi)001:7860: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gis phyi'i rgyun spos /
NK033(gi)001:7861: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu 'o ma dang bcas pa za'o //
NK033(gi)001:7862: de ltar zos pas mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7863: bcud len gsang ba'i bdud rtsi sgrub pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7864: mi thod mtshan ldan gcig tu 'o ma dang bcas pa za'o //
NK033(gi)001:7865: de ltar zos pas mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7866: bcud len gsang ba'i bdud rtsi sgrub pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:7867: mi thod mtshan ldan gcig tu tshig ma phyung la
NK033(gi)001:7868: khu ba sus sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar
NK033(gi)001:7869: te mo thod nang du blugs nas pho thod mtshan
NK033(gi)001:7870: ldan gcig gis kha bcad de dar dkar pos dril
NK033(gi)001:7871: / de nas dmar pos dril te many+dzi'i khar bzhag nas 'og tu me btang /
NK033(gi)001:7874: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)001:7876: bdud rtsi'i dri tshor ba'i rtags byung nas 'o ma dang bcas la baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7877: de ltar byas pas mthar phyin par 'gyur nas rdo
NK033(gi)001:7878: rje lta bu'i lus thob ste tshe nyi zla dang
NK033(gi)001:7880: des tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob //
NK033(gi)001:7881: de nas sems nyid rnam par dag nas /
NK033(gi)001:7882: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob /
NK033(gi)001:7883: de la rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob /
NK033(gi)001:7884: de la 'pho 'gyur med pas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:7885: de nas rig 'dzin gyis thob ste rig 'dzin gyi
NK033(gi)001:7886: sa la gnas pa ste 'khor ba rgyun bcad pa'o
NK033(gi)001:7888: lus 'gag pa ni bcud len gyi dus su byed de /
NK033(gi)001:7889: bu chung gi klad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7891: sprul pa'i a sho a d+har gyi sron de baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:7892: sngon po byung na sbrul zer ro //
NK033(gi)001:7893: phag sgur po glang dkar gyi khrag dang /
NK033(gi)001:7894: kar ra bi ra zer te nya brid ma'i me tog dang /
NK033(gi)001:7895: dom mkhris rnams mnyam par byas te /
NK033(gi)001:7896: lug mig pa'i me tog kyang gtong /
NK033(gi)001:7897: nang ma gsum la tshad byi sgong re re 'phrad
NK033(gi)001:7898: du ra dkar mo'i 'o ma'am 'o ma gang yang
NK033(gi)001:7900: sman gong ma tsho'i ka ra gnyis 'gyur btang la kha bsgyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7901: de yis phyag rgya'i thig le 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:7902: bcud len gyi lag len yin no //
NK033(gi)001:7905: de nas madzo'am dre'u'i klad pa'am da li na mung dkar po'i me tog kyang gtong /
NK033(gi)001:7906: 'dis ni skye ba'i rgyun rdzas kyis gcod pa'o ////
NK033(gi)001:7908: dang po phyag rgya ma'i mtshan nyid brtags /
NK033(gi)001:7909: mtshan ldan dang po nyi shu rtsa gcig lon pa rnyed nas tshogs kyis mchod /
NK033(gi)001:7910: rab dang 'bring dang tha ma gsum //
NK033(gi)001:7911: ltas dang reg dang sbyor bas tshim //
NK033(gi)001:7912: tha ma sbyor ba bya ba ni //
NK033(gi)001:7913: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:7914: yab kyis yum gyi g.yon nas 'khyud //
NK033(gi)001:7915: dang po yab yum lha ru sgom //
NK033(gi)001:7916: gnyis pa mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab //
NK033(gi)001:7917: gsum pa 'bebs la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)001:7918: bzhi pa bkram la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)001:7919: lnga pa ldog la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)001:7920: drug pa 'dren la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)001:7921: de dus zag bcas bde ba ste //
NK033(gi)001:7922: rgyud la skyes na bde ba yang //
NK033(gi)001:7923: rtsol ba dang bcas pa lus la gnas pa'i rlung
NK033(gi)001:7924: dang zag bcas lus la gnas pa'i bde ba gnyis
NK033(gi)001:7926: zag med kyi bde ba gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:7927: brda yis 'dzin pa'i dus su rtsol bcas dang zag
NK033(gi)001:7928: bcas gnyis 'dzin par mi 'dod kyang ngo shes pa
NK033(gi)001:7930: dang po bem po'i ngo bo sbyar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:7932: gnyis pa lus kyi gnad rnams bcos /
NK033(gi)001:7933: gsum pa rtsa chen gnyis zhugs srog rtsa dbu mar bsgom /
NK033(gi)001:7934: bzhi pa mdog rnams byung na bsil ba'i bdud rtsi 'bab /
NK033(gi)001:7935: lus la drod 'bar ba'i rtsol bcas rlung gi gdams pa rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:7936: bdag nyid ye shes seng ge yis //
NK033(gi)001:7937: yi ger bris pa bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)001:7938: gdams ngag zab mo dag la yang //
NK033(gi)001:7939: lag len dag tu ma byas na //
NK033(gi)001:7940: bslab pa dag gis mi phan no ////
NK033(gi)001:7942: ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung 'di la gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:7943: phyi rgya mtsho khrus lung dang /
NK033(gi)001:7944: nang rgya mtsho khrus lung gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:7945: de la phyi rgya mtsho'i khrus la brten pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK033(gi)001:7950: rlan tsam gsher tsam las brten pas rgya mtsho 'byung bas na brten rgya matsho'o //
NK033(gi)001:7951: rdul phra rab la brten pa ri bo'o //
NK033(gi)001:7952: mchog rab 'byung ba ni phyi brten pa'i ri bo'o //
NK033(gi)001:7953: 'di ni rgya mtsho khrus lung yin pas bum pa brten pa'i phyir ro //
NK033(gi)001:7954: bum chu brten rgya mtsho yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:7958: snod ldom pa la mi ldom pa /
NK033(gi)001:7960: sman ldom la mi ldom pa /
NK033(gi)001:7962: spos ldom la mi ldom pa yang gla rtsi mi btang /
NK033(gi)001:7964: dang po ni snod kyi mtshan nyid nii bum pa bre gang 'gro ba zhabs stegs yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7965: gdan rim pa gsum yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7969: ske la mu tig gi phreng ba yod pa /
NK033(gi)001:7971: chu srog chags med pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7975: snying po lnga la sogs bstsal nas /
NK033(gi)001:7976: ras sam bal gyi mgul chings dang shing 'bras bu can gyi kha rgyan yod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:7977: man+dala me tog tshom bu lnga la sogs par bzhugs su gsol nas de ni sbyor ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:7978: dngos gzhi ni bdag stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NK033(gi)001:7979: bdag gi thugs kar +amo kha dog lnga pa gcig gsal ba las /
NK033(gi)001:7980: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ha sarba d+harmahswa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK033(gi)001:7981: zhes brjod pas bum pa mi dmigs par bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:7983: yi ge lam ser po gcig tu gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:7984: lam las gser gyi bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7985: pam las pad+ma'i sdong por gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7987: pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru la h+aum ljang khu sgril ma gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:7988: de kyur gyis 'gyur ba las khro bo bdud rtsi
NK033(gi)001:7989: 'khyil ba ljang sngon phyag g.yas na gser gyi rdo
NK033(gi)001:7990: rje bsnams pa / phyag g.yon na shel gyi dril bu bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:7991: phyag gnyis dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)001:7992: de lta bu gcig bum pa'i nang du lam gyis bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:7993: yang rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros pas
NK033(gi)001:7994: mdun gyi nam mkha' la h+aum sgril ma gcig tu
NK033(gi)001:7995: gyur / de gyur pas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba snga ma lta bu gcig tu gyur /
NK033(gi)001:7996: yang bdag gi snying kha nas 'od zer 'phros pas
NK033(gi)001:7997: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK033(gi)001:7998: bcud bsdus / tshur 'dus mdun gyi bdud rtsi 'khyil pa la phog pas /
NK033(gi)001:7999: dam tshig sems dpa' zhu ste bum pa'i nang du bdud rtsi dkar mer gyis song bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8001: gzungs thag la sngags kyi yig 'bru dang /
NK033(gi)001:8002: rdo rje lu gu brgyud du bcas nas bum pa'i nang du dkar chur gyis song bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8004: e ho shud+d+he shud+d+he bi ho shud+d+he shud+d+he ram ho
NK033(gi)001:8005: shud+d+he shud+d+he yam ho shud+d+he shud+d+he a bi ram na
NK033(gi)001:8006: shud+d+he shud+d+he / a a +aah zhes brgya rtsa brgyad dgong mo brjod nas /
NK033(gi)001:8007: +aahmh'u zhes pas bdag gi thugs ka nas lag pa g.yas pa'i gung mo la /
NK033(gi)001:8008: mdzub mo la +aah srin lag la h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:8010: +aahmh'u zhes brjod nas bum pa'i kha la reg reg byas pas /
NK033(gi)001:8011: bum pa'i bdud rtsi'i steng du bar chad bsrung ba
NK033(gi)001:8012: la yi ge gsum spris ma'i tshul du byung bar
NK033(gi)001:8013: bsam / gzungs thag bzed la nyal /
NK033(gi)001:8014: de nas nangs par lang tsa na ma bu thams
NK033(gi)001:8015: cad la phan 'dogs pa'i phyir bdag yar la langs
NK033(gi)001:8016: nas zhwa gyon pas bla ma spyi bor 'khur bar
NK033(gi)001:8017: bsam / gnam 'dud gyon pas khrel dang dam tshig ngo tsha shes par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8018: lhwam gyon pas 'gro ba'i don la brtson par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8019: ral gu gyon pas rdo rje'i go chas bar chad kyis mi tshugs par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8020: ske rags bcings pas rdo rje'i bka' nan bcings par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:8021: de nas mdzub mo dang gung mos bum pa'i ske nas bzung ste /
NK033(gi)001:8023: zhes brjod pas yi ge las 'od lnga phar la 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)001:8024: phyogs bcu'i ta th+aa ga ta thams cad kyi bcud
NK033(gi)001:8025: bsdus nas shar phyogs nas lha mo dkar mo bum
NK033(gi)001:8026: pa dkar po phyag na bsnams pa /
NK033(gi)001:8030: sku mdog dang mthun pa'i bum pa bsnams nas spyi
NK033(gi)001:8031: bor byon par bsam la bdag la dbang bskur bar
NK033(gi)001:8032: bsam la / khrus bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:8033: e ho'i sngags la a +aa dang s+w+aa h+aa btags
NK033(gi)001:8034: la chu de la khyor ba gang gnam la gtor
NK033(gi)001:8035: bas bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang /
NK033(gi)001:8036: ta th+aa ga ta thams cad la bdud rtsi phul
NK033(gi)001:8037: bas dgyes nas thugs rnam par dag ste dam tshig
NK033(gi)001:8038: nyams pa thams cad bskang ba dang bshags par gyur
NK033(gi)001:8039: par bsam mo // de nas byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:8040: de nas rang gi gdong pa bkrus pas /
NK033(gi)001:8041: lus kyi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8042: kha bshal bas ngag gi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8043: btung bas yid kyi sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8044: lhag ma khyor ba gsum gtor bas khams gsum gyi
NK033(gi)001:8045: sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK033(gi)001:8046: sgrib pa dag nas nam mkha' lta bur gyur par
NK033(gi)001:8047: bsam mo // de ni phyi'i rgya mtsho'i khrus lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8048: nang rgya mtsho khrus lung la gnas pa'i ri bo dang /
NK033(gi)001:8049: gnas rgya mtsho ni lus la rtsa gnas /
NK033(gi)001:8050: rtsa la khrag dang chu ser gnas pa'i rgya matsho'o //
NK033(gi)001:8051: sha dang rus pa dang chu rgyus las lus su gnas pa ni gnas pa'i ri bo'o //
NK033(gi)001:8052: 'di ni rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung yin pas lus gnas pa'i ri bo'o //
NK033(gi)001:8053: dri chu ni gnas pa'i rgya matsho'o //
NK033(gi)001:8054: ri bo gang na gnas pa rgya mtsho gnas /
NK033(gi)001:8055: rgya mtsho gang na gnas pa na ni ri bo gnas so //
NK033(gi)001:8060: kham phor du blugs pas chu g.yon nas g.yas su
NK033(gi)001:8061: 'khor ba dang rlung g.yon nas 'gyu ba 'dzom na
NK033(gi)001:8063: de nas chu kha gting 'khrugs na ngan no //
NK033(gi)001:8067: de yang pho dgos pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8068: pi wang la ri mo dang ma nu'i gzugs dang
NK033(gi)001:8069: dum bur chad na de yang phor dgos pa yin
NK033(gi)001:8070: no // kha sangs phyed pa dang sangs se ba
NK033(gi)001:8071: la spris ma ser pos kha bad kyis chod pa
NK033(gi)001:8072: gcig byung na de ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dar
NK033(gi)001:8073: ya kan bya ba yin pas de ni dbu ma
NK033(gi)001:8074: dang mi spangs bya ba'i sgros chags pas mi 'abo'o
NK033(gi)001:8075: no // // de nas bdud rtsi brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8077: snod kyi nang du yi ge mam ser po cig bsam ste /
NK033(gi)001:8078: de 'od du zhu ba las gser snod ser po che ba gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8079: de'i nang du yi ge bam dmar po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8080: de 'od du zhu ba las sna tshogs pad+ma'i sdong po gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8081: de'i ge sar la h+aum ljang gu gcig bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8082: de la h+aum zhes lce rtse bkug tsam brjod pas
NK033(gi)001:8083: h+aum las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba sku mdog ljang sngon
NK033(gi)001:8084: phyag gnyis dkur brten pa gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8086: ma bu'i don byas tshur 'dus pa las ye shes
NK033(gi)001:8087: kyi 'od de dam tshig gi bdud rtsi 'khyil ba
NK033(gi)001:8088: la phog pas 'od du zhu nas dkar mer gyis
NK033(gi)001:8096: a a zhes lan nyi shu rtsa gcig brjod /
NK033(gi)001:8098: de nas +aa a +aa a zhes brjod pas lha
NK033(gi)001:8099: mo bzhis bdud rtsi'i bum pa sku mdog dang mthun
NK033(gi)001:8100: pa bsnams nas bdag gi spyi bor dbang bskur bar
NK033(gi)001:8101: bsam mo // lus shel sgong phyis pa ltar dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8106: chu lhag ma gtor bas khams gsum sems can gyi sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8107: bdag dang sems can thams cad dbyer mi phyed pa
NK033(gi)001:8108: bde gsal gnyis med kyi ngang la thub tshad gcig
NK033(gi)001:8109: bzhag go // de yang rgya mtsho khrus lung las /
NK033(gi)001:8110: phung po lnga ni dag byed cing //
NK033(gi)001:8111: nyon mongs lnga ni sbyong byed pa //
NK033(gi)001:8112: ye shes lnga ni ngo bor gnas //
NK033(gi)001:8114: ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus kyi lung rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:8117: brgyud las btus pa'i rdo rje zam pa'i dam tshig nyi shu pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:8118: gsan yig la lar nyi shu rtsa bzhi zer ba'ang snang gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:8119: bla ma rgyud las btus pa /
NK033(gi)001:8120: dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8124: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang /
NK033(gi)001:8125: rim pa dbang gis bsgrod do //
NK033(gi)001:8126: don man ngag gis bsgrub pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8128: de yang gzhung rtsa ba'i las gsang dbang rim pas nod /
NK033(gi)001:8129: dam tshig mi sku gsung thugs /
NK033(gi)001:8132: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung gis /
NK033(gi)001:8134: dam tshig gis bzung la brtul zhugs kyi /
NK033(gi)001:8142: nyi shu dang po la gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:8146: rgyas par bshad pa la nyi shu las /
NK033(gi)001:8147: dang po gcan gzan rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la mi bsdo /
NK033(gi)001:8148: ngan sems dang log par mi lta /
NK033(gi)001:8149: spyi bor bkur zhing mnyes pa'i yon dbul /
NK033(gi)001:8150: gyi rgyal po seng ge mi bsad pa /
NK033(gi)001:8151: za ma tog gi slob dpon gyi yum la mi spyad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8153: log par mi lta ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8155: nang du dug mi spyod pa /
NK033(gi)001:8156: rin dad pa can gyi tshogs mi bcag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8157: po che'i lcugs phran mi breg pa ba ling mchod pa dang dus mchod mi bcag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8159: gangs dkon mchog gi dngos po'i dkor la mi 'bag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8160: bla ma'i nor la longs mi spyad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8161: kyi zhun chu khol ma mi btung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8162: pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru kha dam tshig gcig pa'i yum la mi 'bag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8167: snod bug dam tshig la mi gnas pa la gsang sngags bshad par mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8168: rdol can du bcud mi blugs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8169: ma brtags pa'i rdzas byin gyis ma brlabs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8170: bkra mi shis pa'i thod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8176: shel shes pa can gyi mi la zhor zlos dang /
NK033(gi)001:8179: snying nas yon tan la mi smad do //
NK033(gi)001:8180: gong dkar po 'dam bu mi bsnub pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8183: las kyi nyan du gzhug pa'i dbang dang /
NK033(gi)001:8185: de nyams pa la mi bskur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8186: 'o ma snod ngan du mi blugs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8187: yid bzhin de yang gzhung dang mthun pa'i bla mas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8190: lha'i lung 'bogs pa la sogs pa rnams snod ngan pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8192: nyams pa la mi bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8193: gyi nor bu mi bsreg pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8194: bya rgyal thabs dang shes rab bral bar mi bya /
NK033(gi)001:8195: thabs bskyed rim shes rab rdzogs rim gnyis dang bral bar mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8196: khu byug gi gshog pa mi bcag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8197: gnam rnal 'byor pa nang mi 'thab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8200: gzhan gyi zlog pa mi bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8201: lcags ngur mo sa la mi gdab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8202: stag gzig rol pa'i zas lhag mi za ba gzhan gyi nyams pa'i rdzas la mi 'jug pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8203: yug sa mo dang dkor la 'bags pa'i zas mi bza' ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8205: rdo rjes rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku mi bslu /
NK033(gi)001:8207: bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa mi bcag /
NK033(gi)001:8208: gtams pa'i brag mi bshigs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8209: rdo rje dam bcas pa'i mtshams mi dbye ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8211: yi dam mi bcag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8213: 'bar ba'i gong mi dgar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8214: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me mi bsad bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la skyon mi bgrang /
NK033(gi)001:8216: rdo rje chu yi 'ol kha 'dzab dang cho ga rgyun mi bcad /
NK033(gi)001:8217: sngags dang phyag rgya ma nor bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8219: rgyal po sku dbang rtags kyi rdo rje dang dril
NK033(gi)001:8220: bu thod pa bum pa rnga dang thang ka mi
NK033(gi)001:8222: rtags kyi phyag rgya mi sbyin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8223: rdo rje mkhar rdzong gi rmang mi rtsa ba dang yan lag las ma 'das par bya dgos so //
NK033(gi)001:8225: nor bu rin po che rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo
NK033(gi)001:8226: las mi 'bog spyir rdo rje slob dpon la skyon
NK033(gi)001:8227: mi bgrang / yon tan brjod la gus pas /
NK033(gi)001:8228: lus ngag yid gsum gus par byas la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:8230: rtsa ba'i khungs dum bu drug /
NK033(gi)001:8231: rgyud las mdor bsdus dam tshig pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8232: dam tshig nyi shu po ni /
NK033(gi)001:8233: dga' rab rdo rje dang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen nas rim par brgyud /
NK033(gi)001:8234: man ngag las yid ches par rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i dam tshig la /
NK033(gi)001:8236: bla ma brgyud pa'i rim pa bstan pa rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:8237: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8238: he ru ka ro ham gyi gdams pa 'di la don gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:8242: sing+ga la'i rgyal po gzhon nu dpal gyi sras /
NK033(gi)001:8243: rgyal po nyi ma'i seng ge'i 'od kyis /
NK033(gi)001:8244: yang dag gsang ba thugs kyi sgrub pa 'di /
NK033(gi)001:8245: sing+ga la'i dur khrod du bsgrubs pas /
NK033(gi)001:8246: zhag bdun na he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po rten gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa gzigs nas /
NK033(gi)001:8248: he ru ka galpo la sogs pa'i rgyud sde mang po spyan drangs te /
NK033(gi)001:8249: gshin po la phan pa'i cho ga 'di mdzad do //
NK033(gi)001:8250: shi ba po dga' ldan du bskyal thabs byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8251: ha shang ma h+aa su dra spyan drangs gto dang
NK033(gi)001:8252: dpyad la brten nas gri can gri rgab bcad pa'i
NK033(gi)001:8254: rgyud he ru ka rol pa la brten nas gri mtshun chos skyong du bsgrub pa 'di byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8255: khro bo h+aum bzhi pa'i rgyud la brten nas gri can rdul du brlag pa'i gdams pa byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8256: de nas rgyal por ma phal zhes bya bar mtshan bsgyur te /
NK033(gi)001:8257: dga' rab rdo rje la yang brgyud par 'dod do //
NK033(gi)001:8258: yang lugs gcig la a wa d+hu ti pa zhes bya bar mtshan bsgyur ba'ang yod /
NK033(gi)001:8259: des mtshan ri brag rab tu gsang ba la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:8260: des rab zhi lo ts+aa ba chos kyi shes rab la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:8261: des ka na blo gros dbang phyug la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:8262: des sba sgom ye shes dbang phyug la /
NK033(gi)001:8263: des rje d+harma bo d+hi ya /
NK033(gi)001:8264: des joo sras rdo rje d+r+wa ba la /
NK033(gi)001:8265: des jo sras 'o la yab sras la /
NK033(gi)001:8266: des 'dzeng bsod nams rgyal po la /
NK033(gi)001:8270: gnyis pa gdams ngag la bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:8271: gri can rdul du brlag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8272: gri can gri rgab bcad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8273: gri mtshun chos skyong du bsgrub pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8274: shi ba po dga' ldan du bskyal ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8276: gtor ma gsum bshams la dkon mchog la mchod pa
NK033(gi)001:8277: 'bul zhing byin gyis rlobs shig par gsol ba gdab
NK033(gi)001:8278: / gcig gshin de'i srog gcod par byed pa'i bdud
NK033(gi)001:8279: dang gri bo la sogs pa'i yi dwags la byin
NK033(gi)001:8280: / la / bdud dang gri bo la sogs pa
NK033(gi)001:8281: khyod kyis gshin tshe las 'das pa ch+gee mo zhes
NK033(gi)001:8282: bya ba'i gson gyi bdud gcod kyang gshin gyi lcags
NK033(gi)001:8287: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis lus ngag rdul du brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8289: de nas gzhi 'di na gnas pa'i sa bdag la
NK033(gi)001:8290: sogs pa rnams la yang gtor ma btang zhing bden
NK033(gi)001:8291: pa brdar ro // bdag rang dpal chen po'i ting nge 'dzin du zhugs la /
NK033(gi)001:8292: skra spyi bor bcings pa la gos bardzesa la /
NK033(gi)001:8293: khro bo'i lta stangs kyis zhi dmigs bzlog la chu
NK033(gi)001:8294: shing dbyug pas ro la la drag tu brdungs zhing
NK033(gi)001:8295: gri can bdud pra ma na ra na da du
NK033(gi)001:8296: dzah zhes mang du brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:8297: khro bo h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags dang /
NK033(gi)001:8298: gzhan yang bgegs bskrad pa'i sngags ci mang bzlas so //
NK033(gi)001:8299: gnyis pa gri can gri rgab bcad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:8300: g.yam pa skya bo tshal pa gcig gi mu khyud la /
NK033(gi)001:8301: spar kha gang la shi ba de'i spar kha'i phyag rgya gdab la bris /
NK033(gi)001:8302: lte ba la rdo rje rgya gram bris la rol tu gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:8303: gsum pa gri mtshun chos skyong du bsgrub pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:8304: gshin po de'i ming chos ming du bsgyur ba la
NK033(gi)001:8305: gos dregs pa can nam tshor la rten byas la
NK033(gi)001:8306: / ming nas 'bod cing za bas mchod do //
NK033(gi)001:8307: skabs su kho la pho nya yang bcol lo //
NK033(gi)001:8308: bzhi pa shi ba dga' ldan du bskyal ba'i 'khor lo ni /
NK033(gi)001:8309: dbu'i gtsug tor du gtsug tor dri ma med pa'i 'khor lo gdags so //
NK033(gi)001:8310: snying khar sgrib pa rgyun gcod kyi 'khor lo gdags so //
NK033(gi)001:8311: lte bar ye shes kyi 'khor lo gdags so //
NK033(gi)001:8312: dmigs pa ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyi
NK033(gi)001:8313: rnam shes kun gzhi'i nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i
NK033(gi)001:8314: snod zhe sdang gi cha de /
NK033(gi)001:8315: gri can gri ru za ba de yin te /
NK033(gi)001:8316: 'od ljang nag gcig tu rdzus te lte ba nas
NK033(gi)001:8317: lus srid par byed pa'i 'byung ba bzhi yi ge
NK033(gi)001:8318: bzhi bstims la / bdag he ru kar gsal ba'i
NK033(gi)001:8319: thugs ka nas thugs ye shes kyi mes bsreg go
NK033(gi)001:8320: bzhi bstims la / // til lam yungs kar la basngagasa la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8321: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam sarba p+aa pam sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8322: bsreg rdzas brgya rtsa brgyad du 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)001:8323: gzhi don snying po dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi thig
NK033(gi)001:8324: le de ljang rgyang lam la byas nas bdag dga'
NK033(gi)001:8325: ldan du gshegs par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:8326: de'i lung ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK033(gi)001:8327: phyi ma'i phyi ma dri ma med pa nas /
NK033(gi)001:8329: dbu'i gtsug tor du gtsug tor dri ma med pa'i
NK033(gi)001:8330: gzungs 'di gzhug na tshe las 'das pa 'di dga'
NK033(gi)001:8333: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:8335: sngags 'chang gi rgyal po bzhi sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK033(gi)001:8336: de'i dus su bka' bgros nas gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:8337: gro ga'am shog gu la 'khor lo rim pa gnyis
NK033(gi)001:8338: byas nas lte bar 'byung ba'i yi ge bzhi bris
NK033(gi)001:8340: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)001:8341: sarba p+aa pam sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8343: til lam yungs kar la basngagasa te sbyin bsreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8345: 'di mtshams sku gsung thugs kyi gdams pa don gyis
NK033(gi)001:8346: bstan pa zhes bzhugs kyang dpe rgyun la ma rnyed
NK033(gi)001:8350: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8351: bde ba stobs dang ldan pa la brten nas /
NK033(gi)001:8352: nyin mo snang ba tshogs drug lam du khyer ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK033(gi)001:8353: sems bskyed sngon du song nas ni /
NK033(gi)001:8354: e bam ma ya zhes yi ge bzhi ru tshig brjod do //
NK033(gi)001:8355: de nas bla ma bkur ba'i don du zhwa gyon /
NK033(gi)001:8356: de nas gos bgos la lus rdo rje'i zhu lugs su gyur par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8357: de nas ske rags bcings te /
NK033(gi)001:8358: rdo rje'i bka' nan bcings par bsam /
NK033(gi)001:8359: de nas khrus dang phyag bya /
NK033(gi)001:8360: de ni khrus kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:8361: de nas dang por sarba ka te /
NK033(gi)001:8363: de nas sarba pa te zhes pas dang por dkon mchog mchod /
NK033(gi)001:8371: de ni zas kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK033(gi)001:8372: de nas snang ba tshogs drug lam khyer ni /
NK033(gi)001:8373: mig gis gzugs mthong ba gzugs kyi mchod pa /
NK033(gi)001:8374: de bzhin du sgra'i mchod pa /
NK033(gi)001:8378: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad kyang dbyings kyi mchod par dbul lo //
NK033(gi)001:8379: de nas nyal tsa na gos phud nas de nas
NK033(gi)001:8380: bdag gis sbyin sogs 'di dag gi sems can thams
NK033(gi)001:8381: cad myur du byang chub thob par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8383: de ni snang ba tshogs drug lam du khyer ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8384: mtshan mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa ni /
