NK033(gi)001:8385: yi ge bzhi snying gi dkyil du +amo kha dog lnga pa la bskor bar bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:8386: de nas dge sbyor gnyid mi chog gi bar du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8387: de nas yi ge sgom pa'i ngang du gnyid nyal /
NK033(gi)001:8388: de la ma yengs par rmi lam na yang dran par bya snyam du dung nge bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8389: de'i ngang du gnyid nyal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8390: des ni shes bya bum par tshud nas bag chags mi sdang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8391: +amo shes bya bum du gzhugs pa'i gdams ngag go //
NK033(gi)001:8392: bla ma pa ri dz+ny+aa ti la badz+ra la gnang /
NK033(gi)001:8395: des khangs pa bsgom pa la /
NK033(gi)001:8399: des 'o la rdo rje kun grags la'o //////
NK033(gi)001:8401: slob dpon ram pha la'i bcing pa gsum gyi gdams ngag /
NK033(gi)001:8405: de la rgas pa bcing ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:8407: gyi bya dkar 'o mar ma bcug par shi ba'i ro ni dug yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8408: ma shi ba 'o ma'i nang du bcug la kho shi ba'i ro dang /
NK033(gi)001:8409: blug po che dkar po mdzub mo tsam pa shing gi rtsa ba'i gseb nas 'ong ba /
NK033(gi)001:8410: gnyer ma can de dang gnyis 'o ma'i nang bam ni nyon mongs pa mi gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:8411: ri mnyam nyid ye shes las mi 'da' ha chags
NK033(gi)001:8412: pa dang bral ba sa rgyu mi dmigs pa re'u
NK033(gi)001:8413: mig &&&matshana mo shes bya bum par gzhug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8414: lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas pa ni 'bru lnga dmar ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8415: sngags kyi chos nyid la gnas pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8417: du bcug nas btsos pas de gnyis ka zhu nas zhag tu mer gyis 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:8418: de nas na mal gcig tu 'thungs pas lus gzhon sha chags la rgas pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8419: na ba dang 'chi ba bcing ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:8420: ba ser skya'i 'o ma spos bror 'ong bas de'i 'o ma bre do'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:8421: a ru ra gser mdog phyin pa nyi shu rtsa lnga tsam blugs la /
NK033(gi)001:8422: zhag gsum tsam bzhi tsam sbang du gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:8423: 'o ma de zho skad kyis chags nas 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:8425: a ru ra phyung la grib ma la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:8426: zho de dkrugs la mar de srang la gzhal la /
NK033(gi)001:8428: nyin mo snang ba sna tshogs lam du khyer ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8430: zhes nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas /
NK033(gi)001:8431: +amo kha dog lnga pa e bam ma ya bzhi
NK033(gi)001:8432: po kha dog dkar po +amo ya phyag rgya chen
NK033(gi)001:8433: po / e chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK033(gi)001:8435: ma dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK033(gi)001:8437: &a&a&ade tsam pa gnyis shug pa'i khan+da dang /
NK033(gi)001:8438: pho rog sgo nga gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:8440: ngur pa'i mar srang gnyis byung ba dang khan+da dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:8442: don la mar dang log po log po'o //
NK033(gi)001:8443: ra tsam gyis kyang gtub gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:8445: mar dang de bzhin bsres la /
NK033(gi)001:8446: da ci'i a ru ra'i rus pa bo la lkog pa brdungs pa dang yang bsres la /
NK033(gi)001:8447: thur ma re lto stong la bza' /
NK033(gi)001:8448: zhag 'ga' gong nas lto gtsang chu gtsang /
NK033(gi)001:8449: sngon 'gro dang rjes legs par bsrung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8452: dug gis mi tshugs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:8455: slob dpon ra ma pha la'i gdams bcing ba gsum
NK033(gi)001:8456: bla ma 'dzeng ba'i tshe bsring ba'i bcud len ngo
NK033(gi)001:8461: ma nor ma bcos brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8462: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag 'di la /
NK033(gi)001:8463: bcing ba rnam pa gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:8464: na ba bcing ba rdo rje khu tshur gyi gdams ngag dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:8465: rga ba bcing ba drang srong rdzogs byed kyi gdams ngag dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:8466: 'chi ba bcing ba dpal kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes kyi gdams ngag dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:8467: de lan ba bcing ba rdo rje khu tshur gyi gdams ngag ni /
NK033(gi)001:8468: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dga' ldan du gshegs nges pa gcig gi ring ba srel /
NK033(gi)001:8469: ma rnyed na rus pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:8474: de rnams dar dkar pos dril /
NK033(gi)001:8476: de rin po che'i snod du bcug /
NK033(gi)001:8477: bal tshon sna lnga'i skud pas khab mig gcig tu bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:8478: de tsho sbrel te rang gi spyi gtsug tu btags so //
NK033(gi)001:8479: sngags ni rten 'brel gyi snying po la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8480: de rdo rje sems dpa'i khu tshur gyi gdams ngag
NK033(gi)001:8481: zhes bya ste las dang rkyen bcing ba'i gdangs ngag
NK033(gi)001:8482: yin no // rgas pa bcing ba drang srong rdzogs byed kyi gdams ngag la /
NK033(gi)001:8483: bcud len bdud rtsi'i khag len ni /
NK033(gi)001:8484: bdud rtsi'i khu ba 'don pa zhal gyi gdams pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:8485: dang po rgyun spo ba la nas bzang po sbrus la /
NK033(gi)001:8488: nas phul re'i tshad tsam nyin mo gsum yar du bza' /
NK033(gi)001:8489: nam gung la re re baza'o //
NK033(gi)001:8490: de nas bdud rtsi de rdza phor gyi nang du btang la /
NK033(gi)001:8493: de'i bar du chang zhim po la sum yar du btung /
NK033(gi)001:8494: dri chu yang yang rdza ma'i nang du bsag /
NK033(gi)001:8495: de ltar zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bsag /
NK033(gi)001:8496: de nas dri chen skam po de nas tsam sran
NK033(gi)001:8497: tsam du brdung la de la chang zhim po'i kha
NK033(gi)001:8498: phru btab / yibs rus dang mi sha tshon po'i rdor btab /
NK033(gi)001:8499: bdud rtsi a mri ta'i kha tshar btab pas bar chad bsrung /
NK033(gi)001:8500: de nas rdza ma stong pa gcig tu chang zhim
NK033(gi)001:8501: po khyad par gang tsam blug pa de sa 'og
NK033(gi)001:8502: sbas la kha deng nge bya /
NK033(gi)001:8503: rdza ma gsar pa gcig tu bdud rtsi de rnams
NK033(gi)001:8504: rdzongs la kha gyo mog gi g.yam du bu ga
NK033(gi)001:8505: lnga tsam dod pa gcig gis bcad la /
NK033(gi)001:8506: rdza de'i sked nas phar la bug pa phug la
NK033(gi)001:8507: lcags gzer gyis bcad kha chod de mi brul bar
NK033(gi)001:8508: bya / de nas sa 'og gi de'i thog tu
NK033(gi)001:8509: kha sbub la thog tu kha dang la me dang
NK033(gi)001:8512: de nas bzhu ba'i khu ba tsho dang dri chu gnyis cha mnyam la gadu'o //
NK033(gi)001:8513: de nas dri chu tsam gcig skam pa dang logs su tshags byas la /
NK033(gi)001:8514: de nas cong zhi nas rtsam brdungs pa'i bre gang
NK033(gi)001:8515: tsam zhig la chu bre gang tsam zhig la gdus
NK033(gi)001:8516: la khu ba phul phyed tsam du song tsa na
NK033(gi)001:8517: yang bdud rtsi dang bsres la cha mnyam la gadu'o
NK033(gi)001:8518: // de nas gang rung tsam gcig tu song tsa na 'o ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:8521: rgya sran rnams gang la byed kyang bdud rtsi'i chu la gsum ldab tu bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8522: de nas bdud rtsi'i chu tsam gcig skam nas 'dom
NK033(gi)001:8523: tsam pa gcig lus pa dang zhu ba de la
NK033(gi)001:8524: nyin re 'ju tshad tsam re 'thung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8525: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gis rgas pa med cing
NK033(gi)001:8526: bu mo lo bcu drug lon pa'i sha tshugs su
NK033(gi)001:8528: de tshe lo stong thub bo //
NK033(gi)001:8529: yang na bdud rtsi'i chu phul gang /
NK033(gi)001:8530: rgya sran btsos pa'i khu ba phul brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:8531: mar khu phul gang rnams bkol te /
NK033(gi)001:8532: mar khu tsam gcig lus pa dang grangs su bcug /
NK033(gi)001:8533: sbrang rtsi bre phyed tsam dang sbyar te zla ba
NK033(gi)001:8534: gcig gi bar du ran tshod 'thung na blo rno
NK033(gi)001:8535: la yid gzhungs pa lo bcu drug lon pa'i sha
NK033(gi)001:8536: tshugs sam mdangs dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8538: yang na bdud rtsi'i chu'i nang du mar bre bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:8539: til phul gang bugs nas bkol te /
NK033(gi)001:8540: lus kun la byug na rgas pa med cing thos pa mi brjed par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8541: yang na zla ba gcig gi bar du nang re
NK033(gi)001:8542: bdud rtsi'i chu khyor re 'thung rgas pa med cing
NK033(gi)001:8543: tshe lo lnga brgya thub par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8544: bdud rtsis zla ba gcig tu khrus byas na rgas pa med cing gzhon sha chags par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8545: yang na zla ba gcig gi bar du nyin re bzhin 'thung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8546: sna bug tu blugs na yang rgas pa med cing 'go ba'i nad kyis mi tshugs par 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:8550: sbrang rtsi dang mar dang lhan cig tu sbyar la /
NK033(gi)001:8552: de la 'chi ba mi yong bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8553: de ni bdud rtsi'i mchog yin /
NK033(gi)001:8554: mdor na mang du smos mi 'tshal te /
NK033(gi)001:8555: ji ltar sgrub pa yang sman bcud len gyi bya ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8556: bdud rtsi'i chu dang dngul chu na ra la bcal ba'i rnam gnyis dang /
NK033(gi)001:8557: lag mthil du mnyed na dngul chur 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:8558: gser zho gnyis tsam la byas pa'i snod du bstum
NK033(gi)001:8559: ste khar bcug na rang re'i lus mi mthong bar
NK033(gi)001:8560: 'gyur la / gzhan gyi longs spyod kun la dbang zhing longs spyod par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8561: tshe nyi zla dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8562: de lta bu'i bcud len bdud rtsi'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:8563: yang lugs gcig la mon gyi byi ba dkar po
NK033(gi)001:8564: dang sbrul blag pa zer te sprangs pa'am shugs pa'i
NK033(gi)001:8565: sdong po'i bar nas 'bu dkar po gcig 'ong ba
NK033(gi)001:8566: de / sbrul ser khra zer te sbrul pa'am a
NK033(gi)001:8567: sho g+han+d+ha ra la sogs pa'i 'bru gu ser khra'am
NK033(gi)001:8568: sngo khra thig le can 'ong ba de la bya'o
NK033(gi)001:8569: de / // de gsum 'o mar btsos pas zhu nas de'i khu ba phyed btung /
NK033(gi)001:8570: lhag ma phyed po de dang /
NK033(gi)001:8571: a ru ra phyed ma gnyis mang du bsres la 'o ma mang du blugs zhor mnan /
NK033(gi)001:8574: ngang ngur gyi sgo nga dang sbyar la za'o //
NK033(gi)001:8575: skyobs su sbrang rtsi la rta byas na rab bo //
NK033(gi)001:8576: des ni tshe lo stong thub ste rgas pa med
NK033(gi)001:8577: pa bu mo lo bcu drug lon pa'i gzhon sha
NK033(gi)001:8579: de ni rgas pa bcing ba drang srong rdzogs byed kyi bcud len no //
NK033(gi)001:8580: 'chi ba 'ching ba dpal kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes kyi gdams ngag ni /
NK033(gi)001:8581: de la yang sa rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:8586: de la lta ba tshig thog tu 'byams su mi 'jug ste /
NK033(gi)001:8587: don dang rang du rig cing rang du gsal ba de la lta ba'i sa /
NK033(gi)001:8588: sgom pa blo thog tu dmigs su mi 'jug ste /
NK033(gi)001:8589: blo'i rtog pa gang yang mi gnas te sgom pa'i sa /
NK033(gi)001:8590: spyod pa 'bras bu yin thog tu gol mi 'jug
NK033(gi)001:8591: pa de blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang
NK033(gi)001:8592: mi gnas pa de 'bras bu'i sa /
NK033(gi)001:8593: de tsa na gsal bas ma rig pa dag /
NK033(gi)001:8595: bde bas sdug bsngal dang bral /
NK033(gi)001:8596: dbyer mi phyed pa la blo'i mtha' zab cing phra
NK033(gi)001:8597: ba tsam yang mi gnas pas blo tshig las 'das
NK033(gi)001:8599: chos kyi dbyings de ni byas pa dang bcos pa med de /
NK033(gi)001:8600: dus gsum du 'gyur ba med pa'i gnas lugs de
NK033(gi)001:8601: la ni skye ba dang 'chi ba bya ba'i 'du
NK033(gi)001:8602: 'bral med pas na 'chi ba bcings pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8603: bcing ba gsum gyi gdams pa rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:8604: thig le gor ba dang rtsa kha sdom pa'i man ngag bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:8609: lug mig mkhan pas ri la skye ba'i mi che ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8611: da lis ba lu dkar po yin nam snyam /
NK033(gi)001:8612: dkar po'i me tog gang rung re'i phye ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:8613: mnyam gsung ste re re bag tsam tsham du dgos snyam gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:8616: g.yu sbrul thig le dkar dmar /
NK033(gi)001:8619: g.yu sbrul gnyis kyi phye ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:8623: phag khrag dang brgyad po bung mnyam la phye mar sbyar la /
NK033(gi)001:8624: ka ra yang de tsho'i sum cha tsam du sbyar la /
NK033(gi)001:8625: ra dkar mo'i 'o yo og pa /
NK033(gi)001:8627: gzhan phul phyed 'ga' tsam bkol la dang po la
NK033(gi)001:8628: ba'i dus su co ka'i sgo nga btab la zhog
NK033(gi)001:8630: de yang sngon du rtsa bshal gcig btang na yang legs so //
NK033(gi)001:8631: de min rlung bag re mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:8632: zhag 'ag'i gong du lto gtsang du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8633: do mod dgong nas bsnyung bar byas la /
NK033(gi)001:8634: nangs pa bya tsam na btang la /
NK033(gi)001:8635: nam langs nas zhog par dom mkhris thun gcig /
NK033(gi)001:8636: pad+ma r+aa ga thun gcig sbyar la btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8637: de nas gro gung tsam na mar khu phul phyed
NK033(gi)001:8638: zhan tsam zan med par hub 'thungs su btang ngo
NK033(gi)001:8639: // de nas nyi ma phyed yol ba dang lto gtsang ba zhag gcig btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:8641: sman dgu pos thig le bsgom pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:8642: gnyis pos rtsa kha sdom pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:8643: de lta bu'i gdams pa 'di ni /
NK033(gi)001:8644: slob dpon 'dzeng chen pos jo sras 'dzeng zhag gsum du lto gcod dgos pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8647: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dga' ldan du gshegs nges pa'i ring bsrel rnyed na rab /
NK033(gi)001:8648: de ma rnyed na rus pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:8653: de lnga dar dkar pos dril /
NK033(gi)001:8655: de nas rin po che'i snod du bcug la spyi bor gdags so //
NK033(gi)001:8656: sngags ni rten 'brel snying po la bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8657: de ni rdo rje sems dpa' khu tshur gyi gdams ngag las rkyen bcings pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:8658: na ba bcing ba'i gdams ngag go //
NK033(gi)001:8660: 'di'i mtshams mkha' 'gro sde gsum gyi bsnyen pa dang sgrub pa las sbyor gnyis kyi zhal gdams dang /
NK033(gi)001:8661: mkha' 'gro'i las kyi mgo mjug tu las bcu gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)001:8662: stegs bu'i zhal gdams rnams gong du sgrub pa'i skor na yod do ////
NK033(gi)001:8663: d+aa ki sde gsum gyi sngags 'bum logs su bkol ba bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:8664: sh+r+ai he ru ka na mo /
NK033(gi)001:8665: mkha' 'gro sde gsum gyi spyan drangs pa /
NK033(gi)001:8667: da ha na he dzam si sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK033(gi)001:8668: dzah d+ha ra sa na pa ke ro na g+h+rih+na
NK033(gi)001:8669: a gad dzah a gad dzah a gad dzahs+w+aa h+aa
NK033(gi)001:8675: sde gsum gyi mchod pa 'bul ba /
NK033(gi)001:8676: da ha na mu kha he p+au dza ba ling+ta g+h+rih+na dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8679: dz+wa la ma he mu kha'i 'agre'o //
NK033(gi)001:8680: ka ka mu khi kam kam dmar nag las wa'i mgo can ma /
NK033(gi)001:8682: dzam dzam ser las lce spyang gdong can ma /
NK033(gi)001:8683: su khi mu khi mu khi dzam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8684: shwa shwa dmar po las shwa na'i mgo can ma /
NK033(gi)001:8685: na mu khi sham des g.yog gsum mched /
NK033(gi)001:8688: u ti un ta be ta ya b+ha ling+ta /
NK033(gi)001:8689: me ra b+ha ya b+ha ling+ta grih+na ma ma ka ram pa ha ya khyi'i ros bcun /
NK033(gi)001:8691: a ru lu ru lu he ru ka'i bsrung /
NK033(gi)001:8693: tsi ti b+hu d+hu ma ne phre ya y+aa s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8694: dz+wa la d+ha la da la mu khi sh+aa t+r+aum /
NK033(gi)001:8695: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK033(gi)001:8698: hri da ya sa ma s+ya h+aum phata phata phata gu ru g+h+rih+na dz+ny+aa a ma ri ya dz+ny+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8699: mkha' 'gro ma sde gsum gyi bsnyen pa'i sngags la /
NK033(gi)001:8701: dz+wa la ha na mu kha dz+wa la zhag gsum /
NK033(gi)001:8702: na la ne h+r+ai h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:8703: d+ha mkha' la gshegs ma ha na mu ke dz+wa la zhag gsum na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:8705: ha na mu khe dz+wa la zhag gsum /
NK033(gi)001:8707: zhag gsum na las re re nub dgu la zhun mar gyi mar me gsum /
NK033(gi)001:8712: dz+wa la ha na d+ha ha na da ha gtso mo gsum gyi bsnyen sngags yin /
NK033(gi)001:8713: na mu khe dz+wa la na la ne h+r+aihh+aum phata /
NK033(gi)001:8714: ka ka g.yog mo gsum gyi bsnyen sngags /
NK033(gi)001:8715: mu khi kam dzam su khi mu khi dzam sho na mu khi sham h+aum dza phata /
NK033(gi)001:8716: d+ha ha na sbyin sreg gi sngags yin /
NK033(gi)001:8718: da ha na mu khe s+w+aa h+aa phata /
NK033(gi)001:8719: dz+wa la ha na mu khe s+w+aa h+aa phata /
NK033(gi)001:8720: 'di ni 'khrul 'khor la dgod pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:8722: dz+ny+aa h+na gri ru gu phata phata phata h+aum s+ya ma sa ya da hri /
NK033(gi)001:8725: ya ra m+aa ya ra m+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8726: trum d+aa ki sde gsum gyi sngags 'bum mo //
NK033(gi)001:8727: tsakra rtsibs brgyad pa'i rtse mo nang du bstan pa'i lte ba la ling+ga bri /
NK033(gi)001:8729: sha khi mu la da la d+ha la dz+wa /
NK033(gi)001:8730: gtso mo gsum la de'i nang du gri snying srog dang srog snying gzhug la gdams /
NK033(gi)001:8731: snying sna tshogs pa'i gtor ma /
NK033(gi)001:8732: g.yog klad khrag zhag gtor sha gtor khrag gtor mo gsum la gtor mi zhun rta sha ma gsum /
NK033(gi)001:8733: snying sna gsum khwa ta'i snying /
NK033(gi)001:8735: spyang ki'i snying srog nang du gzhug /
NK033(gi)001:8737: sa'i ro gsum rdzas zhal gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:8742: skas kha rnying pa'i shing dang /
NK033(gi)001:8744: zam pa'i shing dang gsum bsregs pa'i sol ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8745: chu'i ro gsum la brtsod chu chu mig lkugs pa /
NK033(gi)001:8747: da me ser ba'i chu chu dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:8749: ling ga de ro gnya' lag bskyig pa'i tshul du byas la /
NK033(gi)001:8750: de'i snying khar ling+ga bstsal te /
NK033(gi)001:8753: bong bu'i rngams bskyigs te gtor tshugs nang gi chos 'byung du bstsal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8754: dgra la rtags byung nas gri dong gri khug zer /
NK033(gi)001:8756: de lung gsum gyi mdo gtor tshugs 'og tu ru mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:8757: mtshams khongs su shi na de rangs su mnan no //
NK033(gi)001:8758: d+aa ki sde gsum gyi sngags 'bum /
NK033(gi)001:8759: zhal gdams logs su bkod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8762: shin then wa la sha'i mdo las rkyen gyis thar pa'i lung /
NK033(gi)001:8763: 'dzam gling skye gnas dag pa las //
NK033(gi)001:8764: grol ba dang ni rang grol 'byung //
NK033(gi)001:8766: de la rang grol ba la bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:8768: yang rab skye ba chig chod /
NK033(gi)001:8772: rkyen gyis thar pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:8774: bud med rtsa pad+ma can khrag tu 'o ma can dang 'phrad na rkyen gyis thar pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:8775: thod pa dum bu gcig pa rdo rje'i gtsug phud can dang 'phrad na rkyen gyis thar pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:8776: byang chub sems dpa' mtshan rab zhi zla 'od kyis glog la phyin pa'i lam ri logs gcig la /
NK033(gi)001:8777: sa g.yul thang tsam la gcig gi thog na bar
NK033(gi)001:8778: na nam mkha' na 'phar 'gro bar byung nas de
NK033(gi)001:8779: nas bltas pas thod pa dum bu gcig pa rdo
NK033(gi)001:8780: rje'i gtsug phud can rnyed nas de tshag byas pas
NK033(gi)001:8781: lus nam mkha' la 'gro bar gyur te dga' ldan
NK033(gi)001:8782: du gshegs so // skye ba bdun pa'i sha zos
NK033(gi)001:8783: na rkyen gyis khu byug sgo nga nas thon pa
NK033(gi)001:8784: 'dra ba grib ma mdun du 'ong ba /
NK033(gi)001:8785: skad snyan pa mig gsang 'gebs pa dkyus ring ba
NK033(gi)001:8786: dri zhim pa lus la 'od 'dom gang yod pa
NK033(gi)001:8788: 'gro na bya ngang pa'i 'gros su 'gro ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:8789: de rnyed na seng ge bzhin no //
NK033(gi)001:8791: mkha' spyod du gshegs nges pa'i ring bsrel mid shes na nor bu chu dwangs 'dra ba lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:8793: ring bsrel mid thabs gdams pa 'di /
NK033(gi)001:8795: 'di bzhi rnyed nas brten shes na don 'grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:8796: de rnams chos la mi brten pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:8797: grol ba ni brda' dang ngag ste /
NK033(gi)001:8798: de la lus kyi brda' la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:8799: gnad kyi brda' yis gnas bsgyur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8802: gnad dang dus kyi brda la gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:8803: de la dus kyi brda' ni /
NK033(gi)001:8804: rlung sna bug g.yon nas rgyu ba'i dus su //
NK033(gi)001:8805: bla ma'i byin rlabs 'jug pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:8807: rgyal chen n+aa ro'i chos bzhi'am rnam snang gi chos bdun la sogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:8810: 'og rlung yid tsam de gsum bde ba'i brda' /
NK033(gi)001:8812: lce yar rkan mar rkan la mi reg /
NK033(gi)001:8818: dbyer mi phyed pa gcig rang shugs la mi skye mi srid do //
NK033(gi)001:8819: de ltar bsgoms pas dang po rtse gcig sgyu ma lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:8820: gnyis pa du ma ro gcig stong pa'i nyams /
NK033(gi)001:8821: gsum pa spros bral rnam dag gi /
NK033(gi)001:8822: rtags rnams kyang de'i ngang la 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:8823: de ni chos la nyams len dgos /
NK033(gi)001:8824: brten pa de sgom pa la 'bad par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:8825: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag 'dir 'dus
NK033(gi)001:8826: pas snod dang mi ldan pa la shin tu gsang
NK033(gi)001:8828: rdzas la brten nas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin sgrub pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:8831: ba dmar gyi chur zhag bdun sbang /
NK033(gi)001:8832: de nas bton la 'o ma bre gsum du zhag bdun sbang /
NK033(gi)001:8833: de zho ru btsos la mar dbyung /
NK033(gi)001:8834: a ru ra de cong zhi chu bre gsum gyi nang du btsos la chu bre phyed du btang /
NK033(gi)001:8835: mdzo mo'i 'o ma bre gang gdus la bre phyed du btang /
NK033(gi)001:8837: da ci'i mar dang bcas la bskol /
NK033(gi)001:8840: pho rog gi sgo nga gnyis dkar po dbyung la ser po blugs /
NK033(gi)001:8841: shug pa'i nor bu phul gang blugs /
NK033(gi)001:8842: de la yi dam gyi sngags zhag bdun bzlas la /
NK033(gi)001:8843: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu rol /
NK033(gi)001:8844: de 'dra ba zla ba gsum byas na /
NK033(gi)001:8845: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8846: dga' rab rdo rje'i ye shes kyi lha'i dbang dbab pa'i gdams pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:8848: rdo rje zam pa'i tshe chog nyung du bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:8849: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8850: tshe chog las kyi rim pa /
NK033(gi)001:8851: bum pa dar dmar po'i mgul chings can dang bcas pa /
NK033(gi)001:8852: nang du snying po lnga blugs /
NK033(gi)001:8855: me long dang dar dmar po btags pa thogs la /
NK033(gi)001:8856: 'bru brgyad bgrang zhing bum pa'i tshe zan la bstim /
NK033(gi)001:8858: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK033(gi)001:8859: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NK033(gi)001:8860: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:8861: mnyam nyid sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8862: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK033(gi)001:8863: gsung mchog rnam par dag pa'i gsung //
NK033(gi)001:8864: mkha' dang 'dra ba'i gsung mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:8865: mnyam nyid gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8866: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK033(gi)001:8867: thugs mchog mi rtog pa yi thugs //
NK033(gi)001:8868: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)001:8869: mnyam nyid thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:8870: rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:8876: sarba ro pa sid+d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8878: nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam rtog bral //
NK033(gi)001:8879: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas skye shi med //
NK033(gi)001:8880: rin chen dbyings phyug ma ni dgos 'dod re ba skong //
NK033(gi)001:8881: pad+ma dbyings phyug ma ni 'dzin med chags dang bral //
NK033(gi)001:8882: las kyi dbyings phyug ma ni mngon spyod phrin las mdzad //
NK033(gi)001:8883: dbyings phyug chen mo lnga rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)001:8884: rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)001:8886: shar phyogs ke ke ru yi gzhal yas nas //
NK033(gi)001:8887: dkar mo mgyogs ma zhi byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:8888: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:8889: gsang ba'i lha mo bde ba rgyas 'debs ma //
NK033(gi)001:8890: rigs kyi lha mo yum chen sangs rgyas spyan //
NK033(gi)001:8891: phyag rgya'i lha mo badz+ra l+aa s+ya ma //
NK033(gi)001:8892: p+au dza'i lha mo badz+ra d+h+au pe ma //
NK033(gi)001:8893: 'gugs pa'i lha mo rdo rje lcags kyu ma //
NK033(gi)001:8894: shar phyogs tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)001:8895: shar phyogs dri za'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK033(gi)001:8896: shar lho me lha'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig /
NK033(gi)001:8897: mi 'gyur tshe yi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)001:8900: lho phyogs bee d+aur+ya yi zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:8901: sngon mo drag shul 'od zer 'phro ba'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:8902: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:8903: gsang ba'i lha mo bde ba za byed ma //
NK033(gi)001:8904: rigs kyi lha mo yum chen m+aa ma k+ai /
NK033(gi)001:8905: phyag rgya'i lha mo badz+ra m+aa l+ye ma //
NK033(gi)001:8906: mchod pa'i lha mo badz+ra push+pe ma //
NK033(gi)001:8907: 'ching ba'i lha mo rdo rje zhags pa ma //
NK033(gi)001:8908: lho phyogs tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)001:8909: lho phyogs gshin rje'i lag nas tshe khug la //
NK033(gi)001:8910: lho nub srin po'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig /
NK033(gi)001:8912: nub phyogs pad+ma dbang gi zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:8913: dmar mo dbang sdud zhi byed 'od 'phros tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:8914: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:8915: gsang ba'i lha mo bde ba rmongs byed ma //
NK033(gi)001:8916: rigs kyi lha mo yum chen na bza' dkar //
NK033(gi)001:8917: phyag rgya'i lha mo badz+ra girti ma //
NK033(gi)001:8918: p+au dza'i lha mo badz+ra +aa lo ke //
NK033(gi)001:8919: bsdom pa'i lha mo rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma //
NK033(gi)001:8920: nub phyogs tshe bdag chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)001:8921: nub phyogs klu yi lag nas tshe khug la //
NK033(gi)001:8922: nub byang rlung lha'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig /
NK033(gi)001:8924: byang phyogs in+d+ra ni la'i zhing khams nas //
NK033(gi)001:8925: ljang gu phrin las 'od zer 'phro ba'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)001:8926: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:8927: gsang ba'i lha mo bde ba tshe 'phel ma //
NK033(gi)001:8928: rigs kyi lha mo yum chen dam tshig sgrol //
NK033(gi)001:8929: phyag rgya'i lha mo badz+ra ni rti ma //
NK033(gi)001:8930: mchod pa'i lha mo badz+ra gan+d+he ma //
NK033(gi)001:8931: 'bebs pa'i lha mo rdo rje dril bu ma //
NK033(gi)001:8932: byang phyogs tshe bdag chen mo khyed kyi rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)001:8933: byang phyogs gnod sbyin lag nas tshe khug la //
NK033(gi)001:8934: byang shar 'byung po'i lag nas dpal skyobs shig /
NK033(gi)001:8937: de nas tshe yar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:8939: ldeg pa rnams bkug la bum par bstim /
NK033(gi)001:8940: a yu dz+ny+aa na tshe yi mchog /
NK033(gi)001:8941: sa la nyams na gser la bsdu //
NK033(gi)001:8942: chu la nyams na chang la bsdu //
NK033(gi)001:8943: rtsi la nyams na mar la bsdu //
NK033(gi)001:8944: 'bru la nyams na til la bsdu //
NK033(gi)001:8945: 'bru lnga yi ni snying po lnga //
NK033(gi)001:8946: gnas lnga dag tu byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)001:8947: rnal 'byor tshe la bar chad med //
NK033(gi)001:8948: rnal 'byor tshe la dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)001:8949: de nas tshe dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:8951: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)001:8952: nam mkha' gsang ba'i yum las byung //
NK033(gi)001:8953: nam mkha' rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8954: dbang bskur chen po dam pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:8955: bud+d+ha k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK033(gi)001:8956: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)001:8957: rdo rje gsang ba'i yum las byung //
NK033(gi)001:8958: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8959: dbang bskur chen po dam pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:8960: h'u badz+ra k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)001:8961: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)001:8962: rin chen gsang ba'i yum las byung //
NK033(gi)001:8963: rin chen rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8964: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:8965: s+w+aa rat+na k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8966: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)001:8967: pad+ma gsang ba'i yum las byung //
NK033(gi)001:8968: pad+ma rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8969: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:8970: +aam pad+ma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aamh ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)001:8971: las rab gsang ba'i yum las byung //
NK033(gi)001:8972: las kyi rigs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)001:8973: dbang bskur chen po dam pa sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:8974: h+aa karma k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:8975: mgo bo'i gnas lngar bum pas dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)001:8976: bud+d+ha lo tsa na a yu she /
NK033(gi)001:8980: de nas smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:8981: bden pa brdar ba'i rjes la /
NK033(gi)001:8982: rigs kyi bu 'di la rdo rjee tshe yi dbang bskur bas tshe dbang du gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8983: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8984: skye med kyi ye shes su gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8985: 'chi med kyi bdud rtsir gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8986: mi 'gyur ba'i g.yung drung du gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8987: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan du gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8988: mi shigs pa'i rdo rjer gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:8989: tshe'i cho ga chung ba rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:8992: g.yas tshe'i bum pa g.yon gyi rdo rje rgya gram
NK033(gi)001:8993: yab yum gyi sku la 'khril sbyor du yod par
NK033(gi)001:8995: yum na bza' dkar mo sku mdog dmar mo /
NK033(gi)001:9002: sangs rgyas rigs kyi spyan dkar g.yas rdo rje /
NK033(gi)001:9004: lho ru za byed ma gsang ba'i yum de bi /
NK033(gi)001:9006: m+aa ma rigs kyi k+ai sngon g.yas rin chen /
NK033(gi)001:9008: nub tu rmongs gsang ba'i yum de bi byed ma dang /
NK033(gi)001:9009: gos rigs kyi dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pad+ma /
NK033(gi)001:9011: byang du tshe gsang ba'i yum de bi /
NK033(gi)001:9013: dam rigs tshig sgrol ma ljang gu /
NK033(gi)001:9014: g.yas rdo rje g.yon rgya gram /
NK033(gi)001:9015: de nas rtsibs shar lho'i mchan du /
NK033(gi)001:9020: lho nub tu m+aa l+ye ma sngon mo g.yas phreng ba /
NK033(gi)001:9030: bdug spos ma gru chad la mchod pa'i lha mo shar lho /
NK033(gi)001:9038: mar nub byang gru chad la /
NK033(gi)001:9042: dri chab byang shar gru chad la /
NK033(gi)001:9046: lcags sgo ma bzhi las shar du /
NK033(gi)001:9052: sku mdog dkar mthing dmar ljang rim pa /
NK033(gi)001:9054: g.yas ming gis mtshon pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9055: g.yon shel mthing byu ru g.yu'i bum pa thogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9056: tshe chung gi dal du bsgom rung /
NK033(gi)001:9057: mngon rtogs su byed kyang de bzhin du bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:9059: sangs rgyas tshul bzhi'i zhal gdams //
NK033(gi)001:9060: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9061: rna brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa 'di la gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:9064: nag khrid la don rnam pa gsum gyi skya bar
NK033(gi)001:9065: nas brda' bzhi'i ngo sprod la brten nas bde gsal
NK033(gi)001:9066: ngo sprad pa mun khung gi sgron me lta bu
NK033(gi)001:9067: / blo chung ba la lam du bstan no //
NK033(gi)001:9068: dmar khrid la bzhi skor bsdoms kyi skya bar nas /
NK033(gi)001:9069: dus gsum gcig chod la brten nas /
NK033(gi)001:9070: gang shar thogs med du ngo sprad pas /
NK033(gi)001:9071: dper na sems can tshim pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9072: de la rdo rje tshig lam sems kyi lde mig bstan pa 'di la /
NK033(gi)001:9073: rdo rje chos nyid kyi gshis brtan spros pa dang bral ba lam gyi gdams ngag bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9074: rang la gnas pa lde mig gis nyams su myong bar ngo sprad pas skye ba med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9076: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la skar ma rgyal
NK033(gi)001:9077: gyi nyin par phyag spyi bor bzhag nas byin gyis
NK033(gi)001:9078: brlabs pas / a ha ho'i sgra byung bas yi ge 'bru bzhi la lam byas te bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9080: a skye ba med pa'i don bzhis bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9081: ha 'gyur ba med pa don gzer bzhis bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9082: ho 'gags pa med pa'i don brda' bzhis bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9083: 'i dbyer mi phyed pa'i don bzhis bstan te /
NK033(gi)001:9092: ho dbang po ma bkag pa /
NK033(gi)001:9095: lce'i rtse mo gar yang mi brten /
NK033(gi)001:9100: sems nyid de dang po gang nas kyang ma byung bas /
NK033(gi)001:9101: skye ma myong bas chos nyid kyi tshul lo //
NK033(gi)001:9102: tha ma gang du yang mi 'gro bas /
NK033(gi)001:9103: da lta skye mi srid pas dbyings kyi tshul /
NK033(gi)001:9104: da lta gang na yang mi gnas pas bde ba'i tshul /
NK033(gi)001:9105: de ye nas rang la yod par shes pas ye shes kyi tshul lo //
NK033(gi)001:9106: sems nyid skye ma myong bas rnam rtog glo bur du byung yang /
NK033(gi)001:9108: rjes med pa ltar skyon gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9109: de mi skye bas nyon mongs dag /
NK033(gi)001:9112: de ltar ngos bzung med pas /
NK033(gi)001:9115: ma 'gags pas ma shar ba yang lta ba /
NK033(gi)001:9117: dper na nam mkha' la sprin byung yang /
NK033(gi)001:9118: nam mkha' la phan gnod med pa'i phyir ma byung
NK033(gi)001:9119: yang nam mkha' la dngos po dang mtshan mar ma
NK033(gi)001:9121: lta bar gtan la 'bebs pas rtsol bsgrub dang bral ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9122: a skye ba med pa'i don no //
NK033(gi)001:9124: ma ltas phyogs ris kun dang bral /
NK033(gi)001:9125: mi bcos mi bslad ma bcos pa ru bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:9126: de'i ngang las blo mi gnas /
NK033(gi)001:9129: de'i ngang la yin min la sogs snyems byed kun dang bral /
NK033(gi)001:9130: de lta bu gcig tu rtogs tsa na snang stong gnyis med chos kyi dbyings /
NK033(gi)001:9131: dper na thang la nyi ma shar ba 'dra /
NK033(gi)001:9132: mun pa btsal bas mi rnyed /
NK033(gi)001:9133: sems nyid rnam par dag pa de la /
NK033(gi)001:9134: rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pas gol sa btsal yang mi rnyed /
NK033(gi)001:9135: thams cad lta bar gyur pas cir snang lta bar gtan la phebs /
NK033(gi)001:9136: de la ming du btags pas /
NK033(gi)001:9137: lta ba blo bral snyems chod zer te /
NK033(gi)001:9138: lta ba mi 'gyur ba'i gzer thebs so //
NK033(gi)001:9139: de tsam na dmigs pa la gtad sa med de /
NK033(gi)001:9140: ci shar sgom pa'i klong du gyur pas /
NK033(gi)001:9141: yengs su med de sgom pa'i gzer thebs so //
NK033(gi)001:9142: de la ming du btags pas /
NK033(gi)001:9143: sgom pa gtad med yengs med yin /
NK033(gi)001:9144: de tsam na snang ba ci shar cir snang yang shar ba ma 'gags 'dzin pa med /
NK033(gi)001:9145: ci shar rang sar dag pas /
NK033(gi)001:9146: dper na bya 'phur ba la rjes med pa dang 'dra bas /
NK033(gi)001:9147: spyod pa klong du gyur pas /
NK033(gi)001:9149: de la ming du btags pas /
NK033(gi)001:9150: spyod pa snang yang mi 'dzin yin /
NK033(gi)001:9151: de chos nyid ye nas rnam par dag pa /
NK033(gi)001:9152: de gang zag gi rgyud la nyams su myong bas /
NK033(gi)001:9153: dri ma can gyi rlung dag /
NK033(gi)001:9154: nyon mongs can gyi gzhi dag /
NK033(gi)001:9155: bag chags sogs byed kyi snod dag /
NK033(gi)001:9156: sa bon cha'i kun gzhi dag /
NK033(gi)001:9159: de la ming du btags na /
NK033(gi)001:9160: 'bras bu ka dag dbyings grol zer /
NK033(gi)001:9161: des ha 'gyur ba med pa'i don yin no //
NK033(gi)001:9162: ho brda' bzhi la dbang po ma bkag pa gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:9163: ma g.yos pa mi rtog pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:9164: 'og rlung 'then pas lus yod du mi tshor ba bde ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:9165: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang ma brten pas dbyer mi phyed pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:9166: gsal med rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba yin /
NK033(gi)001:9167: mi rtog pa de mi rtog pa'i chos nyid /
NK033(gi)001:9168: lus yod du mi tshor ba de zag med kyi bde ba /
NK033(gi)001:9169: dbyer mi phyed pa chos nyid kyis rnam par dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9170: des ho 'gags pa med pa'i don no //
NK033(gi)001:9172: brda' don bsre ba'i man ngag yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9173: tha mal gyi shes pa blo las ma byung ba /
NK033(gi)001:9177: gnyug ma de ni de'i ngang las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9179: so ma ni rang lus yod du mi tshor ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9180: lhug pa ni de'i ngang la rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9181: de ltar shar ba gtan la phebs pa'i sems kyis sems ngo shes /
NK033(gi)001:9182: sems nyid rang ngo shes pas rten med kyi rig pa rang grol /
NK033(gi)001:9183: 'dzin med kyi shes pa rang gsal bas thogs med kyi shes rab rang shar /
NK033(gi)001:9185: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa 'dir /
NK033(gi)001:9188: sems can don du kun la bshad //
NK033(gi)001:9189: dmar khrid sems kyi dkyil du sbas //
NK033(gi)001:9190: 'phel na mkha' 'gro gsum gyi bka' chad 'ong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:9192: zhal gdams 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor /
NK033(gi)001:9193: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9194: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la don rnam pa gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:9195: chos spyi'i rnam pa gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9196: don rang gi mtshan nyid du gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9197: dang po de gtan la 'bebs pa la /
NK033(gi)001:9202: nam mkha' la rnam pa gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9206: dpe'i nam mkha' ni yar gyi nam mkha' kha dog dang bcas pa de ma yin /
NK033(gi)001:9207: mar sa la nye ba de yang ma yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9208: bar gyi nam mkha' stong pa 'di la /
NK033(gi)001:9209: ston zla gsum la sa'i rdul ni non /
NK033(gi)001:9210: sprin dang khu rlangs ni yal ba de'i dus su
NK033(gi)001:9211: shin tu dag pa rdzas su ma grub pa de
NK033(gi)001:9212: la ngos bzung dang bral ba /
NK033(gi)001:9213: de la sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin zer nas gtan la 'bebs te /
NK033(gi)001:9214: de la sangs rgyas dgongs pa de ngos bzung du mi btub ste rang rgyud la ma reg go //
NK033(gi)001:9216: don gyi nam mkha' ni shes pa la ma byas pa /
NK033(gi)001:9219: rang lugs su bzhag pas rnam par rtog pa phra zhing phra ba yang ma skyes par /
NK033(gi)001:9223: mi phyed pa gcig rgyud la lhag gis 'char /
NK033(gi)001:9224: rtogs pas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dbye bsri med pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:9226: min na yo min pa gcig rgyud pa 'char ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9227: de ni don gyi nam mkha' 'o //
NK033(gi)001:9229: chos thams cad la don du snang yang don du mi 'dzin /
NK033(gi)001:9231: nam mkha' bzhin du yid la mi byed pa /
NK033(gi)001:9232: rkyen ci shar yang mi bde ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:9233: sems can thams cad la rang bzhin gyis byams pa /
NK033(gi)001:9234: snying rje che ba la ched du 'dzin pa'i blo med pa gcig 'byung /
NK033(gi)001:9235: de ni rtags kyi nam mkha' 'o //
NK033(gi)001:9238: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs lhun grub chen po
NK033(gi)001:9239: ci yin zer nas chos kyi gtan la phebs pas
NK033(gi)001:9240: / snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul yin zer nas /
NK033(gi)001:9244: de ltar ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa'i sems yin /
NK033(gi)001:9245: de ltar du ngo shes tsam na sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs yin zer ba des ni /
NK033(gi)001:9246: rang rgyud bzlog tu ma btub ste /
NK033(gi)001:9248: de ni dpe'i sems nyid do //
NK033(gi)001:9250: bla mas gdams ngag bstan pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:9251: brda' ngos zin nas don rang gi rgyud la ngos med du yer gyis nyams su myong nas /
NK033(gi)001:9252: chos thams cad skad cig ma gcig gis steng du bden par zad nas /
NK033(gi)001:9253: yar sangs rgya la 'dod pa'i mtha' chod /
NK033(gi)001:9254: mar 'khor ba la dogs pa'i snyems zhig nas /
NK033(gi)001:9255: da lta'i shes pa 'di 'khor 'das gnyis med du nyams su myong ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9256: de la don gyi sems nyid ces bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9258: chos thams cad stong pa nyid du shes shing /
NK033(gi)001:9259: stong pa nyid du gyur nas /
NK033(gi)001:9260: tshogs drug stong par nyams su myong bas /
NK033(gi)001:9261: spyod pa bab col du spyod /
NK033(gi)001:9262: snang ba gzhan gyis khol mi gnod /
NK033(gi)001:9263: ched du 'dzin pa kho la med pas /
NK033(gi)001:9264: chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shes nas /
NK033(gi)001:9266: zhen gang la yang ma zhen pa gcig kho la yod /
NK033(gi)001:9267: de ni rtags kyi sems nyid do //
NK033(gi)001:9270: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de rang du rig
NK033(gi)001:9271: cing rang gsal ba ni me long lta bu'i ye
NK033(gi)001:9272: shes / yod pa sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la yod pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK033(gi)001:9273: de bla ma'i gdams ngag gis bstan du yod pas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK033(gi)001:9274: de rang gis go bar byung bas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK033(gi)001:9275: de la rang bzhin med pas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes zer nas /
NK033(gi)001:9276: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa na yod pa de yin zer /
NK033(gi)001:9277: de ni dpe'i ye shes yin /
NK033(gi)001:9279: bla ma'i gdams ngag gis rgyud la sbyar bas /
NK033(gi)001:9280: 'khor 'das gnyis med du nyams su myong nas /
NK033(gi)001:9281: re dogs kyi mdud pa zhig nas /
NK033(gi)001:9284: snang stong rtag chad kyi mtha' chod /
NK033(gi)001:9285: rtog mi rtog gnyis su med pa'i dpe'i rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9286: de ni don gyi ye shes so //
NK033(gi)001:9288: chos thams cad spros pa dang bral ba /
NK033(gi)001:9289: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa rgyud la shar nas /
NK033(gi)001:9290: 'di yin 'di min med par gnyis med du thug phrad du gyur nas /
NK033(gi)001:9291: rnam par rtog pa bya ba ming yang med do //
NK033(gi)001:9292: dpe ni nyi ma shar ba dang 'dra'o //
NK033(gi)001:9293: 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9294: don la rtogs pa'i gdams ngag yin no //
NK033(gi)001:9296: rdo rje sems dpa'i rdo rje'i tshig rdo rje zam
NK033(gi)001:9297: par grags pa brdas don sprod pa zhes pa de
NK033(gi)001:9299: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9300: slob dpon nyang byang chub grags kyi lta ba sgom
NK033(gi)001:9301: gyi rde'u bcu drug las dang po 'di yin no
NK033(gi)001:9302: // lta sgom ngos 'dzin gyi rde'u bzhi ni /
NK033(gi)001:9303: mi skye mi 'gags pa'i lta ba ngos bzung ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:9304: lta stangs kyi sgom pa ngos bzung ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:9305: shugs 'byung gi spyod pa ngos bzung ba dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9306: 'gyur med mtha' dbus kyi 'bras bu ngos bzung ba dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9307: mtshon pa dpe'i rde'u bzhi ni /
NK033(gi)001:9308: 'gags med nam mkha' lta bu'i dpe mtshon /
NK033(gi)001:9309: ri bo 'jug nyal sgom pa'i dpe mtshon /
NK033(gi)001:9310: spre'u rtod la mnan pas spyod pa'i dpe mtshon /
NK033(gi)001:9311: dgos pa 'byung ba nor bus 'bras bu dpe mtshon pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:9313: shar ba skyon med lta bu'i rjes 'jug /
NK033(gi)001:9314: gsal ba sgom med sgom pa'i rjes 'jug /
NK033(gi)001:9315: dran pa brjed bskul spyod pa'i rjes 'jug /
NK033(gi)001:9317: ldang tshad kyi rde'u bzhi ni /
NK033(gi)001:9318: blo bral gyi snyems chod lta ba'i ldang tshad /
NK033(gi)001:9319: ma gtad ma yengs sgom pa'i ldang tshad /
NK033(gi)001:9320: snang yang ma spyod pa spyod pa'i ldang tshad /
NK033(gi)001:9321: ka dag dbyings grol 'bras bu'i ldang tshad do ////
NK033(gi)001:9322: sems kyi gdar sha bcad pa /
NK033(gi)001:9323: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9324: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyi //
NK033(gi)001:9325: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don gdar sha bcad pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9326: lung dang man ngag gnyis kyis gtan la dbab ste /
NK033(gi)001:9328: gsang sngags kyi theg bsdus ni /
NK033(gi)001:9329: ye shes rang rig pa'i rang bzhin ni dbyings nas 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:9330: de sems pa dang brjod par byas na 'jig rten gyi khams g.yo bar 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:9331: kha nas khrag dron mo skyug par 'gyur /
NK033(gi)001:9333: dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa rnams kyang /
NK033(gi)001:9334: sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi thog mtha' btsal du mi rung /
NK033(gi)001:9336: de la shes nas rung bar bstan pa'i lung ni /
NK033(gi)001:9337: rten 'brel gyi cho ga zhib mo nas /
NK033(gi)001:9338: mi rung spangs nas rung 'tshol na //
NK033(gi)001:9339: de la rung ba gang yang med //
NK033(gi)001:9340: mi rung ba nyid du shes na //
NK033(gi)001:9341: de la mi rung gang yang med //
NK033(gi)001:9343: de la rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag gis gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9344: dag dang ma dag rlung nyid las //
NK033(gi)001:9346: sems kyi rang bzhin rlung nyid de //
NK033(gi)001:9347: zab cing kun khyab rkyen las 'char //
NK033(gi)001:9348: grol ba dang ni rang grol 'byung //
NK033(gi)001:9350: de nas gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9351: rang bzhin gyi dbyings dang chos kyi dbyings so //
NK033(gi)001:9352: de la dang po rang bzhin gyi dbyings 'di las /
NK033(gi)001:9353: rlung rnam pa bzhi g.yos te /
NK033(gi)001:9354: de yang rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK033(gi)001:9355: g.yo mi g.yos la yid tsam g.yos //
NK033(gi)001:9356: sngar rtog ma skyes rtog pa'i rnam pa skyes //
NK033(gi)001:9358: de la bud+d+ha la mkhyen pa'i ye shes mnga' /
NK033(gi)001:9359: sems can la rig pa'i ye shes bya ba yod do /
NK033(gi)001:9360: de yang bu d+d+ha'i mkhyen pa'i ye shes su'ang ma gyur /
NK033(gi)001:9361: sems can gyi rig pa ye shes ma gyur pa'i dus su ming du gdags su ma btub ste /
NK033(gi)001:9364: sku gzugs lta bur yang ma gyur ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9365: de yang rang bzhin lung ma bstan gyi dbyings so //
NK033(gi)001:9366: de'i dus su dper na rgya zho mnan pa lta bu'am /
NK033(gi)001:9367: bre kha bcad pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:9368: rang bzhin gyi dbyings 'di la dang po kun tu 'tshol ba'i rlung byung /
NK033(gi)001:9369: de las en gcig je rags su song ba las /
NK033(gi)001:9370: dran pa brtan par byed pa'i rlung byung /
NK033(gi)001:9371: de las en gcig je rags su song ba las /
NK033(gi)001:9372: bstan pa nye bar 'jog pa'i rlung byung /
NK033(gi)001:9374: dag gsal ba dag pa nye bar 'jog pa /
NK033(gi)001:9375: mi rtog pa dag pa nye bar 'jog pa /
NK033(gi)001:9376: bde ba dag pa nye bar 'jog pa /
NK033(gi)001:9377: dbyer mi phyed pa nye bar 'jog pa /
NK033(gi)001:9378: pa dang ma dag pa phyed de /
NK033(gi)001:9379: dag pa ni rang gi ngo bo rang gsal /
NK033(gi)001:9380: gsal ba de rang du rig /
NK033(gi)001:9381: de tsa na blo mi gnas te /
NK033(gi)001:9383: de tsa na lus su mi gnas te snyems byed med de rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed /
NK033(gi)001:9384: dbyer dbyer mi phyed pa de ngo shes tsam na /
NK033(gi)001:9385: rtogs pa mngon 'gyur gyi sangs rgyas so //
NK033(gi)001:9386: de nas yod pa de ngo shes pa rang bzhin lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas so //
NK033(gi)001:9387: de ngo bo nyid kyi sku'o //
NK033(gi)001:9388: de tha dad dang bral bas gsang ba'i sku'o //
NK033(gi)001:9389: mi phyed pa de nyid rang bzhin gyis mtha' las 'das so //
NK033(gi)001:9390: de la dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9391: de thog ma med pa nas tha ma med par
NK033(gi)001:9392: rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings su dbyar dgun gnyis med
NK033(gi)001:9394: nyid mtshan gnyis su med de na bun dengs pa tsam du rang gshegs te /
NK033(gi)001:9395: de brjod cing shes par mi nus /
NK033(gi)001:9396: bgrang zhing gzhal bar mi nus so //
NK033(gi)001:9398: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK033(gi)001:9400: sangs rgyas kyi thog mtha' btsal du mi rung ba yang de nyid do //
NK033(gi)001:9401: de la chos kyi dbyings zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9402: de ni dag pa'i lung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:9403: ma dag pa ni rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma dag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9404: rkyen gzhan du snang ba'i ma dag pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9405: gnyis nas byung ba'i log pa'i ma dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9406: rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma dag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9407: rang gi ngo bo rang gis ma shes pas 'dod chags te /
NK033(gi)001:9409: de ni rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9410: rkyen gzhan du snang ba'i ma dag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9411: rang gis 'tshal du ma shes pas yul dang yul can du bcad de rang bzhin 'khrul pas /
NK033(gi)001:9412: rkyen gzhan du snang ba'i ma dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9413: gnyis las byung ba'i log pa'i ma dag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9414: rang ngo rang gis ma shes pas yul du phar snang ba'i shes pa shar /
NK033(gi)001:9415: de gnyis su med pa ma shes pas ngo bo ma rig par gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:9416: gnyis las byung ba'i log pa'i ma dag pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9417: de gsum dbyer med pa ni ma rig pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9418: ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed do //
NK033(gi)001:9421: bsod nams ma yin pa'i 'du byed dang /
NK033(gi)001:9423: mi g.yo ba ma yin pa'i 'du byed do //
NK033(gi)001:9424: bsod nams kyi 'du byed cha phra mo'i rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:9425: rnam par shes pa'i rkyen gyis ming dang gzugs /
NK033(gi)001:9426: ming dang gzugs kyi rkyen gyis skye mched drug /
NK033(gi)001:9427: skye mche drug gi rkyen gyis reg pa /
NK033(gi)001:9428: reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba /
NK033(gi)001:9429: tshor ba'i rkyen gyis sred pa /
NK033(gi)001:9430: sred pa'i rkyen gyis len pa /
NK033(gi)001:9431: len pa'i rkyen gyis srid pa /
NK033(gi)001:9432: srid pa'i rkyen gyis skye ba /
NK033(gi)001:9433: skyes skye ba bzhi las rdzus te skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9434: 'gro ba drug las lhar rdzus te skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9435: gling bzhi las shar lus 'phags po rdzus te skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9436: 'du byed cha phra mo bzhi las bsod nams kyi 'du byed /
NK033(gi)001:9440: shi nas ma rig pa'i thog tu ldog ste /
NK033(gi)001:9441: 'du byed gang la yang 'jug cing rtsis gdab mi btub ste /
NK033(gi)001:9442: 'o na yang bsod nams ma yin pa'i 'du byed
NK033(gi)001:9443: kyi cha phra mo'i rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa
NK033(gi)001:9452: skye ba bzhi las drod gsher las skyes pa /
NK033(gi)001:9454: gling bzhi las byang sgra mi snyan drod gsher las skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9455: 'du byed bzhi las bsod nams ma yin pa'i 'du byed do //
NK033(gi)001:9459: shi nas ma rig pa'i thog tu ldog ste /
NK033(gi)001:9460: 'du byed gang la 'jug cing rtsis gdab mi btub ste /
NK033(gi)001:9461: 'o na yang mi g.yo ba'i 'du byed phra mo'i rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:9469: skye 'du byed bzhi las mi g.yo ba'i 'du byed /
NK033(gi)001:9470: skye ba bzhi las mngal skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9471: rigs drug las mi ru skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9472: gling bzhi las lho 'dzam bu gling pa mngal las skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9477: shi nas ma rig pa'i thog tu ldog ste /
NK033(gi)001:9478: 'du byed gang la yang 'jug cing rtsis gdab mi btub ste /
NK033(gi)001:9479: 'o na yang mi g.yo ba ma yin pa'i 'du byed phra mo'i rkyen gyis /
NK033(gi)001:9488: skye skye ba bzhi las sgo nga las skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9489: rigs drug las yi dwags las skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9490: gling bzhi las nub ba glang spyod pa sgong nga las skyes /
NK033(gi)001:9491: 'du byed bzhi las mi g.yo ba ma yin pa'i 'du byed /
NK033(gi)001:9492: dmyal ba ni zhe sdang rags pas dmyal bar skye ste /
NK033(gi)001:9498: yang ma rig pa'i thog tu ldog ste /
NK033(gi)001:9499: 'du byed gang la 'jug cing rtsis gdab mi btub bo //
NK033(gi)001:9500: de ni 'khor ba lugs su 'byung nas shar ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9502: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag gis gtan la dbab ste /
NK033(gi)001:9503: rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma dag pa de /
NK033(gi)001:9504: rang rig rang gsal ba'i ngo bo bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9505: rkyen gzhan du snang ba'i ma dag pa de /
NK033(gi)001:9507: nyid mi rtog bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag gis
NK033(gi)001:9508: ngo sprad pa de ni thar pa mya ngan las
NK033(gi)001:9510: las ma yin pa'i 'du byed yin pas las la mi ltos gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:9511: de yang dang po sangs rgyas rgyu med pa zer ro //
NK033(gi)001:9513: gnyis las byung ba'i log pa'i ma dag pa de /
NK033(gi)001:9514: don sku ni chos sku'i ngo bor bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9515: chos nyid bde ba'i ngo bo bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9516: de gsum dbyer mi phyed pa de ma rig pa
NK033(gi)001:9517: yin te de don sku ni ngo bo nyid kyi
NK033(gi)001:9518: skur ngo sprad / chos nyid dbyer mi phyed pa'i ngo bo bstan /
NK033(gi)001:9519: dbyer med pa'i dus na dbyer med bya ba tsam
NK033(gi)001:9520: gyi blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK033(gi)001:9521: gnas pas don sku ni gsang ba'i sku zhes ngo
NK033(gi)001:9522: bstan dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK033(gi)001:9523: chos nyid zhes ngo bo bstan no //
NK033(gi)001:9524: de tsa na ma rig pa gdar sha bcad /
NK033(gi)001:9526: pa des su brdas ma rig pa dwangs pa'i rang gi ngo bo rang du gsal ba /
NK033(gi)001:9528: des ma rig pa gdar sha bcad de /
NK033(gi)001:9529: rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma dag pa de 'dod chags kyi cha /
NK033(gi)001:9530: rkyen gzhan du snang ba'i ma dag pa de zhe sdang gi cha /
NK033(gi)001:9531: gnyis las byung ba'i log ngo bo ma rig pa /
NK033(gi)001:9534: pa de gti mug gi cha yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9535: dus gsum rang sar dag pas ma rig pa gdar sha chod /
NK033(gi)001:9537: rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis des su brdas pas skye ba med de /
NK033(gi)001:9538: 'khrul pa des su brdas zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9539: sems nyid rang sar brda' dang ngag gi ngo sprad pas /
NK033(gi)001:9540: rang rig dwangs pa'i so la bzhag ces bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9541: des sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi thog mtha' bcad pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9542: sems nyid gdar sha bcad pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9543: lung dang man ngag gis gtan la phab pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9545: mi mnyam pa'i mya ngan las 'da' ba ste /
NK033(gi)001:9546: chos de ni ma sprul pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9547: ngo bo nyid kyi stong pa nyid gang yin pa de ni mya ngan las 'da' ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9548: zhes tha du ma nas gsungs so //////
NK033(gi)001:9549: zhal gdams kun tu bzang po thugs ye shes kyi me long gi ye shes 'di la lnga ste /
NK033(gi)001:9555: de la gdams ngag gi sa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9556: ye shes kyi me long dngos su bstan te /
NK033(gi)001:9557: ye shes mig gcig dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:9559: smin phrag thad kar rtag lta yin /
NK033(gi)001:9560: sgo bkag snang sel chad lta yin //
NK033(gi)001:9561: steng lta mu stegs tshangs pa'i lam //
NK033(gi)001:9562: 'og lta mu stegs zhi ba'i lam /
NK033(gi)001:9563: dus kyi brda' la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:9565: snang ba'i dbang po ma bkag ma g.yos sna rtser bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:9566: ro yi dbang po gang la yang ni ma brten bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:9567: dpe ni rlung gis mar me ma bskyod pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:9568: de yang ye shes snang ba lam me ba //
NK033(gi)001:9569: 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron //
NK033(gi)001:9571: de yang smin pa rnams la sangs rgyas /
NK033(gi)001:9572: ma smin pa la sems can /
NK033(gi)001:9573: de yang 'dod chags kyi ngad yal te brda'i ngo bo nyid de /
NK033(gi)001:9575: srid pa'i 'dod chags spangs pa ste //
NK033(gi)001:9577: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i rtse mo can //
NK033(gi)001:9580: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin //
NK033(gi)001:9581: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog /
NK033(gi)001:9583: de kun tu bzang po kun gyi thugs phrad kyi gdams pa lags so //
NK033(gi)001:9584: lta ba'i sa ni gdams ngag gi stobs kyis chos thams cad ro gcig par /
NK033(gi)001:9585: skad cig gcig la chos kun ro gcig par khong du chud pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9587: chos kun ma nor bar rtogs par de /
NK033(gi)001:9589: rkyen gyis ji ltar snang yang ngo bo rang sar dag pa de la /
NK033(gi)001:9590: shes pa 'ba' zhig nges gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:9592: sgom pa'i sa ni gdams ngag gi stobs kyis mun pa'i bar chad med de /
NK033(gi)001:9594: nyin mtshan med par gsal bas /
NK033(gi)001:9595: 'od bzang ston kha'i zla ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)001:9596: nyi ma 'char ka'i dal ltar mdzes //
NK033(gi)001:9598: spyod pa'i sa ni gdams ngag gi stobs kyis mnyam par bzhag pa las sad pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:9599: ye shes sems dpa'i dal yid la 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:9601: sna tshogs gzugs can yid las skyes //
NK033(gi)001:9602: gzugs rnams thams cad snang ba'i dpal //
NK033(gi)001:9604: 'bras bu'i sa ni gdams ngag gi stobs kyis phyi rol gyi snang ba med de /
NK033(gi)001:9605: snang ba bde ba chen por myong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:9606: de yang srid gsum dga' ba chen po la /
NK033(gi)001:9607: de yang 'bras bu dag pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:9608: glo bur byung ba ma yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9609: rang bzhin gyis byung ba yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9611: sangs rgyas thog ma mtha' ma med //
NK033(gi)001:9612: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa //
NK033(gi)001:9614: ye shes de nyid g.yas g.yon te /
NK033(gi)001:9615: mgo tha dad la bltas pas gar bltas kyang sku'i thug phrad do //
NK033(gi)001:9617: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK033(gi)001:9618: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK033(gi)001:9620: chos sku de nyid las sems can gyi don du gzugs sku rnam gnyis 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:9622: phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed //
NK033(gi)001:9623: ji bzhin 'gro ba'i don byed pa //
NK033(gi)001:9625: nam mkha'i lam la rab gnas pa //
NK033(gi)001:9626: yid bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang //
NK033(gi)001:9629: chos la mi brten rkyen gyis grol ba'i dpe bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:9631: mdun rgyab med g.yas g.yon med par 'gro shes pa ri dwags dbang po yang rab kyi dpe /
NK033(gi)001:9633: ma'i mngal nas 'phur shes pa bya dri skye ba gcig gi rdzogs pa'i dpe /
NK033(gi)001:9635: gnyid sad sbyangs pa'i las 'phro can gyi dpe /
NK033(gi)001:9636: pa dang rmi lam dran pa skyes bu gnyid sad pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9637: dpe rkyen gyi thar pa'i dpe /
NK033(gi)001:9638: dang don du mthun pa dung g.yas su 'khyil ba lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9639: 'di rnams chos la mi brten no //
NK033(gi)001:9641: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK033(gi)001:9642: dus kyi brda' la brten nas kyang //
NK033(gi)001:9643: sdug bsngal chu bo che las grol //
NK033(gi)001:9649: myang shes rab 'byung gnas kyis rgyu sems can la //
NK033(gi)001:9650: 'bras bu sangs rgyas su bsgyur ba la /
NK033(gi)001:9651: mi dgos pa'i rde'u bcu tham pa 'adi'o /
NK033(gi)001:9652: 1sgrub pa thabs kyi rgyud mar me gcig nas gcig tu spel ba dang 'dra bas /
NK033(gi)001:9653: thos pa mang mi dgos pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:9654: 6skad cig ma'i mtshang go ba'i phu thag /
NK033(gi)001:9655: da ltar gyi snang ba la 'khrul pas gzhan la dri mi dgos pa dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:9656: 2lta stangs kyis spyod pa ngos 'dzin pa /
NK033(gi)001:9657: spyod lam rnam bzhir dran pa'i rtsis zin nas bsgom pa thun du bcad mi dgos pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:9658: 7gdams ngag ston pas yig nag dpe cha mi dgos pa dang bdun /
NK033(gi)001:9659: 3rig pa sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i gcer bu lhing
NK033(gi)001:9660: ba de rjes la skyal na nyon mongs pa la
NK033(gi)001:9661: gnyen po brten mi dgos pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9662: 8sems ye dag chen por ngos 'dzin pas chos rnams
NK033(gi)001:9663: rim gyis stong ste 'khor ba la 'jigs mi dgos
NK033(gi)001:9664: pa dang brgyad / 4go rtogs thams cad mos pa
NK033(gi)001:9665: dang gsol ba btab pa las 'byung bas ched du
NK033(gi)001:9666: bsgom mi dgos pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9667: 9dang po rgyu med pa la sems byung nas tshogs
NK033(gi)001:9668: gnyis las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu yin pas gol
NK033(gi)001:9669: sa mi dgos pa dang dgu /
NK033(gi)001:9670: 5don thams cad nges shes kyi steng nas 'char bas
NK033(gi)001:9671: sde snod la blta rtog bya mi dgos pa dang
NK033(gi)001:9672: lnga / 10dang po bde gshegs bka'i thabs ma nor
NK033(gi)001:9673: ba grub thob lung gi brgyud pa ma chad pa'i
NK033(gi)001:9674: gdams ngag yin pas phyi ma rnams the tshom mi
NK033(gi)001:9676: chos 'di gnyis ni slob dpon jo sras 'dzing gi
NK033(gi)001:9677: bla ma phata po la zin bris byas nas gnang
NK033(gi)001:9679: dpe bshus te bris pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:9680: 'dzin med ngang la mi gnas la //
NK033(gi)001:9681: g.yo 'dzin rlung gi man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:9683: rtsol ba dang bcas pa la lnga ste /
NK033(gi)001:9689: de ltar lnga ni mi 'dzin te shes dgos so //
NK033(gi)001:9690: 'dzin pa ni yid la gnas pa'i rlung 'dzin te /
NK033(gi)001:9691: 'o na yid dngos med gcig la rlung dngos med
NK033(gi)001:9692: gcig 'dzin du btub bam byas pa la bzung du
NK033(gi)001:9693: btub ste / 'o na khyod gdams ngag re che zer ba la /
NK033(gi)001:9694: nga gdams ngag che ba rang yin bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9695: 'o na de cis 'dzin na brdas 'dzin no //
NK033(gi)001:9697: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i yid dang /
NK033(gi)001:9698: rnam par byang ba'i yid do //
NK033(gi)001:9699: kun nas nyon mongs la gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9700: nyon mongs gti mug pa kun gyi gzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9701: bag chags sogs byed kyi snod /
NK033(gi)001:9702: zhe sdang sa 'dod chags bon cha'i kun gazhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:9703: rnam par byang ba ni brdas 'dzin te /
NK033(gi)001:9704: gnad bzhis don rgyud la skyes pa dang snying po ye shes kyi dus kyi brda' dang /
NK033(gi)001:9705: gnad kyi brda' bzhis gtan gtan la ma phebs pa de ni bag chags sogs byed do //
NK033(gi)001:9706: la phebs pa de ni rnam par byang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9707: sems rlung ni tshogs drug tu 'gyur te /
NK033(gi)001:9708: de ni rtsa ba'i 'gyur lugs so //
NK033(gi)001:9709: de la rtsa ni g.yas kyi rtsa ro ma las 'brel ba'i lce dang sna gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:9710: g.yon gyi rtsa rkyang ma las rna ba dang 'brel
NK033(gi)001:9711: lo dbus kyi rtsa la lba d+hu ti las mig
NK033(gi)001:9712: dang 'brel lo // tshogs drug gi reg bya tshor
NK033(gi)001:9713: ba ni rtsa gsum po de las rtsa phran nyi
NK033(gi)001:9714: khri chig stong drug brgyar gyes so //
NK033(gi)001:9715: dus la lnga ste tsakra lnga'o //
NK033(gi)001:9716: kyi brda' la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)001:9717: gnad kyi brda yis gnas bsgyur ba //
NK033(gi)001:9718: gnas bsgyur ba la gnyis 'dzin med //
NK033(gi)001:9720: spun po sprul sku bsgyur ba ni //
NK033(gi)001:9721: nyi khri chig stong drug bargya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9722: bdun brgya bdun cu rtsa lnga ni //
NK033(gi)001:9723: ye shes rlung du grags pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:9724: nyi khri brgyad brgya nyi shu rtsa lnga ni //
NK033(gi)001:9725: spun po rtsa bying po yin sems /
NK033(gi)001:9728: dus kyi 'khor lo nas gsungs so ////
NK033(gi)001:9729: rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag las sku rnam pa lnga /
NK033(gi)001:9736: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK033(gi)001:9737: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK033(gi)001:9739: brdas bstan pa'i don nyams su myong ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:9740: dgag bya ni nyon mongs pa nyi khri chig stong drug brgya 'gag /
NK033(gi)001:9741: non bya ni sa bcu gnyis non /
NK033(gi)001:9742: lus kyi bkod pa mi 'dra ba bye ba phrag brgya 'gyed pa /
NK033(gi)001:9743: de tsa na sprul pa'i sku bye ba phrag brgya 'gyed nus la /
NK033(gi)001:9744: zad par gyi skye mched bcu 'byongs pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:9749: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9752: 'di 'tshams rlung gi man ngag sam badz+ra k+airti sa
NK033(gi)001:9753: zhus pa zhig gsan yig na bzhugs kyang dpe ma
NK033(gi)001:9754: byung /// dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi lung bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:9756: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi lung 'bogs pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:9757: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:9758: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK033(gi)001:9759: 'phags pa thams cad kyis bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK033(gi)001:9761: dus 'di nas bzung ste snying po byang chub la
NK033(gi)001:9762: mchis kyi bar du lo byung ngo cog gi zla
NK033(gi)001:9763: ba ra ba bzhi'i nya gsum la /
NK033(gi)001:9764: ma dag pa dag par byed pa rgya mtsho khrus
NK033(gi)001:9765: kyi lung la mngon par phyogs par bgyid lags so
NK033(gi)001:9766: // ma smin pa smin par byed pa sgo gsum
NK033(gi)001:9767: las kyi spyod pa la mngon par spyod pa bgyid
NK033(gi)001:9768: // lags so // ma grol ba grol bar byed
NK033(gi)001:9769: pa sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la mngon par
NK033(gi)001:9771: grol ba mthar phyin par byed pa snying po ye shes kyi rlung rdo rje la /
NK033(gi)001:9772: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor gyi rjes su 'jug rjes su bgyid /
NK033(gi)001:9775: mngon pa phyogs par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:9777: mchog tu gyur pa lags so //
NK033(gi)001:9779: bzhi pa zhal gdams gdams pa'i skor la phyi nang gsang gsum las /
NK033(gi)001:9780: dang po phyi'i zhal gdams kyi skor la ///
NK033(gi)001:9781: zam chung bsdus pa thun cig ma bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:9782: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9785: nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyi //
NK033(gi)001:9786: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa //
NK033(gi)001:9789: ma smin pa smin par byed pa /
NK033(gi)001:9790: smin pa grol bar byed pa snying po ye shes kyi rlung /
NK033(gi)001:9791: dbang po'i sgo ji ltar ma bkag pa /
NK033(gi)001:9795: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang ma brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9803: lhug pa de la yang yang blta bas lta ba /
NK033(gi)001:9804: de la ma sba sgom gyis gsungs skad /
NK033(gi)001:9806: de grogs su gyur pa spyod pa /
NK033(gi)001:9807: de mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu /
NK033(gi)001:9808: gsal bas sems tsam dang mthun /
NK033(gi)001:9809: mi rtog pas dbu ma dang mthun /
NK033(gi)001:9810: bde bas gsang sngags dang mthun /
NK033(gi)001:9811: dbyer mi phyed pas phyag rgya chen po dang mthun no //
NK033(gi)001:9812: de la 'bras bu med dam zhe na yod de /
NK033(gi)001:9817: bde de la grub mtha' dang sgo mthun pa med dam zhe na yod de /
NK033(gi)001:9820: dbyer mi phyed pas ngo bo rang chas su rang gi rgyud la 'dug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9822: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed ces bya
NK033(gi)001:9823: ba tsam gyi blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba'am tshig
NK033(gi)001:9824: gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas
NK033(gi)001:9825: pas rdzogs pa chen po dngos po gshis kyi gnas
NK033(gi)001:9826: lugs te gsang ba'i sku rang chas so //
NK033(gi)001:9827: zhal gyi gdams pa zam chung thun gcig ma +thii //////
NK033(gi)001:9828: zam chung yig sna thun mong dang khyad par ba gnyis bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:9829: thun mong dang khyad par gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:9830: thun mong gi lus ngag yid gsum gus pa'i sgo
NK033(gi)001:9831: nas rat+na gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba gdams ngag
NK033(gi)001:9832: dang bcas pa'o // khyad par ni bla ma'i brda'
NK033(gi)001:9833: dang ngag gis bstan pas bde gsal du rang gi
NK033(gi)001:9835: brda' dang ngag de gnyis chos /
NK033(gi)001:9836: de ltar rgyud la shar ba de dge 'dun /
NK033(gi)001:9837: de ltar na rat+na gsum rang gi rgyud la tshang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:9838: thun mong dang khyad par gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:9839: thun mong ni mi 'bral khas len gyis sems bskyed
NK033(gi)001:9840: sems can gyi don du brda' thob pa 'dod pa'i
NK033(gi)001:9841: bsam pas cho ga dang bcas te sems bskyed pa'o
NK033(gi)001:9842: // khyad par ba bla mas brda' dang ngag gis
NK033(gi)001:9843: bstan pas bde gsal mi rtog pa rang gi rgyud
NK033(gi)001:9844: la shar ba de don dam sems bskyed dam khyad
NK033(gi)001:9846: des rang don du chos sku thob nas gzhan don
NK033(gi)001:9847: du gzugs sku gnyis ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba'o
NK033(gi)001:9848: // phyi'i dbang bskur bas rang rig rang gsal du 'char /
NK033(gi)001:9849: gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas mi rtog par 'char /
NK033(gi)001:9850: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur bas bde bar 'char /
NK033(gi)001:9851: tshig dbang rin po ches dbyer mi phyed pa rgyud
NK033(gi)001:9852: la 'char te shar na dbang gi cho ga ma
NK033(gi)001:9854: de rgyud la ma skyes na dbang gi cho ga rdzogs kyang don ma rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)001:9855: 'di mtshams tshig chad song ngam snyam /
NK033(gi)001:9856: de gtan la cang phebs sam /
NK033(gi)001:9857: yid dngos med dang rlung dngos med gcig gnas pa gcig bzung du cang btub bam zhe na /
NK033(gi)001:9858: de btub ste bla ma dam pa'i brda' dang ngag gis mtshon nas bstan pas rtogs so //
NK033(gi)001:9859: brda' nyid gzhung nyid las gsal /
NK033(gi)001:9860: gsal brgyud la ji lta bu zhig 'char na /
NK033(gi)001:9862: mi rtog pa chos nyid kyi don blo la rtog pa ci yang mi gnas pa zhig 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:9863: zag pa med pa'i bde ba lus yod du mi bor ba zhig 'bar ro //
NK033(gi)001:9864: de rnams ngo bo tha dad kyang don gcig tu dbyer med pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9865: tshig la tha dad kyang don dbyer mi byed pa zhig rgyud la 'char ro //
NK033(gi)001:9866: nyams dang rtogs pa ming 'dogs kyi bye brag tha
NK033(gi)001:9867: mal gyi shes pa gsal ba la lta sgom du
NK033(gi)001:9868: ming btags pa lta ba snyems chod de 'dzeng d+harma
NK033(gi)001:9869: bo d+hi'o // mi rtog pa la gnyug mar 'dogs te sgom pa ma gtad ma yengs /
NK033(gi)001:9870: bde ba la so mar btags te spyod pa snang
NK033(gi)001:9871: yang mi 'dzin pa dbyer mi phyed pa la lhug
NK033(gi)001:9872: pa zhes ming du btags so //
NK033(gi)001:9873: rtag chad gnyis med kyi shes rab la //
NK033(gi)001:9874: phyogs lhung med na lta ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:9875: zhes 'dzeng d+harma bo d+his gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:9876: stong gsal bde chen gyi nyams myong la //
NK033(gi)001:9877: bying rgod med na sgom pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:9878: tha mal rang spyod lhug pa la //
NK033(gi)001:9879: bcas bcos med na spyod pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:9880: 'khor 'das gnyis med kyi dgongs pa la //
NK033(gi)001:9881: re dogs med na 'bras bu yin //
NK033(gi)001:9882: de la 'bras bu ka dag dbyings grol zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:9883: dang po chos zhu ba la ma nor ba gal che /
NK033(gi)001:9884: de nas mos gus kyis bla ma'i thugs zin pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:9885: de nas ma shes bar du the tshom 'dri ba gal che /
NK033(gi)001:9886: de nas gdams pa la yid ches pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:9887: de nas rjes su dam tshig bsrung ba gal che /
NK033(gi)001:9888: de nas de rnams bsdus pas snying rus bskyed nas bsgom pa gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:9889: de nas chos nor phyir mi 'tshong ba gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:9890: zhes 'dzeng d+harma bo d+his gal chen gyi gdams pa gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:9892: ngo bo bsgom pa'i gang zag gis chags sdang gi /
NK033(gi)001:9893: gtam dang bzlas brjod spang ngo //////
NK033(gi)001:9894: zam chung gi bsdus don bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:9896: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i khyad par gyi gdams pa thun gcig ma 'di la don gsum ste /
NK033(gi)001:9901: mchod ma nor par brjod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9906: don gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9907: don nyams su shar ba'i dus dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:9909: gzhi skyabs lam sems smin dbang grol du gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9910: brda' dbang po'i sgo so so bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9911: bzhis ye shes kyi rlung gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9912: rgyud la gsal ba zhes pa la sogs bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9914: gtan la pheb pa la gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9915: nyams tha mal zhes pa bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:9916: rtogs gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9917: lta de ltar yang yang lta /
NK033(gi)001:9918: bsgom gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:9919: grub gsal bas sems tsam sogs /
NK033(gi)001:9920: mtha' gtan la phebs par bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9921: don nyams su shar ba la gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9922: thun gsal ba sprul sku zhes gsum /
NK033(gi)001:9923: mong gi 'bras bu sku gsum rang chas su shar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:9924: khyad par dbyer mi byed pas /
NK033(gi)001:9925: gyi 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyi sku rang chas su shar ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:9926: yang blo mtha' zab cing phra ba /
NK033(gi)001:9927: dag gi 'bras bu a ti gsang ba'i sku rang chas su shar bar bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9929: don gyis rdzogs zhal gyi gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:9931: zam chung thun gcig ma'i bsdus don rdzogs zam chung
NK033(gi)001:9932: 'di la don rkang grangs sum cu rtsa gnyis yod
NK033(gi)001:9933: pas / chos sde sum cu rtsa gnyis bya bar yang byas 'dug go //
NK033(gi)001:9934: dkyus ma 'di dgong mo yi ge mi mthong la khad pa'i dus su bris par gada'o //
NK033(gi)001:9936: snyan brgyud rin po che'i nyams kyi phreng bka' brgyud nyams kyi phreng ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9938: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:9939: rdzogs pa chen po bka' babs phyi ma'i bka' babs snga ma ni sems sde dang /
NK033(gi)001:9943: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la /
NK033(gi)001:9944: rdo rje sems dpas de kho na nyid kyi don /
NK033(gi)001:9946: ye shes spyi blugs su shar ba nyi ma shar ba lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9947: chos nyid thug phrad du shar ba rgyal po lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9948: rnam rtog ye shes su ldang ba nags kyi me lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9949: mtshan mar rang sar grol ba nam mkha' lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9950: ting nge 'dzin 'byung 'jug dang bral ba rin po che gser gling lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:9951: de lta bu dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor la gol 'grib med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9952: spang len med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9953: mtshan sgom med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9954: rtsol ba bya mi dgos par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9955: ces dga' rab rdo rje la gdams pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9957: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:9958: thag chod rdo rje'i tshig ni /
NK033(gi)001:9959: snang srid nam mkha'i ngang du gcig pas /
NK033(gi)001:9960: dngos po la rang bzhin med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9961: snying po sems su gyur pas /
NK033(gi)001:9962: sangs rgyas gzhan na med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9963: bde ba sgyu mar snang bas /
NK033(gi)001:9964: sdug bsngal rang bzhin med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9965: stong pa 'od gsal du yod pas /
NK033(gi)001:9966: ye shes rang rgyud du shar bar thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9967: ye shes la skye 'gag med pas /
NK033(gi)001:9968: 'chi 'pho bas 'jigs pa med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9970: sems can gyi las zad pas thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:9973: sh+r+ai sing ha la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:9974: de kho na nyid la la bzla bar gsungs pa /
NK033(gi)001:9975: lta ba'i la zlo na mun pa'i smag la 'dug /
NK033(gi)001:9976: sgom pa'i la zlo na rang srog chod la ltos /
NK033(gi)001:9977: spyod pa'i la zlo na mnyam nyid yengs la bor /
NK033(gi)001:9978: skye shi'i la zlo na sems can gyi srog chod /
NK033(gi)001:9979: 'bras bu'i la zlo na re dogs kyi mtha' chod /
NK033(gi)001:9980: ye shes la zlo na rgyu rkyen phyags mas thob /
NK033(gi)001:9983: bee ro tsa na la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:9984: 'gyu ba rlung gi gdams ngag gsungs pa /
NK033(gi)001:9991: dus mnyam pa'i dus ji ltar mnyam na 'gyu ba'i
NK033(gi)001:9992: rig pa glo bur btol cer shar ba'i dus su
NK033(gi)001:9993: / 'gyus pa ni rig pa rang shar khyugs gyis yul shar ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:9994: bltas pa ni yul la bltas pas /
NK033(gi)001:9995: yul sngon med zang thal du song ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:9996: dwangs pa ni rig pa zang thal dngos med du shar ba'i dus su'o //
NK033(gi)001:9997: sangs pa ni snang ba yul med par rig pa dngos med dbyer med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:9998: grol ba ni zang thal yul med dbyer med ngo bo nyid du rang grol bas /
NK033(gi)001:9999: blo'i yul du ma grub pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:10000: blo 'das chen por sangs kyis grol ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10002: mi pham mgon po la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10003: rlung gsum rang sar dwangs pa'i gdams ngag ni /
NK033(gi)001:10004: phyi 'tshub byed kyi rlung snang rgyu 'dzin pa ba rang sar dwangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10005: nang 'tshub byed kyi rlung gsal 'gyu 'dzin mkhan rang sar dwangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10006: gsang ba 'tshub byed kyi rlung stong rgyu 'dzin mkhan rang sar dwangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10007: yang slob dpon bee ro tsa nas spang mi pham
NK033(gi)001:10008: mgon po la don dam chos nyid kyi ngang tshul
NK033(gi)001:10009: las mi 'da' bar yid ches par bya ba'i ched
NK033(gi)001:10010: du gdams ngag mdor bsdus te bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:10011: ye shes 'khyil ba rdo rje'i bum //
NK033(gi)001:10012: ye shes chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:10013: ye shes lnga yi bde ba rgyas //
NK033(gi)001:10014: rang lus ye shes rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:10015: rig pa'i ye shes skur gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:10016: dag snang rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK033(gi)001:10017: rang rig ye shes rgyun chad med //
NK033(gi)001:10018: rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:10019: ye shes nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)001:10020: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10021: 'di la yang dag ngos bzung med //
NK033(gi)001:10022: ting 'dzin sems kyi rig rtsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10023: lus dang ngag gi bya btsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10024: 'di la dmigs dang bya btsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10026: gnas dang ldan yang rten pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10027: yul du snang yang 'gag pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10028: longs spyod ldan yang chags pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10029: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10038: stong nyid bde ba'i man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:10039: dam pa'i bde ba mngon du bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10040: rig pa'i reg bya'i bde ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10041: bde ba rig pa chen po ste //
NK033(gi)001:10042: bde ba chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:10043: gcig tu 'dus pa'i bde chen yin //
NK033(gi)001:10044: bde ba chen po mi 'bral bzung //
NK033(gi)001:10045: bde ba rgyas pa'i dbang thob ste //
NK033(gi)001:10046: zhing khams gnyis kar bde longs spyod //
NK033(gi)001:10047: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10048: rtsol dang bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK033(gi)001:10049: rgyu 'bras med pa'i mthar thug yin //
NK033(gi)001:10050: sngags tshig bral ba'i nus mthu yin //
NK033(gi)001:10051: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon yin //
NK033(gi)001:10052: las bzhi bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK033(gi)001:10053: 'ching bral ston pas lta ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10054: 'da' ba med pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK033(gi)001:10055: rtog 'dzin spangs pa sangs rgyas yin //
NK033(gi)001:10056: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10065: zhes tshul shing la bris nas gnang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10067: yang slob dpon bee ro tsa nas spang mi pham
NK033(gi)001:10068: mgon po la don dam chos nyid kyi sogs nas
NK033(gi)001:10069: / 'di'i bar ma dpe khams spar la mi 'dug
NK033(gi)001:10070: kyang dpe gzhan dang go bsdur gyis gsal bsnan gyis
NK033(gi)001:10073: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10077: rig pa gcig chod de man ngag bzhi dang ldan par bya /
NK033(gi)001:10078: gcig bzhag bya lta bu'i rnam par rtog pa ngos bzung /
NK033(gi)001:10080: thug phrad rgyal po lta bu la /
NK033(gi)001:10081: dran rtog thams cad ye shes su ngos bzung /
NK033(gi)001:10082: ngos bzung thams cad dang bral bar 'ong gis /
NK033(gi)001:10083: rang brdol bkol ma'i chu lta bur chos thams cad mnyam nyid du shes par gyis /
NK033(gi)001:10084: rang grol du sangs kyis 'gro yis /
NK033(gi)001:10085: tshig chod nyi ma lta bus chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du shes par gyis /
NK033(gi)001:10086: thams cad ngo bo nyid du la bazla'o //
NK033(gi)001:10089: za ngam rin chen dbyig la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10093: snang ba rang snang du shes pas phyi'i 'jug sgo gtan la phebs te lus su ma song /
NK033(gi)001:10094: 'char ba rang gi mkhyen tshad du shes pas nang
NK033(gi)001:10095: gi 'jug sgo gtan la phebs te sems su ma
NK033(gi)001:10096: song / yin lugs yin par shes pas gsang ba'i 'jug sgo gtan la phebs te /
NK033(gi)001:10097: rlung rang gi rtsal du nor pas lus sems gnyis
NK033(gi)001:10098: kyi 'brel thag chad de 'gro sa sangs rgyas las
NK033(gi)001:10100: de sgrib pa gsum las grol te /
NK033(gi)001:10101: snang ba rang snang du shes pas /
NK033(gi)001:10102: rkyen gzhan las byung ba'i ma rig pa sangs /
NK033(gi)001:10103: shar ba mkhyen tshad du shes pas /
NK033(gi)001:10104: rlung las byung ba'i ma rig pa /
NK033(gi)001:10106: rlung rtsal du byung bas gnyis ka las byung ba'i
NK033(gi)001:10107: ma rig pa sangs pas 'gro sa sangs rgyas las
NK033(gi)001:10108: gzhan med do // zhes gdams so //
NK033(gi)001:10110: khu 'gyur gsal ba mchog la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10111: 'gags pa med pa stag mgo dgu pa lta bu /
NK033(gi)001:10112: de'i phyi rol tu ltos dang /
NK033(gi)001:10114: de gnyis kyi bar du ltos dang /
NK033(gi)001:10116: de la brjod du med do //
NK033(gi)001:10123: dpe rang byung mchod rten lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:10126: nyang byang chub grags pa la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10127: de kho na nyid kyi man ngag gsungs pa /
NK033(gi)001:10128: de kho na nyid la mthong ba med pas /
NK033(gi)001:10129: lta ba yin pa la yin par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:10130: de la sgom du ci zhig yod de /
NK033(gi)001:10131: sgom du med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:10132: de la spyod pa spyod du med kyis /
NK033(gi)001:10133: spang len byar med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:10135: re dogs med par thag chod /
NK033(gi)001:10137: nyang byang chub grags pa des /
NK033(gi)001:10138: nyang shes rab 'byung gnas la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10139: sangs rgyas par 'dod na rtsol ba mi bya /
NK033(gi)001:10140: sems la lta bar 'dod na rang gi dbugs la ltos /
NK033(gi)001:10141: bde ba thob par 'dod na rang gi sdug bsngal la ltos /
NK033(gi)001:10142: dran pa 'gags na ye shes su mi 'char bas /
NK033(gi)001:10143: dran pa ye shes su blta'o //
NK033(gi)001:10144: phugs zhe 'dod dang bral bar gyis /
NK033(gi)001:10147: rba sgom ye shes byang chub la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10158: shes bcu ldan na grol bar 'gyur //
NK033(gi)001:10161: 'dzeng d+harma b+ho d+hi la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10162: dge sdig gnyis ka tha snyad tsam //
NK033(gi)001:10163: bdud dang 'khor ba gdod nas med //
NK033(gi)001:10164: skye med chos la rtsol med de //
NK033(gi)001:10165: rnam grol rnam par bcings pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:10166: snying po de yang gdod nas med //
NK033(gi)001:10167: rang gis de ltar ma rig ste //
NK033(gi)001:10168: don med sgra phyir 'brangs pa rnams //
NK033(gi)001:10169: dge ba'i chos ni rnam spangs te //
NK033(gi)001:10173: slob dpon 'dzeng jo sras la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10174: phyi stong nang stong stong pa rgya bo che //
NK033(gi)001:10175: phyi gsal nang gsal gsal ba 'od po che //
NK033(gi)001:10176: phyi bde nang bde bde ba lhun grub bo //
NK033(gi)001:10179: 'o la ban de la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10180: phyi yi snang ba sna tshogs 'di //
NK033(gi)001:10181: 'khrul pa yin par blo thag chod //
NK033(gi)001:10183: sems rlung yin par blo thag chod //
