NK033(gi)001:10185: 'od gsal yin par blo thag chod //
NK033(gi)001:10186: nam mkha' lta bu'i dgongs pa la //
NK033(gi)001:10187: phyogs ris med par blo thag chod //
NK033(gi)001:10189: bka' brgyud rin po che nyams kyi phreng ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10192: 'o la dge slong la gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10193: bla ma la sangs rgyas su ltos dang //
NK033(gi)001:10194: byin rlabs thams cad nges par 'byung gis //
NK033(gi)001:10195: dka' thub de sgrub pa la gyis dang //
NK033(gi)001:10196: dngos grub thams cad nges par 'byung gis //
NK033(gi)001:10197: rnam rtog de chos sku'i ngang du bor dang //
NK033(gi)001:10198: blos byas kyi mtshan ma thams cad nges par 'jig gis //
NK033(gi)001:10199: chos kyi rtsa ba de dam tshig la gyis dang //
NK033(gi)001:10200: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong nges par 'du yis //
NK033(gi)001:10201: zog po'i tshul 'chos de shig la thong dang //
NK033(gi)001:10202: ci byas thams cad chos su 'gro yis //
NK033(gi)001:10204: 'dzeng gi rgyab sha tshad ma bzhi'i gdams pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10206: theg rtsod bzlog lung gi tshad mas /
NK033(gi)001:10207: pa chen po'i sgrub thabs dang //
NK033(gi)001:10208: gsang sngags kun gyi lta ba dang //
NK033(gi)001:10209: rna bshad kun gyi dgongs pa mchog /
NK033(gi)001:10210: bdag gis bstan par mi nus te //
NK033(gi)001:10211: rdzogs chen brgyud pa tha ma yi //
NK033(gi)001:10212: rgyab sha tshad ma bzhi po ni //
NK033(gi)001:10213: bla ma sangs rgyas gsungs pas na //
NK033(gi)001:10214: de don bdag gis bstan par bya //
NK033(gi)001:10215: bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na //
NK033(gi)001:10216: ma dag dag byed rgya mtsho khrus lung bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10217: ma smin smin byed sgo gsum las spyod bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10218: smin pa grol byed bla ma'i byin rlabs bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10219: grol mthar phyin byed snying po ye shes rlung //
NK033(gi)001:10220: dus brda' la brten gnad brdas nyams su len //
NK033(gi)001:10221: nyams len de dus de tshe na //
NK033(gi)001:10222: don gcig nyams shar skad cig ste //
NK033(gi)001:10223: d+hu tir tshud pa'i rlung zhes bya //
NK033(gi)001:10224: shes pa'ang d+hu tir tshud ces bya //
NK033(gi)001:10225: pha rol phyin pa'i theg pa las //
NK033(gi)001:10226: rnam thar sgo mtshan med pa dang //
NK033(gi)001:10227: smon med stong pa nyid ces bya //
NK033(gi)001:10228: dus bzhi'i rnal 'byor nyams su blang //
NK033(gi)001:10229: de ltar nyams su len pa la //
NK033(gi)001:10230: rtog ge can dag smra gyur na //
NK033(gi)001:10231: rig pas 'thad pa rang rig tshad mas bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:10232: gtan tshig rgyas pa lung gi tshad mas bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:10233: don dang mi 'gal man ngag tshad mas bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:10234: nyams myong dran bsam blo yi tshad mas bzlog /
NK033(gi)001:10235: de la rang rig tshad ma ni //
NK033(gi)001:10236: rdo rje gzegs mas rgyu la rnam dpyad nas //
NK033(gi)001:10237: rgyu ni ma nges gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10238: gcig dang du bral ngo bo rnam dpyad nas //
NK033(gi)001:10239: ngo bo ma grub ma nges gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10240: yod med skye 'gags 'bras bu rnam dpyad nas //
NK033(gi)001:10241: 'bras bu ma grub ma nges gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10242: mu bzhi skye 'gog rgyu 'bras gnyis ka dpyad //
NK033(gi)001:10243: rgyu 'bras ma nges ma grub gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10244: rten 'brel chen pos snang srid 'khor 'das kyi //
NK033(gi)001:10245: snang ba thams cad ma nges gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10246: ma nges nges grub kyis ni stong pa yang //
NK033(gi)001:10247: ma nges par ni gtan la 'bebs pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:10248: sgra mthun don dpags rigs pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:10249: gnyis ka yang ni ma nges gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10250: ma nges nges grub stong pa nges par gtan la 'bebs //
NK033(gi)001:10251: man ngag gis ni tshad ma ni //
NK033(gi)001:10252: brjod bya rjod byed sgra yi tshad ma yin //
NK033(gi)001:10253: dran bsam blo yi tshad ma yin //
NK033(gi)001:10254: dbyings dag 'das pa man ngag tshad ma yin //
NK033(gi)001:10255: slob dpon 'dzeng chen de skad gsungs //
NK033(gi)001:10257: gnyis pa nang gi zhal gdams la ///
NK033(gi)001:10258: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i gdams pa rna brgyud tshig don gsum pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:10259: slob dpon sh+ri sing ha'i gdams pa /
NK033(gi)001:10260: rna brgyud tshig don gsum pa /
NK033(gi)001:10261: ye shes rang snang gi nam mkha' la //
NK033(gi)001:10262: rang snang blo yi nam mkha' bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:10263: de tshe sangs rgyas nam mkha' nyid //
NK033(gi)001:10264: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha nas rim par brgyud pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10265: mtshan ma dbyibs kyi rnal 'byor ni sku /
NK033(gi)001:10266: 'phro ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor ni gsung /
NK033(gi)001:10267: zab pa chos nyid kyi rnal 'byor ni thugs /
NK033(gi)001:10268: sku gsung thugs gsum du 'dus par go ////
NK033(gi)001:10269: rna brgyud tshig don gsum pa /
NK033(gi)001:10270: rang snang ye shes kyi nam mkha' la /
NK033(gi)001:10271: rang rig blo yi nam mkha' bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:10272: de tshe sangs rgyas nam mkha' nyid //
NK033(gi)001:10274: rna brgyud tshig don gsum pa 'di //
NK033(gi)001:10275: sh+r+ai sing has gdams pa yin //
NK033(gi)001:10276: sems nyid dang chos nyid 'dres pa na //
NK033(gi)001:10277: sangs rgyas logs nas btsal du med //
NK033(gi)001:10279: ngam shod mtha' bzhi'i khyad chos yin ///
NK033(gi)001:10280: bla rin po che'i gdung sgrub /
NK033(gi)001:10281: ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10282: gsang sngags kyi gdams par gyur pa'i /
NK033(gi)001:10283: rin po che'i gdung sgrub bshad par bya /
NK033(gi)001:10284: gnas rang ni gar 'thad dga' bar pa'i phyogs su /
NK033(gi)001:10287: rang nyid yi dam lha ru bsgom //
NK033(gi)001:10289: skyil krung bca' zhing sgal tshigs rnams drang por du /
NK033(gi)001:10291: sgal tshig rnams kyang rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:10292: dung khang nang stong par mdog dkar /
NK033(gi)001:10294: de 'i nang ring bsrel gyi mdog dkar 'od dang 'od zer dang bcas pa /
NK033(gi)001:10296: che chung yungs kar 'bring po'i tshad /
NK033(gi)001:10298: tshigs pas nang yo ring bsrel gyis /
NK033(gi)001:10300: de la snying po brgya skor bzlas //
NK033(gi)001:10302: tshigs sgal tshig pa 'og dag pa'i ring bsrel gyi /
NK033(gi)001:10304: kha bcad gong rnams de nas sgal tshigs gong ma /
NK033(gi)001:10306: ya gi ltag gor man chad nas //
NK033(gi)001:10307: gzhug gu thugs ni yan chod du //
NK033(gi)001:10308: ring bsrel gong ma bzhin du /
NK033(gi)001:10310: lus sgal tshigs ni drang por bsrang bar bya //
NK033(gi)001:10311: ngag ni rten ye d+harma 'brel snying po bzlas //
NK033(gi)001:10312: yid sgal tshigs ring bsrel dang bcas /
NK033(gi)001:10313: ni lha yi sku la gtad /
NK033(gi)001:10314: de bzhin rgyun chad med par bzlas //
NK033(gi)001:10316: the tshom yid gnyis mi bya bar //
NK033(gi)001:10317: gus pa'i sems kyis bsgrub par bya //
NK033(gi)001:10318: de ltar bsgom pa'i rnal mi gang na gang zhig 'byor de //
NK033(gi)001:10319: lan gcig shi nas ro bsreg na sgal tshigs khrod nas gdung /
NK033(gi)001:10321: sha ri ram ni mar po 'byung //
NK033(gi)001:10323: dpal ldan zhe sdang rdo rje zhes bya bas tshigs bcad du bsgrigs pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10324: badz+ra shwa ra nas gnang ba'i sngags so //
NK033(gi)001:10325: gsang sngags rin po che'i gdung sgrub bya ba +thii /
NK033(gi)001:10326: ye d+harma he tu pra b+ha w+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK033(gi)001:10327: te shany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa //////
NK033(gi)001:10328: bsre ba rnam bzhi'i zhal gdams bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:10330: brdas su rgyud la sbyor ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10331: ngo sprad nas nyams su myong ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10334: 'dres ma 'dres kyi drod tshad shes pa /
NK033(gi)001:10335: bsre ba rnam pa bzhi'i gdams ngag la /
NK033(gi)001:10336: gsal ba dang snang ba bsre /
NK033(gi)001:10337: mi rtog pa dang rtog pa bsre /
NK033(gi)001:10338: bde ba dang sdug bsngal bsre /
NK033(gi)001:10339: dbyer mi phyed pa dang sna tshogs basre'o //
NK033(gi)001:10340: gsal ba dang snang ba bsre ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10341: dbang po'i sgo ma bkag par bzhag pas /
NK033(gi)001:10342: snang ba ma 'gags par gsal ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10343: ched du 'dzin pa med par don gnyis su med par gcig tu rgyud la lhang gis 'char /
NK033(gi)001:10344: de la yin min gyi blos ma reg par gnas na /
NK033(gi)001:10345: gsal ba dang snang ba 'dres pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10346: da rung gnyis 'dzin gyi bye brag byung na ma 'dres pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10347: mi rtog pa dang rtog pa bsre ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10348: dbang po'i sgo ma g.yos par bzhag pas yid kyi
NK033(gi)001:10349: 'gyu ba chad nas rtog pa ma bsubs par dran
NK033(gi)001:10350: pa 'gags nas don dmigs pa med par rgyud la
NK033(gi)001:10351: lhang gis 'char / de la yin min gyi ngos mi bzung ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10352: mi rtog pa dang rtog pa 'dres pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10353: da rung yin min gyi sngo bgrang byung na ma 'dres pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10354: bde ba dang sdug bsngal bsre ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10355: rtsol ba chen po med par 'og rlung yid tsam
NK033(gi)001:10356: 'then nas shes pa bde ba la lus sems yod
NK033(gi)001:10357: du mi tshor ba yang ba gcig lus kyi ngo
NK033(gi)001:10358: bo mi dmigs par rgyud la lhang gis 'char /
NK033(gi)001:10359: de la tshor mi tshor gyi snyems byed med par gnas na /
NK033(gi)001:10360: bde ba dang sdug bsngal 'dres pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10361: da rung myong tshor gyi ro la zhen na ma 'dres pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10362: sna tshogs dang dbyer med bsre ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10363: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang ma reg par bzhag pas /
NK033(gi)001:10364: chos thams cad kyi mtshon pa ma 'dres par tha dad du gsal ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10365: de thams cad kyi don gsal bar nyams su myong
NK033(gi)001:10366: ba la 'di 'dra ba'i mtshon pa med par rgyud
NK033(gi)001:10368: de la bsgrub bya'i khyer so med pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:10369: sna tshogs dang dbyer med du 'dres pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10370: grub mtha'i bzhed gzhung gcig byung na da rung ma 'dres pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10371: dang po brda' bzhi'i ngo sprod med na /
NK033(gi)001:10372: tshig la mkhas kyang tha mal gyi blo ldog tu mi btub /
NK033(gi)001:10373: bar du dbyer med du bsre ma shes na chos
NK033(gi)001:10374: thams cad kyi yin lugs shes kyang chos nyid dang
NK033(gi)001:10376: tha mar chos nyid kyi nyam myong rjes la ngos zin nas /
NK033(gi)001:10377: snang ba la bden pa med par ma song na /
NK033(gi)001:10378: lta ba rgyud la ma skyes pa'i snying khams la ltos pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10379: sgom pa rang bzhin med par ma shes pa'i zhi
NK033(gi)001:10380: gnas tshan po che yis sangs tshe 'di nyid la
NK033(gi)001:10381: mi rgya / chos 'di slob dpon 'dzeng gi slob
NK033(gi)001:10382: ma dgas chung ma bya bas dpe'i gdar sha bcad
NK033(gi)001:10383: pa'i dpe'i gsham na bris nas 'dug /
NK033(gi)001:10384: ston pa rdor lha'i dpe la dam bus zhus /
NK033(gi)001:10385: bsre ba rnam bzhi bya ba 'di ngas bris /
NK033(gi)001:10386: sgom pa la phan pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10387: slob dpon 'dzeng chung ba la dris pas /
NK033(gi)001:10388: lha rje sgam po la bsre ba skor gsum bya ba yod zer /
NK033(gi)001:10389: nga'i 'di bsre ba rnam pa bzhi bya ba yin gsungs so //
NK033(gi)001:10390: legs nyes rgyud la sbyor la ltos /
NK033(gi)001:10391: tha snyad tshig gis shes pa min no //
NK033(gi)001:10393: sems nyid gdar sha gcod pa 'chi kha bar do'i gdams pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10394: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10395: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyi //
NK033(gi)001:10396: ngo bo nyid kyi dbyings su dag pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:10397: lung dang man ngag gis gtan la dbab ste /
NK033(gi)001:10398: de la lung gis gsang sngags kyi mdor bsdus nas /
NK033(gi)001:10399: mched pa dang ni nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:10400: rang bzhin bar do gnyis la 'char //
NK033(gi)001:10402: man ngag gis rna brgyud zam pa las /
NK033(gi)001:10403: smig rgyu du ba srin bu'i me //
NK033(gi)001:10405: gti mug stong pa 'od gsal ni //
NK033(gi)001:10406: srid pa la ni nyams su myong //
NK033(gi)001:10407: chu tshod bdun bdun rim gyis 'pho //
NK033(gi)001:10410: rang bzhin 'chi kha'i bar do la /
NK033(gi)001:10411: mched pa rnam pa gsum 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10412: sa chu la 'dus pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10414: sgyu lta bu'i mer mer ba'i /
NK033(gi)001:10416: lus kyi rkang lag la sogs pa sdud mi shes /
NK033(gi)001:10418: chu me la 'dus pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10420: ba lta bu'i thu lu thu lu ba 'byung /
NK033(gi)001:10424: me rlung la 'dus pa'i dus su mig res nar
NK033(gi)001:10425: nar srin bu me khyer lta bu'i mched par 'char
NK033(gi)001:10426: / 'then dbugs nar nar ba'i dus yin /
NK033(gi)001:10427: rlung rnam par shes pa la 'dus pa'i dus /
NK033(gi)001:10430: rig pa'i rlung rtsa ro ma'i nang du sib kyis 'gro ste /
NK033(gi)001:10431: de'i dus na gti mug nyams su myong ba yong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10432: rnam par shes pa nye bar len pa'i shes pa la 'dus pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10433: rig pa'i rlung rtsa rkyang ma'i nang du 'gro ste /
NK033(gi)001:10434: stong pa'i nyams su myong ba 'ong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10435: nye bar shes pa 'od gsal la thim pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10436: rig pa'i rlung de rtsa kun dar ma'i nang du 'gro ste /
NK033(gi)001:10437: don chos nyid nyams su myong ba gcig 'char te /
NK033(gi)001:10438: chos nyid de da lta bla ma'i byin rlabs dang gdams ngag gis ngo sprad nas /
NK033(gi)001:10439: ma'i pang du bu 'jug pa bzhin du rtsa kun dar ma'i nang du /
NK033(gi)001:10441: spyi bo'i gtsug a wa d+hu ti'i nang na yar la don te /
NK033(gi)001:10443: da lta bla ma'i byin rlabs dang brda' dang ngag gis ngo ma sprad na /
NK033(gi)001:10444: don chos nyid mi shes te /
NK033(gi)001:10445: rang bzhin gyi gnyis 'dzin gyi sgrog ma chod pas /
NK033(gi)001:10448: 'od dkar dbugs chad nas dar cig lon nas mig nang la me chu lhug pa gcig 'ong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10449: po la chags na rig pa'i rlung de mig la 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10450: lha'i nga rgyal shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10453: 'od ljang gu la chags na lha ma phrag dog shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10455: rig pa'i rlung de rna ba las 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10457: 'od ser po la chags na mi 'dod chags shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10459: rig kha chu'am sna chu lhug pa gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:10460: pa'i rlung de kha dang sna las 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10462: 'od smug po la chags na byol gti mug shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10464: rig pa'i rlung de lte ba lte ba phyir 'bur
NK033(gi)001:10465: la rdul che ba'am rlangs chung bun pa gcig 'ong
NK033(gi)001:10468: 'od dmar po la chags na yi ser sna shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10469: dwags kyi gnas su skye ste /
NK033(gi)001:10470: rig thig le dkar dmar lhug pa rlangs chung bun pa gcig 'ong /
NK033(gi)001:10471: pa'i rlung de gsang ba las 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10473: 'od mthing ka la chags na dmyal zhe sdang shas che na /
NK033(gi)001:10475: rig sdig pa che ba mtshams med lnga byas pa gcig la bar do mi 'ong ste /
NK033(gi)001:10476: dmyal bar rdo 'phangs pa bzhin du 'gro gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:10477: pa'i rlung de gshang lam nas 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10479: gang zag dbang po rab la bar do mi 'byung ste /
NK033(gi)001:10481: gang zag dbang po 'bring ni 'dir bzhag phyis mi len te /
NK033(gi)001:10483: gang zag dbang po tha ma gcig ni bar do la 'tshang rgya'o //
NK033(gi)001:10484: so so'i skye bo rnams ni bar do la chags te 'khor bar 'khyam mo //
NK033(gi)001:10485: gang zag dad pa dang ldan pa rnams ni dge
NK033(gi)001:10486: ba'i las la spyod de thad kar 'bras bu mi
NK033(gi)001:10487: baslu'o // sems su dag pa rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:10488: zla ba bzhi pa'i 'chi ltas brtag pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10489: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10490: phyi'i 'chi ltas brtag par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:10491: dang po rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyis tshe'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK033(gi)001:10493: dus ni rnam pa bzhi dag tu //
NK033(gi)001:10494: tshe yi grib ma ring 'gyur tshe //
NK033(gi)001:10495: srog gi bla nas rab lta zhing //
NK033(gi)001:10496: sa yi mig gi rgyun mi 'chad //
NK033(gi)001:10497: tshe yi mgo bo chad gyur na //
NK033(gi)001:10498: de tshe zla ba bzhi na 'chi //
NK033(gi)001:10499: tshe gzugs zlum por gyur pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:10500: de tshe zla ba gnyis na 'chi //
NK033(gi)001:10501: tshe gzugs spyi tshugs gyur pa na //
NK033(gi)001:10502: de tshe zla ba gcig na 'chi //
NK033(gi)001:10503: tshe gzugs yan lag ma tshang na //
NK033(gi)001:10504: gtor ma bzhi yis phyogs bcur mchod //
NK033(gi)001:10505: tshe gzugs dmar bar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK033(gi)001:10506: nad dang rma ngo yong pas na //
NK033(gi)001:10507: cho ga gtor mas bzlog par gsungs //
NK033(gi)001:10508: zhes rgyud las bstan pas na /
NK033(gi)001:10509: de'i don ma na ngag gis bstan par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:10510: nam mkha' la sprin la sogs med pa'i dus dang /
NK033(gi)001:10511: ser bu'i nyag med pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10512: grong yul las sa phyogs mi med pa'i dgon par phyin la der man+dala bya /
NK033(gi)001:10513: de'i steng du h'u gcig bri /
NK033(gi)001:10514: yi dam la mchod bstod byas la /
NK033(gi)001:10515: de nas tshe yi phyag rgya bzhi zhes bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10516: nyi ma shar ma thag dang /
NK033(gi)001:10517: nyi ma nub la khad pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10518: de bzhin du zla ba shar nub gnyis kyi dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10519: de bzhin du gang yang rung ba gcig la blta ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10520: skra yod na spyi bor bcings la /
NK033(gi)001:10523: rkang pa gnyis gshibs nas langs te /
NK033(gi)001:10524: rang gi grib ma'i snying kha'i h'u la blta /
NK033(gi)001:10525: de la yun ring bar bltas la /
NK033(gi)001:10526: de nas phyogs bzhir bskor bar bltas te /
NK033(gi)001:10527: de ltar byas pas mig 'grib cing 'thibs par byung na /
NK033(gi)001:10528: mig yar yar nam mkha' la bltas pas /
NK033(gi)001:10529: nam mkha' la tshe gzugs dkar po gcig 'ong ste de la brtag go //
NK033(gi)001:10530: de la yang ma mthong na /
NK033(gi)001:10531: lus rdo rje skyil mo krung byas la /
NK033(gi)001:10532: lag pa mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya byas la brtag go //
NK033(gi)001:10533: de la gzugs ci yang ma byung na skyon mi blta ste /
NK033(gi)001:10534: nam mkha' sprin ser po'i zhag chags pa yin te mi 'gal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10535: de la gong du bstan pa bzhin du zla ba bzhi lta bu'i 'chi ltas byung na /
NK033(gi)001:10536: 'chi bslu zla ba gcig bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:10537: yang sngar bzhin brtags pas yan lag thams cad rdzogs na /
NK033(gi)001:10539: de'i dus su ma bslus te gzugs zlum por gyur nas byung na /
NK033(gi)001:10541: yang 'chi ba bslu ba zla ba gcig tu byas te /
NK033(gi)001:10542: dge sbyor la sogs pa thams cad ldab tu blta'o //
NK033(gi)001:10543: de nas zla ba gcig lon nas bltas pas ma bslus te /
NK033(gi)001:10544: spyi tshugs su gyur pa mthong na /
NK033(gi)001:10546: yang dge sbyor la sogs pa byas pas ma bslus na /
NK033(gi)001:10547: de'i rnam smin zad pa yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:10549: mi dga' pa med par dngos po thams cad sgyu
NK033(gi)001:10550: ma lta bu yin snyam pa'i 'dun pa drag po
NK033(gi)001:10552: zla ba bzhi pa'i 'chi ltas brtags pa zhes bya ba'i zhal gdams rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:10553: 'chi ba brtags pa bslu ba 'pho ba gsum bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10555: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i 'pho ba'i gdams ngag la /
NK033(gi)001:10557: bar du 'chi bar 'dug na 'chi ba bslu ba /
NK033(gi)001:10558: tha ma bslus pas ma bslus na sku gsum la 'pho ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10559: dang po 'chi mi 'chi brtag pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:10560: tshe lung chen po bya ba nas //
NK033(gi)001:10561: mig gi a 'bras stor gyur na //
NK033(gi)001:10562: lus can nyi ma gcig la 'pho //
NK033(gi)001:10564: snying po ye shes kyi rlung rgyu ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10565: srin lag g.yon pas a 'bras la bltas pas 'dug na mi 'chi /
NK033(gi)001:10566: mi 'dug na nam dang nyi ma cha mnyam pa'i nyin gcig gam nub gcig na 'achi'o //
NK033(gi)001:10567: bar du 'chi ba bslu ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10570: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa'i sngags /
NK033(gi)001:10571: sdug bsngal thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i sngags smras pa /
NK033(gi)001:10573: de yang sdug bsngal gyi nang nas 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal che ste /
NK033(gi)001:10574: de lta bu yang 'dis zhi bar byed pa yin te /
NK033(gi)001:10575: ye shes kyi rlung 'gyu ba'i dus su a 'bras chad na dus de ring nyid du /
NK033(gi)001:10576: lag pa g.yon pa'i mthil du mchil ma btab la de phyis la /
NK033(gi)001:10577: de nas ga te ga te p+aa ra ga te p+aa ra sam ga te bo d+hi s+w+aah+aa /
NK033(gi)001:10578: zhes dbugs gcig la lan bdun bgrangs la lag pa
NK033(gi)001:10579: g.yon pa'i mthil du mchil ma thud thud byas la
NK033(gi)001:10580: / de nas de rang gis 'dag go //
NK033(gi)001:10581: de la a 'bras bltems pas 'dug na 'chi ba bslus pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:10582: mi 'dug na ldabs la dbugs re la de 'dra lan bdun bdun byas la /
NK033(gi)001:10583: nyi shu rtsa gcig byas la mchil ma gdab /
NK033(gi)001:10584: des 'chi ba bslus sam ma bslus blta /
NK033(gi)001:10585: des kyang ma bslus na lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bskyar /
NK033(gi)001:10586: des mi bslu mi srid do //
NK033(gi)001:10587: des kyang a 'bras ma log par 'dug na /
NK033(gi)001:10588: da cis kyang tshe zad pa yin pas /
NK033(gi)001:10590: tha ma 'chi ba bslus pas ma bslus na sku gsum la 'pho ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10591: nyal stabs kyis sprul pa'i sku la 'pho ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:10592: rten 'brel gyis longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la 'pho ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:10593: lta stangs kyis chos kyi sku la 'pho ba dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:10594: nyal stabs kyis sprul pa'i sku la 'pho ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10598: rkang pa lho ru brkyang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10599: shing 'o ma can bstab mar skyes pa de sor gnyis tsam du bcad de /
NK033(gi)001:10600: gdong pa la yi ge k+sh+nim 'di bris la ye shes kyi rlung 'gyu ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10601: sna bug g.yas su shing gi hril mo de btsug la nyal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10602: des ngan song gi sgo khegs te ngan song gi rgyun bcad nas sprul pa'i sku ru 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)001:10603: rten 'brel gyis longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la 'pho ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10604: ring bsrel ma nor ba gcig /
NK033(gi)001:10605: srin bal en gcig gis dril /
NK033(gi)001:10606: mar byugs nas mtheb mos dril la /
NK033(gi)001:10607: ye shes kyi rlung rgyu ba'i dus su sna bug
NK033(gi)001:10608: g.yon du bcug la dbugs nang du rdubs pas tsha
NK033(gi)001:10609: sing nge byung na rtsa kun tu rgyal ba'i nang
NK033(gi)001:10612: yang na sran dkar gyi phye zhib mo'i ril bu sran ma tsam pa gcig byas la /
NK033(gi)001:10614: ril bu re re la sngags 'di bcu gcig brjod la /
NK033(gi)001:10618: ga te ga te p+aa ra ga te p+aa ra sam ga te bo d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)001:10619: des ring bsrel phyir mi 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)001:10620: ring bsrel phal cher longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur 'gyur
NK033(gi)001:10621: ba'i rtags yin pas 'o skol kyang de bzhin du
NK033(gi)001:10623: ma rig pa dang sdig sgrib dwangs te /
NK033(gi)001:10625: nor bu mchil ma lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)001:10626: lta stangs kyis chos kyi sku la 'pho ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10629: yang na skyil krung du bcas la /
NK033(gi)001:10630: dus kyi brda'i dus su gnad kyi brda'i rgyud la
NK033(gi)001:10631: sbyar bas bde gsal gnyis med rgyud la phril gyis
NK033(gi)001:10632: byung na / lta stangs yar la bltas pas ltag pa bskyed la /
NK033(gi)001:10633: lta stangs nam mkha'i dkyil du dkrug gis song ba dang khrogs kyis 'achi'o //
NK033(gi)001:10634: sems nyid dang nam mkha' gnyis ngo bo gcig tu dbyer med par dkrug gis 'gro ste /
NK033(gi)001:10635: de nas mi 'chug mi 'gyur te des chos kyi sku la 'pho ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10636: gnad gcod kyi sdug bsngal mi 'ong bas /
NK033(gi)001:10637: 'chi kha ma las kyi ril po che /
NK033(gi)001:10638: rtsol ba med pa las 'pho ba lags so //
NK033(gi)001:10639: slob dpon 'dzeng gi 'pho ba'i gdams ngag go //
NK033(gi)001:10641: 'di skabs lnga pa'i gsan yig tu shing p+aa la
NK033(gi)001:10642: sha la brten nas gsang ba'i dgra gsum bsad pa
NK033(gi)001:10643: zhes pa 'dug kyang dpe la ma byung ngo ////
NK033(gi)001:10644: yongs su ma smin pa'i sems can ngan song gi gnas las srung ba'i sbyor ba bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10645: yongs su ma smin sems can la /
NK033(gi)001:10646: ngan song gsum gyi gnas bsrung ba'i sbyor ba bya /
NK033(gi)001:10648: ting nge 'dzin gyis srung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:10649: sbyor ba rdzas kyis srung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10650: de la rdzas ni dug gsum yin /
NK033(gi)001:10651: zhe sdang sbrul gyi klad pa /
NK033(gi)001:10653: gti mug phag gi klad pa gsum rab chad mdzo'i
NK033(gi)001:10654: mar gyis sbyar la ril bu gcig la rgyu ma
NK033(gi)001:10655: nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags la /
NK033(gi)001:10657: de dum bu gsum du bya /
NK033(gi)001:10660: gcig la h+aum brgya bzlas la /
NK033(gi)001:10663: h+aum can lte ba la byug /
NK033(gi)001:10664: de'i phyi phyogs 'dom gang ba ru bsdad nas /
NK033(gi)001:10665: dmigs pa gshang lam la gtad la /
NK033(gi)001:10668: sems kyi ngo bo sbrul du byung ba bsregs nas /
NK033(gi)001:10669: dwangs ma kha la thon nas /
NK033(gi)001:10670: lha ma yin gyi gnas su song bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:10671: de nas dmigs pa gsang gnas su gtad /
NK033(gi)001:10674: 'dod chags bya'i ngo bo byung ba bsregs nas /
NK033(gi)001:10675: dwangs ma mig la thon nas lha'i gnas su song bar bsam /
NK033(gi)001:10676: de nas dmigs pa lte bar gtad /
NK033(gi)001:10679: gti mug phag byung ba bsregs nas /
NK033(gi)001:10680: sems kyi dwangs ma spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga
NK033(gi)001:10681: nas don nas mkha' spyod gnas su song bar bsam
NK033(gi)001:10682: / dus gsum ngos zin na gang rung gcig bsgom pas chog go //
NK033(gi)001:10683: ngos ma zin na 'di ltar bsgom dgos so //
NK033(gi)001:10686: las dang skal bar ldan pa la ston pa /
NK033(gi)001:10687: kun la byin na dam tshig nyams /
NK033(gi)001:10690: gsum pa gsang ba'i zhal gdams la ///
NK033(gi)001:10691: gsang ba'i rdzas khyad par can gyis 'od gsal rgyud la skye ba'i gdams pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10692: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10693: rdzas khyad par can gyis 'od gsal rgyud la skyes pa'i thabs la /
NK033(gi)001:10694: shing rkang gsum la gcig phyi 'phyings pas bstum zer /
NK033(gi)001:10695: la mi'i klad rgyas g.yogs la de'i nang nas mar la 'od shing la gsal le mngal /
NK033(gi)001:10698: 'og tu cong zhi 'am thod le kor gyi nang
NK033(gi)001:10699: du zhun gyi me btang la gu gul ma zhu
NK033(gi)001:10700: tsam bya / me mar gyi mtshan thub par bya /
NK033(gi)001:10701: klad rgyas mar me'i 'od phyir ma shor bar bya /
NK033(gi)001:10702: de'i nub mo bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum la gsol ba drag tu gdab /
NK033(gi)001:10704: de yang dus bzang de yang nya rang la bya /
NK033(gi)001:10706: de nas gu gul de ril bu sran rdog tsam byas la /
NK033(gi)001:10707: ril bu re re tsam rgya sol gyi me la bsreg la /
NK033(gi)001:10708: sna bug g.yon du bdug pas 'od gsal brda' dang sbyar na legs gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:10709: rgyud la skye ba yin gsungs /
NK033(gi)001:10710: 'di la the tshom bla ma rin po che 'dzeng gi gdams pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:10712: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i zhal 'dzeng d+harma bo
NK033(gi)001:10713: d+hi'i gal chen gyi gdams pa zhes pa de 'di
NK033(gi)001:10714: yin nam / gzhan ma byung bas brtag dgos /
NK033(gi)001:10717: rdo rje zam pa'i brgyud pa 'dzin pa'i mi rnams la /
NK033(gi)001:10718: kun la med pa'i bdag 'o la la /
NK033(gi)001:10719: gdams ngag yod de bla ma'i bka' rgya yod pas /
NK033(gi)001:10721: grags pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i gsang sngags rgyud //
NK033(gi)001:10722: bdag la rgyud rdo rje zam pa'i brgyud pa'i bka' babs byung ba'i tshigs bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10723: sde bcu gsum sgrub sde bcu gsum snying po babs //
NK033(gi)001:10724: gser gdams ngag zhus pa'i tshigs bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10725: la sogs pa'i zhabs tog med kyang gdams ngag mang du mnyan //
NK033(gi)001:10726: lung dang bka' la brten pa'i dam chos mang po bdag la brgyud //
NK033(gi)001:10727: dgon pa 'dzin nam snyam nas gdams ngag sna kha mang por zhus //
NK033(gi)001:10728: sbar 'dzin gdams ngag zhus pa'i tshigs bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10729: bla ma'i chos la byas pa'i gdams pa tshang ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10730: gdams gdams ngag khyad par 'phags pa'i tshigs bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10731: ngag 'di ni brda yis bla ma'i /
NK033(gi)001:10732: stoon pas gnad kyi brda' dang /
NK033(gi)001:10733: dang dus kyi brda' gnyis kyi khyad //
NK033(gi)001:10734: dpal sems zhing dul bar byas pas bla ma'i bka' bzhin du //
NK033(gi)001:10735: chos gzhan dang mi 'dra ba 'di brda' rna brgyud kyi gdams pa thams cad /
NK033(gi)001:10736: bzhis rang gi rgyud la sbyor bas khyad du 'phags //
NK033(gi)001:10737: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kyi dkyil nas 'ongs //
NK033(gi)001:10739: grub par bya ba'i he bsgrub na grub thob 'byung ba'i tshigs bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10742: thob bya 'bras bu sku gsum yin pas lam khyer zam 'bras bu dang bcas pa /
NK033(gi)001:10745: dang lung sgrub sde bcu gsum /
NK033(gi)001:10746: la brten pa yin pas bcos rang bzo spangs pa /
NK033(gi)001:10748: dpal sems brtan zhing dka' thub byas na dngos grub rnam gnyis mchog dang thun mong 'ong ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10749: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i zhal gdams dang bcas pa rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:10750: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i nyams kyi skyug pa
NK033(gi)001:10751: zhes pa gsan yig la snang rung dpe la ma
NK033(gi)001:10753: me long ngo sprad kyi gdams pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10754: ma nor ma bcos pa'i don de ngo sprad pa la /
NK033(gi)001:10755: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long bstan pa /
NK033(gi)001:10756: 'phrul gyi me long la mig gis ma mthong ba'i yul mthong /
NK033(gi)001:10757: de bzhin du rig pa dwangs pas ni /
NK033(gi)001:10758: pha rol ci byed mthong bar nus /
NK033(gi)001:10760: me long g.ya' dag pa ste /
NK033(gi)001:10761: mdzod mun khung shar phyogs na skar khung yod pa ru khyer te /
NK033(gi)001:10762: nyi ma shar ba'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10763: rkyen med par bag la nyal te /
NK033(gi)001:10764: gzhi la yod kyang gsal bar ma nus /
NK033(gi)001:10765: nyi zer shar ba'i dus su gsal ba gzhi la yod pa de /
NK033(gi)001:10766: rkyen nyi mas byas pas rang gi ngo bo rang gsal la phyi nang mdun rgyab med par gsal /
NK033(gi)001:10767: me long g.yos pa'i dus su mun khung 'ja' dang 'od kyis khengs /
NK033(gi)001:10768: de ni rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa'i rtsa la dpe de bzhin du /
NK033(gi)001:10769: sems can la sems nyid gzhi la gnas kyang grol ma nus /
NK033(gi)001:10770: rkyen bla ma'i gdams ngag gis byas pas /
NK033(gi)001:10771: don rang la yod pa de ngo sprad /
NK033(gi)001:10774: rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa'i skal ldan des //
NK033(gi)001:10775: rig pa dwangs pa'i rtsal gyis ni //
NK033(gi)001:10776: mchog thun mong gi yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK033(gi)001:10778: bde chen lam du 'jug pa yis //
NK033(gi)001:10779: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10780: me long ngo sprad kyi gdams ngag yin //
NK033(gi)001:10781: las can sems nyid mthong ba gces ////
NK033(gi)001:10782: 'di skabs rdzas la brten nas rlung gi gnas 'gyur
NK033(gi)001:10783: ba zhes pa de gong na gzhung dang yig sna'i
NK033(gi)001:10784: skor gyi rlung gnas 'gyur gyi mtha' na yod do
NK033(gi)001:10785: ////// rdo rje zam pa'i man ngag nying khu bzhugs /
NK033(gi)001:10786: ma khrid yig nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10787: don gnyis su med pa'i gdams pa mdor bsdus pa /
NK033(gi)001:10788: dang po lus dang sems kyi gnad bsam pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10789: bar du brda' bzhis lus tshugs bcos pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10790: tha ma bying ba gseng ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:10791: dang po lus kyi bde ba gsal ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10793: nyi ma la gdong pa mi gtad pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10794: zas che chung ran par za ba de rnams so //
NK033(gi)001:10795: bar du brda' bzhis lus kyi 'dug tshugs bcos pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:10796: mig sna'i rtse mo mtho gang tsam du dbab pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10797: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang mi reg pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10798: khar smyug ma 'bring po shong ba tsam du cung zad deng nge ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:10800: dbugs sna bug g.yon par rgyu tsam na bsgom pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:10801: dbang po dang lus mi g.yo bar bsgom pa rnams so //
NK033(gi)001:10802: tha ma bying ba gseng ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10804: mi bsgom tsa na mi 'ong bar bying nas 'dug pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:10805: yang na ting nge 'dzin las 'bral mi phod pa 'ong bas /
NK033(gi)001:10806: de'i dus su 'dug sa yang yang spos la bsgom mo //
NK033(gi)001:10807: 'dug sa gar spos su ting nge 'dzin skye'am mi skye blta'o //
NK033(gi)001:10808: ting nge 'dzin ji lta bu zhig nyams su myong na /
NK033(gi)001:10809: shes pa dwangs se ba la blo'i rtog pa ci yang med pa gcig 'dod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10810: de la yun ring du bsgoms pas bsgom gyi yun je ring la 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:10811: sgom nyams rtse gcig stong pa spros bral gsum po rim gyis skye'o //
NK033(gi)001:10813: sgom rten tshul shing rnams dang mi 'bral te /
NK033(gi)001:10814: dge sbyor gyi brjed tho yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK033(gi)001:10815: gong ma'i byin rlabs 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK033(gi)001:10816: de yang dang por bsgom khar sems can gyi don du sems bskyed bya /
NK033(gi)001:10817: bla ma la gsol ba drag po gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:10819: tha mar bsgom las 'byung khar rjes la sems can gyi don du bsngo zhing /
NK033(gi)001:10820: thun bar du mkha' 'gro ma gsum la gtor ma btang la /
NK033(gi)001:10821: gang dang gang 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK033(gi)001:10822: mjug dge ba'i rtsa ba byang chub chen por bsngosa la /
NK033(gi)001:10823: dmigs med kyis rgyas gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:10824: de nas spyod lam gyi dus su yang /
NK033(gi)001:10825: 'gro ba'i don du brda' bzhi'i don du mi 'bral bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:10826: 'di 'dra'i man ngag zab mo mdor bsdus pa //
NK033(gi)001:10827: sems kyi don 'tshol mun sel sgron me yin //
NK033(gi)001:10828: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i man ngag nying khu ma /
NK033(gi)001:10831: d+aa ki ma'i mkha' 'gro ma'i zhal gdams /
NK033(gi)001:10833: zhen chags kyi g.yang lugs bshu ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:10834: gzung 'dzin gyi mdud pa dgrol ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:10835: dwangs snyigs kyi dbye bsal phye ba dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:10836: byams sdang gi gnad gso ba dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:10837: rang gi nyams myong rang gis rig pa /
NK033(gi)001:10838: byi dor byas na rgyud dar bas 'jam /
NK033(gi)001:10839: sems mnyam pa nyid du bzhag pa'i ngang la bde
NK033(gi)001:10840: chen gyi glang po nyal ba ni gyad stobs chen
NK033(gi)001:10841: gyis mi lhongs / kun gzhi nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la /
NK033(gi)001:10842: rig pa ye shes shar nub med /
NK033(gi)001:10843: sems dang chos su thug gis 'phrad pa ni rten sa med /
NK033(gi)001:10844: lus dang grib ma bzhin du phral kyang mi phrol /
NK033(gi)001:10846: mkha' gshegs dkar mo'i gdams pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10847: chos mdzad kun rgyud smin pa'i chas su bcug na /
NK033(gi)001:10849: rgyud thos bsam gyi chas su bcug la lta spyod kyi dregs pa bcad /
NK033(gi)001:10850: rgyud dang po'i chas su bcug la 'chi ba rjes su dran par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:10851: rgyud brtson 'grus kyi chas su bcug la /
NK033(gi)001:10852: bla ma'i gdams ngag nyams su blangs /
NK033(gi)001:10853: tshogs gsog pa'i yul la dmigs pa med pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:10854: bsags mkhan rten la ser sna med pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:10855: gzhi dad pa la 'gyur ldog med pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:10856: tha mar 'gyod sems med pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:10857: snang ba la dngos po med /
NK033(gi)001:10860: nyon mongs pa la skye ba'i yul med /
NK033(gi)001:10862: mkha' spyod ma dmar mo'i gdams pa yin no //
NK033(gi)001:10863: nyi ma'i snying po mun pa med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10864: chos kyi sku la dri ma med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10865: gnas pa'i sems la dus med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10866: dus gsum la 'gyur ba med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10867: bla ma la bkur sti byed pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:10868: lha dkon mchog gsum la mos gus byed pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:10869: che chung med pa'i sdig pa la 'dzem pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:10870: yang dag pa'i chos la brtson 'grus bskyed pa gal che /
NK033(gi)001:10871: lta ba la rang byan tshud pa /
NK033(gi)001:10872: tshul khrims la ngo lkog med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10873: sbyin pa la phyogs ris med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10874: sgom pa la bying rgod med pa /
NK033(gi)001:10876: 'bar ba'i gdong can nag mo'i gad mo'o //
NK033(gi)001:10878: rten med kyi rig pa rang grol ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10879: thogs med kyi shes rab rang shar /
NK033(gi)001:10880: rtag chad gnyis med kyi shes rab la /
NK033(gi)001:10881: phyogs ris med na lta ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10882: gtad med kyi rig pa rang grol la /
NK033(gi)001:10883: zhen med kyi nyams myong rang shar /
NK033(gi)001:10884: stong gsal bde chen gyi nyams myong la /
NK033(gi)001:10885: bying rgod med na sgom pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:10886: 'dzin med kyi rig pa rang grol la /
NK033(gi)001:10887: chags med kyi spyod pa rang shar /
NK033(gi)001:10888: tha mal rang spyod kyi lhug pa la /
NK033(gi)001:10889: blang dor med na spyod pa yin /
NK033(gi)001:10890: gnyis med kyi rig pa rang grol ba la /
NK033(gi)001:10891: btsal med kyi 'bras bu rang shar /
NK033(gi)001:10892: 'khor 'das gnyis med kyi dgongs pa la /
NK033(gi)001:10893: re dogs med na 'bras bu yin /
NK033(gi)001:10895: gu ru'i nyams skyes pa'i tshig don ni smyon pa 'dzeng dkar gyi'o //
NK033(gi)001:10896: sgom rten la bris skad do //////
NK033(gi)001:10897: ye 'di rnams tshul shing logs la bri'o //
NK033(gi)001:10899: ye shes kyi tshul gtad pa /
NK033(gi)001:10900: ye shes chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:10901: ye shes lnga yi bde ba rgyas //
NK033(gi)001:10902: rang lus ye shes rin po che //
NK033(gi)001:10903: rig pa'i ye shes skur gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:10904: gang snang rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK033(gi)001:10905: rang rig ye shes rgyun chad med //
NK033(gi)001:10906: rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba //
NK033(gi)001:10907: ye shes nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)001:10908: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10909: 'di la dbyings kyi tshul gtad pa /
NK033(gi)001:10911: ting 'dzin sems kyi rig rtsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10912: lus dang ngag gi bya btsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10913: 'di la dmigs dang bya btsal med //
NK033(gi)001:10915: gnas dang ldan yang brten pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10916: yul du snang yang 'gags pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10917: longs spyod ldan yang chags pa med //
NK033(gi)001:10918: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10928: stong bde ba'i tshul gtad pa /
NK033(gi)001:10929: nyid bde ba'i man ngag sbyin //
NK033(gi)001:10930: dam pa'i bde ba mngon du bstan //
NK033(gi)001:10931: rig pa'i reg bya'i bde ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10932: bde ba rig pa chen po ste //
NK033(gi)001:10933: bde ba chen po'i ros gang ba //
NK033(gi)001:10934: gcig tu 'dus pa'i bde chen yin //
NK033(gi)001:10935: bde ba chen po mi 'bral bzung //
NK033(gi)001:10936: bde ba rgyas pa'i dbang thob ste //
NK033(gi)001:10937: zhing khams gnyis kar bde longs spyod //
NK033(gi)001:10938: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10939: rtsol chos nyid kyi tshul gtad pa /
NK033(gi)001:10940: dang bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK033(gi)001:10941: rgyu 'bras med pa'i mthar thug yin //
NK033(gi)001:10942: sngags tshig bral ba'i nus mthu yin //
NK033(gi)001:10943: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon yin //
NK033(gi)001:10944: las bzhi bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK033(gi)001:10945: 'ching bral ston pas lta ba yin //
NK033(gi)001:10946: 'da' ba med pas dam tshig yin //
NK033(gi)001:10947: rtog 'dzin spangs pas sangs rgyas yin //
NK033(gi)001:10948: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)001:10957: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi skyabs 'gro sems bskyed kyi cho ga bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:10958: bla ma dang dkon mchog rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:10959: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi dus su /
NK033(gi)001:10960: phyi pa mu stegs pa las khyad par 'phags pa la /
NK033(gi)001:10961: skyabs su 'gro ba bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:10962: de yang dang po gang la skyabs su 'gro ba /
NK033(gi)001:10964: tshul lam thabs ji ltar du skyabs su 'gro ba /
NK033(gi)001:10965: skyabs su phyin pa la dgos pa ci yod pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:10966: de yang dang po yul gang la skyabs su 'gro na /
NK033(gi)001:10967: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su 'agro'o //
NK033(gi)001:10969: rten lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas skyabs su 'agro'o //
NK033(gi)001:10970: tshul lam thabs ji ltar du skyabs su 'gro na /
NK033(gi)001:10971: lus gus ngag dag sems nyid mos pa'i sgo nas skyabs su 'agro'o //
NK033(gi)001:10972: skyabs su phyin pa la dgos pa ci yod na /
NK033(gi)001:10973: tshe 'di'i las dang sdig sgrib dag nas bla na
NK033(gi)001:10974: med pa'i byang chub thob par byed pa'i dgos pa
NK033(gi)001:10975: yod pa'o // skyabs su 'gro ba la don bcu gcig ste /
NK033(gi)001:10976: skyabs su 'gro ba'i ngo bo dang 1 /
NK033(gi)001:10985: ma song ba'i nyes dmigs dang 10 /
NK033(gi)001:10986: khyad par dang mi yong ba'i tshad bstan pa dang 11dang bcu gcig go //
NK033(gi)001:10987: de la dang po ngo bo ni /
NK033(gi)001:10988: thabs shes rab gnyis su med par 'dzom pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10990: dkon mchog gsum rang bzhin gyis dkon pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:10992: khams gsum gyi sems can la dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:10993: dpe ci dang 'dra bar dkon na sangs rgyas nor bu rin po che lta bur dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:10994: chos u dum wa ra'i me tog lta bur dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:10995: dge 'dun 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po lta bur dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:10997: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du 'byon daka'i phyir ram /
NK033(gi)001:10998: byon yang bzhugs yun thun pa'i phyir ram /
NK033(gi)001:10999: sems can gdul bya ma dag pa'i phyir dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:11000: de ltar du ston pa 'byung dka' bas na /
NK033(gi)001:11002: de bzhin du chos de sgrub pa'i dge 'dun kyang dkon no //
NK033(gi)001:11003: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo ni zag pa dang bcas pa'i chos thams cad sangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11004: nges tshig ni zag med kyi chos thams cad rgyas pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11005: dbye na sangs rgyas la drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:11010: tshul tha dad pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK033(gi)001:11011: rten du btsug pa'i sangs rgyas dang drug go //
NK033(gi)001:11013: sangs rgyas de spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:11014: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:11015: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:11016: shes bya ji snyed pa dang ji lta ba mkhyen pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11017: chos kyi ngo bo ni gzhi'i 'dug tshul lo //
NK033(gi)001:11018: nges tshig ni bya ba dang byed pa med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11019: chos kyi dbye ba la drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:11020: don dam pa zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos dang /
NK033(gi)001:11021: sgrub pa lam gyi chos dang /
NK033(gi)001:11022: lung du bstan pa'i chos dang /
NK033(gi)001:11024: tshul tha dad pa'i chos dang /
NK033(gi)001:11025: rten du btsug pa'i chos dang drug go //
NK033(gi)001:11027: thog mar dge ba ni don bzang po /
NK033(gi)001:11028: bar du dge ba ni tshig 'bru bzang po /
NK033(gi)001:11029: tha mar dge ba ni ma 'dres pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11030: dge 'dun gyi ngo bo ni dge ba dang mi phyed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11031: nges tshig ni sdig pas ma gos pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11032: dge 'dun gyi dbye ba la drug ste /
NK033(gi)001:11033: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun dang /
NK033(gi)001:11034: rang sangs rgyas kyi dge 'dun dang /
NK033(gi)001:11037: tshul tha dad pa'i dge 'dun dang /
NK033(gi)001:11038: rten du btsug pa'i dge 'dun dang drug go //
NK033(gi)001:11039: dge 'dun gyi mchog dang po lta bar mthun /
NK033(gi)001:11041: tha ma 'bras bur mthun pas na mchog go //
NK033(gi)001:11042: yang na dkon pa la bzhi ste /
NK033(gi)001:11043: dpe gang dang 'dra ba dkon pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11044: yul gang du dkon pa dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11045: gang zag gang la dkon pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11046: tshul ji ltar du dkon pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11049: phyag btsal bas dmigs pa'i yul bstan /
NK033(gi)001:11050: dgos pa ni phyi nang gi bar chad mi 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)001:11051: bkra shis pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)001:11052: don du 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11054: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:11055: sangs rgyas la chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:11056: chos la don dam pa'i chos zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa /
NK033(gi)001:11057: sgrub pa'i chos 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa /
NK033(gi)001:11058: ston pa'i chos gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:11059: dge 'dun la byang chub sems dpa' rang rgyal nyan thos dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)001:11060: dkon mchog gsum la ci'i phyir phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi na /
NK033(gi)001:11061: sangs rgyas ni sgrub pa'i yul lam 'dren pa'i slob
NK033(gi)001:11062: dpon yin te phyi ru phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su
NK033(gi)001:11063: mchi'o // chos ni sgrub pa'i thabs sam lam yin pas na phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su 'gro /
NK033(gi)001:11064: dge 'dun ni sgrub pa'i rten nam grogs yin pa'i phyir na phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su 'agro'o //
NK033(gi)001:11065: bzhi pa skyabs 'gro gsum thob pa'i rgyu ni /
NK033(gi)001:11066: yul dkon mchog gsum la dad pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11067: lnga pa thob pa'i dus ni /
NK033(gi)001:11068: slob dpon gyis lan gsum brjod pa'i cha tha ma de la thob pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11069: drug pa skyabs 'gro mi thob pa'i gegs ni /
NK033(gi)001:11070: khe dang grags pas skyabs 'gro'i sdom pa blang na mi thob /
NK033(gi)001:11071: 'jig rten 'di'i don du blang na mi thob pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11072: bdun pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i cho ga bya ba la lnga ste /
NK033(gi)001:11073: skyabs su 'gro ba'i sngon 'gro bar chad dri ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11074: skyabs su 'gro ba'i bar chad dri ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11075: skyabs su 'gro zhing bshags pa bya ba dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11076: skyabs su 'gro ba'i cho ga dngos gzhi dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:11077: skyabs su 'gro ba'i sdom pa dpog pa dang lnga'o //
NK033(gi)001:11078: de la dang po skyabs su 'gro ba'i sngon 'gro bar chad dri ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11079: bslab pa thams cad kyi gzhi /
NK033(gi)001:11080: sdom pa thams cad kyi rten /
NK033(gi)001:11081: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par byed pa'i 'dren skas /
NK033(gi)001:11082: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro zhing nga la bla mar zhu ba dad lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11086: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i bar chad dri ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11087: rigs kyi bu khyod nga la bla mar zhu zhing dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro na /
NK033(gi)001:11088: rgyal pos gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11089: lus bdag gis gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11090: khyim bdag gis gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11093: spun zlas gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11094: grogs kyi gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11097: theg pa las ma 'das pa ma yin nam /
NK033(gi)001:11098: ye shes las thal ba ma yin nam /
NK033(gi)001:11100: legs so zhes lan gdab bo //
NK033(gi)001:11102: dang po skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11103: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK033(gi)001:11104: dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i khyad par dang /
NK033(gi)001:11105: gsang sngags yang dag gi lha tshogs rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11106: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK033(gi)001:11107: nas snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du
NK033(gi)001:11109: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11110: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK033(gi)001:11112: tshogs bsags pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK033(gi)001:11114: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la bdag skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11115: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK033(gi)001:11116: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la skyabs su
NK033(gi)001:11117: mchi'o // mkhyen rab kyi bdag po 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11118: thugs rje'i bdag po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11119: mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11120: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK033(gi)001:11121: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11122: dngos bshams yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK033(gi)001:11123: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:11124: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK033(gi)001:11125: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK033(gi)001:11126: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK033(gi)001:11127: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)001:11128: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK033(gi)001:11129: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK033(gi)001:11130: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK033(gi)001:11131: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11132: bskul ba'i sa las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)001:11133: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK033(gi)001:11134: ma grol ba ni rnam dgrol phyir //
NK033(gi)001:11135: sems can mya ngan 'das la dgod //
NK033(gi)001:11136: bdag la gnas pa'i lus 'di ni //
NK033(gi)001:11137: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la 'bul //
NK033(gi)001:11138: tshe rabs bsags pa'i dge rnams kun //
NK033(gi)001:11139: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK033(gi)001:11140: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa rnams //
NK033(gi)001:11141: thob nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams bcom byas te //
NK033(gi)001:11142: skye rga na 'chi'i dba' klong 'khrugs pa yi //
NK033(gi)001:11143: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba 'don par shog /
NK033(gi)001:11144: gnyis pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11145: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11146: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK033(gi)001:11147: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11149: skye ba thogs ma med pa nas tha ma da lta la mchis kyi bar du /
NK033(gi)001:11150: dug gsum gyi dbang gis lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK033(gi)001:11151: sgo nas sdig pa mi dge ba ci bgyis pa
NK033(gi)001:11153: sangs rgyas la mi dad cing ma gus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11154: chos la mi dad cing ma gus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11155: dge 'dun la mi dad cing ma gus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11156: nyan thos kyi bslab pa nyams pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11157: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyams pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11158: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11159: grogs tshangs par mtshungs pa la ma dad cing ma gus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11160: bla ma dang slob dpon la ma dad cing ma gus pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11161: mdor na mtho ris dang thar pa'i gegs su gyur pa /
NK033(gi)001:11162: ngan song dang 'khor ba'i rgyur gyur pa ci mchis
NK033(gi)001:11163: pa de dag thams cad bla ma dang slob dpon
NK033(gi)001:11165: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyan sngar mthol lo bshags so //
NK033(gi)001:11169: slan chad kyang gcod cing sdom par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:11170: bzhi pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i cho ga dngos gzhi ni /
NK033(gi)001:11171: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK033(gi)001:11172: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid /
NK033(gi)001:11173: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa la bdag skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11175: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11176: 'phags pa 'i lam yan lag brgyad pa /
NK033(gi)001:11177: yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa'i chos
NK033(gi)001:11178: rnams la bdag dang sems can thams cad skyabs su
NK033(gi)001:11179: mchi'o // 'phags pa'i dge 'dun sa chen po la
NK033(gi)001:11180: rab tu bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK033(gi)001:11181: chen po phyir mi ldog pa rnams la skyabs su
NK033(gi)001:11182: mchi'o // mchi'o // yon tan thams cad rgyud la sbyor mdzad pa'i /
NK033(gi)001:11183: dus gsum bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11184: rgyal ba thams cad dbyer med dbyings mnyam yang /
NK033(gi)001:11185: yi dam he ru ka la bdag skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11186: ma sring byams pa'i tshogs kyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)001:11187: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11188: lnga pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i sdom pa dbog pa ni //
NK033(gi)001:11189: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK033(gi)001:11190: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:11191: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11193: lus kyi sgo nas srog gcod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11194: ngag gi sgo nas rdzun smras pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11195: yid kyi sgo nas gnod sems bgyis pa de dag las slar ldog par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:11196: lus kyi sgo nas srog gcod pa'i yan lag tu /
NK033(gi)001:11197: ma byin pa len par bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11198: mi tshangs pa spyod par bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11199: rdzun du smra ba'i yan lag tu ngag 'khyal ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11202: gnod sems kyi yan lag tu /
NK033(gi)001:11203: brnab sems dang log par lta ba bgyis pa de dag las slar ldog par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:11204: brgyad pa bslab bya dpog pa la rnam pa brgyad de /
NK033(gi)001:11205: thad kar grangs bgrang mi shes par snang /
NK033(gi)001:11207: thun mong gi bslab bya gsum la /
NK033(gi)001:11208: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi nas lha gzhan la phyag mi 'tshal /
NK033(gi)001:11209: lugs su blug pa'am 'bur du gtod pa'am /
NK033(gi)001:11210: ris su bris pa rnams la yang /
NK033(gi)001:11211: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bkod pa yin pas bcom ldan 'das dngos yin par bsam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11212: chos la skyabs su mchis nas sems can la rnam par 'tshe ba mi bya /
NK033(gi)001:11213: de yang mi dge ba bcu mi bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:11216: yid kyi sgo nas gsum ste bcu tham pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11217: de la sogs te mi shes pa la bzo bcol ba yang sems can la rnam par 'tshe ba /
NK033(gi)001:11218: mi theg pa la khur bskur ba yang rnam par 'tshe ba /
NK033(gi)001:11219: mi yong ba'i las ka bcol ba yang rnam par 'tshe ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:11220: phyin ci log gi po ti dang gleg bam la mi mos so zhe na /
NK033(gi)001:11222: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dngos yin par bsam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11223: dge 'dun la skyabs su song nas /
NK033(gi)001:11224: mi mu stegs can dang mi 'grogs /
NK033(gi)001:11225: de dang sla ste ser gos gyon pa rnams la mi mos pa'i skyon spong ste /
NK033(gi)001:11226: ser gos gyon pa mu stegs yin nam so so'i skye bo yin ngo mi shes te /
NK033(gi)001:11227: de yang ma 'ongs pa'i dus na ba dmar glang
NK033(gi)001:11228: dmar gyi gos gyon pa yang bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK033(gi)001:11229: byin gyis brlabs pa yin pas ser gos gyon pa
NK033(gi)001:11230: gcig tsam la yang bcom ldan 'das kyi chos gos
NK033(gi)001:11231: dngos yin par bsam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11232: thun mong ma yin pa'i bslab bya gsum la /
NK033(gi)001:11233: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchis nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK033(gi)001:11234: gzugs brnyan chu'i nang du shar ba tsam la yang
NK033(gi)001:11235: 'dzem / chos la skyabs su mchis nas po ti
NK033(gi)001:11236: dang glegs bam dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' dri
NK033(gi)001:11237: ma med pa tsam la yang 'dzem /
NK033(gi)001:11238: dge 'dun la skyabs su mchis nas bla ma dang
NK033(gi)001:11239: mkhan po dang slob dpon gyi dri ma tsam la
NK033(gi)001:11241: sku dang mchod rten dang 'phags pa nyan thos kyi
NK033(gi)001:11242: dge 'dun dang byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun gyi
NK033(gi)001:11243: grib ma tsam la yang mi 'gong ngo //
NK033(gi)001:11244: srog dang bya dag'i ched du yang dkon mchog gsum mi spong ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11245: pha dang ma'i ngor yang sdig pa'i las mi byed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11246: lus dang srog gi phyir yang dam pa'i chos mi spong ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11247: mdo las byung ba'i bslab pa gsum las dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan dran par bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11248: skyabs su 'gro ba'i phan yon dran par bya /
NK033(gi)001:11249: skyabs su 'gro ba yang mang du brjod par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:11250: gdams ngag las byung ba'i bslab bya rnam pa gsum la /
NK033(gi)001:11251: lha dkon mchog gsum las skyabs gnas gzhan du mi 'tshol ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11252: zas ci za ba'i phud kyis dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11253: phyogs dang mtshams gang du 'gro yang lha dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro zhing /
NK033(gi)001:11254: don gyi dmigs pa gal che ba la lha dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba 'debs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11255: de las gzhan pa'i bslab bya gsum la /
NK033(gi)001:11256: sangs rgyas la che chung dang bzang ngan du mi byed /
NK033(gi)001:11257: chos la zab mi zab dang legs mi legs su mi dbye /
NK033(gi)001:11258: dge 'dun la dga' mi dga' ngang yin min du mi dabye'o //
NK033(gi)001:11259: dgu pa skyabs su 'gro ba byas pa'i phan yon la brgyad de /
NK033(gi)001:11260: phyi pa mu stegs pa las log nas nang pa sangs rgyas su tshud pa'i phan yon dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11261: sdom pa thams cad kyi rten du 'gyur ba'i phan yon dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11262: dkar po'i lha rnams kyis 'go zhing stong grogs byed pa'i phan yon dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11263: mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams kyi gnod pas mi tshugs pa'i phan yon dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:11264: sdig pa thams cad zad cing srab bar byed pa'i phan yon dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:11265: dge ba thams cad 'phel zhing rgyas par byed pa'i phan yon dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:11266: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par byed pa'i phan yon dang bdun /
NK033(gi)001:11267: mthar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par byed pa'i phan yon dang brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:11268: bcu pa skyabs su mi 'gro ba'i nyes dmigs la'ang brgyad de /
NK033(gi)001:11269: phyi pa mu stegs pa las nang la sangs rgyas pa ru mi tshud pa'i nyes dmigs dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11270: sdom pa thams cad kyi rten med pa'i nyes dmigs dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11271: ji ltar du bsam pa la yid mi ches shing /
NK033(gi)001:11272: bsam pa mi 'grub pa'i nyes dmigs dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11273: ngan song rnam pa gsum du lhung ba'i nyes dmis dang bzhi //
NK033(gi)001:11274: dkar po'i chos kyi snang ba mi 'char ba'i nyes dmigs dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:11275: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i gnod pas tshugs pa'i nyes dmigs dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:11276: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs mi 'phel zhing yang dag
NK033(gi)001:11277: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la mi 'gro
NK033(gi)001:11279: bdag gzhan gnyis la phan mi thogs pa'i nyes dmigs dang brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:11280: de bas skyabs su 'gro ba ni shin tu nas kyang gal che ba yin no //
NK033(gi)001:11281: skyabs 'gro thon nas gtor ma gcig btang ngo //
NK033(gi)001:11283: mi yong ba'i tshad bstan pa de chad snang /
NK033(gi)001:11285: skyabs su 'gro ba'i cho ga khyad par can rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)001:11286: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11287: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi dus su /
NK033(gi)001:11288: theg pa chung ngu las khyad par du byas nas
NK033(gi)001:11289: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa la gnyis te
NK033(gi)001:11290: / kun rdzob dang don dam pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11291: dang po kun rdzob la smon pa dang 'jug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11292: de la dang po smon pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:11293: de la dang po khams gsum gyi sems can thams
NK033(gi)001:11294: cad gcig kyang ma lus par 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK033(gi)001:11295: las thar bar bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11296: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu sangs rgyas par
NK033(gi)001:11297: gyur na ci ma rung zhes dga' ba drag po
NK033(gi)001:11298: bskyed pa dang / 'dod pa drag po bskyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11299: smon pa drag po bskyed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11300: gnyis pa 'jug pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:11302: zang zing gi sbyin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11303: mi 'jigs pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11304: byams pa'i sems kyis don byed cing byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la nges par 'jug pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11305: de gnyis ni kun rdzob bo //
NK033(gi)001:11306: de ltar kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems smon 'jug gnyis skyes nas /
NK033(gi)001:11307: de gnyis ka la tshad med pa bzhi la gnas par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:11308: tshad med pa bzhi la gnyis te /
NK033(gi)001:11309: rtag tu dngos su spyod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11310: thun gyi dus su sems ngo la bsgom pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11312: sems can rnams rtag tu sdug bsngal ba la snying rje bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:11313: de la rtag tu byams pas phan gdags /
NK033(gi)001:11314: sems can thams cad sdug bsngal dang bral nas bde ba dang ldan pa la dga' ba bskyed /
NK033(gi)001:11315: rtag tu sems can rnams la nye ring med pa'i btang snyoms la bslab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:11316: gnyis pa thun gyi dus su sems ngo la sgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:11317: sems can thams cad kyi lus ni mi rtag pas 'gyur zhing gsar rnying barje ba ru 'dug /
NK033(gi)001:11318: sems ni stong pa ma rig cing mi 'dzad pas /
NK033(gi)001:11319: 'khrul 'phro mi chad par rtag tu myong bar 'dug pas /
NK033(gi)001:11320: sems can lhag ma ma lus par 'khor ba las
NK033(gi)001:11321: thar bar bya ba'i don du lus ngag yid gsum
NK033(gi)001:11322: gsang sngags kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i don
NK033(gi)001:11323: du smin par bya ba'i dbang zhus la /
NK033(gi)001:11324: grol bar bya ba'i gsang sngags kyi don ma nor bar bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)001:11325: sems can ma lus pa 'khor ba las thar bar bya'o snyam du bsam mo //
NK033(gi)001:11326: des kun rdzob byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa bstan nas /
NK033(gi)001:11327: gnyis pa don dam pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:11328: chos thams cad chos nyid don dam pa ji lta bur gnas pa bzhin du rtogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11329: chos nyid don dam pa ji lta bar gnas su she na /
NK033(gi)001:11330: don dam pa skye 'gag med par gnas pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11331: skye ba med pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK033(gi)001:11332: chos thams cad sems su 'dus la /
NK033(gi)001:11333: sems nyid dngos po dang mtshan mar ma grub pas skye ba med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11334: sems stong pa de la dran pa'i cho 'phrul mi 'gags te /
NK033(gi)001:11335: cir yang snang du rung ba'o //
NK033(gi)001:11336: chos nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de nyid skye ba
NK033(gi)001:11337: med kyang cho 'phrul sna tshogs snang zhing 'gags pa
NK033(gi)001:11338: med do // cho 'phrul de nyid kyang rang bzhin med pas stong pa nyid do //
NK033(gi)001:11339: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni snang la rang bzhin med de /
NK033(gi)001:11340: don dam par ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa /
NK033(gi)001:11341: gang du yang mi gnas pa /
NK033(gi)001:11342: ci la yang dmigs pa med pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11343: don dngos po'i gnas lugs de rtogs par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK033(gi)001:11344: rgyu las skye ba'i thabs dang /
NK033(gi)001:11345: dmigs su med pa'i 'bras bu ste de'ang don dam
NK033(gi)001:11346: pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa 'adi'o
NK033(gi)001:11347: // de ltar byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis
NK033(gi)001:11348: bskyed nas bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don la brtson par
NK033(gi)001:11349: // zhugs te / lhag pa'i bsam pa khyad par can 'da' bzhud med par gyur na /
NK033(gi)001:11350: de la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK033(gi)001:11351: dpa' rnams ngo mtshar skyes nas zhal 'dzum pa mdzad
NK033(gi)001:11352: do // de ce'i phyir zhal 'dzum pa mdzad ces 'khor rnams kyis dri bar gyur to //
NK033(gi)001:11353: de'i tshe bud+d+ha rnams kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK033(gi)001:11354: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di skad ces bya ba na /
NK033(gi)001:11355: gang zag 'di skad ces bya ba zhig byang chub
NK033(gi)001:11356: mchog tu sems bskyed nas bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don
NK033(gi)001:11358: bsam pa bzang po gser lta bu dang ldan pa yod kyi /
NK033(gi)001:11359: khyed rnams kyis kyang bsrung ba dang bskyab pa dang byin gyis rlobs par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)001:11361: de bas na sems bskyed pa 'di gal che'o //
NK033(gi)001:11362: de nas sems bskyed pa'i dus su /
NK033(gi)001:11363: sems bskyed kyi thun mong gi bar chad dri ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11364: rigs kyi bu khyod nga la bla mar zhu zhing /
NK033(gi)001:11365: bla na med pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa rgyal pos gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11366: yul bdag gis gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11367: khyim bdag gis gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11370: spun zlas gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11371: grogs pos gnang ba lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11374: theg pa las 'das pa ma yin nam /
NK033(gi)001:11375: ye shes las thal ba ma yin nam /
NK033(gi)001:11378: de nas thun mong ma yin pa'i spro ba dri ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11379: rigs kyi bu skal ba dang ldan pa khyod /
NK033(gi)001:11380: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed par 'dod cing /
NK033(gi)001:11381: nga la bla mar zhu ba la dad lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11385: rjes su 'jug par bgyid lags sam /
NK033(gi)001:11387: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das dang gzhan gyi chos la skur ba btab pa las ldog nas /
NK033(gi)001:11388: rang gi mos pa bla na med pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11389: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das dang de bzhin
NK033(gi)001:11390: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK033(gi)001:11391: sangs rgyas rig pa dang rkang par ldan pa /
NK033(gi)001:11397: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
NK033(gi)001:11398: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas ring por ma
NK033(gi)001:11399: lon pa de dag la dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor
NK033(gi)001:11400: lo bla na med pa bskor bar bskul lo //
NK033(gi)001:11402: dam pa rnams dang rgyang ring ba spang zhing nye
NK033(gi)001:11403: bar mi 'bral bar bya ba'i don du phyogs bcu'i
NK033(gi)001:11404: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyang 'gro
NK033(gi)001:11405: ba sems can 'khor ba las ma grol gyi bar
NK033(gi)001:11406: du / sems can mya ngan las 'da' bar bya ba'i don du /
NK033(gi)001:11407: bde bar gshegs pa rnams mya ngan las mi 'da' bar bzhugs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11408: gzhan gyis dge ba'i rtsa ba byed pa la phrag dog pa las ldog par bya ba'i don du /
NK033(gi)001:11409: phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK033(gi)001:11410: dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas tha
NK033(gi)001:11411: ma mngon par rdzogs par sangs ma rgyas kyi bar
NK033(gi)001:11412: du dge ba'i rtsa ba gang lags pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11414: 'gro ba gzhan gyis dge ba'i rtsa ba bgyis pa la rjes su yi rang bar bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:11415: bdag gis sngar byas pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams byang chub mchog tu bsngo ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11416: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas 'khor ba thog ma
NK033(gi)001:11417: med pa nas tha ma da lta la thug gi
NK033(gi)001:11418: bar du / pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK033(gi)001:11419: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK033(gi)001:11421: skyabs su 'gro ba byas pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11422: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11423: rigs drug gi gnas su kham cig tsam bstsal ba'i
NK033(gi)001:11424: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bsdus shing bsdoms nas bzlums
NK033(gi)001:11425: te / bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi mchog chen por bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11426: da dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba ni /
NK033(gi)001:11427: bdag gi lus dang longs spyod ji srid yod par gyur pa'i mchod rdzas thams cad /
NK033(gi)001:11428: rdo rje slob dpon dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK033(gi)001:11429: dal gyi lha'i khyad par dang /
NK033(gi)001:11430: gsang sngags kyi lha tshogs thams cad dang /
NK033(gi)001:11431: sems can thams cad la thun mong du 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)001:11432: de nas khrus byas la phyag btsal lo //
NK033(gi)001:11434: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang phyogs
NK033(gi)001:11435: bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK033(gi)001:11436: dpa' rnams dang / dal gyi lha tshogs bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11437: bdag gi skye ba 'di dang skye ba gzhan dag tu sbyin pa las byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11438: tshul khrims las byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11439: bsgom pa las byung ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba ci bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11441: gzhan gyis bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba bgyis ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba des /
NK033(gi)001:11442: ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis /
NK033(gi)001:11443: nyid dang por bla na med pa yang dag par
NK033(gi)001:11444: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu thugs bskyed par mdzad pa
NK033(gi)001:11445: debazhina du / dus 'di nas bzung nas snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK033(gi)001:11447: sems can ma smin pa rnams smin par bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11448: sems can ma grol ba rnams dgrol bar bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11449: sems can dbugs ma phyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung bar bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11450: sems can yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa
NK033(gi)001:11451: rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar bya ba'i
NK033(gi)001:11452: don du / bla na med pa yang dag par
NK033(gi)001:11453: rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed par
NK033(gi)001:11456: phyag btsal me tog gtor ro //
NK033(gi)001:11457: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang phyogs
NK033(gi)001:11458: bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang dal gyi lha
NK033(gi)001:11459: tshogs rnams dang / 'phags pa dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11460: bdag gis skye ba thog ma med pa nas tha ma da lta la thug gi bar du /
NK033(gi)001:11461: dug gsum gyi dbang gis lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK033(gi)001:11462: sgo nas sdig pa ci bgyis pa thams cad bshags
NK033(gi)001:11464: 'dod chags chen po'i dbang gis dkon mchog gi dkor la 'bags pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11465: zhe sdang chen po'i dbang gis srog gcod ye rngams bgyis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11466: gti mug chen po'i dbang gis dge sdig don ma rtogs pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11467: lus kyis srog gcod sdig pa dngos su byas pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11468: ngag gis rdzun smras pa dang gzhan la ngan du brjod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11469: sems kyis blo nor log par bsam pa la sogs /
NK033(gi)001:11470: 'di 'dra 'khor ba'i dmyal sogs ci bsags pa thams
NK033(gi)001:11471: cad bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang
NK033(gi)001:11472: / phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK033(gi)001:11473: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:11474: 'phags pa thams cad kyi spyan sngar mthol lo bshags so //
NK033(gi)001:11479: slan chad kyang gcod cing sdom par bgyid lags so //
NK033(gi)001:11481: bdag nyid gcig pu sdug bsngal las grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11482: bde ba la gnas par bya ba'i phyir zhus pa ma lags kyi /
NK033(gi)001:11483: 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha'i mthar thug pa'i sems
NK033(gi)001:11484: can thams cad la nongs par gyur pa ci mchis
NK033(gi)001:11485: pa dang / 'gal bar gyur pa ci mchis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11486: ltung bar gyur pa ci mchis pa de dag thams cad bzod par gsol lags na /
NK033(gi)001:11487: bzod pa dang du bzhes su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11488: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang /
NK033(gi)001:11489: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang dkyil 'khor
NK033(gi)001:11490: gyi lha tshogs dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang
NK033(gi)001:11491: 'phags pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11492: bden pa'i tshig grub par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:11494: dri chab kyi chu lan gsum 'thung du gzhug go //
NK033(gi)001:11495: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang phyogs
NK033(gi)001:11496: bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang dal gyi lha
NK033(gi)001:11497: tshogs dang / byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:11498: 'phags pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11500: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11501: da lta'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon sum du sbyar ba 'di na ci mchis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11502: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba da rung du
NK033(gi)001:11503: yid las byung ba dang dge ba'i rtsa ba ci
NK033(gi)001:11504: bgyis pa de dag thams cad gcig tu bsdus te
NK033(gi)001:11505: bsdoms nas / dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya che bar bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11506: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang /
NK033(gi)001:11507: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK033(gi)001:11509: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK033(gi)001:11510: 'phags pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)001:11512: 'das pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11513: da lta'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon sum du sbyar ba 'di na ci mchis pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11514: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba da rung yid las 'byung ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11515: gzhan gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba ci bgyis pa la
NK033(gi)001:11516: rjes su yi rang ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang
NK033(gi)001:11517: / dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag thams cad gcig tu bsdus shing bsdoms nas /
NK033(gi)001:11518: rigs drug gi sems can thams cad kyi don du
NK033(gi)001:11519: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di mi mdzad par
NK033(gi)001:11520: gyur cig / yongs su mi 'dzad par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:11521: shin tu mi 'dzad par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:11522: dpag tu mi 'dzad par gyur cig /
NK033(gi)001:11524: me tog gtor la phyag lan gsum du bya'o //
NK033(gi)001:11525: de yan chad ni sems bskyed kyi cho ga'o //
NK033(gi)001:11526: de ltar du sems bskyed pa la dgos pa'i yan lag bzhi ni /
NK033(gi)001:11527: sems bskyed pa'i slob dpon la ston pa bcom ldan 'das kyi 'du shes bskyed pa dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11528: sems bskyed pa'i gang zag la byang chub sems dpar lta ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11529: sems can thams cad la g.yo dang sgyus mi bslu ba dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11530: gang zag gzhan gyi rgyud la 'gyod pa mi bskyed pa dang bzhi'o //
NK033(gi)001:11531: byang chub sems pa'i sdom pa nyi shu pa ni /
NK033(gi)001:11532: srog gcod pa spong ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11533: ma byin par len pa spong ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11534: mi tshangs pa spyod pa spong ba dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11535: rdzun smra ba spong ba dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:11536: skyabs su kheb che na mi spong ste brgya thar na gcig gsod /
NK033(gi)001:11537: ser sna khrol na ma byin par len /
NK033(gi)001:11538: srog thon na rdzun du smra /
NK033(gi)001:11539: theg pa chen po'i lta ba thon na khab tu bzhes /
NK033(gi)001:11540: de ni rtsa ba'i sdom pa brgyad do //
NK033(gi)001:11541: yan lag gi sdom pa bcu gnyis la /
NK033(gi)001:11542: nad pa la nad dri ba bya ba dang gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11543: shi ba la mya ngan bsang ba dang gnyis /
NK033(gi)001:11544: mgron gyi bod kha yangs pa dang gsum /
NK033(gi)001:11545: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra tshar gcod pa dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)001:11546: ku re dang bre mo'i gtam mi bya ba dang lnga /
NK033(gi)001:11547: sgom pa la brtson par byed pa dang drug /
NK033(gi)001:11548: nyan thos kyi lta ba spang ba dang bdun /
NK033(gi)001:11549: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro la mi chags pa dang brgyad /
NK033(gi)001:11550: sbyin pa btang ba dang dgu /
NK033(gi)001:11551: ngag snyan por smra ba dang bcu /
NK033(gi)001:11552: chos kyi don dang mthun pa dang bcu gcig /
NK033(gi)001:11553: sems can thams cad dang lta spyod sdig mi gsog par mthun par bya ba dang bcu gnyis so //
NK033(gi)001:11554: byang chub kyi sems nyams par byed pa'i chos bzhi las ldog par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:11555: bla ma dang mchod par 'os pa bslu ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11556: gzhan 'gyod pa med pa la 'gyod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11557: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la zhe sdang gi tshig tu bcad pa brjod pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11558: sems can thams cad g.yo sgyus su spyod pa las ldog par byed pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11559: byang chub kyi sems de mi nyams par byed pa'i chos bzhi la bslab par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:11560: srog gi phyir yang bsam bzhin du rdzun mi smra ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11561: sems can thams cad la lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam
NK033(gi)001:11562: par dag pas chos la gnas par bya ba las
NK033(gi)001:11563: / g.yo dang sgyus su gnas pa ma yin pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11564: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed cing /
NK033(gi)001:11565: phyogs bcur yang dag pa'i yon tan brjod par bya ba dang /
NK033(gi)001:11566: sems can phan thogs pa rnams dge ba la dgod par bya ste /
NK033(gi)001:11567: de dag kyang bla na med pa'i byang chub la dgod kyi /
NK033(gi)001:11568: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas la ma yin no //
NK033(gi)001:11569: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'o //
NK033(gi)001:11570: sems bskyed kyi cho ga dang bslab bya rdzogs so //////
NK033(gi)001:11571: dbang chog che ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshon tho ni /
NK033(gi)001:11581: rdo rje bri ba yang yod /
NK033(gi)001:11589: byang ser po mthing kha yin no //
NK033(gi)001:11591: chos 'byung gi nang khong dmar po /
NK033(gi)001:11595: chos 'byung rtse'i rdo rje ser po /
NK033(gi)001:11608: byang ser mthing kha po yin no //
NK033(gi)001:11609: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bum pa'i nang du sman blugs la bzhag /
NK033(gi)001:11610: de'i khar thod pa'i nang du sin+d+hu ra brdal la chang blugs /
NK033(gi)001:11611: de'i khar me long nang du bu ram mar sbrang rtsi bsres pa'i ril bu bzhag go //
NK033(gi)001:11612: de ltar na de dag gis klong sde rdo rje
NK033(gi)001:11613: zam pa'i gzhung pod yongs su rdzogs pa kun gzigs
NK033(gi)001:11614: lnga pa rin po che'i gsan yig na tshan pa
NK033(gi)001:11615: re re bzhin zhal gsal bas de ltar bkod pa
NK033(gi)001:11616: yin pas yid ches su rung ba yod do //
NK033(gi)001:11617: smin gling gter chen rin po che'i gsan yig na
NK033(gi)001:11618: bsdus che bas don gyi 'gags 'dra bas de ltar
NK033(gi)001:11620: da rung gsan yig snga phyi thams cad na mi
NK033(gi)001:11621: bzhugs pa'i sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi skyabs
NK033(gi)001:11622: 'gro sems bskyed kyi cho ga zhes pa dang /
NK033(gi)001:11624: dbang chog che chung gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshon tho ldeb gcig bcas yod do ////
NK033(gi)001:11625: de yang spyir lo chen bee ro tsa na'i sku
NK033(gi)001:11626: tshe'i stod la rje mnga' bdag rgyal po la gdams
NK033(gi)001:11627: pa phog kyang rgyal po snyan srab cing btsun mo
NK033(gi)001:11628: dang blun po gdug pa ches pas chos mthar ma
NK033(gi)001:11629: phyin / sku tshe'i smad la rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la rdzogs par gnang /
NK033(gi)001:11630: des gnyags dz+ny+aan ku m+aa ra sogs la tha snyad skor bstan kyang gtad rgya mthar ma phyin /
NK033(gi)001:11631: g.yu sgra khams su log nas spang mi pham mgon
NK033(gi)001:11632: po la rgyas gtad rgya gsum pa'i lugs tshang ba
NK033(gi)001:11633: zhig bzhag zer ba lugs gzhan yin /
NK033(gi)001:11634: de nas mar byon te rgya blo gros gzhon nu
NK033(gi)001:11635: la rgyud nyi shu rtsa lnga phra mo dang bcas
NK033(gi)001:11636: pa gtad / de nas zhing gzhan du 'pho khar dbas rdo rje rgyal mtshan la rdzogs par gnang /
NK033(gi)001:11637: des mdo smad dan tig dgon par bskyangs zhes lo
NK033(gi)001:11638: rgyus su gnas pa rnams brgyud pa bar ma'i skor
NK033(gi)001:11639: yin kyang deng sang rgyun mi bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)001:11640: 'di ni spang mi pham mgon po la gnang ba
NK033(gi)001:11641: las byung ba'i brgyud pa tha ma'i gzhung gdams ngag
NK033(gi)001:11642: yongs su rdzogs pa yin no ////
